taM zabdamabhinidhyAya rAkSasI krodhamUrchitA . zrutvA cAbhyadravat kruddhA yatra zabdo viniHsRtaH .
tAM dRSTvA rAghavaH kruddhAM vikRtAM vikRtAnanAm . pramAmenAtivRddhAM ca lakSmaNaM so ' bhyabhASata .
pazya lakSmaNa yakSiNyA bhairavaM dAruNaM vapuH . bhidyeran darzanAdasyA bhIrUNAM hRdayAni ca .
etAM pazya durAdharSAM mAyAbalasamanvitAm . vinivRttAM karomyadya hRtakarNAnanAsikAm .
na hyenAmutsahe hantuM strIsvabhAvena rakSitAm . vIryaM cAsyA gatiM caiva hanyAmiti hi me matiH .
evaM bruvANe rAme tu tATakA krodhamUrcchitA . udyamya bAhuM garjantI rAmamevAbhyadhAvata .
vizvAmitrastu brahmarSihu~kAreNAbhibhay/a tAm . svasti rAghavayorastu jayaM caivAbhyabhASata .
uddhanvAnA rajo ghoraM tATakA rAghavAvubhau . rajomeghena mahatA muhUrtaM sA vyamohayat .
tato mAyAM samAMsthAya zilAvarSeNa rAghavau . avAkirat sumahatAM tatazcakrodha rAghavaH .
zilAvarSaM mahat tasyAH zaravarSeNa rAghavaH . prativAryopadhAvantyAH karau ciccheda patribhiH .
tatazchinnabhujAM zrAntAmabhyAze parigarjatIm . saumitrirakarot krodhAddhatakarNAgranAsikAm .
kAmarUpadharA sA tu kRtvA rUpANyanekazaH . antardhAnaM gatA yakSI mohayantI svamAyayA .
azmavarSaM vimuJcantI bhairavaM vicacAra sA . tatastAvazmavarSeNa kIryamANau samantataH . dRSTvA gAdhisutaH zrImAnidaM vacanamabravIt . alaM te ghRNayA rAma pApaiSA duSTvAriNI . yajJavighnakarI yakSI purA vardheta mAyayA . vadhyatAM tAvadevaiSA purA saMdhyA pravartate . rakSAMsi saMdhyAkAle tu durdharSANi bhavanti hi .
ityuktaH sa tu tAM yakSImazmavRSTayAbhivarSiNIm . darzayazabdavedhitvaM tAM rurodha sa sAyakaiH .
sA ruddhA bANajAlena mAyAbalasamanvitA . abhidudrAva kAkutsthaM lakSmaNaM ca vineduSI . tAmApatantI vegena vikrAntAmazanImiva . zareNorasi vivyAdha sA papAta mamAra ca .
tAM hatAM bhImasaMkAzAM dRSTvA surapatistadA . sAdhu sAdhviti kAkutsthaM surAzcApyabhipUjayan .
uvAca paramaprItaH sahasrAkSaH purandaraH . surAzca sarve saMhRSTA vizvAmitramathAbruvan .
mune kauzika bhadraM te sendrAH sarve marudgaNAH . toSitAH karmaNAnena snehaM darzaya rAghave . prajApateH kRzAzvasya putrAn satyaparAkramAn . tapobalabhRto brahman rAghavAya nivedaya .
pAtrabhUtazca te brahmastavAnugamane rataH . kartavyaM sumahat karma surANAM rAjasUnunA .
evamuktvA surAH sarve jagmurhaSTA vihAyasam . vizvAmitraM pUjayantastataH saMdhyA pravartate .
tato munivaraH prItastATakAvadhatoSitaH .32 . . mUrdhni rAmamupAghrAya idaM vacanamabravIt .
ihAdya rajanI rAma vasAma zubhadarzana . zvaH prabhAte gamiSyAmastadAzramapadaM mama .
vizvAmitravacaH zrutvA hRSTo dazarathAtmajaH . uvAsa rajanI tatra tATakAyA vane sukham .
muktazApaM vanaM tacca tasminneva tadAhani . ramaNIyaM vibabhrAja yathA caitrarathaM vanam .
nihatya to yakSasutAM sa rAmaH prazasyamAnaH surasiddhasaMghaiH . uvAsa tasmin muninA sahaiva prabhAtavelAM pratibodhyamAnaH .
RSyamUkAt sa dharmAtmA kiSkindhAM lakSmaNAgrajaH . jagAma saha sugrIvo vAlivikramapAlitAm . samudyamya mahaccApaM rAmaH kAJcanabhUSitam . zarAMzcAdityasaMkAzAn gRhItvA raNasAdhakAn .
agratastu yayau tasya rAghavasya mahAtmanaH . sugrIvaH saMhatagrIvo lakSmaNasya mahAbalaH .
pRSThato hanumAn vIro nalo nIlazca vIryavAn . tArazcaiva mahAtejA hariyUthapayUthapaH .
te vIkSamANA vRkSAMzca puSpabhArAvalambinaH . prasannAmbuvahAzcaiva saritaH sAgaraMgamAH . kandarANi ca zailAMzca nirdarANi guhAstathA . zikharANi ca mukhyAni darIzca priyadarzanAH .
vaidUryavimalaistoyaiH padyaizcAkozakuDmalaiH . zobhitAn sajalAn mArge taTAkAMzcAvalokayan . kAraNDaiH sArasaiha~sairvaJjulairjalakukkuTaiH . cakravAkaistathA cAnyaiH zakunaiH pratinAditAn .
mRduzaSpAGkurAhArAnnirbhayAn vanagocarAn . carataH sarvataH pazyan sthalISu hariNAn sthitAn .
taTAkavairiNazcApi zukladantavibhUSitAn . ghorAnekacarAnvanyAn dviradAn kUlaghAtinaH . mattAn giritaTotkRSTAn parvatAniva jaGgamAn . vAnarAn dviradaprakhyAn mahIreNusamukSitAn . vane vanacarAMzcAnyAn khecarAMzca vihaMgamAn . pazyantastvaritA jagmuH sugrIvavazavartinaH .
teSAM tu gacchatAM tatra tvaritaM raghunandanaH . dumaSaNDavanaM dRSTvA rAmaH sugrIvamabravIt .
eSa megha ivAkAze vRkSaSaNDaH prakAzate . meghasaMghAtavipulaH paryantakadalIvRtaH . kimetajjJAtumicchAmi sakhe kautUhalaM mama . kautUhalApanayanaM kartumicchAmyahaM tvayA .
tasya tadvacanaM zrutvA rAghavasya mahAtmanaH . gacchannevAcacakSe ' tha sugrIvastanmahad vanam .
etad rAghava vistIrNamAzramaM zramanAzanam . udyAnavanasampannaM svAdumUlaphalodakam . atra saptajanA nAma munayaH saMzitavratAH . saptavAsannadhaHzIrSA niyataM jalazAyinaH . saptarAtre kRtAhArA vAyunAcalavAsinaH . divaM varSazatairyAtAH saptabhiH sakalevarAH .
teSAmetatprabhAveNa dumaprAkArasaMvRtam . AzramaM sudurAdharSamapi sendraiH surAsuraiH .
pakSiNo varjayantyetat tathAnye vanacAriNaH . vizanti mohAd ye ' pyatra na nivartanti te punaH .
vibhUSaNaravAzcAtra zrUyante sakalAkSarAH . tUryagItasvanazcApi gandho divyazca rAghava .
tretAgnayo ' pi dIpyante dhUmo hyeSa pradRzyate . veSTayanniva vRkSAgrAn kapotAGgAruNo ghanaH .
ete vRkSAH prakAzante dhUmasaMsaktamastakAH . meghajAlapraticchannA vaidUryagirayo yathA .
kuru praNAmaM dharmAtmasteSAmuddizya rAghava . lakSmaNena saha bhrAtrA prayataH saMhatAJjaliH .
praNamanti hi ye teSAmRSINAM bhAvitAtmanAm . na teSAmazubhaM kiMciccharIre rAma vidyate .
tato rAmaH saha bhrAtrA lakSmaNena kRtAJjaliH . samuddizya mahAtmAnastAnRSInabhyavAdayat .
abhivAdya ca dharmAtmA rAmo bhrAtA ca lakSmaNaH . sugrIvo vAnarAzcaiva jagmuH saMhaSTamAnasAH .
te gatvA dUramadhvAnaM tasmAt saptajanAzramAt . daddazustAM durAdharSAM kiSkindhAM vAlipAlitAm .
tatastu rAmAnujarAmavAnarAH pragRhya zastrANyuditogratejasaH . purI surezAtmajavIryapAlitAM vadhAya zatroH punarAgatAstviha .
sA tathoktA tu vaidehI nirbhayA zokakarzitA . tRNamantarataH kRtvA rAvaNaM pratyabhASata .
rAjA dazaratho nAma dharmaseturivAcalaH . satyasaMdhaH parijJAto yasya putraH sa rAghavaH . nAmo nAma sa dharmAtmA triSu lokeSu vizrutaH . dIrghabAhurvizAlAkSo daivataM sa patirmama .
ikSvAkUNAM kule jAtaH siMhaskandho mahAdyutiH . lakSmaNena saha bhrAtrA yaste prANAn vadhiSyati . pratyakSaM yadyahaM tasya tvayA vai dharSitA balAt . zayitA tvaM hataH saMkhye janasthAne yathA kharaH .
ya ete rAkSasAH proktA ghorarUpA mahAbalAH . rAghave nirviSAH sarve suparNe pannagA yathA .
tasya jyAvipramuktAste kharAH kAJcanabhUSaNAH . zarIraM vidhamiSyanti gaGgAkUlamivormayaH .7 . .
asurairvA surairvA tvaM yadyavadhyo ' si rAvaNa . utpAdya sumahad vairaM jIvaMstasya na mokSyase .
sa te jIvitazeSasya rAghavo ' ntakaro balI . pazoDUMpagatasyeva jIvitaM tava durlabham .
yadi pazyet sa rAmastvaM roSadIptena cakSuSA . rakSastvamadya nirdagdho yathA rudreNa manmathaH .
yazcandraM nabhaso bhUmau pAtayennAzayeta vA . sAgaraM zoSayed vApi sa sItAM mocayediha .
gatAsustvaM gatazrIko gatasattvo gatendriyaH . laGkA vaidhavyasaMyuktA tvatkRtena bhaviSyati .
na te pApamidaM karma sukhodakaM bhaviSyati . yAhaM nItA vinAbhAvaM patipArdhvAt tvayA balAt .
sa hi devarasaMyukto mama bhartA mahAdyutiH . nirbhayo vIryamAzritya zUnye vasati daNDake .
sa te vIryaM balaM darpamutsekaM ca tathAvidham . vyapaneSyati gAtrebhyaH zaravarSeNa saMyuge .
yadA vinAzo bhUtAnAM dRzyate kAlacoditaH . tadA kArye pramAdyanti narAH kAlavazaM gatAH .
mAM pradhRSya sa te kAlaH prApto ' yaM rAkSasAdhama . Atmano rAkSasAnAM ca vadhAyAntaHpurasya ca .
na zakyA yajJamadhyasthA vediH srugbhANDamaNDitA . dvijAtimantrasampUtA caNDAlenAvamarditum .
tathAhaM dharmanityasya dharmapatnI dRDhavratA . tvayA spraSTuM na zakyAhaM rAkSasAdhama pApinA .
krIDantI rAjahaMsena padmaSaNDeSu nityazaH . haMsI sA tRNamadhyasthaM kathaM drakSyeta madgukam .
idaM zarIraM ni : saMjJaM bandha vA ghAtayasva vA . nedaM zarIraM rakSyaM me jIvitaM vApi rAkSasa .
na tu zakyamapakrozaM pRthivyAM dAtumAtmanaH . evamuktvA tu vaidehI krodhAt suparuSaM vacaH .
rAvaNaM jAnakI tatra punarnovAca kiMcana . sItAyA vacanaM zrutvA paruSaM romaharSaNam . pratyuvAca tataH sItAM bhayasaMdarzanaM vacaH .
zRNumaithili madvAkyaM mAsAn dvAdaza bhAmini . kAlenAnena nAbhyeSi yadi mAM cAruhAsini . tatastvAM prAtarAzArthaM sUdAzchetsyanti lezazaH .
ityuktvA paruSaM vAkyaM rAvaNaH zatrurAvaNaH . rAkSasIzca tataH kruddha idaM vacanamabravIt .
zIghrameva hi rAkSasyo virUpA ghoradarzanAH . darpamasyApaneSyantu mAMsazoNitabhojanAH .
vacanAdeva tAstasya sughorA ghoradarzanAH . kRtaprAJjalayo bhUtvA maithilI paryavArayan .
sa tAH provAca rAjAsau rAvaNo ghoradarzanAH . pracalya caraNotkarSairdArayanniva medinIm .
azokavanikAmadhye maithilI nIyatAmiti . tatreyaM rakSyatAM gUDhaM yuSmAbhiH parivAritA . tatrainAM tarjanaioraiH punaH sAntvaizca maithilIm . AnayadhvaM vazaM sarvA vanyAM gajavadhUmiva .
iti pratisamAdiSTA rAkSasyo rAvaNena tAH . azokavanikAM jagmurmaithilI parigRhya tu . sarvakAmaphalairvRkSairnAnApuSpaphalairvRtAm . sarvakAlamadaizcApi dvijaiH samupasevitAm .
sA tu zokaparitAGgI maithilI janakAtmajA . rAkSasIvazamApannA vyAghrINAM hariNI yathA .
zokena mahatA trastA maithilI janakAtmajA . na zarma labhate bhIruH pAzabaddhA mRgI yathA .
na vindate tatra tu zarma maithilI virUpanetrAbhiratIva tarjitA . patiM smarantI dayitaM ca devaraM vicetanAbhUd bhayazokapIDitA .
itaH paraM prakSipto ' yaM sargaH . . pravezitAyAM sItAyAM laGkAM prati pitAmaha . tadA provAca devendra parituSTaM zatakratum .
trailokyasya hitArthAya rakSasAmahitAya ca . laGkAM pravezitA sItA rAvaNena durAtmanA .
pativratA mahAbhAgA nityaM caiva sustraidhitA . apazyantI ca bhatauraM pazyantI rAkSasIjanam . rAkSasIbhiH parivRtA bhartRdarzanalAlasA .
niviSTA hi purI laGkA tIre nadanadIpateH . kathaM jJAsyati tAM rAmastatrasthAM tAmaninditAm .
duHzaM saMcintayanitI sA bahuzaH paridurlabhA . prANayAtrAmakurrANA prANAMstyakSyatyasaMzayam . sa bhUyaH saMzayo jAtaH sItAyAH prANasaMkSaye .
sa tvaM zIghramito gatvA sItAM pazya zubhAnanAm . pravizya nagarI laGkAM prayaccha haviruttamam .
evamukto ' tha devendraH purI rAvaNapAlitAm . AgacchannidrayA sArdha bhagavAn pAkazAsanaH .
nidrAM covAca gaccha tvaM rAkSasAn sampramohaya . sA tathoktA maghavatA devI paramaharSitA . devakAryArthasiddhayarthaM prAmohayata rAkSasAn .
etasminnantare devaH sahasrAkSaH zacIpatiH . AsamAda vanasthAM tAM vacanaM cedamabravIt .
devarAjo ' smi bhadraM te iha cAsmi zucismite . ahaM tvAM kAryaniddadhyarthaM rAghavasya mahAtmanaH . sAhAyyaM kalpayiSyAmi mA zuco janakAtmaje .
matprasAdAt samudraM sa tariSyati balaiH saha . mayaiveha ca rAkSasyo mAyAya mohitAH zubhe .
tasmAdannamidaM sIte haviSyAnnahaM svayam . sa tvAM saMgRhya vaidehi AgataH saha nidrayA .14 . .
etadatsyasi maddhastAnna tvAM vAdhiSyate zubhe . kSudhA tRSA ca rambhoru varSANAmayutairapi .
evamuktA tu devendramuvAca parizaGkitA . kathaM jAnAmi devendraM tvAmihasthaM khajApatim .
devaliGgAni dRSTAni rAmalakSmaNasaMnidhau . tAni darzaya devendra yadi tvaM devarAT svayam .
sItAyA vacanaM zrutvA tathA cakre zacIpatiH . gRthivIM nAspRzat padbhyAmanimeSekSaNAni ca . arajo ' mbaradhArI ca namlInakusumastathA . taM jJAtvA lakSNaiH sItA vAsavaM pariharSitA .
uvAca vAkyaM rudatI bhagavan rAghavaM prati . kaha bhrAtrA mahAbAhurdiSTayaH me zrutimAgataH .
yathA me zvazuro rAjA yathA ca mithilAdhipaH . sathA tvamadya pazyAmi sanAtho me patistvayA .
tavAjJayA ca devendra payobhUtamidaM haviH . aziSyAmi tvayA dattaM raghUNAM kulavarghanam .
indrahastAd gRhItvA tat pAyasaM sA zucismitA . nyavedayata bharne sA lakSmaNAya ca maithilI .
yadi jIvati me bhartA saha bhrAtrA mahAbalaH . idamastu tayorbhaktyA tadAznAt svayam .
itIva tat prAzya havirvarAnanA jahau kSudhAduHkhasamudbhavaM ca tam . indrAt pravRttimupalabhya jAnakI kAkutsthayoH prItamanA babhUva .
sa cApi zakrastridivAlayaM tadA prIto yayau rAghavakAryasiddhaye . Amantrya sItAM sa tato mahAtmA jagAma nidrAsahitaH svamAlayam .
tataH zUrpaNakhAM dRSTvA bruvantI paruSaM vacaH . amAtyamadhye saMkruddhaH paripapraccha rAvaNaH .
kazca rAmaH kathaMvIryaH kiMrUpaH kiMparAkramaH . kimarthe daNDakAraNyaM praviSTazca sudustaram .
AyughaM kiM ca rAmasya yena te rAkSasA hatAH . kharazca nihataH saMkhye dUSaNastrizirAstathA .
tattvaM brUhi manojJAGgi kena tvaM ca virUpitA . ityuktA rAkSasendreNa rAkSasI krodhamUrchitA .
tato rAmaM yathAnyAyamAkhyAtumupacakrame . dIrghabAhurvizAlAkSazcIrakRSNAjinAmbaraH . kandarpasamarUpazca rAmo dazarathAtmajaH .
zakracApanibhaM cApaM vikRSya kanakAGgadam . dIptAn tripati nArAcAn saniva mahAviSAn .
nAdadAnaM zarAn ghorAn vimuJcantaM mahAbalam .7 . . na kArmukaM vikarSantaM rAmaM pazyAmi saMyuge . hanyamAnaM tu tatsainyaM pazyAmi zaravRSTibhiH . indreNevottamaM sasyamAhataM tvazmavRSTibhiH . rakSasAM bhImavIryANAM sahasrANi caturdaza . nihatAni zaraistIkSNaistenaikena padAtinA . ardhAdhikamuhUrtena kharazca sahadUSaNaH . RSINAmabhayaM dattaM kRtakSemAzca daNDakAH . ekA kathaMcitmuktAhaM paribhUya mahAtmanA . strIvadhaM zaGkamAnena rAmeNa viditAtmanA . bhrAtA cAsya mahAtejA guNatastulyavikramaH .
anuraktazca bhaktazca lakSmaNo nAma vIryavAn . amarSI durjayo jetA vikrAnto buddhimAn balI . rAmasya dakSiNo bAhunityaM prANo bahizcaraH .
rAmasya tu vizAlAkSI pUrNendusadRzAnanA . dharmapatnI priyA nityaM bhartuH priyahite ratA .
sA sukezI sunAsorU : surUpA ca yazasvinI . devateva vanasyAsya rAjate zrIrivAparA .
taptakAJcanavarNAbhA raktatuGganakhI zubhA . sItA nAma varArohA vaidehI tanumadhyamA .
naiva devI na gandharvI na yakSI na ca kiMnarI . tathArUpA mayA nArI dRSTapUrvA mahItale .
yasya sItA bhaved bhAryA yaM ca hRSTA pariSvajet . abhijIvet sa sarveSu lokeSvapi puraMdarAt .
sA suzIlA vapuHzlAdhyA rUpeNApratimA bhuvi . tavAnurUpA bhAryA sA tvaM ca tasyAH patirvaraH .
tAM tu vistIrNajaghanAM pInottuGgapayodharAm . bhAryArthe tu tavAnetumudyatAhaM varAnanAm . virUpitAsmi krUreNa lakSmaNena mahAbhuja .
tAM tu dRSTvAdya vaidehI pUrNacandranibhAnanAm . manmathasya zarANAM ca tvaM vidheyo bhaviSyasi .
yadi tasyAmabhiprAyo bhAryAtve tava jAyate . zIghramudbhiyatAM pAdo jayArthamiha dakSiNaH .
rocate yati te vAkyaM mamaitad rAkSasezvara . kriyatAM nirvizaGkena vacanaM mama rAvaNa .
vijJAyaiSAmazaktiM ca kriyatAM ca mahAbala . sItA tavAnavadyAGgI bhAryAtve rAkSasezvara .
hatAJjanasthAnagatAn nizAcarAn . kharaM ca dRSTvA nihataM ca dUSaNaM tvamadya kRtyaM pratipattumarhasi .
