evamuktvA mahAtejA rAvaNaH punarabravIt . caritA bhavatA senA ke ' tra zUrAH plavaMgamAH .
kiMprabhAH kIdRzAH saumya vAnarA ye durAsadAH . kasya putrAzca pautrAzca tattvamAkhyAhi suvrata .
tathAtra pratipatsyApi jJAtvA teSAM balAbalam . avazyaM khalu saMkhyAnaM kartavyaM yuddhamicchatA . .18
athaivamuktaH zArdUlo rAvaNenottamazcaraH . idaM vacanamArebhe vaktuM rAvaNasaMnidhau .
atharbharajasaH putro yudhi rAjansudurjayaH . gadgadasyAtha putro ' tra jAmbavAniti vizrutaH .
gadgadasyAtha putro ' nyo guruputraH zatakratoH . kadanaM yasya putreNa kRtamekena rakSasAm .
suSeNazcAtra dharmAtmA putro dharmasya vIryavAn . saumyaH somAtmajazcAtra rAjandadhimukhaH kapiH .
sumukho durmukhazcAtra vegadarzI ca vAnaraH . mRtyurvAnararUpeNa nUnaM sRSTaH svayaMbhuvA .
putro hutavahasyAtra nIlaH senApatiH svayam . anilasya tu putro ' tra hanUmAniti vizrutaH .
naptA zakrasya durdharSo balavAnaGgado yuvA . maindazca dvividazcobhau balinAvazvisaMbhavau .
putrA vaivasvatasyAtha paJca kAlAntakopamAH . gajo gavAkSo gavayaH zarabho gandhamAdanaH .
daza vAnarakoTyazca zUrANAM yuddhakAkSiNAm . zrImatAM devaputrANAM zeSa nAkhyAtumutsahe .
putro dazarathasyaiSa siMhasaMhanano yuvA . dUSaNo nihato yena svarazca trizirAstathA .
nAsti rAmasya sadRzo vikrame bhuvi kazcana . virAdho nihato yena kabandhazcAntakopamaH .
vaktuM na zakto rAmasya guNAnkazcinnaraH kSitau . janasthAnagatA yena tAvanto rAkSasA hatAH .
lakSmaNazcAtra dharmAtmA mAtaGgAnAmivarSabhaH . yasya bANapathaM prApya na jIvedapi vAsavaH .
zveto jyotirmukhazcAtra bhAskarasyAtmasaMbhavau . varuNasyAtha putro ' tha hemakUTaH plavaMgamaH .
vizvakarmasuto vIro nalaH plavagasattamaH . vikrAnto vegavAnatra vasuputraH sa durdharaH .
rAkSasAnAM variSThazca tava bhrAtA vibhISaNaH . pratigRhya purIM laGkAM rAghavasya hite rataH .
iti sarvaM samAkhyAtaM tathA vai vAnaraM balam . suvele ' dhiSThitaM zaile zeSakArye bhavAngatiH .
tasya tad vacanaM zrutvA kuzanAbhasya dhImataH . zirobhizcaraNo spRSTvA kanyAzatamabhASata .
vAyuH sarvAtmako rAjan pradharSayitumicchati . azubhaM mArgamAsthAya na dharmaM pratyavekSate .
pitRmatyaH sma bhadraM te svacchande na vayaM sthitAH . pitaraM no vRNISva tvaM yadi no dAsyate tava .
tena pApAnubandhena vacanaM na pratIcchatA . evaM bruvantyaH sarvAH sma vAyunAbhihatA bhRzam .
tAsAM tu vacanaM zrutvA rAjA paramadhArmikaH . pratyuvAca mahAtejAH kanyAzatamanuttamam .
kSAntaM kSamAvatAM putryaH kartavyaM sumahat kRtam . aikamatyamupAgamya kulaM cAvekSitaM mama .
alaMkAro hi nArINAM kSamA tu puruSasya vA . duSkaraM tacca vai kSAntaM tridazeSu vizeSataH . yAdRzI vaH kSamA putryaH sarvAsAmavizeSataH .
kSamA dAnaM kSamA satyaM kSamA yajJAzca putrikAH . kSamA yazaH kSamA dharmaH kSamAyAM viSThitaM jagat .
visRjya kanyAH kAkutstha rAjA tridazavikramaH . mantrajJo mantrayAmAsa pradAnaM saha mantribhiH . deze kAle ca kartavyaM sadRze pratipAdanam .
etasminneva kAle tu cUlI nAma mahAdyutiH . UrdhvaretAH zubhAcAro brAhmaM tapa upAgamat .
tapasyantamRSiM tatra gandharvI paryupAsate . somadA nAma bhadraM te UrmilAtanayA tadA .
sA ca taM praNatA bhUtvA zuzrUSaNaparAyaNA . uvAsa kAle dharmiSThA tasyAstuSTo ' bhavad guruH .
sa ca tAM kAlayogena provAca raghunandana . parituSTo ' smi bhadraM te kiM kami tava priyam .
parituSTaM muniM jJAtvA gandharvI madhurasvaram . uvAca paramaprItA vAkyajJA vAkyakovidam .
lakSmyA samudito brAhmayA brahmabhUto mahAtapAH . brAhmaNa tapasA yuktaM putramicchAmi dhArmikam .
apatizcAsmi bhadraM te bhAryA cAsmi na kasyacit . brAhmaNopagatAyAzca dAtumarhasi me sutam .
tasyAH prasanno brahmarSirdadau brAhmamanuttamam . brahmadatta iti khyAtaM mAnasaM cUlinaH sutam .
sa rAjA brahmadattastu purImadhyavasat tadA . kAmpilyAM parayA lakSmyA devarAjo yathA divam .
sa buddhiM kRtavAn rAjA kuzanAbhaH sudhArmikaH . brahmadattAya kAkutstha dAtuM kanyAzataM tadA .
tamAhUya mahAtejA brahmadattaM mahIpatiH . dadau kanyAzataM rAjA sugrIvenAntarAtmanA .
yathAkramaM tadA pANiM jagrAha raghunandana . brahmadatto mahIpAlastAsAM devapatiryathA .
spRSTamAtre tadA pANau vikubjA vigatajvarAH . yuktaM paramayA lakSmyA babhau kanyAzataM tadA .
sa dRSTvA vAyunA muktAH kuzanAbho mahIpatiH . babhUva paramaprIto harSaM lebhe punaH punaH .
kRtodvAhaM tu rAjAnaM brahmadattaM mahIpatim . sadAraM preSayAmAsa sopAdhyAyagaNaM tadA .
somadApi sutaM dRSTvA putrasya sadRzIM kriyAm . yathAnyAyaM ca gandhavIM snuSAstAH pratyanandata . spRSTvA ca tAH kanyAH kuzanAbhaM prazasya ca .
somadApi sutaM dRSTvA putrasya sadRzIM kriyAm . yathAnyAyaM ca gandhavIM snuSAstAH pratyanandata . spRSTvA ca tAH kanyAH kuzanAbhaM prazasya ca .
atha tAM rajanIM tatra kRtArthoM rAmalakSmaNau . uSaturmuditau vIrau prahRSTenAntarAtmanA .
prabhAtAyAM tu zarvaryAM kRtapaurvAhnikakriyau . vizvAmitramRSIMzcAnyAn sahitAvabhijagmatuH .
abhivAdya munizreSThaM jvalantamiva pAvakam . UcatuH paramodAraM vAkyaM madhurabhASiNau .
imau sma munizArdUla kiMkarau samupAgatau . AjJApaya munizreSTha zAsanaM karavAva kim .
evamukte tayorvAkye sarvaM eka maharSayaH . vizvAmitraM puraskRtya rAmaM vacanamabruvan .5 . .
maithilasya narazreSTha janakasya bhaviSyati . yajJaH paramadharmiSThastatra yAsyAmahe vayam .
tvaM caiva narazArdUla sahAsmAbhirgamiSyasi . adbhutaM ca dhanUratnaM tatra tvaM draSTumarhasi .
taddhi pUrvaM narazreSTha dattaM sadasi daivataiH . aprameyabalaM ghoraM makhe paramabhAsvaram .
nAsya devA na gandharvA nAsurA na ca rAkSasAH . kartumAropaNaM zaktA na kathaMcana mAnuSAH .
dhanuSastasya vIryaM hi jijJAsanto mahIkSitaH . na zekurAropayituM rAjaputrA mahAbalAH .
taddhanurnarazArdUla maithilasya mahAtmanaH . tatra drakSyasi kAkutstha yajJaM ca paramAdbhutam .
taddhi yajJaphalaM tena maithilenottamaM dhanuH . yAcitaM narazArdUla sunAbhaM sarvadaivataiH .
AyAgabhUtaM nRpatestasya vezmani rAghava . arcitaM vividhairgandhaidhUpaizcAgurugandhibhiH .
evamuktvA munivaraH prasthAnamakarot tadA . sarSisaGghaH sakAkutstha Amantrya vanadevatAH .
svasti vo ' stu gamiSyAmi siddhaH siddhAzramAdaham . uttare jAhnavItIre himavantaM ziloccayam .
ityuktvA munizArdUlaH kauzikaH sa tapodhanaH . uttarAM dizamuddizya prasthAtumupacakrame .
taM vrajantaM munivaramanvagAdanusAriNAm . zakaTIzatamAtraM tu prayANe brahmavAdinAm .
mRgapakSigaNAzcaiva siddhAzramanivAsinaH . anujagmurmahAtmAnaM vizvAmitraM tapodhanam .
nivartayAmAsa tataH sarSisaGghaH sa pakSiNaH . te gatvA dUramadhvAnaM lambamAne divAkare . vAsaM cakrurmunigaNAH zoNAkUle samAhitAH . te ' staM gate dinakare snAtvA hutahutAzanAH . vizvAmitraM puraskRtya niSeduramitaujasaH . rAmo ' pi sahasaumitrirmunIstAnabhipUjya ca . jagrato niSasAdAtha vizvAmitrasya dhImataH .
atha rAmo mahAtejA vizvAmitraM tapodhanam . papraccha munizArdUlaM kautUhalasamanvitam . bhagavan ko nvayaM dezaH samRddhavanazobhitaH . zrotumicchAmi bhadraM te vaktumarhasi tattvataH .
nodito rAmavAkyena kathayAmAsa suvrataH . tasya dezasya nikhilamRSimadhye mahAtapAH .
tadapriyamamitraghno vacanaM maraNopamam . zrutvA na vivyathe rAmaH kaikeyI cedamabravIt . . .
evamastu gamiSyAmi vanaM vastumahaM tvitaH . jaTAcIradharo rAjJaH pratijJAmanupAlayan .
idaM tu jJAtumicchAmi kimarthaM mAM mahIpatiH . nAbhinandati durdharSo yathApUrvabhariMdamaH .
manyurna ca tvayA kAryo devi brUmi tavAgrataH . yAsyAmi bhava suprItA vanaM cIrajaTAdharaH .
hitena guruNA pitrA kRtajJena nRpeNa ca . niyujyamAno visrabdhaH kiM na kuryAAhaM priyam .
alIkaM mAnasaM tvekaM hRdayaM dahate mama . svayaM yannAha mAM rAjA bharatasyAbhiSecanam .
ahaM hi sItAM rAjyaM ca prANAniSTAn dhanAni ca . hRSTo bhrAtre svayaM dadyAM bharatAya pracoditaH . kiM punarmanujendreNa svayaM pitrA pracoditaH . tava ca priyakAmArthaM pratijJAmanupAlayan .
tathAzvAsaya hrImantaM kiMtvidaM yanmahIpatiH . vasudhAsaktanayano mandamazrUNi muJcati .
gacchantu caivAnayituM dUtAH zIghrajavairhayaiH . bharataM mAtulakulAdadyaiva nRpazAsanAt .
daNDakAraNyameSo ' haM gacchAmyeva hi satvaraH . avicArya piturvAkyaM samA vastuM caturdaza .
sA hRSTA tasya tad vAkyaM zrutvA rAmasya kaikayI . prasthAnaM zraddadhAnA sA tvarayAmAsa rAghavam .
yAsyanti dUtAH zIghrajavairhayaiH . bharataM mAtulakulAdihAvartayutaM narAH .
evaM bhavatu tava tvahaM kSamaM manye notsukasya vilambanam . rAma tasmAditaH zIghraM vanaM tvaM gantumarhasi .
vrIDAnvitaH svayaM yacca nRpastvAM nAbhibhASate . naitat kiMcinnarazreSTha manyureSo ' panIyatAm .
yAvattvaM na vanaM yAtaH purAdasmAdatitvaram . pitA tAvannate rAma snAsyate bhokSyate ' pi vA .
dhikkaSTamiti niHzvasya rAjA zokapariplutaH . mUrcchito nyapatat tasmin paryaGke hemabhUSite .
rAmo ' pyutthAppa rAjAnaM kaikeyyAbhipracoditaH . kazayeva hato vAjI vanaM gantuM kRtatvaraH .
tadapriyamanAyA vacanaM dAruNodayam . zrutvA gatavyatho rAmaH kaikeyIM vAkyamabravIt .
nAhamarthaparo devi lokamAvastumutsahe . viddhi mAmRSibhistulyaM vimalaM dharmamAsthitam .
yat tatra bhavataH kiMcicchakyaM kartuM priyaM mayA . prANAnapi parityajya sarvathA kRtameva tat .
na hyato dharmacaraNaM kiMcidasti mahattaram . yathA pitari zuzrUSA tasya vA vacanakriyA .
anukto ' pyatrabhavatA bhavatyA vacanAdaham . vane vatsyAmi vijane varSANIha caturdaza .
na nyUnaM mayi kaikeyi kiMcidAzaMsase guNAn . yad rAjAnamavocastvaM mamezvaratarA satI .
yAvanmAtaramApRcche sItAM jAnunayAmyaham . tato ' dyaiva gamiSyAmi daNDakAnAM mahad vanam .
bharataH pAlayed rAjyaM zuzrUSecca pituryathA . tathA bhavatyA kartavyaM sa hi dharmaH sanAtanaH .
rAmasya tu vacaH zrutvA bhRzaM duHkhagataH pitA . zokAdazaknuvan vaktuM praruroda mahAsvanam .
vanditvA caraNau rAjJo visaMjJasya pitustadA . kaikeyyAzcApyanA yA niSpapAta mahAdyutiH .
sa rAmaH pitaraM kRtvA kaikeyIM ca pradakSiNam . niSkramyAntaHpurAt tasmAt svaM dadarza suhajjanam .
taM bASpaparipUrNAkSaH pRSThato ' nujagAma ha . lakSmaNaH paramakruddhaH sumitrAnandavardhanaH .
AbhiSecanikaM bhANDaM kRtvA rAmaH pradakSiNam . zanairjagAma sApekSo dRSTiM tatrAvicAlayan .
na cAsya mahatIM lakSmI rAjyanAzo ' pakarSati . lokakAntasya kAntatvAcchItarazmeriva kSayaH .
na vanaM gantukAmasya tyajatazca vasuMdharAm . sarvalokAtigasyeva lakSyate cittavikriyA .
pratiSidhya zubhaM chatraM vyajane ca svalaMkRte . visarjayitvA svajanaM rathaM paurAMstathA janAn . dhArayan manasA du : khamindriyANi nigRhya ca . pravivezAtmavAn vezma mAturapriyazaMsivAn .
sarvo ' pyabhijanaH zrImAJzrImataH satyavAdinaH . nAlakSayata rAmasya kaMcidAkAramAnane .
ucitaM ca mahAbAhurna jahau harSamAtmavAn . zAradaH samudIrNAMzuzcandrasteja ivAtmajam .
vAcA madhurayA rAmaH sarvaM sammAnayaJjanam . mAtuH samIpaM dharmAtmA praviveza mahAyazAH .
taM guNaiH samatAM prApto bhrAtA vipulavikramaH . saumitriranuvavrAja dhArayan duHkhamAtmajam .
pravizya vezmAtibhRzaM mudA yutaM samIkSya tAM cArthavipattimAgatAm . na caiva rAmo ' tra jagAma vikriyAM suhRjjanasyAtmavipattizaGkayA .
kharaM tu virathaM rAmo gadApANimavasthitam . mRdupUrvaM mahAtejAH paruSaM vAkyamabravIt .
gajAzvarathasambAdhe bale mahati tiSThatA . kRtaM te dAruNaM karma sarvalokajugupsitam . udvejanIyo bhUtAnAM nRzaMsaH pApakarmakRt . trayANAmapi lokAnAmIzvaro ' pi sa tiSThati . karma lokaviruddhaM tu kurvANaM kSaNadAcara . tIkSNaM sarvajano hanti saSa duSTamivAgatam .
lobhAt pApAni kurvANaH kAmAd vA yo na budhyate . hRSTaH pazyati tasyAntaM brAhmaNI karakAdiva .
vasato daNDakAraNye tApasAn dharmacAriNaH . kiM nu hatvA mahAbhAgAn phalaM prApsyasi rAkSasa .
na ciraM pApakarmANaH krUrA lokajugupsitAH . aizvaryaM prApya tiSThanti zIrNamUlA iva drumAH .7 . .
avazyaM labhate kartA phalaM pApasya karmaNaH . ghoraM paryAgate kAle drumaH puSpamivArtavam .
na cirAt prApyate loke pApAnAM karmaNAM phalam . saviSANAmivAnnAnAM bhuktAnAM kSaNadAcara .
pApamAcaratAM ghoraM lokasyApriyamicchatAm . ahamAsAdito rAjJA prANAn hantuM nizAcara .
adya bhitvA mayA muktAH zarAH kAJcanabhUSaNAH . vidAryAtipatiSyanti valmIkamiva pannagAH .
ye tvayA daNDakAraNye bhakSitA dharmacAriNaH . tAnadya nihataH saMkhye sasainyo ' nugamiSyasi .
adya tvAM nihataM bANaiH pazyantu paramarSayaH . nirayasthaM vimAnasthA ye tvayA nihatAH purA .
praharasva yathAkAmaM kuru yatnaM kulAdhama . adya te pAtayiSyAmi zirastAlaphalaM yathA .
evamuktastu rAmeNa kruddhaH saMraktalocanaH . pratyuvAca tato rAmaM prahasan krodhamUcchitaH .
prAkRtAn rAkSasAn hatvA yuddhe dazarathAtmaja . AtmanA kathamAtmAnamaprazasyaM prazaMsasi .
vikrAntA balavanto vA ye bhavanti nararSabhAH . kathayanti na te kiMcit tejasA cAtigarvitAH .
prAkRtAstvakRtAtmAno loke kSatriyapAMsanAH . nirarthakaM vikatthante yathA rAma vikatthase .
kulaM vapadizan vIraH samare ko ' bhidhAsyati . mRtyukAle tu samprApte svayamaprastave stavam .
sarvathA tu laghutvaM te katthanena vidarzitam . suvarNapratirUpeNa tapteneva kuzAgninA .
na tu mAmiha tiSThantaM pazyasi tvaM gadAdharam . dharAdharamivAkampyaM parvataM dhAtubhizcitam .
paryApto ' haM gadApANirhantuM prANAn raNe tava . trayANAmapi lokAnAM pAzahasta ivAntakaH .
kAmaM bahvapi vaktavyaM tvayi vakSyAmi na tvaham . astaM prApnoti savitA yuddhavighnastato bhavet .
caturdaza sahasrANi rAkSasAnAM hatAni te . tvadvinAzAt karomyadya teSAmathupramArjanam .
ityuktvA paramakruddhaH sa gadAM paramAGgadAm . kharazcikSepa rAmAya pradIptAmazani yathA .
kharabAhupramuktA sA pradIptA mahatI gadA . bhasmavRkSAMzca gulmAMzca kRtvAgAt tatsamIpataH .
tAmApatantI mahatI mRtyupAzopamAM gadAm . antarikSagatI rAmazciccheda bahudhA zaraiH .
sA vizIrNA zarairbhinnA papAta dharaNItale . gadA mantrauSadhibalaiAlIva vinipAtitA .
tathA tu taM samAdizya bhrAtaraM raghunandanaH . babandhAsiM mahAtejA jAmbUnadamayatsarum .
tatastrivinataM cApamAdAyAtmavibhUSaNam . Abadhya ca kapAlau dvau jagAmodagravikramaH .
taM vanyarAjo rAjendramApatantaM nirIkSya vai . babhUvAntarhitastrAsAt punaH saMdarzane ' bhavat .
baddhAsirdhanurAdAya pradudrAva yato mRgaH . taM sma pazyati rUpeNa dyotayantamivAgrataH . avekSyAvekSya dhAvantaM dhanuSpANirmahAvane . ativRttamivotpAtAllobhayAnaM kadAcana . zaGkitaM tu samudmAstamutpatantamivAmbaram . dRzyamAnamadRzyaM ca vanoddezeSu keSucit . chinnAbhairiva saMvItaM zAradaM candramaNDalam . muhUrtAdeva dadRze muhurdUrAt prakAzate .
darzanAdarzanenaiva so ' pAkarSata rAghavam . sa dUramAzramasyAsya mArIco mRgatAM gataH .
AsIt kruddhastu kAkutstho vivazastena mohitaH . athAvatasthe suzrAntazchAyAmAzritya zAbale .
sa tamunmAdayAmAsa mRgarUpo nizAcaraH . mRgaiH parivRto ' thAnyairadUrAt pratyadRzyata .
grahItukAmaM dRSTvA taM punarevAbhyadhAvata . tatkSaNAdeva saMtrAsAt punarantarhito ' bhavat .
punareva tato dUrAd vRkSakhaNDAd viniHsRtaH . dRSTvA rAmo mahAtejAstaM hantuM kRtanizcayaH . bhUyastu zaramuddhatya kupitastatra rAghavaH . sUryarazmipratIkAzaM jvalantamarimardanam . saMdhAya sudRDhe cApe vikRSya balavadabalI . tameva mRgamuddizya zvasantamiva pannagam . mumoca jvalitaM dIptamastraM brahmavinirmitam .
zarIraM mRgarUpasya vinirbhidya zarottamaH . mArIcasyaiva hRdayaM bibhedAzanisaMnibhaH .
tAlamItramathotplutya nyapatat sa bhRzAturaH . vyanadad bhairavaM nAdaM dharaNyAmalpajIvitaH .
mriyamANastu mArIco jahau tAM kRtrimA tanum . smRtvA tadvacanaM rakSo dadhyau kena tu lakSmaNam . iha prasthApayet sItA tAM zUnye rAvaNo haret .
sa prAptakAlamAjJAya cakAra ca tataH svanam . sadRzaM rAghavasyeva hA sIte lakSmaNeti ca . tena marmaNi nirviddhaM zareNAnupamena hi . mRgarUpaM tu tat tyaktvA rAkSasaM rUpamAsthitaH .
cakre sa sumahAkAyo mArIco jIvitaM tyajan . taM dRSTvA patitaM bhUmau rAkSasaM bhImadarzanam . rAmo rudhirasiktAGga ceSTamAnaM mahItale . jagAma manasA sItAM lakSmaNasya vacaH smaran .
mArIcasya tu mAyaiSA pUrvoktaM lakSmaNena tu . tat tathA hyabhavaccAdya mArIco ' yaM mayA hataH .
hA sIte lakSmaNetyevamAkruzya tu mahAsvanam . mamAra rAkSasaH so ' yaM zrutvA sItA kathaM bhavet .
lakSmaNazca mahAbAhuH kAmavasthAM gamiSyati . iti saMcintya dharmAtmA rAmo hRSTatanUrUhaH . tatra rAmaM bhayaM tIvramAviveza viSAdajam . rAkSasaM mRgarUpaM taM hatvA zrutvA ca tatsvanam .
nihatya pRSataM cAnyaM mAMsamAdAya rAghavaH . tvaramANo janasthAnaM sasArAbhisukhaM tadA .
tAM tu pArzve sthitAM prahvAM rAmaH saMmekSya maithilIm . hRdayAntargataM bhAvaM vyAhartumupacakrame .
eSAsi nirjitA bhadre zatru jitvA raNAjire . pauruSAt yadanuSTheyaM mayaitadupapAditam .
gato ' smyantamamarSasya dharSaNA saMpramArjitA . avamAnazca zatruzca yugapatrihatau mayA .
adya me pauruSaM dRSTamadya me saphalaH zramaH . adya tIrNapratijJo ' haM prabhavAmyadya cAtmanaH .
yA tvaM virahitA nItA calacittena rakSasA . daivasaMpAdito doSo mAnuSeNa mayA jitaH .
saMprAptamavamAnaM yastejasA na pramArjati . kastasya pauruSeNArtho mahatApyalpacetasaH .
laGghanaM ca samudrasya laGkAyAzcApi mardanam . saphalaM tasya ca zlAghyamadya karma hanUmataH .
yuddhe vikramatazcaiva hitaM mantrayatastayA . sugrIvasya sasainyasya saphalo ' dya parizramaH .
vibhISaNasya ca tathA saphalo ' dya parizramaH . viguNaM bhrAtaraM tyaktvA yo mAM svayamupasthitaH . . . .
ityevaM vadataH zrutvA sItA rAmasya tadvacaH . mRgIvotphullanayanA babhUvAzrupariplutA .
pazyatastAM tu rAmasya samIpe hRdayapriyAm . janavAdabhayAdrAjJo babhUva hRdayaM dvidhA .
sItAmutpalapatrAkSI nIlakuJcitamUrdhajAm . avadadvai varArohAM madhye vAnararakSasAm .
yatkartavyaM manuSyeNa dharSaNAM pratimArjatA . tatkRtaM rAvaNaM hatvA mayedaM mAnakAGkSiNA . nirjitA jIvalokasya tapasA bhAvitAtmanA . agastyena durAdharSA muninA dakSiNeva dik .
viditazcAstu bhadraM te yo ' yaM raNaparizramaH . sutIrNaH suhRdAM vIryAnna tvadarthaM mayA kRtaH .
rakSatA tu mayA vRttamapavAdaM ca sarvataH . prakhyAtasyAtmavaMzasya nyaGgaM ca parimArjatA .
prAptacAritrasaMdehA mama pratimukhe sthitA . dIpo netrAturasyeva pratikUlAsi me dRDhA .
tadgaccha tvAnujAne ' dya yatheSTaM janakAtmaje . etA daza dizo bhadre kAryamasti na me tvayA .
kaH pumAMstu kule jAtaH striyaM paragRhoSitAm . tejasvI punarAdadyAtsuhRllobhena cetasA .
rAvaNAGkaparikliSTAM dRSTAM duSTena cakSuSA . kathaM tvAM punarAdadyAM kulaM vyapadizanmahat .
yadartha nirjitA me tvaM so ' yamAsAdito mayA . nAsti me tvayyabhiSvaGgo yatheSTaM gamyatAmiti .
tadadya vyAhRtaM bhadre mayaitatkRtabuddhinA . lakSmaNe vAtha bharate kuru buddhiM yathAsukham . zatrughne vAtha sugrIve rAkSase vA vibhISaNe . nivezaya manaH sIte yathA vA sukhamAtmanA .
nahi tvAM rAvaNo dRSTvA divyarUpAM manoramAm . marSayatyaciraM sIte svagRhe paryavasthitAm .
tataH priyAhazravaNA tadapriyaM priyAdupazrutya cirasya mAninI . mumoca bASpaM rudatI tadA bhRzaM gajendrahastAbhihateva vallarI .
tadA vRtravadhaM sarvamakhilena sa lakSmaNaH . kathayitvA narazreSThaH kathAzeSa pracakrame . tato hate mahAvIrye vRtre devabhayaMkare . brahmahatyAvRtaH zakraH saMjJAM lebhe na vRtrahA .
so ' ntamAzritya lokAnAM naSTasaMjJo vicetanaH . kAlaM tatrAvasatkaMcidveSTamAna ivoragaH .
atha naSTe sahasrAkSe udvignamabhavajjagat . bhUmizca dhvastasaMkAzA niHsnehA zuSkakAnanA . niHsrotasaste sarve tu hRdAzca saritastathA . saMkSobhazcaiva sattvAnAmanAvRSTikRto ' bhavat .
kSIyamANe tu loke ' sminsaMbhrAntanasaH surAH . yaduktaM viSNunA pUrvaM taM yajJaM samupAnayan .
tataH sarve suragaNAH sopAdhyAyAH saharSibhiH . taM dezaM samupAjagmuryavendro bhayamohitaH . te tu dRSTvA sahasrAkSamAvRtaM brahmahatyayA . taM puraskRtya devezamazvamedhaM pracakrire .
tato ' zvamedhaH suhAnmahendrasya mahAtmanaH . vavRte brahmahatyAyAH pAvanArthaM narezvara . tato yajJe samApte tu brahmahatyA mahAtmanaH . abhigamyAbravIdvAkyaM kva me sthAnaM vidhAsyatha . te tAmUcustato devAstuSTAH prItisamanvitAH . caturdhA vibhajAtmAnamAtmanaiva durAsade .
devAnAM bhASitaM zrutvA brahmahatyA mahAtmanAm . saMdadhau sthAnamanyatra varayAmAsa durvasA . ekenAMzena vatsyAmi pUrNodAsu nadISu vai . caturo vArSikAnmAsAndarpaghnI kAmacAriNI .
bhUmyAmahaM sarvakAlamekenAMzena sarvadA . vasiSyAmi na saMdehaH satyenaitadbravImi vaH . . yo ' yamaMzastRtIyo me strISu yauvanazAliSu . trirAtraM darpapUrNAsu vasiSye darpaghAtinI . hantAro brAhmaNAnye tu mRSApUrvamadUSakAn . tAMzcaturthena bhAgena saMzrayiSye sarurSabhAH .
pratyUcustAM tato devA yathA vadasi durvase . tathA bhavatu tatsarvaM sAdhayasva yadIpsitam .
tataH prItyAnvitA devAH sahasrAkSaM vavandire . vijvaraH pUtapApmA ca vAsavaH samapadyata .
prazAntaM ca jagatsarvaM sahasrAkSe pratiSThite . yajJaM cAdbhutasaMkAzaM tadA zakro ' bhyapUjayat .
IdRzo hyazvamedhasya prasAdo raghunandana . yajasva sumahAbhAga hayamedhena pArthiva .
iti lakSmaNavAkyamuttamaM nRpatiratIva manoharaM mahAtmA . paritoSamavApa hRSTacetAH sa nizamyendrasamAnavikramaujAH . .
pratigRhya tato ' strANi prahRSTavadanaH zuciH . gacchanneva ca kAkutstho vizvAmitramathAbravIt .
gRhItAstro ' smi bhagavan durAdharSaH surairapi . astrANAM tvahamicchAmi saMhArAn munipuGgava .
evaM bruvati kAkutsthe vizvAmitro mahAtapAH . saMhArAn vyAjahArAtha dhRtimAn suvrataH zuciH .
satyavantaM satyakIrtiM dhRSTaM rabhasameva ca . pratihArataraM nAma parAGmukhamavAGmukham . lakSyAlakSyAvimau caiva dRDhanAbhasunAbhako . dazAkSazatavaktrau ca dazazIrSazatodarau . padmanAbhamahAnAbhau dundunAbhasvanAbhako . jyotiSa zakunaM caiva nairAsyavimalAvubhau . yaugaMdharavinidrau ca daityapramathanau tathA . zucibAhurmahAbAhuniSkalivirucastathA . sArcimAlI dhRtimAlI vRttimAn rucirastathA . pitryaH saumanasazcaiva vidhUtamakarAvubhau . paravIraM ratiM caiva dhanadhAnyau ca rAghava . kAmarUpaM kAmaruciM mohamAvaraNaM tathA . jRmbhakaM sarpanAthaM ca panthAnavaruNau tathA . kRzAzvatanayAn rAma bhAsvarAn kAmarUpiNaH . pratIccha mama bhadraM te pAtrabhUto ' si rAghava .
bADhamityeva kAkutsthaH prahaSTenAntarAtmanA . divyabhAsvaradehAzca mUrtimantaH sukhapradAH . kecidaGgArasadRzAH kecit dhUmopamAstathA . candrArkasadRzAH kecit prahvAJjalipuTAstathA . rAmaM prAJjalayo bhUtvAbruvan madhurabhASiNaH . ime sma narazArdUla zAdhi kiM karavAma te .
gamyatAmiti tAnAha yatheyaM raghunandanaH . mAnasAH kAryakAleSu sAhAyyaM me kariSyatha .
atha te rAmAmantrya kRtvA cApi pradakSiNam . evamastviti kAkutsthamuktvA jagmuryathAgatam . sa ca tAn rAghavo jJAtvA vizvAmitraM mahAmunim . gacchannevAtha madhuraM zlakSNaM vacanamabravIt . kimetanmeghasaMkAzaM parvatasyAvidUrataH . vRkSakhaNDamito bhAti paraM kautUhalaM hi me .
darzanIyaM mRgAkIrNaM manoharamatIva ca . nAnAprakAraiH zakunairvalgubhASairalaMkRtam .
niHsRtAH smo munizreSTha kAntArAd romaharSaNAt . anayA tvavagacchAmi dezasya sukhavattayA .
sarvaM me zaMsa bhagavan kasyAzramapadaM tvidam . samprAptA yatra te pApA brahmaghnA duSTacAriNaH . tava yajJasya vighnAya durAtmAno mahAmune . bhagavaMstasya ko deza : sA yatra tava yAjJikI . rakSitavyA kriyA brahman mayA vadhyAzca rAkSasAH . etat sarvaM munizreSTha zrotumicchAmyahaM prabho .
visRjya tu suhRdvarga buddhyA nizcitya rAghavaH . samIpe dvA : sthamAsInamidaM vacanamabravIt .
zIghramAnaya saumitri lakSmaNaM zubhalakSaNam . bharataM ca mahAbhAgaM zatrughnamaparAjitam .
rAmasya vacanaM zrutvA dvA : stho mUrdhni kRtAJjaliH . lakSmaNasya gRhaM gatvA pravivezAnivAritaH .
uvAca sumahAtmAnaM vardhayitvA kRtAJjaliH . draSTumicchati rAjA tvAM gamyatAM tatra mA ciram .
bADhamityeva saumitriH kRtvA rAghavazAsanam . prAdravadrathamAruhya rAghavasya nivezanam .
prayAntaM lakSmaNaM dRSTvA dvA : stho bharatamantikAt . uvAca bharataM tatra vardhayitvA kRtAJjaliH . vinayAvanato bhUtvA rAjA tvAM draSTumicchati .
bharatastu vacaH zrutvA dvAHsthAdrAmasamIritam . utpapAtAsanAttUrNaM padbhyAmeva mahAbalaH .
dRSTvA prayAntaM bharataM tvaramANaH kRtAJjaliH . zatrughnabhavanaM gatvA tato vAkyamuvAca ha .
ehyAgaccha raghuzreSTha rAjA tvAM draSTumicchati . gato hi lakSmaNaH pUrvaM bharatazca mahAyazAH .
zrutvA tu vacanaM tasya zatrughnaH paramAsanAt . zirasA vandya dharaNI prayayau yatra rAghavaH .
dvAHsthastvAgamya rAmAya sarvAneva kRtAJjaliH . nivedayAmAsa tathA bhrAtRnsvAnsamupasthitAn .
kumArAnAgatAJchrutvA cintAvyAkulitendriyaH . avAGmukho dInamanA dvAHsthaM vacanamabravIt . pravezaya kumArAMstvaM matsamIpaM tvarAnvitaH . eteSu jIvitaM mahyamete prANAH priyA mama .
AjJaptAstu narendreNa kumArAH zuklavAsasaH . prahvAH prAJjalayo bhUtvA vivizuste samAhitAH .
te tu dRSTvA mukhaM tasya sagrahaM zazinaM yathA . saMdhyAgatamivAdityaM prabhayA parivarjitam . vASpapUrNe ca nayane dRSTvA rAmasya dhImataH . hatazobhaM yathA padmaM mukhaM vIkSya ca tasya te .
tato ' bhivAdya tvaritAH pAdau rAmasya mUrdhabhiH . tasthuH samAhitAH sarve rAmastvazrUNyavartayat .
tAnpariSvajya bAhubhyAmutthApya ca mahAbalaH . AsaneSvAsatetyuktvA tato vAkyaM jagAda ha .
bhavanto mama sarvasvaM bhavanto jIvitaM mama . bhavadbhizca kRtaM rAjyaM pAlayAmi narezvarAH . bhavantaH kRtazAstrArthA buddhyA ca pariniSThitAH . saMbhUya ca madartho ' yamanveSTavyo narezvarAH .
tathA vadati kAkutsthe avadhAnaparAyaNAH . udvignamanasaH sarve kiM nu rAjAbhidhAsyati .
rAmastu sahasaumitriH sutIkSNenAbhipUjitaH . pariNAmya nizAM tatra prabhAte pratyabudhyata .
utthAya ca yathAkAlaM rAghavaH saha sItayA . upaspRzya suzItena toyenotpalagandhinA . atha te ' gni surAMzcaiva vaidehI rAmalakSmaNau . kAlyaM vidhivadabhyarcya tapasvizaraNe vane . udayantaM dinakaraM dRSTvA vigatakalmaSAH . sutIkSNamabhigamyedaM zlakSNaM vacanamabruvan .
sukhoSitAH sma bhagavaMstvayA pUjyena pUjitAH . ApRcchAmaH prayAsyAmo munayastvarayanti naH .
tvarAmahe vayaM draSTuM kRtsnamAzramamaNDalam . RSINAM puNyazIlAnAM daNDakAraNyavAsinAm .
abhyanujJAtumicchAmaH sahaibhirmunipuMgavaiH . dharmanityaistapodAntairvizikhairiva pAvakaiH .
aviSahyAtapo yAvat sUryo nAtivirAjate . amArgeNAgatAM lakSmI prApyevAnvayavarjitaH . tAvadicchAmahe gantumityuktvA caraNau muneH . vavande sahasaumitriH sItayA saha rAghavaH .
tau sospRzantau caraNAvutthApya munipuMgavaH . gADhamAzliSya sasnehamidaM vacanamabravIt .
ariSTaM gaccha panthAnaM rAma saumitriNA saha . sItayA cAnayA sArdhaM chAyayevAnuvRttayA .
pazyAzramapadaM ramyaM daNDakAraNyavAsinAm . eSAM tapasvinAM vIra tapasA bhAvitAtmanAm .
suprAjyaphalamUlAni puSpitAni vanAni ca . prazastamRgayUthAni zAntapakSigaNAni ca . phullapaGkajakhaNDAni prasannasalilAni ca . kAraNDavavikIrNAni taTAkAni sarAMsi ca . drakSyase dRSTiramyANi giriprasravaNAni ca . ramaNIyAnyaraNyAni mayUrAbhirutAni ca .
gamyatAM vatsa saumitre bhavAnapi ca gacchatu . AgantavyaM ca te dRSTvA punarevAzramaM prati .
evamuktastathetyuktvA kAkutsthaH sahalakSmaNaH . pradakSiNaM muniM kRtvA prasthAtumupacakrame .
tataH zubhatare tUNI dhanuSI cAyatekSaNAH . dadau sItA tayordhAtroH khaGgau ca vimalau tataH .
Abadhya ca zubhe tUNI cApe cAdAya sasvane . niSkrAntAvAzramAd gantumubhau tau rAmalakSmaNau .
zIghraM tau rUpasampannAvanujJAtau maharSiNA . prasthitau dhRtacApAsI sItayA saha rAghavau .
zRNu rAjanmahAsatva yadarthamahamAgataH . pitAmahena devena preSito ' smi mahAbala .
tavAhaM pUrvake bhAve putraH parapuraMjaya . mAyAsaMbhAvito vIra kAla : sarvasamAharaH .
pitAmahazca bhagavAnAha lokapatiH prabhuH . samayaste kRtaH saumya lokAnsaMparirakSitum .
sakSipya hi purA lokAnmAyayA svayameva hi . mahArNave zayAno ' psu mAM tvaM pUrvamajIjanaH .
bhogavantaM tato nAgamanantamudakezayam . mAyayA janayitvA tvaM dvau ca sattvau mahAbalau . madhuM ca kaiTabhaM caiva yayorasthicayairvatA . iyaM parvatasaMbAdhA medinI cAbhavattadA .
padma divye ' rkasaMkAze nAbhyAmutpAdya mAmapi . prAjApatyaM tvayA karma mayi sarva nivezitam .
so ' haM saMnyastabhAro hi tvAmupAsya jagatpatim . rakSAM vidhatsva bhUteSu mama tejaskaro bhavAn . . . .
tatastvamasi durdharSAttasmAdbhAvAtsanAtanAt . rakSAM vidhAsyanbhUtAnAM viSNutvamuphjagmivAn .
adityAM vIryavAnputro bhrAtRRNAM vIryavardhanaH . samutpanneSu kRtyeSu teSAM sAhyAya kalpase .
sa tvamujjAsyamAnAsu prajAsu jagatovara . rAvaNasya vadhAkAGkSI mAnuSeSu mano ' dadhAH .
dazavarSasahasrANi dazavarSazatAni ca . kRtvA vAsasya niyamaM svayamevAtmanA purA .
sa tvaM manomayaH putraH pUrNAyurmAnuSeSviha . kAlo naravarazreSTha samIpamupavartitum .
yadi bhUyo mahArAja prajA icchasyupAsitum . vasa vA vIra bhadraM te evamAha pitAmahaH . atha vA vijigISA te suralokAya rAghava . sanAthA viSNunA devA bhavantu vigatajvarAH .
zrutvA pitAmahenoktaM vAkyaM kAlasamIritam . rAghavaH prahasanvAkyaM sarvasaMhAramabravIt .
zrutvA me devadevasya vAkyaM paramamadbhutam . prItirhi mahatI jAtA tavAgamanasaMbhavA . trayANAmapi lokAnAM kAryArtha mama saMbhavaH . bhadraM te ' stu gamiSyAmi yata evAhamAgataH .
hRdgato hyasi saMprApto na me tatra vicAraNA . mayA hi sarvakRtyeSu devAnAM vazavartinAm . sthAtavyaM sarvasaMhAra yathA hyAha pitAmahaH .
tAMstu te saMpravakSyAmi prekSamANasya yUthapAna . rAghavArthe parAkrAntA ye na rakSanti jIvitam .
snigdhA yasya bahuvyAmA dIrghalAMgUlamAzritAH . tAmrAH pItAH zvetAH prakIrNA ghorakarmaNaH . pragRhItAH prakAzante sUryasyeva marIcayaH . pRthivyAM cAnukRSyante haro nAmaiSa vAnaraH . yaM pRSThato ' nugacchanti zatazo ' tha sahasrazaH . vRkSAnudyamya sahasA laGkArohaNatatparAH . yUthapA harirAjasya kiMkarAH samupasthitAH .
nIlAniva mahAmeghAMstiSThato yAMstu pazyasi . asitAJjanasaMkAzAnyuddhe satyaparAkramAn . asaMkhyeyAnanirdezyAnparaM pAramivodadheH . parvateSu ca ye kecidviSayeSu nadISu ca . ete tvAmabhivartante rAjanRkSAH sudAruNAH . eSAM madhye sthito rAjA bhImAkSo bhImadarzanaH . parjanya iva jImUtaiH samantAtparivAritaH . RkSavantaM girizreSThamadhyAste narmadAM piban .
sarvANAmadhipatidhUmro nAmaiSa yUthapaH . yavIyAnasya tu bhrAtA pazyainaM parvatopamam . bhrAtrA samAno rUpeNa viziSTazca parAkrame . sa eSa jAmbavAnAma mahAyUthapayUthapaH . prazAnto guruvartI ca saMprahAreSvamarSaNaH .
etena sAhyaM tu mahattkRtaM zakrasya dhImatA . devAsure jAmbavatA labdhAzca bahavo varAH .
Aruhya parvatAgrebhyo mahAbhravipulAH zilAH . muzcanti vipulAkArA na mRtyorudvijanti ca . rAkSasAnAM ca sadRzAH pizAcAnAM ca romazAH . etasya sainyA bahavo vicarantyamitaujasaH .
ya enamabhisaMrabdhaM plavamAnamavasthitam . prekSante vAnarAH sarve sthitaM yUthapayUthapam . eSa rAjansahasrAkSaM paryupAste harIzvaraH . balena balasaMyukto rambho nAmaiSa yUthapaH .
yaH sthitaM yojane zailaM gacchanpArzvena sevate . UrdhvaM tathaiva kAyena gataH prApnoti yojanam . yasmAttu paramaM rUpaM catuSpAtsu na vidyate . zrutaH saMnAdano nAma vAnarANAM pitAmahaH . yena yuddhaM tadA dattaM raNe zakrasya dhImatA . parAjayazca na prAptaH so ' yaM yUthapayUthapaH .
yasya vikramamANasya zakrasyeva parAkramaH . eSa gandharvakanyAyAmutpannaH kRSNavartmanA . tadA devAsure yuddhe sAhyAtha tridivaukasAm . yatra vaizravaNo rAjA jambUmupaniSevate . yo rAjA parvatendrANAM bahukiMnarasevinAm . vihArasukhado nityaM bhrAtuste rAkSasAdhipa . tatraiSa ramate zrImAnbalavAnvAnarottamaH . yuddheSvakatthano nityaM krathano nAma yUthapaH . vRtaH koTisahasreNa harINAM samavasthitaH . eSaivAzaMsate laGkA svenAnIkena marditum .
yo gaGgAmanuparyeti trAsayangajayUthapAn . hastinAM vAnarANAM ca pUrvavairamanusmaran . eSa yUthapatirnetA garjanigariguhAzayaH . gajAnrodhayate vanyAnArujaMzca mahIruhAn . harINAM vAhinImukhyo nadIM haimavatImanu . uzIrabIjamAzritya mandaraM parvatottamam . ramate vAnarazreSTho divi zakra iva svayam . enaM zatasahasrANAM sahasramabhivartate .28 . . vIryavikramadRptAnAM nardatAM bAhuzAlinAm . sa eSa netA caiteSAM vAnarANAM mahAtmanAm .29 . . sa eSa durdharo rAjanpramAthI nAma yUthapaH . vAtenevoddhataM meghaM yamenamanupazyasi . anIkamapi saMrabdhaM vAnarANAM tarasvinAm . udbhUtamaruNAbhAsaM pavanena samantataH . vivartamAnaM bahuzo ya tadbahulaM rajaH .
ete sitamukhA ghorA golAGgalA mahAbalAH . zataM zatasahasrANi dRSTvA vai setubandhanam . golAGgulaM mahArAja gavAkSaM nAma yUthapam . parivAryAbhinardante laGkAM marditumojasA .
bhramarAcaritA yatra sarvakAlaphaladrumAH . yaM sUryastulyavarNAbhamanuparyeti parvatam . yasya bhAsA sadA bhAnti tadvarNA mRgapakSiNaH . yasya prasthaM mahAtmAno na tyajanti maharSayaH . sarvakAmaphalA vRkSAH sarve phalasamanvitAH . madhUni ca mahArhANi yasminparvatasattame . tatraiSa ramate rAjanamye kAJcanaparvate . mukhyo vAnaramukhyAnAM kesarI nAma yUthapaH .
SaSTirgirisahasrANi ramyAH kAJcanaparvatAH . teSAM madhye girivarastvamivAnagha rakSasAm .
tatraike kapilAH zvetAstAmrAsyA madhupiGgalAH . nivasantyantimagirau tIkSNadaMSTrA nakhAyudhAH . siMhA iva caturdaSTrA vyAghrA iva durAsadAH . sarve vaizvAnarasamA jvaladAzIviSopamAH . sudIrghAJcitalAphUlA mattamAtaMgasaMnibhAH . mahAparvatasaMkAzA mahAjImUtaniHsvanAH . vRttapiGgalanetrA hi mahAbhImagatisvanAH . . mardayantIva te sarve tasthurlaGkAM samIkSya te .
eSa caiSAmadhipatirmadhye tiSThati vIryavAn . jayArthI nityamAdityamupatiSThati vIryavAn . nAmnA pRthivyAM vikhyAto rAjazatabalIti yaH .
eSaivAzaMsate laGkAM svenAnIkena marditum . vikrAnto balarAJchUraH pauruSe sve vyavasthitaH . .45 rAmapriyArthaM prANAnAM dayAM na kurute hariH .
gajo gavAkSo gavayo nalo nIlazca vAnaraH . ekaikameva yodhAnAM koTibhirdazabhirvRtaH .
tathAnye va. razreSThA vindhyaparvatavAsinaH . na zakyante bahutvAttu saMkhyAtuM laghuvikramAH .
sarve mahArAja mahAprabhAvAH sarve mahAzailanikAzakAyAH . sarve samarthAH pRthivIM kSaNena kartuM pravidhvastavikIrNazailAm .
tvaramANastato gatvA janasthAnAdakampanaH . pravizya laGkAM vegena rAvaNaM vAkyamabravIt .
janasthAnasthitA rAjan rAkSasA bahavo hatAH ! kharazca nihataH saMkhye kathaMcidahamAgataH .
evamukto dazagrIvaH kruddhaH saMraktalocanaH . akampanamuvAcedaM nirdahanniva tejasA .
kena bhImaM janasthAnaM hataM mama parAsunA . ko hi sarveSu lokeSu gati nAdhigamiSyati .
sa hi me vipriyaM kRtvA zakyaM maghavatA sukham . prAptuM vaizravaNenApi na yamena ca viSNunA .
kAlasya cApyahaM kAlo daheyamapi pAvakam . mRtyu maraNadharmeNa saMyojayitumutsahe .
vAtasya tarasA vegaM nihantumapi cotsahe . daheyamapi saMkruddhastejasA ' ' dityapAvakau .
tathA kruddhaM dazagrIvaM kRtAJjalirakampanaH . bhayAt saMdigdhayA vAcA rAvaNaM yAcate ' bhayam .
dazagrIvo ' bhayaM tasmai pradadau rakSasAM varaH . sa visrabdho ' bravId vAkyamasaMdigdhamakampanaH .
