atha ghoSaH sutumulo harINAM samajAyata . vRkSAnArujatAM caiva gurvI gRhNatAM zilAH . nadatAM rAkSasAnAM ca vAnarANAM ca garjatAm . ubhe pramudite sainye rakSogaNavanaukasAm . . vegitAnAM samarthAnAmanyonyavadhakAkSiNAm . parasparaM cAhvayatAM ninAdaH zrUyate mahAn .
