prasthApya tu sa zatrughnaM bhrAtRbhyAM saha rAghavaH . pramumoda sukhI rAjyaM dharmeNa paripAlayan .
tataH katipayAhaHsu vRddho jAnapado dvijaH . mRtaM bAlamupAdAya rAjadvAramupAgamat .
kiM nu me duSkRtaM karma purA dehAntare kRtam . rudanbahuvidhA vAcaH snehaduHkhasamanvitaH . asakRtputra putreti vAkyametaduvAca ha . kiM nu me duSkRtaM karma purA dehAntare kRtam . yadahaM putramekaM tu pazyAmi nidhanaM gatam .
aprAptayauvanaM bAlaM paJcavarSasahasrakam . akAle kAlamApannaM mama duHkhAya putraka . alpairahobhinidhanaM gamiSyAmi na saMzayaH . ahaM ca jananI caiva tava zokena putraka .
na smarAmyanRtaM hyuktaM na ca hiMsAM smarAmyaham . sarveSAM prANinAM pApaM na smarAmi kadAcana .7 . . kenAdya duSkRtenAyaM bAla eva mamAtmajaH . akRtvA pitRkAryANi gato vaivasvatakSayam .
nedRzaM dRSTapUrvaM me zrutaM vA ghoradarzanam . mRtyuraprAptakAlAnAM rAmasya viSaye hyayam .
