soDhuM na ca samartho ' haM yuddhakAmasya saMyuge . sugrIvasya ca saMrambhaM hInagrIvasya garjitam .
na ca kAryo viSAdaste rAghavaM prati matkRte . dharmajJazca kRtajJazca kathaM pApaM kariSyati .
