ahaM hyAjisthitasyAsya kariSyAmi yadIpsitam . vRkSairmuSTiprahAraizca pIDitaH pratiyAsyati .
na me garvitamAyastaM sahiSyati durAtmavAn . kRtaM tAre sahAyatvaM darzitaM sauhRdaM mayi .
