purANi na ca taM zekurdAnavAH prativIkSitum . zaraM kAlAgnisaMyuktaM viSNusomasamAyutam .
purANi dagdhavantaM taM devI yAtA pravIkSitum . bAlamaGkagataM kRtvA svayaM paJcazikhaM punaH .
