na ca zakto ' smi te kartuM moghamAgamanaM khaga . na cAzAmasya viprarSevitathIkartumutsahe . tat tu dAsyAmi yat kAryamidaM sampAdayiSyati . abhigamya hatAzo hi nivRtto dahate kulam .
nAtaH paraM vainateya kiMcit pApiSThamucyate . yathAzAnAzanAlloke dehi nAstIti vA vacaH .
hatAzo hyakRtArthaH san hataH sambhAvito naraH . hinasti tasya putrAMzca pautrAMzcAkurvato hitam .
tasmAccaturNAM vaMzAnAM sthApayitrI sutA mama . iyaM surasutaprakhyA sarvadharmopacAyinI .
pradAsyanti nRpA sadA devamanuSyANAmasurANAM ca gAlava . kAdikSatA rUpato bAlA sutA me pratigRhyatAm .
asyAH zulkaM rAjyamapi dhruvam . kiM punaH zyAmakarNAnAM hayAnAM dve catuH zate .
sa bhavAn pratigRhNAtu mamaitAM mAdhavIM sutAm . ahaM dauhitravAn syAM vai vara eSa mama prabho .
pratigRhya ca tAM kanyAM gAlavaH saha pakSiNA . punardrakSyAva ityuktvA pratasthe saha kanyayA .
upalabdhamidaM dvAramazvAnAmiti cANDajaH . uktvA gAlavamApRcchya jagAma bhavanaM svakam .
gate patagarAje tu gAlavaH saha kanyayA . cintayAnaH kSamaM dAne rAjJAM vai zulkato ' gamat .
so ' gacchanmanasekSvAkuM haryazvaM rAjasattamam . ayodhyAyAM mahAvIryaM caturaGgabalAnvitam .
kozadhAnyabalopetaM priyapauraM dvijapriyam . prajAbhikAmaM zAmyantaM kurvANaM tapa uttamam .
tamuvAgamya vipraH sa haryazvaM gAlavo ' bravIt . kanyeyaM mama rAjendra prasavaiH kulavardhinI .
iyaM zulkena bhAryArthaM haryazva pratigRhyatAm . zulkaM te kIrtayiSyAmi tacchrutvA sampradhAryatAm .
yudhiSThira uvAca nApadAmasti maryAdA na nimittaM na kAraNam . dharmastu vibhajatyarthamubhayoH puNyapApayoH .
bhIma uvAca prAtikAmyanayat kRSNAM sabhAyAM preSyavat tadA . na mayA nihatastatra tena prAptAH sma saMzayam .
arjuna uvAca vAcastIkSNAsthibhedinyaH sUtaputreNa bhASitAH . atitIvrA mayA kSAntAstena prAptAH sma saMzayam .
sahadeva uvAca zakunistvAM yadAjaiSIdakSadyUtena bhArata . sa mayA na hatastatra tena prAptAH sma saMzayam .
vaizampAyana uvAca tato yudhiSThiro rAjA nakulaM vAkyamabravIt . Aruhya vRkSaM mAdreya nirIkSasva dizo daza .
pAnIyamantike pazya vRkSAMzcApyudakAzritAn . ete hi bhrAtaraH zrAntAstava tAta pipAsitAH .
nakulastu tathetyuktvA zIghramAruhya pAdapam . abravId bhrAtaraM jyeSThamabhivIkSya samantataH .
pazyAmi bahulAn rAjan vRkSAnudakasaMzrayAn . sArasAnAM ca nidimatrodakamasaMzayam .
tato ' bravIt satyadhRtiH kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . gaccha saumya tataH zIghraM tUNaiH pAnIyamAnaya .
nakulastu tathetyuktvA bhrAturyeSThasya zAsanAt . prAdravad yatra pAnIyaM zIghraM caivAnvapadyata .
sa dRSTvA vimalaM toyaM sArasaiH parivAritam . pAtukAmastato vAcamantarikSAt sa zuzruve .
yakSa uvAca mA tAta sAhasaM kArmima pUrvaparigrahaH . praznAnuktvA tu mAdreya tataH piba harasva ca .
anAdRtya tu tad vAkyaM nakulaH supipAsitaH . apibacchItalaM toyaM pItvA ca nipapAta ha .
cirAyamANe nakule kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . abravId bhrAtaraM vIraM sahadevamariMdamam .
bhrAtA hi cirayAto naH sahadeva tavAcajaH . tathaivAnaya sodaryaM pAnIyaM ca tvamAnaya .
sahadevastathetyuktvA tAM dizaM pratyapadyata . dadarza ca hataM bhUmau bhrAtaraM nakulaM tadA .
bhrAtRzokAbhisaMtaptastRSayA ca prapIDitaH . abhidudrAva pAnIyaM tato vAgabhyabhASata .
mA tAta sAhasaM kArmima pUrvaparigrahaH . praznAnuktvA yathAkAmaM pivasva ca harasva ca .
anAhRtya tu tad vAkyaM sahadevaH pipAsitaH . apibacchItalaM toyaM pItvA ca nipapAta ha .
athAbravIt sa vijayaM kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . bhrAtarau te ciragatau bIbhatso zatrukarzana .
tau caivAnaya bhadraM te pAnIyaM ca tvamAnaya . tvaM hi nastAta sarveSAM duHkhitAnAmapAzrayaH .
evamukto guDAkezaH pragRhya sazaraM dhanuH . AmuktakhaGgo medhAvI tat saraH pratyapadyata .
tataH puruSazArdUlo pAnIyaharaNe gatau . tau dadarza hatau tatra bhrAtarau zvetavAhanaH .
prasuptAviva tau dRSTvA narasiMhaH suduHkhitaH . dhanurudyamya kaunteyo vyalokayat tad vanam .
nApazyat tatra kiJcit sa bhUtamasmin mahAvane . savyasAcI tataH zrAntaH pAnIyaM so ' bhyadhAvata .
abhidhAvaMstato vAkyamantarikSAt sa zuzruve . kimAsIdasi pAnIyaM tacchakyaM balAt tvayA . .
kaunteya yadi praznAMstAn mayoktAn pratipatsyase . tataH pAsyasi pAnIyaM hariSyasi ca bhArata .
vAritastvabravIt pArtho dRzyamAno nivAraya . yAvad bANairvinirbhinnaH puna : vaM vadiSyasi .
evamuktvA tataH pArthaH zarairastrAnumantritaiH . pravavarSa dizaH kRtsnA : zabdavedhaM ca darzayan .
karNinAlIkanArAcAnutsRjan bharatarSabha . sa tvamoghAniSUna muktvA tRSNAyAbhiprapIDitaH .
anekairiSusaGghAtairantarikSe vavarSa ha .
yakSa uvAca kiM vighAtena te pArtha praznAnuktvA tataH piba .
anuktvA ca piban praznAn pItvaiva na bhaviSyasi . evamuktastataH pArthaH savyasAcI dhanaMjayaH . avajJAyaiva tAM vAcaM pItvaiva nipapAta ha .
athAbravId bhImasenaM kuntIputro yudhiSThiH . nakulaH sahadevazca bIbhatsuzca paraMtapa ! ciraM gatAstoyahetorna cAgacchanti bhArata . tAMzcaivAnaya bhadraM te pAnIyaM ca tvamAnaya .
bhImasenastathetyuktvA taM dezaM pratyapadyata . yatra te puruSavyAghrA bhrAtaro ' sya nipAtitAH . tAn dRSTvA duHkhito bhImastRSayA ca prapIDitaH .
amanyata mahAbAhuH karma tad yakSarakSasAm . sa cintayAmAsa tadA yoddhavyaM dhruvamadya vai .
pAsyAmi tAvat pAnIyamiti pArtho vRkodaraH . tato ' bhyadhAvat pAnIyaM pipAsuH puruSarSabhaH .
yakSa uvAca mA tAta sAhasaM kArmima pUrvaparigrahaH . praznAnuktvA tu kaunteya tataH piba harasva ca .
evamuktastadA bhImo yakSeNAmitatejasA . anuktvaiva tu tAn praznAn pItvaiva nipapAta ha .
tataH kuntIsuto rAjA pracintya puruSarSabhaH . samutthAya mahAbAhurdahyamAnena cetamA . vyapetajananirghoSaM praviveza mahAvanam . rurubhizca varAhaizca pakSibhizca niSevitam .
nIlabhAsvaravarNazca pAdaiparupazobhitam . bhramarairupagItaM ca pakSibhizca mahAyazAH .
sa gacchan kAnane tasmin hemajAlapariSkRtam . dadarza tat saraH zrImAn vizvakarmakRtaM yathA .
upetaM nalinIjAlaiH sindhuvAraiH savetasaiH . ketakaiH karavIraizca pippalaizcaiva saMvRtam . zramArtastadupAgamya saro dRSTvAtha vismitaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca kathaM mRdau kathaM tIkSNe mahApakSe ca pArthiva . Adau varteta nRpatistanme brUhi pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . bRhaspatezca saMvAdamindrasya ca yudhiSThira .
bRhaspati devapatirabhivAdya kRtAJjaliH . upasaMgamya papraccha vAsavaH paravIrahA . .
indra uvAca ahiteSu kathaM brahman pravarteyamatandritaH . asamucchidya caivaitAn niyaccheyamupAyataH .
senayorvyatiSaGgeNa jayaH sAdhAraNo bhavet . kiMkurvANaM na mAM jahyAjjvalitA zrIH pratApinI .
tato dharmArthakAmAnAM kuzalaH pratibhAnavAn . rAjadharmavidhAnajJaH pratyuvAca puraMdaram .
bRhaspatiruvAca na jAtu kalahenecchenniyantumapakAriNaH . bAlairAsevitaM hyetad yadama ! yadakSamA .
na zatrurvivRtaH kAryo vadhamasyAbhikAGgatA . krodhaM bhayaM ca harSaM ca niyamya svayamAtmani .
amitramupaseveta vizvastavadavizvasan . priyameva vadennityaM nApriyaM kiMcidAcaret .
viramecchuSkavairebhyaH kaNThAyAsAMzca varjayet . yathA vaitaMsiko yukto dvijAnAM sadRzasvanaH . tAn dvijAn kurute vazyAMstathA yukto mahIpatiH . vazaM copanayecchan nihanyAcca puraMdara .
na nityaM paribhUyArIn sukhaM svapiti vAsava . jAgaryeva hi duSTAtmA saMkare ' gnirivotthitaH .
na saMnipAtaH kartavyaH sAmAnye vijaye sati . vizvAsyaivopasannArtho vaze kRtvA ripuH prabho .
sampradhArya sahAmAtyairmantravidbhirmahAtmabhiH . upekSyamANo ' vajJAto hRdayenAparAjitaH . athAsya praharet kAle kiMcidvicalite pade . daNDaM ca dUSayedasya puruSairAptakAribhiH .
AdimadhyAvasAnajJaH pracchannaM ca vidhArayet . balAni dUSayedasya jAnanneva pramANataH . bhedenopapradAnena saMsRjedauSadhaistathA . na tvevaM khalu saMsargaM rocayedaribhiH saha .
dIrghakAlamapIkSeta nihanyAdeva zAtravAn . kAlAkAGkSIhi kSapayed yathA vizrambhamApnuyuH . na sadyo ' rIn vihanyAcca draSTavyo vijayo dhruvaH .
na zalyaM vA ghaTayati na vAcA kurute vraNam . prApte na praharet kAle na ca saMvartate punaH . hantukAmasya devendra puruSasya ripUn prati .
yo hi kAlo vyatikrAmet puruSaM kAlakAkSiNam . durlabhaH sa punastena kAlaH karmacikIrSuNA .
ojazca janayedeva saMgRhNan sAdhusammatam . akAle sAdhayenmitraM na ca prApte prapIDayet .
vihAya kAmaM krodhaM ca tathAhaMkArameva ca . yukto vivaramanvicchedahitAnAM punaH punaH .
mArdavaM daNDa AlasyaM pramAdazca surottama . mAyAH suvihitAH zakra sAdayantyavicakSaNam .
nihatyaitAni catvAri mAyAM prati vidhAya ca . tataH zaknoti zatrUNAM prahartumavicArayan .
yadaivaikena zakyeta guhyaM kartuM tadAcaret . yacchanti sacivA guhyaM mitho vizrAvayantyapi .
azakyamiti kRtvA vA tato ' nyaiH saMvidaM caret . brahmadaNDamadRSTeSu dRSTeSu caturaGgiNIm .
bhedaM ca prathamaM yujyAt tUSNIM daNDaM tathaiva ca . kAle prayojayed rAjA tasmiMstasmiMstadA tadA .
praNipAtaM ca gaccheta kAle zatrorbalIyasaH . yukto ' sya vadhamanvicchedapramattaH pramAdyataH .
praNipAtena dAnena vAcA madhurayA brUvan . amitramapi seveta na ca jAtu vizaGkayet . .3
sthAnAni zaGkitAnAM ca nityameva vivarjayet . na ca teSvAzvased rAjA jAgratIha nirAkRtAH .
na hyato duSkaraM karma kiMcidasti surottamA yathA vividhavRttAnAmaizvaryamamarAdhipa . .
tathA vividhavRttAnAmapi sambhava ucyate . yatate yogamAsthAya mitrAmitraM vicArayet .
mRdumapyavamanyante tIkSNAdudvijate janaH mA tIkSNo mA mRdurbhUstvaM tIkSNo bhava mRdurbhava .
yathA vapre vegavati sarvataH samplutodake . nityaM vivaraNAd bAdhastathA rAjyaM pramAdyataH .
na bahUnabhiyuJjIta yaugapadyena zAtravAn . sAmnA dAnena bhedena daNDena ca puraMdara . ekaikameSAM niSpiSya ziSTeSu nipuNaM caret . na tu zakto ' pi medhAvI sarvAnevArabhennRpaH .
yadAsyAnmahatI senA hayanAgarathAkulA . padAtiyantrabahulA anuraktA SaDaginI . yadA bahuvidhAM vRddhiM manyeta pratilomataH . tadA vivRtya prahared dasyUnAmavicArayan .
na sAmadaNDopaniSat prazasyate na mArdavaM zatruSu yAtrikaM sadA . na sasyaghAto na ca saMkarakriyA na cApi bhUyaH prakRtervicAraNA .
mAyAvibhedAnupasarjanAni tathaiva pApaM na yazaHprayogAt . AptairmanuSyarUpacArayeta pureSu rASTreSu ca samprayuktAn .
purApi caiSAmanusRtya bhUmipAH pureSu bhogAnakhilAn jayanti . pureSu nIti vihitAM yathAvidhi prayojayanto balavRtrasUdana .
pradAya gUDhAni vasUnI rAjan pracchidya bhogAnavadhAya ca svAn . duSTAn svadoSairiti kIrtayitvA pureSu rASTreSu ca yojayanti .
tathaiva cAnyairapi zAstravedibhiH svalaMkRtaiH zAstravidhAnadRSTibhiH . suzikSitairbhASyakathAvizAradaiH pareSu kRtyAmupadhArayecca .
indra uvAca kAni liGgAni duSTasya bhavanti dvijasattama . kathaM duSTaM vijAnIyAmetat pRSTo vadasva me .
bRhaspatiruvAca parokSamaguNAnAha sadguNAnabhyasUyate . parairvA kIrtyamAneSu tUSNImAste parAGmukhaH .
tUSNImbhAve ' pi vijJeyaM na cedbhavati kAraNam . niHzvAsaM coSThasaMdaMzaM zirasazca prakampanam .
karotyabhIkSNaM saMsRSTamasaMsRSTazca bhASate . adRSTito na kurute dRze naivAbhibhASate .
pRthagetya samaznAti nedamadya yathAvidhi . Asane zayane yAne bhAvA lakSyA vizeSataH .
ArtirAte priye prItiretAvanmitralakSaNam . viparItaM tu boddhavyamarilakSaNameva tat .
etAnyeva yathoktAni budhyethAstridazAdhipa . puruSANAM praduSTAnAM svabhAvo balavattaraH .
iti duSTasya vijJAnamuktaM te surasattama . nizamya zAstratattvArthaM yathAvadamarezvara .
bhISma uvAca sa tadvacaH zatrunibarhaNe rata stathA cakArAvitathaM bRhaspateH . cacAra kAle vijayAya cArihA vazaM ca zatrUnanayat puraMdaraH .
vaizampAyana uvAca niryAya nagarAcchUrA vyUDhAnIkAH prahAriNaH . trigartAnaspRzan matsyAH sUrye pariNate sati .
te trigartAzca matsyAzca saMrabdhA yuddhadurmadAH . anyonyamabhigarjanto goSu gRddhA mahAbalAH .
bhImAzca mattamAtaGgAstomarAGkuzanoditAH . grAmaNIyaiH samArUDhAH kuzalairhastisAdibhiH .
teSAM samAgamo ghorastumulo lohamarSaNaH . ghnatAM parasparaM rAjan yamarASTravivardhanaH . devAsurasamo rAjannAsIt sUrye ' valambati . padAtirathanAgendrahayArohabalaughavAn .
anyonyamabhyApatatAM nighnatAM cetaretaram . udatiSThad rajo bhauma prAjJAyata kiMcana .
pakSiNazcApatan bhUmau sainyena rajasA ' ' vRtAH . iSubhirvyatisarpadbhirAdityo ' ntaradhIyata .
khadyotairiva saMyuktamantarikSaM vyarAjata . rukmapRSThAni cApAni vyatiSiktAni dhanvinAm . patatAM lokavIrANAM savyadakSiNamasyatAm . rathA rathaiH samAjagmuH pAdAtaizca padAtayaH .
sAdinaH sAdibhizcaiva gajaizcApi mahAgajAH . asibhiH padRizaiH prAsaiH zaktibhistomarairapi .
saMrabdhAH samare rAjan nijaghnuritaretaram . nighnantaH samare ' nyonyaM zUrAH parighabAhavaH .
na zekurabhisaMrabdhAH zUrAn kartuM parAGmukhAn . kRttottaroSThaM sunasaM kRttakezamalaMkRtam . adRzyata zirazchinnaM rajodhvastaM sakuNDalam . adRzyaMstatra gAtrANi zaraizchinnAni bhAgazaH . zAlaskandhanikAzAni kSatriyANAM mahAmRdhe . nAgabhoganikAzaizca bAhubhizcandanokSitaiH . AstIrNA vasudhA bhAti zirobhizca sakuNDalaiH . rathinAM rathibhizcAtra samprahAro ' bhyavartata .
sAdibhiH sAdinAM cApi padAtInAM padAtibhiH . upAzAmyad rajo bhaumaM rudhireNa prasarpatA .
kazmalaM cAvizad ghoraM nirmaryAdamavartata . upAvizan garutmantaH zarairgADhaM pravejitAH . antarikSe gatiryeSAM darzanaM cApyarudhyata . te jantaH samare ' nyonyaM zUrAH parighabAhavaH . na zekurabhisaMrabdhAH zUrAn kartuM parAGmukhAn . zatAnIkaH zataM hatvA vizAlakSazcatuHzatam . praviSTau mahatIM senAM trigartAnAM mahArathau .
tau praviSTau mahAsenAM balavantau manasvinau . ArchatAM bahusaMrabdhau kezAkezi rathArathiH .
lakSayitvA trigartAnAM tau praviSTau rathavrajam . agrataH sUryadattazca madirAkSazca pRSThataH .
virATastatra saMgrAme hatvA paJcazatAn rathAn . hayAnAM ca zatAnyaSTau hatvA paJca mahArathAn .
caran sa vividhAn mArgAn rathena rathasattamaH . trigartAnAM suzarmANamArcchad rukmarathaM raNe .
tau vyavAharatAM tatra mahAtmAnau mahAbalau . anyonyamabhigarjantau goSTheSu vRSabhAviva .
tato rAjA trigartAnAM suzarmA yuddhadurmadaH . matsya samAyAd rAjAnaM dvairathena nararSabhaH .
tato sthAbhyAM rathinau vyatIyaturamarSaNau . zarAn vyasRjatAM zIghraM toyadhArA ghanA iva .
anyonyaM cApi saMrabdhau vicesturamarSaNau . kRtAstrau nizitairbANairasizaktigadAbhRtau .
tato rAjA suzarmANaM vivyAdha dazabhiH zaraiH . paJcabhiH paJcabhizcAsya vivyAdha caturo hayAn .
tathaiva matsyarAjAnaM suzarmA yuddhadurmadaH . paJcAzatA zitairbANairvivyAdha paramAstravit . tataH sainyaM mahArAja matsyarAjasuzarmaNoH . nAbhyajAnAt tadAnyonyaM sainyena rajasA ' ' vRtam .3
sautiruvAca janamejayaH pArikSitaH saha bhrAtRbhiH bhrAtRbhiH kurukSetre dIrghasatramupAste . tasya bhrAtarastrayaH zrutasena . ugraseno bhImasena iti . teSu tatsatramupAsIneSvAgacchatsArameyaH .
janamejayasya bhrAtRbhirabhihato bhrAtRbhirabhihato rorUyamANo mAtuH samIpamupAgacchat .
putraduHkhArtA taM mAtA rorUyamANamuvAca ' kiM rodiSi , kenAsyabhihata ' iti .
pratyuvAca - ' janamejayasya bhrAtRbhirabhihato ' smi ' iti .
taM mAtA pratyuvAca - ' vyaktaM tvayA tatrAparAddham , yenAsyabhihataH ' iti .
sa tAM punaruvAca ' nAparAdhyAmi , kiMcinnAvekSe , havIMSi nAvaliha ' iti .
tacchrutvA mAtA saramA tatsatramupAgacchat , yatra sa janamejayaH saha bhrAtRbhirdIrghasatramupAste .
tayA kruddhayA tatrokta ' ayaM me putro na kiMcidaparAdhyati , nAvekSate , havIMSi , nAvaleDhi , kimarthamabhihataH ' iti .
na kiMciduktavantaste sA tAnuvAca ' yasmAdayamabhihato ' napakArI , tasmAdadRSTaM tvAM bhayamAgamiSyati ' iti . .
janamejaya evamukto devazunyA saramayA bhRzaM saMbhrAnto viSaNNazcAsIt . sa
tasminsatre samApte hAstinapuraM pratyetya purohitamanurUpamanviSyamANaH paraM yatnamakarodyo me pApakRtyAM zamayediti .
sa kadAcinmRgayAM gataH pArikSito janamejayaH kasmiMzcitsvaviSaya Azramamapazyat .
tatra kazcidRSirAsAJcakre zrutazravA nAma . tapasyabhirataH putra Aste somazravA nAma .
tasya taM putramabhigamya janamejayaH pArikSitaH paurohityAya vave .
sa namaskRtya tamRSimuvAca - ' bhagavanyaM tava putro mama purohito ' stu ' iti .
sa evamuktaH pratyuvAca janamejayam ' bho janamejaya , putro ' yaM mama sarmyA jAto mahAtapasvI svAdhyAyasaMpanno mattapovIryasaMbhRto macchukraM pItavatyAstasyAH kukSau jAtaH .
samartho ' yaM bhavataH sarvAH pApakRtyAH zamayitumantareNa mahAdevakRtyAm .
asya tvekamupAMzuvrataM yadenaM kazcid brAhmaNa : kaMcidarthamabhiyAcettaM tasmai dadyAdayam yadyetadutsahase tato nayasvainam ' iti .
tenaivamukto janamejayastaM pratyuvAca - ' bhagavaMstat tathA bhaviSyati .
sa taM purohitamupAdAyopAvRtto bhrAtUnuvAca - ' mayA ' yaM vRta upAdhyAya yadayaM brUyAttat kAryamavicArayadbhirbhavadbhiH ' iti . tenaivamuktA bhrAtarastasya tathA cakruH sa tathA bhrAtRn saMdizya takSazilAM pratyabhipratasthe taM ca dezaM vaze sthApayAmAsa .
etasminnantare kazcid RSiaumyo nAmAyodaH . tasya ziSyAstrayo babhUvuH . upamanyurAruNirvedazceti sa ekaM ziSyamAruNiM pAJcAlyaM preSayAmAsa ' gaccha , kedArakhaNDaM badhAna ' iti .
sa upAdhyAyena saMdiSTa AruNiH pAJcAlyastatra gatvA tam , kedArakhaNDaM barddha nAzakat . klizyamAno ' pazyadupAyam bhavatvevaM kariSyAmi . sa tatra saMviveza kedArakhaNDe . zayAne ca tathA tasmiMstadudakaM tasthau .
tataH kadAcidupAdhyAya Apodo dhaumyaH ziSyAnapRcchat ' kva AruNiH pAJcAlyo gataH ' iti .
te taM pratyUcuH ‘bhagavaMstvayaiva preSitaH ' gaccha kedArakhaNDaM badhAna iti . sa evamuktastAn ziSyAn pratyuvAca ' tasmAttatra sarve gacchAmo yatra sa gataH ' iti . .
sa tatra gatvA tasyAhAnAya zabdaM cakAra - ' bho AruNe , pAJcAlya , kvAsi vatsa , ehi , iti .
sa tacchrutvA AruNirupAdhyAyavAkyaM tasmAt kedArakhaNDAt sahasotyAya tamupAdhyAyamupatasthe .
provAca cainam ' ayamasmi , atra kedArakhaNDe niHsaramANamudakamavAraNIyaM saMroddhaM saMviSTaH , bhagavacchabdaM zrutvaiva , sahasA vidArya kedArakhaNDam , bhavantamupasthitaH . tadabhivAdaye bhagavantam , AjJApayatu bhavAn kamarthaM karavANi iti .29 - 30 .
sa evamukta upAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca ' yasmAdbhavAn kedArakhaNDaM vidAryotthitaH , tasmAduddAlaka eva nAmnA bhavAn bhaviSyati ityupAdhyAyenAnugRhItaH .
 ' yasmAcca tvayA madvacanamanuSThitam , tasmAcchreyo ' vApsyasi . sarve ca te vedAH pratibhAsyanti , sarvANi ca dharmazAstrANi ' iti .
sa evamukta upAdhyAyeneSTaM dezaM jagAma . athApara : ziSyo ' syaivApodasya dhaumyasyopamanyurnAma .
taM copAdhyAyaH preSayAmAsa - ' vatsopamanyo ! gA rakSasva ' iti .
sa upAdhyAyavacanAdarakSadgAH . sa cAhani gA rakSitvA divasakSaye gurugRhamAgamyopAdhyAyasyAgrataH sthitvA namazcakre .
tamupAdhyAyaH pIvAnamapazyaduvAca cainaM ' vatsopamanyo kena ! vRttiM kalpayasi , pIvAnasi dRDham iti .
sa upAdhyAyaM pratyuvAca - ' bho bhaikSyeNa vRttiM kalpayAmi ' iti .
tamupAdhyAyaH ' mayyanivedya bhaikSya nopayoktavyam ' iti . sa tathetyukto bhaikSyaM caritvopAdhyAyAya nyavedayat .
sa tasmAdupAdhyAyaHsarvameva bhaikSyamagRhNAt . sa tathetyuktaH punararakSadgAH . ahani rakSitvA nizAmukhe gurukulamAgamya guroragrata : sthitvA namazcakre .
tamupAdhyAyastathApi pIvAnameva dRSTvovAca ' vatsopamanyo ! sarvamazeSataste bhaikSyaM gRhNAmi . kenedAnIM vRttiM kalpayasi ' iti .
 ' bhagavate nivedya pUrvamaparaM carAmi . tena vRttiM kalpayAmi ' iti .
tamupAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca ' naiSA nyAyyA ' naiSA nyAyyA guruvRttiH anyeSAmapi bhaikSyopajIvinAM vRttyuparodhaM karoSi , ityevaM vartamAno lubdho ' si ' iti .
sa tathettyuktvA gA arakSat . rakSitvA punarupAdhyAyagRhamAgamyopAdhyAyasyAgrataH sthitvA namazcakre .
tamupAdhyAyastathApi pIvAnameva dRSTvA punaruvAca - ' vatsopamanyo ! ahaM te sarvaM bhakSyaM gRhNAmi na cAnyaccarasi . pIvAnasi bhRzam kena vRttiM kalpayasi ' iti .
sa evamuktastamupAdhyAyaM pratyuvAca - ' bho etAsAM gavAM payasA vRtti kalpayAmi ' iti . tamuvAcopAdhyAyaH ' naitanyAyyaM paya upayoktum . bhavato mayA nAbhyanujJAta ' iti .
sa tatheti pratijJAya gA rakSitvA punarupAdhyAyagRhametya guroragrata : sthitvA namazcakre .
tamupAdhyAya : pIvAnameva dRSTovAca ' vatsopamanyo bhaikSya nAznAsi , na cAnyaccarasi , payo na pIbasi , pIvAnasi bhRzam kenedAnI vRtti kalpayasi ' iti .
sa evamukta upAdhyAyaM pratyuvAca - ' bhoH phenaM pibAmi yamime vatsA mAtRNAM stanAtpibanta udgiranti .
tamupAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca ‘ete tvadanukampayA guNavanto vatsAH prabhUtataraM phenamudgiranti . tadeSAmapi tadeSAmapi vatsAnAM vRttyuparodhaM karoSyevaM vartamAnaH . phenamapi bhavAnna pAtumarhati ' iti . sa tatheti pratizrutya punararakSadgAH .
tathA pratiSiddho bhaikSyaM nAznAti na cAnyaccarati payo na pibati . phenaM nopayuGkte sa kadA cidaraNye kSudhArto ' rkapatrANyabhakSayat . tairarkapatraikSitaiH kSAratiktakaTurUkSaistIkSNavipAkaizcakSuSyupahato ' ndho babhUva . tataH so ' ndho ' pi caGkamyamANa : kUpe papAta .
atha tasminnanAgacchati , sUrye cAstAcalAvalambini upAdhyAyaH ziSyAnavocat - ' nAyAtyupamanyuH . ' te Ucu ' vanaM gato gA rakSitum ' iti .
tAnAha upAdhyAya : - ' mayopamanyuH sarvataH pratiSiddhaH sa niyataM kupitastato nAgacchati ciraM tato ' nveSyaH ' ityevamuktvA ziSyaiH sArdhamaraNyaM gatvA tasyAhvAnAya zabdaM cakAra - ' bho upamanyo ! kvAsi vatsa ! ehi ' iti .
sa upAdhyAyavacanaM zrutvA pratyuvAcoccaiH - ' ayamasmin kUpe patito ' ham ' iti . tamupAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca - ' kathaM tvamasmin kUpe patitaH ' iti .
sa upAdhyAyaM pratyuvAca - ' arkapatrANi bhakSayitvA ' ndhIbhUto ' smi . ataH kUpe pattitaH ' iti .
tamupAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca - ' azvinau stuhi . tau devabhiSajau tvAM cakSuSmantaM kartArau ' iti . sa evamukta upAdhyAyenopamanyurazvinau stotumupacakrame devAvazvinau vAgbhidhaMgbhiH .
prapUrvagau pUrvajau citrabhAnU girA vA ' ' zaMsAmi tapasA hyanantau . vadhikSipantau bhuvanAni vizvA .
hiraNmayau zakunI sAmparAyau nAsatyadastrau sunasau vai jayantau . vadhivyayantAvasitaM vivasvataH .
mamuJcatAmazvinau saubhagAya . tAvat suvRttAvanamanta mAyayA vasattamA gA aruNA udAvahan .
SaSTizca gAvastrizatAzca dhenava ekaM vatsaM suvate taM duhanti . stAvazvinau duhato dharmamukthyam .
ekAM nAbhiM saptazatA arAH zritAH pradhiSvanyA viMzatirarpitA arAH . anemi cakraM parivartate ' jaraM mAyA ' zvinau samanakti carSaNI .
ekaM cakraM vartate dvAdazAraM ghaNNAbhimekAkSamRtasya dhAraNam . stAvazvinau muJcataM mA viSIdatam .
azvinAvindumamRtaM vRttabhUyau tirodhattAmazvinau dAsapatnI . hitvA girimazvinau gA mudA carantau tavRSTimahnA prasthitau balasya .
yuvAM dizo janayatho dazAye samAnaM mUrdhni rathayAnaM viyanti . tAsAM yAtamRSayo ' nuprayAnti devA manuSyAH kSitimAcaranti .
yuvAM varNAn vikustho vizvarUpAM ste ' dhikSiyante bhuvanAni vizvA . te bhAnavo ' pyanusRtAzcaranti devA manuSyAH kSitimAcaranti .
tau nAsatyAvazvinau vAM mahe ' haM srajaM ca yAM vibhRthaH puSkarasya . tau nAsatyAvamRtAvRtAvRdhAvRte devAstat prapade na sUte .
mukhena garbhaM labhetAM yuvAnI gatAsuretat prapadena sUte . stAvazvinau muJcatho jIvase gAH .
stotuM na zaknomi guNairbhavantau cakSurvihInaH pathi saMpramohaH . durge ' hamasmin patito ' smi kUpe yuvAM zaraNyau zaraNaM prapadye .
ityevaM tenAbhiSTutAvazvinAvAjagmaturAhatuzcainam - ' prItau svaH , eSa te ' pUpaH , azAnainam ' iti .
sa evamuktaH pratyuvAca - ' nAnRtamUcaturbhagavantau na tvahametamapUpamupayoktumutsahe gurave ' nivedya ' iti .
tatastamazvinAvUcatuH ' AvAbhyAM purastAdbhavata upAdhyAyenaivamevAbhiSTutAbhyAmapUpo dattaH , upayuktaH sa tenAnivedya gurave . tvamapi tathaiva kuruSva yathA kRtamupAdhyAyena ' iti .
evamuktaH pratyuvAca - ' etat pratyanunaye bhavantAvazvinau , notsahe ' hamanivedya gurave ' pUpamupayoktum ' iti .
tamazvinAvAhatu : - ' prItau svastavAnayA gurubhaktyA upAdhyAyasya te kArNAyasA dantA bhavato ' pi hiraNmayA bhaviSyanti , cakSuSmAMzca bhaviSyasIti , zreyazcAvApsyasi iti .
evamukto ' zvibhyAM labdhacakSurupAdhyAyasakAzamAgamyAbhyavAdayat . AcacakSe ca sa cAsya prItimAn babhUva . . Aha cainam ' yathA ' zvinAvAhatustathA tvaM zreyo ' vApsyasi . sarve ca te vedAH pratibhAsyanti , sarvANi ca dharmazAstrANi , iti . eSA tasyApi parIkSopamanyoH .
athAparaH ziSyastasyaivAyodasya dhaumyasya vedo nAma . tamupAdhyAyaH samAdideza - ' vatsa , veda ihAsyatAM tAvanmama gRhe kaJcit kAlam . zuzrUSuNA ca bhavitavyam . zreyaste bhaviSyati ' iti .
sa tathetyuktvA gurukule dIrghakAlaM guruzuzrUSaNaparo ' vasat - gauriva nityaM guruNA dhUrSu niyojyamAnaH zItoSNakSuttRSNAduHkhasahaH sarvatrApratikUlaH . tasya mahatAkAlena guruH paritoSaM jagAma .
tatparitoSAcca zreyaH sarvajJatAM cAvApa . eSA tasyApi parIkSA vedasya .
sa upAdhyAyenAnujJAtaH samAvRttastasmAdgurukulavAsAd gRhAzramaM pratyapadyata . tasyApi svagRhe vasatastrayaH ziSyAH babhUvuH . sa ziSyAnnakiMciduvAca karma vA kriyatA guruzuzrUSA ceti . duHkhAbhijJo hi gurukulavAsasya ziSyAn pariklezena yojayituM neyeSa .
atha kasmiMzcit kAle vedaM brAhmaNaM janamejayaH pauSyazca kSatriyAvupetya varayitvopAdhyAyaM cakratuH .
sa kadAcidyAjyakAryeNAbhiprasthita uttaGkanAmAnaM ziSyaM niyojayAmAsa . ' bho yat kiMcidasmadgRhe parihIyate , tadicchAmyahamaparihIyamAnaM bhavatA kriyamANam ' iti . sa evaM pratisaMdizyottavaM vedaH pravAsaM jagAma .
athottaGkaH zuzrUSurguruniyogamanutiSThamAno gurukule vasati smA sa tatra vasamAna upAdhyAyastrIbhiH sahitAbhirAhUyoktaH .
 ' upAdhyAyinI te RtumatI . upAdhyAyazca proSitaH asyA yathA ' yamRturvandhyo na bhavati , tathA kriyatAm eSA viSIdati ' iti .
evamuktastAH striyaHpratyuvAca - ' na mayA strINAM vacanAdidamakAryaM karaNIyam . hyahamupAdhyAyena saMdiSTaH - akAryamapi tvayA kAryam ' iti .
tasya punarupAdhyAya : kAlAntareNa gRhamAjagAma tasmAt pravAsAt . sa tu tadvRttaM tasyAzeSamupalabhya prItimAnabhUt .
uvAca cainam - ' vatsottaGka , kiM te priyaM karavANi ' iti . dharmato hi zuzrUSito ' smi bhavatA . tena prItiH paraspareNa nau saMvRddhA . tadanujAne bhavantam , sarvAneva kAmAnavApsyasi , gamyatAm iti .
sa evamuktaH pratyuvAca - ' kiM te priyaM karavANi ' iti , evamAhuH .
yazcAdharmeNa vai brUyAdyazcAdharmeNa pRcchati . tayoranyataraH praiti vidveSaM cAdhigacchati .
sohamanujJAto bhavatA icchAmISTaM gurvarthamupahartumiti . tanevaimukta upAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca - ' vatsottaGka ! uSyatAM tAvat ' iti .
sa kadAcidupAdhyAyamAhottaGkaH - ' AjJApayatu bhavAn kiM te priyamupaharAmi gurvartham ' iti .
tamupAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca vatsottaGka bahuzo mAM codayasi gurvarthamupAharAmIti tadgacchainAM pravizyopAdhyAyinIM pRccha kimupAharAmIti . eSA yadvIti tadupAharasveti . evamukta upAdhyAyenopAdhyAyinImapRcchadbhagavatyupAdhyAyenAsamyanujJAto gRhaM gaMtumicchAmISTaM te gurvarthamupahRtyAnRNo gantumiti .
sa sa sa tadAjJApayatu bhavatI kimupaharAmi gurvarthamiti saivamuktopAdhyAyinI tamuttakaM pratyuvAca . gaccha pauSyaM prati rAjAnaM kuNDale bhikSituM tasya kSatriyayA pinaddhe .
Anayasva caturthe ' hani puNyakaM bhavitA tAbhyAmAbaddhAbhyAM zobhamAnA brAhmaNAnyapariveSTumicchAmi tatsaMpAdayasva evaM hi kurvataHzreyo bhavitA ' nyathA kutaHzreya iti .
evamuktastayA prAtiSThatottaGkaH . pathi gacchannapazyadRSabhamatipramANaM tamadhirUDhaM puruSamatipramANameva . sa puruSa uttaGkamabhyabhASata .
bho uttakaitatpurISamasya RSabhasya bhakSayasveti sa evamukto naicchat .
tamAha puruSo bhUyo bhakSayasvettaGka mA vicArayopAdhyAyenApi te bhakSitaM pUrvamiti .
sa evamukto bADhamityuktvA tadA tavRSabhasya mUtraM purISaM ca bhakSayitvottaGkaHsaMbhramAdutthita evApa upaspRzya pratasthe .
yatra sa kSatriyaH pauSyastamupetyAsInamapazyaduttaGkaH . sa uttaGkastamupetyAzIbhirabhinaMdyovAca . pratyuvAca pauSyaH
arthI bhavantamupAgato ' smIti sa enamabhivAdyovAca . bhagavanpauSya : khalvahaM kiM karavANIti .
tamuvAcagurvarthaM kuNDalayorarthenAbhyAgato ' smIti . ye vai te kSatriyayA pinaddhe kuNDale te bhavAndAtu - marhatIti .
taM pauSyaH pravizyAntaHpuraM kSatriyA yAcyatAmiti . sa tenaivamuktaH pravizyAntaHpuraM kSatriyAM nApazyat .
sa pauSyaM punaruvAca na yuktaM bhavatA ' hamanRtenopacarituM na hi te ' ntaHpure kSatriyA sannihitA nainAM pazyAmi .
sa evamuktaH pauSyaHkSaNamAtraM vimRzyottakaM pratyuvAca . niyataM bhavAnucchiSTaH . smara tAvanna hi sA kSatriyA ucchiSTenAzucinA zakyA draSTuM . pativratAtvAtsaiSA nAzucerdarzanamupaitIti .
athaivamukta uttaGkaH smRtvovAcAsti khalu mayotthitenopaspRSTaM gacchatA ceti . taM pauSyaH pratyuvAca eSa te vyatikramo notthitenopaspRSTaM bhavatIti zIghraM gacchatA ceti .
athottaGkastaM tathetyuktvA prADumukha upavizya suprakSAlitapANipAdavadano niHzabdAbhiraphenAbhiranuSNAbhihRdgatAbhirAdbhistriH pItvA dviH parimRjya khAnyadbhipaspRzya cAntaHpuraM praviveza .
tatastAM kSatriyAmapazyat sA ca dRSTvaivottata pratyutthAyAbhivAdyovAca svAgataM te bhagavannAjJApaya kiM karavANIti .
sa tAmuvAcaite kuNDale gurvarthaM me bhikSite dAtumarhasIti . sA prItA tena tasya sadbhAvena pAtramayamanatikramaNIyazceti matvA te kaNDale ' vamucyAsmai prAyacchadAha takSako nAgarAjaH subhRzaM prArthayatyapramatto netumarhasIti .
sa evamuktastAM kSatriyAM pratyuvAca bhagavati sunivRtA bhava . na mAM zaktastakSako nAgarAjo gharSayitumiti .
sa evamuktvA tAM kSatriyAmAmantrya pauSyasakAzamAgacchat . Aha cainaM bhoH pauSya prIto ' smIti tamuttakaM pauSyaH pratyuvAca .
bhagavaMzcireNa pAtramAsAdyate bhavAMzca guNavAnatithistadicche zrAddhaM kartuM , kriyatAM kSaNa iti .
tamuttaGkaH pratyuvAca kRtakSaNa evAsmi zIghramicchAmi . yathopapannamamupaskRtaM bhavateti tathetyuktvA yathopapannenAnnenainaM bhojayAmAsa .
athottaGkaH sakezaM zItamannaM dRSTvA azucyetaditi matvA taM pauSyamuvAca . yasmAnme azucyannaM dadAsi tasmAdandho bhaviSyasIti .
taM pauSyaH pratyuvAca yasmAttvamapyaduSTamannaM dUSayasi tasmAttvamanapatyo bhaviSyasIti tamuttaGkaH pratyuvAca .
na yuktaM bhavatA ' nnamazuci datvA pratizApaM dAtuM tasmAdannameva pratyakSIkuru . tataH pauSyastadannamazuci dRSTvA tasyAzucibhAvamaparokSayAmAsa .
atha tadannaM muktakezyAM striyA yatkRtamanuSNaM sakezaM cAzucyetaditi matvA tamRSimuttakaM prasAdayAmAsa .
bhagavannetadajJAnAdannaM sakezamupAhRtaM zItaM tatkSAmaye bhavantaM na bhaveyamandha iti tamuttaGkaH pratyuvAca .
na mRSA bravImi bhUtvA tvamandho na cirAdanandho bhaviSyasIti . mamApi zApo bhavatA datto na bhavediti .
taM pauSyaH pratyuvAca na cAhaM zaktaH zApaM pratyAdAtuM na hi me manyuradhApyupazamaM gacchati kiM caitadbhavatA na jJAyate tathA .
navanItaM hRdayaM brAhmaNasya , vAci kSuro nizitastIkSNadhAraH . tadubhayametadviparItaM kSatriyasya vADnavanItaM hRdayaM tIkSNadhAramiti .
tadevaM gate na zakto ' haM tIkSNahRdayatvAttaM zApamanyathA kartuM gamyatAmiti . tamuttaGkaH pratyuvAca . pratyuvAca . bhavatA ' hamannasyAzucibhAvamAlakSya pratyanunItaH prAk te ' bhihitam . ca
yasmAdaduSTamannaM dUSayasi tasmAdanapatyo bhaviSyasIti duSTe cAnne naiSa mama zApo bhaviSyatIti .
sAdhayAmastAvadityuktvA prAtiSThatottaMGkaste kuNDale gRhItvA . so ' pazyadatha pathi nagnaM kSapaNakamAgacchantaM muhurmuhurdRzyamAnaM ca .
athottaGkaste kuNDale saMnyasya bhUmAvudakArthaM pracakrame . etasminnantare sa kSapaNakastvaramANa upasRtya te kuNDale gRhItvA prAdravat .
tamuttako ' bhisRtya kRtodakakAryaH zuciH prayato namo devebhyo gurubhyazca kRtvA mahatA javena tamanvayAt .
tasya takSako dRDhamAsannaH sa taM jagrAha gRhItamAtraH sa tadrUpaM vihAya takSakasvarUpaM kRtvA sahasA dharaNyAM vivRtaM mahAbilaM praviveza .
pravizya ca nAgalokaM svabhavanamagacchat . athottaGkastasyAH kSatriyAyA vacaH smRtvA taM takSakamanvagacchat .
sa tadvilaM daNDakASThena cakhAna na cAzakat . taM klizyamAnamindro ' pazyatsa vajraM preSayAmAsa .
gacchAsya brAhmaNasya sAhAyyaM kuruSveti . atha vajraM daNDakASThamanupravizya tadvilamadArayat .
tamutto ' nuviveza tenaiva bilena pravizya ca taM nAgalokamaparyantamanekAvidhaprAsAdahaऱyAvalabhIni ! hazatasaMkulamuccAvacakrIDazcaryasthAnAvakIrNamapazyat .
sa tatra nAgAMstAnastuvadebhiH zlokaiH ya airAvatarAjAnaH sarpAH samitizobhanAH . kSaranta iva jImUtAH savidyutpavaneritAH .
surUpA bahurUpAzca tathA kalmASakuNDalAH . AdityavannAkapRSThe rejurairAvatodbhavAH .
bahUni nAgavezmAni gaGgAyAstIra uttare . tatrasthAnapi saMstaumi mahataH pannagAnaham .
icchetko ' rSAMzusenAyAM cartumairAvataM vinA . zatAnyazItiraSTau ca sahasrANi ca viMzatiH . sarpANAM pragrahA yanti dhRtarASTro yadaijati .
ye cainamupasarpanti ye ca dUrapathaM gatAH . ahamairAvatajyeSThabhrAtRbhyo ' karavaM nama : .
yasya vAsaH kurukSetre khANDave kurukSetre khANDave cAbhavatpurA . taM nAgarAjamastauSaM kuNDalArthAya takSakam .
takSakazcAzvasenazca nityaM sahacarAvubhau . kurukSetraM ca vasatAM nadImikSumatImanu .
jaghanyajastakSakazca zrutaseneti yaH sutaH . avasadyo mahadyumni prArthayannAmamukhyatAm . karavANi sadA cAhaM namastasmai mahAtmane .
evaM stutvA sa viprarSiruttaGko bhujagottamAn . naiva te kuNDale lebhe tatazcintAmupAgamat .
evaM stuvannapi nAgAnyadA te kuNDale nAlabhattadA ' pazyatstriyau tantre adhiropya suveme paTaM vayantyau . tasmiMstantre kRSNAH sitAzca tantavazcakraM cApazyat dvAdazAraM SaDbhiH kumAraiH parivartyamAnaM puruSaM cApazyadazvaM ca darzanIyam . sa tAnsarvAMstuSTAva ebhirmantravadeva zlokaiH .
trINyarpitAnyatra zatAni madhye ghaSTizca nityaM carati dhruve ' smin . cakre caturvizatiparvayoge SaDvai kumArAH parivartayanti .
tantraM cedaM vizvarUpe yuvatyau vayatastaMtUnsatataM vartayantyau . kRSNAnsitAMzcaiva vivartayantyau bhUtAnyajasraM bhuvanAni caiva .
vajrasya bhartA bhuvanasya goptA vRtrasya hantA namucenihantA . kRSNe vasAno vasane mahAtmA satyAnRte yo vivinakti loke .
yo vAjinaM garbhamapAM purANaM vaizvAnaraM vAhanamabhyupaiti . namo ' stu tasmai jagadIzvarAya lokatrayezAya puraMdarAya .
tataH sa enaM puruSaH prAha - ' prIto ' smi te ' hamanena stotreNa , kiM te priyaM karavANi ' iti sa tamuvAca .
nAgA me vazamIyuriti . sa cainaM puruSaH punaruvAca etamazcamapAne dhamasveti .
tato ' zvasyApAnamadhamattato ' zvAddhamyamAnAtsarvastrotobhyaH pAvakArciSaH sadhUmA niSpetuH .
tAbhirnAgaloka upadhUpite ' tha saMbhrAntastakSako ' gnestejobhayAdviSaNNa : kuNDale gRhItvA sahasA bhavanAnniSkramyottaGkamuvAca .
ime kuNDale gRhNAtu bhavAniti sa te pratijagrAhottaGkaH pratigRhya ca kuNale ' cintayat .
adya tatpuNyakamupAdhyAyinyA dUraM cAhamabhyAgata : sa kathaM saMbhAvayeyamiti tata enaM cintayAnameva sa puruSa uvAca .
uttaGka enamevAzvamadhiroha tvAM kSaNenaivopAdhyAyakulaM prApayiSyatIti .
sa tathetyuktvA tamazvamadhiruhya pratyAjagAmopAdhyAyakulamupAdhyAyinI ca smAtA kezAnAvApayantyupaviSTottako nAgacchatIti zApAyAsya mano dadhe .
atha tasminnantare sa uttaGkaH pravizya upAdhyAyakulamupAdhyAyinImabhyavAdayat te cAsyai kuNDale prAyacchatsA cainaM pratyuvAca .
uttaGka deze kAle ' bhyAgataH svAgataM te vatsa tvamanAgasi mayA na zaptaH zreyastavopasthitaM siddhimApnuhIti .
athottaGka upAdhyAyamabhyavAdayat . tamupAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca vatsottaGka svAgataM te kiM ciraMkRtamiti .
tamuttaGka upAdhyAyaM pratyuvAca bhostakSakeNa me nAgarAjena vighnaH kRto ' sminkarmaNi tenA ' smi nAgalokaM gataH .
tatra ca mayA dRSTe striyau tantre ' dhiropya paTaM vayantyau tasmizca kRSNAH sitAzca tantavaH kiM tat .
tatra ca mayA cakraM dRSTaM dvAdazAraM SaDvainaM kumArA : parivartayanti tadapi kim . puruSazcApi mayA dRSTaH sa cA ' pi kaH . azvazcAtipramANo dRSTaH sa cA ' pi kaH .
pathi gacchatA ca mayA RSabho dRSTastaM ca puruSo ' dhirUDhastenA ' smi sopacAramukta uttaGkasya RSabhasya purISaM bhakSaya upAdhyAyenApi te bhakSitamiti .
tatastasya vacanAnmayA tadRSabhasya purISamupayuktaM sa cApi kaH . tadetadbhavatopadiSTamiccheyaM zrotuM kiM taditi . sa tenaivamukta upAdhyAyaH pratyuvAca .
ye te striyau dhAtA vidhAtA ca ye ca te kRSNAH sitAstantavaste rAtryahanI . yadapi taccakraM dvAdazAraM SaDvai kumArAH parivartayanti te ' pi SaRtavaH saMvatsarazcakram .
yaH puruSaH sa parjanyo yo ' zvaH so ' gnirya RSabhastvayA pathi gacchatA dRSTaH sa airAvato nAgarAT .
yazcainamadhirUDhaH puruSaH sa cendro yadapi te bhakSitaM tasya RSabhasya purISaM tadamRtaM tena khalvasi tasminnAgabhavane na vyApannastvam .
sa hi bhagavAnindro mama sakhA tvadanukrozAdimamanugrahaM kRtavAn . tasmAtkRNDale gRhItvA punarAgato ' si .
