uttaGka uvAca anyasminkaraNIye tu kArye pArthivasattama . bAlyAdivAnyadeva tavaM kuruSe nRpasattama .
sautiruvAca evamuktastu vipreNa sa rAjA janamejayaH . arcayitvA yathAnyAyaM pratyuvAca dvijottamam .
janamejaya uvAca AsAM prajAnAM paripAlanena svaM kSatradharmaM paripAlayAmi . prabrUhi me kiM karaNIyamadya yenAsi kAryeNa samAgatastvam .
sautiruvAca sa evamuktastu nRpottamena dvijottamaH puNyakRtAM variSThaH . uvAca rAjAnamadInasatvaM svameva kAryaM nRpate kuruSva .
uttaGka uvAca takSakeNa mahIndrendra yena te hiMsita : pitA . tasmai pratikuruSva tvaM pannagAya durAtmane .
kAryakAlaM hi manye ' haM vidhidRSTasya karmaNaH . tadgacchApaciti rAjanpitustasya mahAtmanaH .
te hyanaparAdhI sa duSTAntarAtmanA . paJcatvamagamadrAjA vajAhata iva dumaH .
baladarpasamutsitastakSakaH pannagAdhamaH . akAryaM kRtavAnpApo yo ' dazatpitaraM tava .
rAjarSivaMzagoptAramamarapratimaM nRpam . yiyAsuM kazyapaM caiva nyavartayata pApakRt .
hetumarhasi taM pApaM jvalite havyavAhane . sarpasatre mahArAja tvaritaM tadvidhIyatAm .
evaM pituzcApacitiM kRtavAMstvaM bhaviSyasi . mama priyaM ca sumahatkRtaM rAjan bhaviSyati .
karmaNaH pRthivIpAla mama yena durAtmanA . vighnaH kRto mahArAja gurvarthaM carato ' nagha .
sautiruvAca etacchrutvA tu nRpatistakSakAya cukopa hai . uttaGkavAkyahaviSA dIpto ' gnirhaviSA yathA .
apRcchatsa tadA rAjA mantriNastAnsuduHkhitaH . uttaGkasyaiva sAnnidhye pituH svargagati prati .
tadaiva hi sa rAjendro duHkhazokAlputo ' bhavat . yadaiva vRttaM pitaramuttaGkAdazRNottadA .
saMjaya uvAca tataH pravavRte yuddhaM kurUNAM bhayavardhanam . saMjayaiH saha rAjendra ghoraM devAsuropamam .
narA rathA gajaughAzca sAdinazca sahasrazaH . vAjinazca parAkrAntA : samAjagmuH parasparam .
gajAnAM bhImarUpANAM dravatA niHsvano mahAn . azrUyata yathA kAle jaladAnAM nabhastale .
nAgairabhyAhatA : kecit sarathA rathino ' patan . vyadravanta raNe vIrA drAvyamANA madotkaTaiH .
hayaudhana pAdarakSAMzca rathinastatra zikSitAH . zaraiH sampreSayAmAsuH paralokAya bhArata .
