tathA ca rathinaM kruddhaM vikirantaM zarAn bahUn . nAgA jaghnurmahArAja parivArya samantataH .
nAgo nAgamabhidrutya rathI ca rathinaM raNe . zaktitomaranArAcairnijane tatra bhArata .
pAdAtAnavamRdnanto rathavAraNavAjinaH . raNamadhye vyadRzyanta kurvanto mahAdAkulam .
hayAzca paryadhAvanta cAmarairupazobhitAH . haMsA himavataH prasthe pibanta iva medinAm .
teSAM tu vAjinA bhUmiH khuraizcitrA vizAmpate . azobhata yathA nArI karajaiH kSatavikSatA .
vAjinAM khurazabdena rathanemisvanena ca . pattInAM cApi zabdena nAgAnAM bRMhitena ca . vAditrANAM ca ghoSeNa zaGkhAnAM ninadena ca . abhavannAditA bhUmirnirghAtairiva bhArata .
dhanuSAM kUjamAnAnAM zastraughAnAM ca dIpyatAm . kavacAnAM prabhAbhizca na prAjJAyata kiJcana .
bahavo bAhavazchinnA nAgarAjakaropamAH . udveSTante viceSTante vegaM kurvanti dAruNam .
zirobhiH patitai ti patatAM dharaNItale . cyutAnAmiva tAlebhyastAlAnAM zrUyate svanaH .
zirobhiH patitai ti rudhirAdrairvasundharA . tapanIyanibhaiH kAle nalinairiva bhArata . udvRttanayanaistaistu gatasattvaiH suvikSataiH . vyabhrAjata mahI rAjan puNDarIkairivAvRtA . .
bAhubhizcandanAdigdhaiH sakeyUrairmahAdhanaiH . patitai ti rAjendra mahAzakradhvajairiva .
Urubhizca narendrANAM vinikRttairmahAhave . hastihastopamairanyaiH saMvRtaM tad raNAGgaNam .
kabandhazatasaMkIrNaM chatracAmarasaMkulam . senAvanaM tacchuzubhe vanaM puSpAcitaM yathA .
tatra yodhA mahArAja vicaranto hyabhItavat . dRzyante rudhirAktAGgAH puSpitA iva kiMzukAH .
mAtaGgAzcApyadRzyanta zaratomarapIDitAH . patantastatra tatraiva chinnAbhrasadRzA raNe .
gajAnIkaM mahArAja vadhyamAnaM mahAtmabhiH . vyadIryata dizaH sarvA vAtanunnA ghanA iva .
te gajA ghanasaMkAzA : peturuA samantataH . vajranunnA iva babhuH parvatA yugasaMkSaye .
hayAnAM sAdibhiH sArdhaM patitAnAM mahItale . rAzayaH sma pradRzyante girimAtrastatastataH .
saMjajJe raNabhUmau tu paralokavahA nadI . zoNitodA rathAvartA dhvajavRkSAsthizarkarA .
bhujanakrA dhanuHsrotA hastizailA hayopalA . medomajAkardaminI chatrahaMsA gadoDupA .
kavacoSNISasaMcchannA patAkAruciradumA . cakracakrAvalIjuSTA triveNUragasaMvRtA .
zUrANAM harSajananI bhIrUNAM bhayavardhanI . prAvartata nadI raudrA kurusRJjayasaMkulA .
tAM nadI paralokAya vahantImatibhaisvAm . teruhinanaubhistaiH : zUrAH paridhabAhavaH .
vartamAne tadA yuddhe nirmayAde vizAmpate . caturaGgakSaye ghore pUrvadevAsuropame .
vyAkrozan bAndhavAnanye tatra tatra paraMtapa . krozAdbhirdayitairanye bhayArtA na nivatire . .
nirmaryAde tathA yuddhe vartamAne bhayAnake . arjuno bhImasenazca mohayAMcakratuH parAn .
sA vadhyamAnA mahatI senA tava narAdhipa . amuhyattatra tatraiva yoSinmadavazAdiva .
mohayitvA ca tAM senAM bhImasenadhanaJjayau . dadhmaturvArijau tatra siMhanAdAMzca cakratuH .
zrutvaiva tu mahAzabdaM dhRSTadyumnazikhaNDInau . dharmarAjaM puraskRtya madrarAjamabhidrutau .
tatrAzcaryamapazyAma ghorarUpaM vizAmpate . zalyena saGgatAH zUrA yadayudhyanta bhAgazaH .
mAdrIputrau tu rabhasau kRtAstrau yuddhadurmadau . abhyayAtAM tvarAyuktau jigISantau paraMtapa .
tato nyavartata balaM tAvakaM bharatarSabha . zaraiH praNunnaM bahudhA pANDavairjitakAzibhiH .
vadhyamAnA camUH sA tu putrANAM prekSatAM tava . bheje dizo mahArAja praNunnA zaravRSTibhiH .
hAhAkAro mahAJjajJe yodhAnAM tava bhArata . tiSTha tiSTheti cApyAsId drAvitAnAM mahAtmanAm .
kSatriyANAM sahAnyonyaM saMyuge jayamicchatAm . prAdravanneva sambhagnAH pANDavaistava sainikAH . tyaktvA yuddhe priyAn putrAn bhrAtRnatha pitAmahAn . mAtulAn bhAgineyAMzca vayasyAnapi bhArata .
hayAn dvipAMstvarayanto yodhA jagmuH samantataH . AtmatrANakRtotsAhAstAvakA bharatarSabha .
avyaktAt pUrvamutpanno mahAnAtmA mahAmatiH . AdirguNAnAM sarveSAM prathamaH sarga ucyate .
mahAnAtmA matirviSNurjiSNuH zambhuzca vIryavAn . buddhiH prajJopalabdhizca tathA khyAtidhRtiH smRtiH . paryAyavAcakaiH zabdairmahAnAtmA vibhAvyate . taM jAnan brAhmaNo vidvAn pramohaM nAdhigacchati .
