mahAprabhAvaH puruSaH sarvasya hRdi nizcitaH . aNimA laghimA prAptirIzAno jyotiravyayaH .
tatra buddhivido lokAH sadbhAvaniratAzca ye . dhyAnino nityayogAzca satvasaMdhA jitendriyAH . jJAnavantazca ye kecidalubdhA jitamanyavaH . prasannamanaso dhIrA nirmamA nirahaMkRtAH .
vimuktAH sarva evaite mahattvamupayAntyuta . Atmano mahato veda yaH puNyAM gatimuttamAm .
ahaMkArAt prasUtAni pahAbhUtAni paJca vai . pRthivI vAyurAkAzamAyo jyotizca paJcamam .
teSu bhUtAni yujyante mahAbhUteSu paJcasu . te zabdasparzarUpeSu rasagandhakriyAsu ca .
mahAbhUtavinAzAnte pralaye pratyupasthite . sarvaprANabhRtAM dhIrA mahadutpadyate bhayam . sa dhIraH sarvalokeSu na mohamadhigacchati .
viSNurevAdisargeSu svayambhUrbhavati prabhuH . evaM hi yo veda guhAzaya prabhu paraM purANaM puruSa vizvarUpam . hiraNmayaM buddhimatAM parAM gatiM sa buddhimAn buddhimatItya tiSThati .
