vaizampAyana uvAca tataH kAvyo bhRguzreSTha samanyurupagamya hA vRSaparvANamAsInamityuvAcAvicArayan .
nAdharmazcarito rAjan sadyaH phalati gauriva . zanairAvay/amAno hi karturmUlAni kRntati .
putreSu vA natRSu vA na cedAtmani pazyati . phalatyeva dhruvaM pApaM gurubhuktamivodare .
yadadhAta yathA vipraM kacamAGgirasaM tadA . apApazIlaM dharmajJaM zuzrUSaM madgRhe ratam .
vadhAdanahatastasya vadhAca duhiturmama . vRSaparvan nibodhedaM tyakSyAmi tvAM sabAndhavam . sthAtuM tvadviSaye rAjan na zakSyAmi tvayA saha .
aho mAmabhijAnAsi daitya mithyApralapinam . yathemamAtmano doSaM na niyacchasyupekSase .
vRSaparvovAca nAdharmaM na mRSAvAdaM tvayi jAnAmi bhArgava . tvayi dharmazca satyaM ca tat prasIdatu no bhavAn . yadyasmAnapahAya tvamito gacchasi bhArgava . samudraM sampravekSyAmo nAnyadasti parAyaNam .
zukra uvAca samudraM pravizadhvaM vA dizo vA dravatAsurAH . duhitu priyaM soDhuM zakto ' haM dayitA hi me .
prasAdyatAM devayAnI jIvitaM yatra me sthitam . yogakSemakaraste ' hamindrasyeva bRhaspatiH .
vRSaparvovAca yat kiMcidasurendrANAM vidyate vasu bhArgava . bhuvi hastigavAzvaM ca tasya tvaM mama cezvaraH .
zukra uvAca yat kiMcidasti draviNaM daityendrANAM mahAsura . tasyezvaro ' smi yadyeSA devayAnI prasAdyatAm .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktastathetyAha vRSaparvA mahAkaviH . devayAnyantikaM gatvA tamartha prAha bhArgavaH .
devayAnyuvAca yadi tvamIzvarastAta rAjJo vittasya bhArgava nAbhijAnAmi tat te ' haM rAjA tu vadatu svayam .
vRSaparvovAca yaM kAmamabhikAmAsi devayAni zucismite . tat te ' haM sampradAsyAmi yadi vApi hi durlabham .
devayAnyuvAca dAsI kanyAsahasreNa zarmiSThAmabhikAmaye . anu mAM tatra gacchet sA yatra dadyAca me pitA .
vRSaparvovAca uttiSTha tvaM gaccha dhAtri zarmiSThAM zIghramAnaya . yaM ca kAmayate kAmaM devayAnI karotu tam .
vaizampAyana uvAca tato dhAtrI tatra gatvA zarmiSThAM vAkyamabravIt . uttiSTha bhadre zarmiSThe jJAtInAM sukhamAvaha .
tyajati brAhmaNa : ziSyAn devayAnyA pracoditaH . sAyaM kAmayate kAmaM sa kAryo ' dya tvayAnaghe .
zarmiSThovAca yaM sA kAmayate kAmaM karavANyahamadya tam . yadyevamAhvayecchukro devayAnIkRte hi mAm . maddoSAnmA gamacchukro devayAnI ca matkRte .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataH kanyAsahasreNa vRtA zibikayA tadA . piturniyogAt tvaritA nizcakrAma purottamAt .
zarmiSThovAca ahaM dAsIsahasreNa dAsI te paricArikA . anu tvAM tatra yAsyAmi yatra dAsyati te pitA .
devayAnyuvAca stuvato duhitAhaM te yAcataH pratigRhNataH . stUyamAnasya duhitA kathaM dAsI bhaviSyasi .
zarmiSThovAca yena kenacidArtAnAM jJAtInAM sukhamAvahet . atastvAmanuyAsyAmi yatra dAsyati te pitA .
vaizampAyana uvAca pratizrute dAsabhAve duhitrA vRSaparvaNaH . devayAnI nRpazreSTha pitaraM vAkyamabravIt .
devayAnyuvAca pravizAmi puraM tAta tuSTAsmi dvijasattama . amoghaM tava vijJAnamasti vidyAbalaM ca te .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamukto duhitrA sa dvijazreSTho mahAyazAH . praviveza puraM hRSTaH pUjitaH sarvadAnavaiH .
vaizampAyana uvAca krozamAnaM prayAteSu pANDaveSu mahAtmasu . padbhyAmanucitA gantuM draupadI samupAvizat .
zrAntA duHkhaparItA ca vAtavarSeNa tena ca . saukumAryAcca pAJcAlI sammumoha tapasvinI .
sA kampamAnA mohena bAhubhyAmasitekSaNA . vRttAbhyAmanurUpAbhyAmUrU samavalambata .
AlambamAnA sahitAvUrU gajakaropamau . papAta sahasA bhUmau vepantI kadalI yathA .
tAM patantIM varArohAM bhajyamAnAM latAmiva . nakulaH samabhidrutya parijagrAha vIryavAn .
nakula uvAca rAjan paJcAlarAjasya suteyamasitekSaNA . zrAntA nipatitA bhUmau tAmavekSasva bhArata .
aduHkhArhA paraM duHkhaM prApteyaM mRdugAminI . AzvAsaya mahArAja tAmimAM zramakarzitAm .
vaizampAyana uvAca rAjA tu vacanAt tasya bhRzaM duHkhasamanvitaH . bhImazca sahadevazca sahasA samupAdravan .
tAmavekSya tu kaunteyo vivarNavadanAM kRzAm . aGkamAnIyadharmAtmA paryadevayadAturaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca kathaM vezmasu gupteSu svAstIrNazayanocitA . bhUmau nipatitA zete sukhArdA varavarNinI .
sukumArau kathaM pAdau mukhaM ca kamalaprabham . matkRte ' dya varArhAyAH zyAmatAM samupAgatam .
kimidaM dyUtakAmena mayA kRtamabuddhinA . AdAya kRSNAM caratA vane mRgagaNAyute .
sukhaM prApsyasi kalyANi pANDavAn prApya vai patIn . iti dupadarAjena pitrA dattA ' ' yatekSaNA .
tat sarvamanavApyeyaM zramazokAdhvakarzitA . zete nipatitA bhUmau pApasya mama karmabhiH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tathA lAlapyamAne tudharmarAje yudhiSThire . dhaumyaprabhRtayaH sarve tatrAjagmurdvijottamAH .
te samAzvAsayAmAsurAzIrbhizcApyapUjayan . rakSoghnAMzca tathA mantrAopuzcakruzca te kriyAH .
paThyamAneSu mantreSu zAntyarthaM paramarSibhiH . spRzyamAnA karaiH zItaiH pANDavaizca muhurmuhuH .
sevyamAnA ca zItena jalamizreNa vAyunA . pAJcAlI sukhamAsAdya lebhe cetaH zanaiH zanaiH .
parigRhya ca tAM dInAM kRSNAmajitanasaMstare . pArthA vizrAmayAmAsurlabdhasaMjJAM tapasvinIm .
tasyA yamau raktatalau pAdau pUjitalakSaNau . karAbhyAM kiNajAtAbhyAM zanakaiH saMvavAhatuH .
paryAzvAsayadapyenAMdharmarAjo yudhiSThiraH . uvAca ca kurazreSTho bhImasenamidaM vacaH .
bahavaH parvatA bhIma viSamaH himadurgamAH . teSu kRSNA mahAbAho kathaM nu vicaMriSyati .
bhImasena uvAca tvAM rAjan rAjaputrIM ca yamau ca puruSarSabha . svayaM neSyAmi rAjendra mA viSAde manaH kRthAH .
haiDimbAzca mahAvIryo vihago madbalopamaH . vahedanagha sarvAnno vacanAt te ghaTotkacaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca anujJAtodharmarAjJA putraM sasmAra rAkSasam . ghaTotkacastudharmAtmA smRtamAtraH pitustadA .
kRtAJjalirupAtiSThadabhivAdyAtha pANDavAn . brAhmaNAMzca mahAbAhuH sa ca tairabhinanditaH .
uvAca bhImasenaM sa pitaraM bhImavikramam . smRto ' smi bhavatA zIghraM zuzrUSurahamAgataH .
AjJApaya mahAbAho sarvaM kartAsmyasaMzayam . tacchrutvA bhImasenastu rAkSasaM pariSasvaje .
bhISma uvAca etat te rAjadharmANAM navanItaM yudhiSThira . bRhaspatirhi bhagavAn nyAyyaM dharmaM prazaMsati .
vizAlAkSazca bhagavAn kAvyazcaiva mahAtapAH . sahasrAkSo mahendrazca tathA prAcetaso manuH . bharadvAjazca bhagavAMstathA gaurazirA muniH . rAjazAstrapraNetAro brahmaNyA brahmavAdinaH .
rakSAmeva prazaMsanti dharmaM dharmabhRtAM vara . rAjJAM rAjIvatAmrAkSa sAdhanaM cAtra me zRNu .
cArazca praNidhizcaiva kAle dAnamamatsarAt . yuktyAdAnaM na cAdAnamayogena yudhiSThira . satAM saMgrahaNaM zauryaM dAkSyaM satyaM prajAhitam . anArjavairArjavaizca zatrupakSasya bhedanam . ketanAnAM ca jIrNAnAmavekSA caiva sIdatAm . dvividhasya ca daNDasya prayogaH kAlacoditaH . sAdhUnAmaparityAgaH kulInAnAM ca dhAraNam . nicayazca niceyAnAM sevA buddhimatAmapi . balAnAM harSaNaM nityaM prajAnAmanvavekSaNam . kAryeSvakhedaH kozasya tathaiva ca vivardhanam . puraguptiravizvAsa : paurasaMghAtabhedanam . arimadhyasthamitrANAM yathAvaccAnvavekSaNam . upajApazca bhRtyAnAmAtmanaH puradarzanam . avizvAsaH svayaM caiva parasyAzvAsanaM tathA . . nItidharmAnusaraNaM nityamutthAnameva ca . ripUNAmanavajJAnaM nityaM cAnAryavarjanam .
utthAnaM hi narendrANAM bRhaspatirabhASata . rAjadharmasya tanmUlaM zlokAMzcAtra nibodha me .
utthAnenAmRtaM labdhamutthAnenAsurA hatAH . utthAnena mahandreNa zreSThyaM prAptaM divIha ca .
utthAnavIraH puruSo vAgvIrAnadhitiSThati . utthAnavIrAn vAgvIrA ramayanta upAsate .
utthAnahIno rAjA hi buddhimAnapi nityazaH . pradharSaNIyaH zatrUNAM bhujaGga iva nirviSaH .
na ca zatruravajJeyo durbalo ' pi balIyasA . alpo ' pi hi dahatyagniviSamalpaM hinasti ca .
ekAGgenApi sambhUtaH zatrurdurgamupAzritaH . sarvaM tApayate dezamapi rAjJaH samRddhinaH .
rAjJo rahasyaM yad vAkyaM jayArthaM lokasaMgrahaH . hRdi yaccAsya jihyaM syAtkAraNena ca yad bhavet . yaccAsya kAryaM vRjinamArjavenaiva dhArayet . dambhanArthaM ca lokasya dharmiSThAmAcaret kriyAm .
rAjyaM hi sumahat tantraM dhAryate nAkRtAtmabhiH . na zakyaM mRdunA voDhumAyAsasthAnamuttamam .
rAjyaM sarvAmiSaM nityamArjaveneha dhAryate . tasmAnmizreNa satataM vartitavyaM yudhiSThira .
yadyapyasya vipattiH syAd rakSamANasya vai prajAH . so ' pyasya vipulo dharma evaMvRttA hi bhUmipAH .
eSa te rAjadharmANAM lezaH samanuvarNitaH . bhUyaste yatra saMdehastad brUhi kurusattama .
vaizampAyana uvAca tato vyAsazca bhagavAn devasthAno ' zma eva ca . vAsudevaH kRpazcaiva sAtyakiH saMjayastathA . sAdhu sAdhviti saMhRSTAH puSSyamANairivAnanaiH . astuvaMzca naravyAghraM bhISmaM dharmabhRtAM varam .
tato dInamanA bhISmamuvAca kurusattamaH . netrAbhyAmazrupUrNAbhyAM pAdau tasya zanaiH spRzan . zva idAnIM svasandehaM prakSyAmi tvAM pitAmaha . upaiti savitA zastaM rasamApIya pArthivam .
tato dvijAtInabhivAdya kezavaH kRpazva te caiva yudhiSThirAdayaH . pradakSiNIkRtya mahAnadIsutaM tato rathAnAruruhurmudAnvitAH .
dRSadvatIM cApyavagAhya suvratAH kRtodakArthAH kRtajaSyamaGgalAH . upAsya saMdhyAM vidhivat paraMtarpA stata : puraM te vivizurgajAhvayam .
saMjaya uvAca dRSTvA karNa maheSvAsaM yuyutsuM samavasthitam . cukruzaH kuravaH sarve hRSTarUpAH samantataH .
tato dundubhinirghoSairbherINAM ninadena ca . bANazabdaizca vividhairgarjitaizca tarasvinAm . niryayustAvakA yuddhe mRtyuM kRtvA nivartanam .
prayAte tu tataH karNe yodheSu muditeSu ca . . cacAla pRthivI rAjan vavAza ca suvistaram .
niHsarantau vyaddazyanta sUryAt sapta mahAgrahAH . ulkApAtAzca saMjajudizAM dAhAstathaiva ca . zuSkAzanyazca sampeturvavurvAtAzca bhairavAH .
mRgapakSigaNAzcaiva pRtanAM bahuzastava . apasavyaM tadA cakrurvedayanto mahAbhayam .
prathitasya ca karNasya nipetusturagA bhuvi . asthivarSaM ca patitamantarikSAd bhayAnakam .
jajvaluzcaiva zastrANi dhvajAzcaiva cakampire . azrUNi ca vyamuJcanta vAhanAni vizAmpate .
ete cAnye ca bahava utpAtAstatra dAruNAH . samutyeturvinAzAya kauravANAM sudAruNAH .
na ca tAn gaNayAmAsuH sarve daivena mohitAH . prasthitaM sUtaputraM ca jayetyUcurnarAdhipAH . nirjitAn pANDavAzcaiva menire tatra kauravAH .
tato rathasthaH paravIrahantA bhISmadroNAvastavIryo samIkSya . samajjvalan bhAskarapAvakAbho vaikartano ' sau rathakuJjaro nRpa .
sa zalyamAbhASya vAkyaM pArthasya karmAtizayaM vicintya . mAnena darpaNa vidahyamAnaH krodhena dIpyaniva niHzvasaMzca .
nAhaM mahendrAdapi vajrapANe : kruddhAd bibhemyAyudhavAn rathasthaH . natIva mAM hyasthiratA jahAti .
mahendraviSNupratimAvanindatau rathAzvanAgapravarapramAthinau . stato na me ' pyasti raNe sAdhvasam .
samIkSya saMkhye ' tibalAn narAdhipAn sasUtamAtaGgarathAn parairhatAn . kathaM na sarvAnahitAn raNe ' vadhId mahAstravid brAhmaNapuGgavo guruH .
sa saMsmaran droNamahaM mahAhave bravImi satyaM kuravo nibodhata . na vA madanyaH prasahed raNe ' rjunaM samAgataM mRtyumivograrUpiNam .
zikSApramAdazca balaM dhRtizca droNe mahAstrANi ca saMnatizca . sa cedagAnmRtyuvazaM mahAtmA sarvAnanyAnAturAnadya manye .
neha dhruvaM kiMcidapi pracintayan vidyAM loke karmaNo nityayogAt . sUryodaye ko hi vimuktasaMzayo bhAvaM kurvItAdya gurau nipAtite .
na nUnamastrANi balaM parAkramaH kriyAH sunItaM paramAyudhAni vA . alaM manuSyasya sukhAya vartituM tathA hi yuddhe nihataH parairguruH .
hutAzanadityasamAnatejasaM parAkrame viSNupurandaropamam . naye bRhaspatyuzanoH sadA samaM na cainamastraM tadupAsta duHsaham .
samprAkruSTe ruditastrIkumAre parAbhUte pauruSe dhArtarASTra . mayA kRtyamiti jAnAmi zalya prayAhi tasmAd dviSatAmanIkam .
yatra rAjA pANDavaH satyasaMdho vyavasthito bhImasenArjunau cA vAsudevaH sAtyakiH sRjAyAzca yamau ca kastAn viSahenmadanyaH .
tasmAt kSipraM madrapate prayAhi raNe paJcAlAn pANDavAn sRJjayAMzca . tAn vA haniSyAmi sametya saMkhye yAsyAmi vA droNapathA yamAya .
na tvevAhaM na gamiSyAmi madhye teSAM zUrANAmiti mAM zalya viddhi . mitradroho marSaNIyo na me ' yaM tyaktvA prANAnanuyAsyAmi droNam .
prAjJasya mUDhasya ca jIvitAnte nAsti pramokSo ' ntakasatkRtasya . ato vidvannabhiyAsyAmi pArthAn diSTaM na zakyaM vyativartituM vai .
kalyANavRttaH satataM hi rAjA vaicitravIryasya suto mamAsIt . tasyArthasiddhyarthamahaM tyajAmi priyAna bhogAn dustyajaM jIvitaM ca .
vaiyAghracarmANamakUjanAkSaM haimatrikoSaM rajatatriveNum . yuktaM prAdAnmahyamimaM hi rAmaH .
dhanUMSi citrANi nirIkSya zalya dhvajAn gadAH sAyakAMcograrUpAn . asiM ca dIptaM paramAyudhaM ca zaGkha ca zubhaM svanavantamugram .
patAkinaM vajranipAtani : svanaM sitAzvayuktaM zubhatUNazobhitam . imaM samAsthAya rathaM stharSabhaM raNe haniSyAmyahamarjunaM balAt .
taM cenmRtyuH sarvaharo ' bhirakSet sadApramattaH samare pANDuputram . taM vA haniSyAmi raNe sametya yAsyAmi vA bhISmamukho yamAya .
yamavaruNakuberavAsavA vA yadi yugapatsagaNA mahAhave . jugupiSava ihaitya pANDavaM kimu bahunA saha tairjayAmi tam .
saMjaya uvAca staduta nizamyavacaH sa madrarAT . avahamadavapanya vIryavAn pratiSiSidhe ca jagAda cottaram .
zalya uvAca datirabhaso ' pyativAcamuktavAn . kva ca hi naravaro dhanaMjayaH kva panaraho puruSAdhamo bhavAn .
yadusadanamupendrapAlitaM tridhazamivAmararAjarakSitam . prasabhamatiriloDya ko haret puruSavarAvarajAmRte ' rjunAt .
tribhuvanavibhumIzvaraM ka iha pumAna bhavamAhvayed yudhi . mRgavadhakalahe Rte ' rjunAt surapativIryasamaprabhAvataH .
asurasuramahoragAn narAn garuDapizAcasayakSarAkSasAn . iSubhirajayadagnigauravAt svabhilaSitaM ca havirdadau jayaH .
smarasi nanu yadA parairhataH sa ca dhRtarASTrasuto ' pi mokSitaH . dinakarasadRzaiH zarottamairyudhA kuruSu bahUn vinihatya tAnarIn .
prathamamapi palAyite tvayi priyakalahA dhRtarASTrasUnavaH . smarasi nanu yadA pramocitAH khacaragaNAnavajitya pANDavaiH .
samuditabalavAhanAH punaH puruSavareNa jitAH stha gograhe . sagurugurusutAH sabhISmakAH kimu na jitaH sa tadA tvayA ' rjunaH .
stava nidhanAya suyuddhamadya vai . yadi na ripubhayAt palAyase samaragato ' dya hato ' si sUtaja .
saMjaya uvAca iti bahu paruSaM prabhASati pramanasi madrapatI ripustavam . bhRzamabhiruSitaH paraMtapaH kurupRtanApatirAha madrapam .
karNa uvAca bhavatu bhavatu ki vikatyase nanu mama tasya hi yuddhamudyatam . yadi sa jayati mAnihAhave tata idamastu sukasthitaM tava .
saMjaya uvAca evamastviti madreza uktvA nottaramuktavAn . yAhi zalyeti cApyenaM karNaH prAha yuyutsayA . sa rathaH prayayau zatrUzvetAzvaH zalyasArathiH . nighnannamitrAn samare tamo ghnan savitA yathA .
tataH prAyAt prItimAn vai rathena vaiyA Na zvetayujAtha karNaH . sa cAlokya dhvajinI pANDavAnAM dhanaMjayaM tvarayA paryapRcchat .
dhRtarASTra uvAca bahUni hi vicitrANi dvaisthAni sma saMjaya . pANDUnAM mAmakaiH sArdhamazrauSaM tava jalpataH .
na caiva mAmakaM kiMcit hRSTaM zaMsasi saMjaya . nityaM pANDusutAn hRSTAnabhagnAn samprazaMsasi .
vai jIyamAnAn vimanaso mAmakAn vigataujasaH . vadase saMyuge sUta diSTametanna saMzayaH .
saMjaya uvAca yathAzaktiM yathotsAhaM yuddhe ceSTanti tAvakAH . darzayAnAH paraM zaktyA pauruSaM puruSarSabha .
gaGgAyAH suranadyA svAdu bhUtvA yathodakam . mahodadherguNAbhyAsAllavaNatvaM nigacchati .
tathA tat pauruSaM rAjaMstAvakAnAM paraMtapa . prApya pANDusutAn vIrAn vyarthaM bhavati saMyuge .
ghaTamAnAn yathAzakti kurvANAn karma duSkaram . na doSeNa kuruzreSTha kauravAn gantumarhasi .
tavAparAdhAt sumahAn saputrasya vizAmpate . pRthivyAH prakSayo ghoro yamarASTravivardhanaH .
AtmadoSAt samutpannaM zocituM nArhase nRpa . na hi rakSanti rAjAna : sarvathA ' trApi jIvitam .
yuddhe sukRtinAM lokAnicchanto vasudhAdhipAH . camU vigAhya yudhyante nityaM svargaparAyaNAH .
pUrvAhne tu mahArAja prAvartata janakSayaH . taM tvamekamanA bhUtvA zRNu devAsuropamam .
Avantyau tu maheSvAsau mahAsenau mahAbalau . irAvantamabhiprekSya sameyAtAM raNotkaTau .
teSAM pravavRte yuddhaM sumahallomaharSaNam . irAvAMstu susaMkruddho bhrAtarau devarUpiNau . vivyAdha nizitaistUrNaM zaraiHsaMnataparvabhiH . tAvenaM pratyavidhyetAM samare citrayodhinau .
yudhyatAM hi tathA rAjan vizeSo na vyadRzyata . yatatAM zatrunAzAya kRtapratikRtaiSiNAm .
irAvAMstu tato rAjannanuvindasya sAyakaiH . caturabhizcaturo vAhAnanayad yamasAdanam .
bhallAbhyAM ca sutIkSNAbhyAM dhanuH ketuM ca mAriSa . ciccheda samare rAjastadadbhutamivAbhavat .
tyaktvAnuvindo ' tha rathaM vindasya rathamAsthitaH . dhanurgRhItvA paramaM bhArasAdhanamuttamam .
tAvekastho raNe vIrAvAvantyau rathinAM varau . zarAn mumugratustUrNamirAvati mahAtmani .
tAbhyAM muktA mahAvegAH zarAH kAJcanabhUSaNAH . divAkarapathaM prApya cchAdayAmAsurambaram .
irAvAMstu raNe kruddho bhrAtarau tau mahArathau . vavarSa zaravarSeNa sArathiM cApyapAtayat .
tasmiMstu patite bhUmau gatasattve tu sArathau ! rathaH pradudrAva dizaH samudghAntahayastataH .
tau sa jitvA mahArAja nAgarAjasutAsutaH . pauruSaM khyApayaMstUrNaM vyadhamat tava vAhinIm .
sA vadhyamAnA samare dhArtarASTrI mahAcamUH . vegAn bahuvidhAMzcakre viSaM pItveva mAnavaH .
haiDimbo rAkSasendrastu bhagadattaM samAdravat . rathenAdityavarNena sadhvajena mahAbalaH .
tataH prAgjyotiSo rAjA nAgarAja samAsthitaH . yathA vajradharaH pUrvaM saMgrAme tArakAmaye .
tatra devAH sagandharvA RSayazca samAgatAH . vizeSaM na sma vividuIDimbabhagadattayoH .
yathA surapatiH zakrastrAsayAmAsa dAnavAn . tathaiva samare rAjA drAvayAmAsa pANDavAn .
tena vidrAvyamANAste pANDavAH sarvato dizam . trAtAraM nAbhyagacchantaH sveSvanIkeSu bhArata .
bhaimaseni rathasthaM tu tatrApazyAma bhArata . zeSA vimanaso bhUtvA prAdravanta mahArathAH .
nivRtteSu tu pANDUnAM punaH sainyeSu bhArata . AsIniSThAnakA ghorastata sainyasya saMyuge .
ghaTotkacastato rAjan bhagadatta mahAraNe . zaraiH pracchAdayAmAsa meruM girimivAmbudaH .
nihatya tAzarAn rAjA rAkSasasya dhanuzcyutAn . bhaimaseni raNe tUrNaM sarvamarmasvatADayat .
sa tADyamAno bahubhiH zaraiH saMnataparvabhiH . na vivyathe rAkSasendro bhidyamAna ivAcalaH .
tasya prAgjyotiSaH kruddhastomarAMzca caturdaza . preSayAmAsa samare tAzciccheda sa rAkSasaH .
sa tAMzchittvA mahAbAhustomarAn nizitaiH zaraiH . bhagadattaM ca vivyAdha saptatyA kaGkapatribhiH .
tataH prAgjyotiSo rAjA prahasanniva bhArata . tasyAzvAMzcaturaH saMkhye pAtayAmAsa sAyakaiH .
sa hatAzve rathe tiSThan rAkSasendraH pratApavAn . zaktiM cikSepa vegena prAgjyotiSagajaM prati .
tAmApatantI sahasA hemadaNDAM suveginIm . tridhA ciccheda nRpatiH sA vyakIryata medinIm .
zaktiM vinihatAM dRSTvA haiDimbaH prAdravad bhayAt . yathendrasya raNAt pUrvaM namucirdaityasattamaH .
taM vijitya raNe zUraM vikrAntaM khyAtapauruSam . ajeyaM samare vIraM yamena varuNena ca .
pANDavIM samare senAM sammamarda sa kuJjaraH . yathA vanagajo rAjan mRnazcarati padminIm .
madrezvarastu samare yamAbhyAM samasajjata . svastrIyau chAdayAMcakre zarauH pANDunandanau .
sahadevastu samare mAtulaM dRzya saMgatam . avArayaccharaugheNa megho yadvad divAkaram .
chAdyamAnaH zaraugheNa hRSTarUpataro ' bhavat . tayozcApyabhavat prItiratulA mAtRkAraNAt .
tataH prahasya samare nakulasya mahArathaH . azvAMzca caturo rAMjazcaturbhiH sAyakottamaiH . preSayAmAsa samare yamasya sadanaM prati . hatAzvAt tu rathAt tUrNamavaplutya mahArathaH .
Aruroha tato yAnaM bhrAtureva yazasvinaH . ekasthau tu raNe zUro dRDhe vikSipya kArmukau .
madrarAjarathaM tUrNaM chAdayAmAsatuH kSaNAt . sa chAdyamAno bahubhiH zaraiH saMnataparvabhiH .
svastrIyAbhyAM naravyAghro nAkampata yathA ' calaH . prahasanniva tAM cApi zastravRSTiM jaghAna ha .
sahadevastataH kruddhaH zaramudgRhya vIryavAn . padrarAjamabhiprekSya preSayAmAsa bhArata . .
sa zaraH preSitastena garuDAnilavegavAn . madrarAjaM vinirbhidya nipapAta mahItale .
sa gADhaviddho vyathito rathopasthe mahArathaH . niSasAda mahArAja kazmalaM ca jagAma ha .
taM visaMjJaM nipatitaM sUtaH samprekSya saMyuge . apovAha rathenAjau yamAbhyAmabhipIDitam .
dRSTvA madrezvararathaM dhArtarASTrAH parAGmukham . sarve vimanaso bhUtvA nedamastItyacintayan .
nirjitya mAtulaM saMkhye mAdrIputrau mahArathau . dadhmaturmuditau zaGkhau siMhanAdaM ca nedatuH .
abhidudruvaturhaSTau tava sainyaM vizAmpate . yathA daityacamUM rAjannindropendrAvivAmarau .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataH pravezanaM tasyAM cakre rAjA yudhiSThiraH . ayutaM bhojayitvA tu brAhmaNAnAM narAdhipaH . sAjyena payasenaiva madhunA mizritena ca . kRsareNAtha jIvantyA haviSyeNa ca sarvazaH .
bhakSyaprakArairvividhaiH phalaizcApi tathA nRpa . coSyaizca vividhai rAjan peyaizca bahuvistaraiH . ahataizcaiva vAsobhirmAlyairuccAvacairapi . tarpayAmAsa viprendrAn nAnAdigbhyaH samAgatAn .
dadau tebhyaH sahasrANi gavAM pratyekazaH punaH . puNyAhaghoSastatrAsIda divaspRgiva bhArata .
vAditrairvividhairdivyairgandhairuccAvacairapi . pUjayitvA kuruzreSTho daivatAni nivezya ca .
tatra mallA naTA jhallA : sUtA vaitAlikAstathA . upatasthurmahAtmAnaM dharmaputraM yudhiSThiram .
tathA sa kRtvA pUjAM tAM bhrAtRbhiH saha pANDavaH . tasyAM sabhAyAM ramyAyAM reme zakro yathA divi .
sabhAyAmRSayastasyAM pANDavaiH saha Asate . AsAMcakrunarendrAzca nAnAdezasamAgatAH .
asito devalaH satyaH sarpirmAlI mahAzirAH . arvAvasuH sumitrazca maitreyaH zunako baliH . bako dAlbhyaH sthUlazirAH kRSNadvaipAyanaH zukaH . sumantujaiminiH pailo vyAsaziSyAstathA vayam . tittiriryAjJavalkyazca sasuto lomaharSaNaH . apsuhomyazca dhaumyazca aNImANDavyakauzikau . dAmoSNISastraibalizca parNAdo ghaTajAnukaH . mauJjAyano vAyubhakSaH pArAzaryazca sArikaH . balivAkaH sinIvAkaH satyapAlaH kRtazramaH . jAtUkarNa : zikhAvAMzca AlambaH pArijAtakaH . parvatazca mahAbhAgo mArkaNDeyo mahAmuniH . pavitrapANi : sAvarNo bhAlukirgAlavastathA . jaGghAbandhuzca raibhyazca kopavegastathA bhRguH . haribabhruzca kauNDinyo babhrumAlI sanAtanaH . kAkSIvAnauzijazcaiva nAciketo ' tha gautamaH . paiGgayo varAhaH zunakaH zANDilyazca mahAtapAH . kukkuro veNujaGgho ' tha kAlApaH kadda eva ca . munayo dharmavidvAMso dhRtAtmAno jitendriyAH .
ete cAnye ca bahavo vedavedAGgapAragAH . upAsate mahAtmAnaM sabhAyAmRSisattamAH . kathayantaH kathAH puNyA dharmajJA zucayo ' malAH . tathaiva kSatriyazreSThA dharmarAjamupAsate .
zrImAn mahAtmA dharmAtmA muJjaketurvivardhanaH . saMgrAmajid dumukhazca ugrasenazca vIryavAn . kakSasenaH kSitipatiH kSemakazcAparAjitaH . kambojarAjaH kamaddaH kampanazca mahAbalaH . satataM kampayAmAsa yavanAneka eva yaH . balapauruSasampannAn kRtAstrAnamitaujasaH . yathAsurAn kAlakeyAn devo vajradharAstathA .
jaTAsuro madrakANAM ca rAjA kuntiH pulindazca kirAtarAjaH . tathA ' ' GgavAGgau saha puNDrakeNa pANDyoDrarAjau ca sahAndhrakeNa . aGgo vaGgaH sumitrazca zaibyazcAmitrakarzanaH . kirAtarAjaH sumanA yavanAdhipatistathA . cANUro devarAtazca bhojo bhImarathazca yaH . zrutAyudhazca kAliGgo jayasenazca mAgadhaH . sukarmA cekitAnazca puszvAmitrakarzanaH . ketumAn vasudAnazca vaideho ' tha kRtakSaNaH . sudharmA cAniruddhazca zrutAyuzca mahAbalaH . anUparAjo durdharSaH kramajicca sudarzanaH . zizupAlaH sahasuta : karUSAdhipatistathA . vRSNInAM caiva durdharSAH kumArA devarUpiNaH . Ahuko vipRthuzcaiva gadaH sAraNa eva ca . akrUraH kRtavarmA ca satyakazca zineH sutaH . bhISmako ' thAkRtizcaiva dhumatsenazca vIryavAn . kekayAzca maheSvAsA yajJasenazca saumakiH .
ketumAn vasumAMzcaiva kRtAstrazca mahAbalaH . ete cAnye ca bahavaH kSatriyA mukhyasammatAH . upAsate sabhAyAM sma kuntIputraM yudhiSThiram . arjunaM ye ca saMzritya rAjaputrA mahAbalAH . azikSanta dhanurvedaM rauravAjinavAsasaH . tatraiva zikSitA rAjan kumArA vRSNinandanAH .
raukmiNeyazca sAmbazca yuyudhAnazca sAtyakiH . sudharmA cAniruddhazca zaibyazca narapuGgavaH .
ete cAnye ca bahavo rAjAnaH pRthivIpate . dhanaMjayasakhA cAtra nityamAste sma tumburuH . upAsate mahAtmAnamAsInaM saptaviMzatiH . citrasenaH sahAmAtyo gandharvApsarasastathA . gItavAditrakuzalAH sAmyatAlavizAradAH . pramANe ' tha laye sthAne kinnarAH kRtanizramAH . saMcoditAstumburuNA gandharvasahitAstadA . gAyanti divyatAnaiste yathAnyAyaM manasvinaH . pANDuputrAnRSIMzcaiva ramayanta upAsate . tasyAM sabhAyAmAsInAH suvratAH satyasaMgarAH . divIva devA brahmANaM yudhiSThiramupAsate .
dhRtarASTra uvAca dRSTvA me nihatAn putrAn bahUnekena saMjaya . bhISmo droNaH kRpazcaiva kimakurvata saMyuge . . .
ahanyahani me putrAH kSayaM gacchanti saMjaya . manye ' haM sarvathA sUta daivenopahatA bhRzam .
yatra me tanayA : jIyante na jayanatyuta . yatra bhISmasya droNasya kRpasya ca mahAtmanaH . saumadattezca vIrasya bhagadattasya cobhayoH . azvatthAmnastathA tAta zUrANAmanivartinAm . anyeSAM caiva zUrANAM madhyagAstanayA mama . yadahanyanta saMgrAme kimanyad bhAgadheyataH .
na hi duryodhano mandaH purA proktamabudhyata . vAryamANo mayA tAta bhISmeNa vidureNa ca .
gAndhAryA caiva durmedhAH satataM hitakAmyayA . nAbudhyata purA mohAt tasya prAptamidaM phalam .
yad bhImasenaH samare putrAn mama vicetasaH . ahanyahani saMkruddho nayate yamasAdanam .
saMjaya uvAca idaM tat samanuprAptaM kSatturvacanamuttamam . na buddhavAnasi vibho procyamAnaM hitaM tadA .
nivAraya sutAn dyUtAt pANDavAn mA duheti ca . suhRdAM hitakAmAnAM bruvatAM tat tadeva ca .
na zuzrUSasi tad vAkyaM martyaH pathyamivauSadham . tadeva tvAmanuprAptaM vacanaM sAdhubhASitam .
viduradroNabhISmANAM tathAnyeSAM hitaiSiNAm . akRtvA vacanaM pathyaM kSayaM gacchanti kauravAH .
tadetat samanuprAptaM pUrvameva vizAmpate . tasmAt tvaM zRNu tattvena yathA yuddhamavartata .
madhyAhne sumahAraudraH saMgrAmaH samapadyata . lokakSayakaro rAjastanme nigadataH zRNu . .
tataH sarvANi sainyAni dharmaputrasya zAsanAt . saMrabdhAnyabhyavartanta bhISmameva jighAMsayA .
dhRSTadyumnaH zikhaNDI ca sAtyakizca mahArathataH . yuktAnIkA mahArAja bhISmameva samabhyayuH .
virATo drupadazcaiva sahitAH sarvasomakaiH . abhyadravanta saMgrAme bhISmameva mahAratham .
kekayA dhRSTaketuzca kuntibhojazca daMzitaH . yuktAnIkA mahArAja bhISmameva samabhyayuH .
arjuno draupadeyAzca cekitAnazca vIryavAn . duryodhanasamAdiSTAn rAjJaH sarvAn samabhyayuH .
abhimanyustathA zUro haiDimbazca mahArathaH . bhImasenazca saMkruddhaste ' bhyadhAvanta kauravAn .
tridhAbhUtairavadhyanta pANDavaiH kauravA yudhi . tathaiva kauravai rAjannavadhyanta pare raNe .
droNastu rathinaH zreSThAn somakAn saMjayaiH saha . abhyadhAvata saMkruddhaH preSayiSyan yamakSayam .
tatrAkrando mahAnAsIt suMjayAnAM mahAtmanAm . vadhyatAM samare rAjan bhAradvAjena dhanvinA .
droNena nihatAstatra kSatriyA bahavo raNe . viceSTanto hyadRzyanta vyAdhikliSTA narA iva .
kUjatAM krandatAM caiva rastanatAM caiva bhArata . anizaM zuzruvai zabdaH kSutkliSTAnAM nRNAmiva .
tathaiva kauraveyANAM bhImaseno mahAbalaH . cakAra kadanaM ghoraM kruddhaH kAla ivAparaH .
vadhyatAM tatra sainyAnAmanyonyena mahAraNe . prAvartata nadI ghorA rudhiraughapravAhinI .
sa saMgrAmo mahArAja ghorarUpo ' bhavanmahAn . kurUNAM pANDavAnAM ca yamarASTravivardhanaH .
tato bhImo raNe kruddho rabhasazca vizeSataH . gajAnIkaM samAsAdya preSayAmAsa mRtyave .
tatra bhArata bhImena nArAjAbhihatA gajAH . peturneduzca seduzca disazca paribabhramuH .
chinnahastA mahAnAgAzchinnagAtrAzca mAriSa . krauJcavad vyanadan bhItAH pRthivImadhizerate .
nakulaH sahadevazca hayAnIkamabhidrutau . te hayAH kAJcanApIDA rukmabhANDaparicchadAH .
vadhyamAnA vyadRzyanta zatazo ' tha sahasrazaH . patidbhisturagai rAjan samAstIryata medinI .
nirjikaizca zvasaddhizca kUjadbhizca gatAsubhiH . hayairbabhau narazreSTha nAnArUpadharairdharA .
arjunena hataiH saMkhye tathA bhArata rAjabhiH . prababhau vasudhA ghorA tatra tatra vizAmpate .
sthairbhagnairdhvajaizchinnainikRttaizca mahAyudhaiH . cAmarairvyajanaizcaiva chatraizca sumahAprabhaiH .
hArairniSkaiH sakeyUraiH zirobhizca sakuNDalaiH . uSNISairapaviddhaizca patAkAbhizca sarvazaH .
anukaSaiH zubhai rAjan yoktraizcaiva sarazmibhiH . saMkIrNA vasudhA bhAti vasante kusumairiva .
evameSa kSayo vRttaH pANDUnAmapi bhArata . kruddha zAntanave bhISme droNe ca rathasattame .
azvatthAmni kRpe caiva tathaiva kRtavarmaNi . tathetareSu kruddheSu tAvakAnAmapi kSayaH .
vyAsa uvAca dhRtarASTra mahAprAjJa nibodha vacanaM mama . vakSyAmi tvAM kauravANAM sarveSAM hitamuttamam .
na me priyaM mahAbAho yad gatAH pANDavA vanam . nikRtyA nikRtAzcaiva duryodhanapurogamaiH .
te smarantaH pariklezAn varSe pUrNe trayodaze . vimokSyanti viSaM kruddhAH kauraveyeSu bhArata .
tadayaM kiM nu pApAtmA tava putraH sumandadhI . pANDavAn nityasaMkruddho rAjyahetorjighAMsati .
vAryatAM sAdhvayaM mUDhaH zamaM gacchatu te sutaH . vanasthAMstAnayaM hantumicchan prANAn vimokSyati .
yathA hi vidura : prAjJo yathA bhISmo yathA vayam . yathA kRpazca droNazca tathA sAdhurbhavAnapi .
vigraho hi mahAprAjJa svajanena vigarhitaH . adharmyamayazasyaM ca mA rAjan pratipadyatAm .
samIkSA yAdRzI hyasya pANDavAn prati bhArata . upekSyamANA sa rAjan mahAntamanayaM spRzet .
athavAyaM sumandAtmA vanaM gacchatu te sutaH . pANDaivaH sahito rAjanneka evAsahAyavAn . tataH saMsargajaH snehaH putrasya tava pANDavaiH . yadi syAt kRtakAryo ' dya bhavestvaM manujezvara . .
athavA jAyamAnasya yacchIlamanujAyate . zrUyate tanmahArAja nAmRtasyApasarpati . kathaM vA manyate bhISmo droNo ' tha viduro ' pi vA . bhavAn vAtra kSamaM kArya purA vo ' rtho ' bhivardhate .
vaizampAyana uvAca bhImasenavacaH zrutvA kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . niHzvasya puruSavyAghraH sampradadhyau paraMtapaH . zrutA me rAjadharmAzca varNAnAM ca vinizcayAH . AyatyAM ca tadAtve ca yaH pazyati sa pazyati .
dharmasya jAnamAno ' haM gatimavayAM sudurvidAm . kathaM balAt kariSyAmi meroriva vimardanam .
sa muhUrtamivadhyAtvA vinizcatyetikRtyatAm . bhImasenamidaM vAkyamapadAntaramabravIt .
yudhiSThira uvAca evametanmahAbAho yathA vadasi bhArata . idamanyat samAdatsva vAcyaM me vAkyakovida .
mahApApAni karmANi yAni kevalasAhasAt . Arabhyante bhImasena vyathante tAni bhArata .
samuntrite suvikrAnte sukRte suvicArite . sidhyantyarthA mahAbAho daivaM cAtra pradakSiNam .
yat tu kevacApalyAd baladapotthitaH svayam . ArabdhavyamidaM kAryaM manyase zRNu tatra me .
bhUrizravAH zalazcaiva jalasaMdhazca vIryavAn . bhISmo droNazca karNazca droNaputrazca vIryavAn . dhArtarASTrA durAdharSA duryodhanapurogamAH . sarva eva kRtAstrAzca satataM cAtatAyinaH . rAjAnaH pArthivAzcaiva ye ' smAbhirupatApitAH . saMzritAH kauravaM pakSaM jAtasnehAzca taM prati .
duryodhanahite yuktA na tathAsmAsu bhArata . pUrNakozA balopetAH prayatiSyanti saMgare .
sarve kauravasainyasya saputrAmAtyasainikAH . saMvibhaktA hi mAtrAbhirbhogairapi ca sarvazaH .
duryodhanena te vIrA mAnitAzca vizeSataH . prANAMstyakSyanti saMgrAme iti me nizcitA matiH .
samA yadyapi bhISmasya vRttirasmAsu teSu ca . droNasya ca mahAbAho kRpasya ca mahAtmanaH . avazyaM rAjapiNDastairnirvezya iti me matiH . tasmAt tyakSyanti saMgrAme prANAnapi sudustyajAn .
sarve divyAstravidvAMsaH sarvedharmaparAyaNAH . ajeyAzceti me buddhirapi devaiH savAsavaiH .
amarSI nityasaMrabdhastatra karNo mahArathaH . sarvAstravidanAdhRSyo hyabhedyakavacAvRtaH .
anirjitya raNe sarvAnetAn puruSasattamAn . azakyo hyasahAyena hantuM duryodhanastvayA .
na nidrAmadhigacchAmi cintayAno vRkodara . atisarvAndhanuAhAn sUtaputrasya lAghavam .
vaizampAyana uvAca etad vacanamAjJAya bhImaseno ' tyamarSaNaH . babhUva vimanAstrasto na caivovAca kiMcana .
tayoH saMvadatorevaM tadA pANDavayordvayoH . AjagAma mahAyogI vyAsa : satyavatIsutaH .
so ' bhigamya yathAnyAyaM pANDavaiH pratipUjitaH . yudhiSThiramidaM vAkyamuvAca vadatAM varaH .
vyAsa uvAca yudhiSThira mahAbAho vedmi te hRdayasthitam . manISayA tataH kSipramAgato ' smi nararSabha .
bhISmAd droNAt kRpAt karNAd droNa putrAcca bhArata . duryodhanAnnRpasutAt tathA duHzAsanAdapi . yat te bhayamamitraghna hRdi samparivartate . tat te ' haM nAzayiSyAmi vidhidRSTena karmaNA .
tacchutvAdhRtimAsthAya karmaNA pratipAdaya . pratipAdya tu rAjendra tataH kSipraM jvaraM jahi .
tata ekAntamunnIya pArAzaryo yudhiSThirama . abravIdupapannArthamidaM vAkyavizAradaH .
zreyasaste paraH kAlaH prApto bharatasattama . yenAbhibhavitA zatrUn raNe pArthodhanurdharaH .
gRhANemAM mayA proktAM siddhiM mUrtimatImiva . vidyAM pratismRti nAma prapannAya bravImi te .
yAmavApya mahAbAhurarjunaH sAdhayiSyati . astrahetormahendraM ca rudraM caivAbhigacchatu . varuNaM ca kuberaM cadharmarAjaM ca pANDava . zakto hyeSa surAn draSTuM tapasA vikrameNa ca .
RSireSa mahAtejA nArAyaNasahAyavAn . purANaH zAzvato devastvajeyI jiSNuracyutaH . astrANIndrAcca rudrAcca lokapAlebhya eva ca . samAdAya mahAbAhurmahat karma kariSyati .
vanAdasmAcca kaunteya vanamanyad vicintyatAm . nivAsArthAya yad yuktaM bhaved vaH pRthivIpate .
ekatra ciravAso hi na prItijanano bhavet . tApasAnAM ca sarveSAM bhavedudvegakArakaH .
mRgANAmupayogazca vIrudoSadhisaMkSayaH . bibharSi ca bahUn viprAn vedavedAGgapAragAn .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktvA prapannAya zucaye bhagavAn prabhuH . provAca lokatattvajJo yogI vidyAmanuttamAm . dharmarAjAyadhImAn sa vyAsaH satyavatIsutaH . anujJAya ca kaunteyaM tatraivAntaradhIyata .
yudhiSThirastudharmAtmA tad brahma manasA yataH . dhArayAmAsa medhAvI kAle kAle sadAbhyasan .
sa vyAsavAkyamudito banAd dvaitavanAt tataH . yayau sarasvatIkUle kAmyakaM nAma kAnanam .
tamanvayurmahArAja zikSAkSaravizAradAH . brAhmaNAstapasA yuktA devendramRSayo yathA .
tataH kAmyakamAsAdya punaste bharatarSabha . nyavizanta mahAtmAnaH sAmAtyAH saparicchadAH .
tatra te nyavasan rAjan kiMcit kAlaM manasvinaH . dhanurvedaparA vIrAH zRNvanto vedamuttamam .
caranto mRgayAM nityaM zuddhairbANairmRgArthinaH . pitRdaivataviprebhyo nirvapanto yathAvidhi .
brAhANa uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . kArtavIryasya saMvAdaM samudrasya ca bhAvini .
kArtavIryArjuno nAma rAjA bAhusahasravAn . yena sAgaraparyantA dhanuSA nirjitA mahI .
sa kadAcit samudrAnte vicaran baladarpitaH . avAkirazarazataiH samudramiti naH zrutam .
taM samudro namaskRtya kRtAJjaliruvAca hA mA muJca vIra nArAcAn brUhi kiM karavANi te .
madAzrayANi bhUtAni tvadvisRSTairmaheSubhiH . vadhyante rAjazArdUla tebhyo dehyabhayaM vibho .
arjuna uvAca matsamo yadi saMgrAme zarAsanadharaH kvacit . vidyate taM samAcakSva yaH samAsIta mAM mRdhe .
samudra uvAca maharSirjamadagniste yadi rAjan parizrutaH . tasya putrastavAtithyaM yathAvat kartumarhati . .
tataH sa rAjA prayayau krodhena mahatA vRtaH . sa tamAzramamAgamya rAmamevAnvapadyata .
sa rAmapratikUlAni cakAra saha bandhubhiH . AyAsaM janayAmAsa rAmasya ca mahAtmanaH .
tatastejaH prajajvAla rAmasyAmitatejasaH . pradahan ripusainyAni tadA kamalalocane . .
tataH parazumAdAya sa taM bAhusahasriNam . ciccheda sahasA rAmo bahuzAkhamiva dumam .
taM hataM patitaM dRSTvA sametAH sarvabAndhavAH . asInAdAya zaktIzca bhArgavaM paryadhAvayan .
rAmo ' pi dhanurAdAya rathamAruhya satvaraH . visRjazaravarSANi vyadhamat pArthivaM balam .
tatastu kSatriyAH kecijjAmadagnyabhayArditAH . vivizurgiridurgANi mRgAH siMhArditA iva .
teSAM svavihitaM karma tadbhayAnnAnutiSThatAm . prajA vRSalatA prAptA brAhmaNAnAmadarzanAt .
evaM te draviDA ' ' bhIrA : puNDrAzca zabaraiH saha . vRSalatvaM parigatA vyutthAnAt kSatradharmiNaH .
tatazca hatavIrAsu kSatriyAsu punaH punaH . dvijairutpAditaM kSatraM jAmadagnyo nyakRntata .
ekaviMzatimedhAnte rAmaM vAgazarIriNI . divyA provAca madhurA sarvalokaparizrutA . rAma rAma nivartasva ke guNaM tAta pazyasi . kSatrabadhUnimAn prANairviprayojya punaH punaH .
tathaiva taM mahAtmAnamRcIkapramukhAstadA . pitAmahA mahAbhAga nivartasvetyathAbruvan .
piturvadhamamRSyaMstu rAmaH provAca tAnRSIn . nArhantIha bhavanto mAM nivArayitumityuta .
pitara UcuH nArhase kSatrabandhuMstvaM nihantuM jayatAM varA neha yuktaM tvayA hantuM brAhmaNena satA nRpAn .
janamejaya uvAca kathaM samabhavad dyUtaM bhrAtRNAM tanmahAtyayam . yatra tad vyasanaM prAptaM pANDavairma pitAmahaiH .
ke ca tatra sabhAstArA rAjAno brahmavittama . ke cainamanvamodanta ke cainaM pratyaSedhayan .
vistareNaitadicchAmi kathyamAnaM tvayA dvijA mUlaM hyetad vinAzasya pRthivyA dvijasattama .
sautiruvAca evamuktastato rAjA vyAsaziSyaH pratApavAn . AcacakSe ' tha yad vRttaM tat sarvaM vedatattvavit .
vaizampAyana uvAca zRNu me vistareNemAM kathAM bhAratasattama . bhUya eva mahArAja yadi te zravaNe matiH .
vidurasya matiM jJAtvA dhRtarASTro ' mbikAsutaH . duryodhanamidaM vAkyamuvAca vijane punaH .
alaM dyUtena gAndhAre viduro na prazaMsati . na hyasau sumahAbuddhirahitaM no vadiSyati .
hitaM hi paramaM manye viduro yat prabhASate . kriyatAM putra tat sarvametanmanye hitaM tava .
devarSirvAsavagururdevarAjAya dhImate . yat prAha zAstraM bhagavAn bRhaspatirudAradhIH . tad veda viduraH sarvaM sarahasyaM mahAkaviH .
sthitastu vacane tasya sadAhamapi putrakA viduro vApi medhAvI kurUNAM pravaro mataH .
uddhavo vA mahAbuddhivRSNInAmarcito nRpa . tadalaM putra dyUtena chUte bhedo hi dRzyate .
bhede vinAzo rAjyasya tat putra parivarjaya . pitrA mAtrA ca putrasya yad vai kAryaM paraM smRtam . prAptastvamasi tannAma pitRpaitAmahaM padam . adhItavAn kRtI zAstre lAlitaH satataM gRhe .
bhrAtRjyeSThaH sthito rAjye vindase kiM na zobhanam . pRthagjanairalabhyaM yad bhojanAcchAdanaM param .
tat prApto ' si mahAbAho kasmAcchocasi putrakA sphItaM rASTraM mahAbAho pitRpaitAmahaM mahat . nityamAjJApayan bhAsi divi devezvaro yathA . tasya te viditaprajJa zokamUlamidaM katham . samutthitaM duHkhakaraM yanme zaMsitumarhasi .
duryodhana uvAca aznAmyAcchAdayAmIti prapazyan pApapUruSaH . nAmarSaM kurute yastu puruSaH so ' dhamaH smRtaH .
na mAM prINAti rAjendra lakSmI : sAdhAraNI vibho . jvalitAmeva kaunteye zriyaM dRSTvA ca vivyathe .
sarvAM ca pRthivIM caiva yudhiSThiravazAnugAm . sthiro ' smi yo ' haM jIvAmi duHkhAdetad bravImi te . .
AvarjitA ivAbhAnti nIpAzcitrakakaukurAH . kAraskArA lohajaGghA yudhiSThiranivezane .
himavatsAgarAnUpAH sarve ratnAkarAstathA . antyAH sarve paryudastA yudhiSThiranivezane .
jyeSTho ' yamiti mAM matvA zreSThazceti vizAmpate . yudhiSThireNa satkRtya yukto ratnaparigrahe .
upasthitAnAM ratnAnAM zreSThAnAmarghahAriNAm . nAdRzyata paraH pAro nAparastatra bhArata .
na me hastaH samabhavad vasu tat pratigRhaNataH . atiSThanta mayi zrAnte gRhya dUrAhRtaM vasu .
kRtAM vindusaroratnairmayena sphATikacchadAm . apazyaM nalinI pUrNAmudakasyeva bhArata .
vastramutkarSati mayi prAhasat sa vRkodaraH . zatrorRddhivizeSeNa vimUDhaM ratnavarjitam .
tatra sma yadi zaktaH syAM pAtaye ' haM vRkodaram . yadi kuryAM samArambhaM bhImaM hantuM narAdhipa . .
zizupAla ivAsmAkaM gatiH syAnnAtra saMzayaH . sapanenAvahAso me sa mAM dahati bhArata .
punazca tAdRzImeva vApI jalajazAlinIm . matvA zilAsamAM toye patito ' smi narAdhipa .
tatra mAM prAhasat kRSNaH pArthena saha susvaram . draupadI ca saha strIbhirvyathayantI mano mama .
klinnavastrasya tu jale kiMkarA rAjanoditAH . dadurvAsAMsi me ' nyAni tacca duHkhaM paraM mama .
pralambhaM ca zRNuSvAnyad vadato me narAdhipa . advAreNa vinirgacchan dvArasaMsthAnarUpiNA . abhihatya zilAM bhUyo lalATenAsmi vikSataH . tatra mAM yamajau dUrAdAlokyAbhihataM tadA . bAhubhiH parigRhNItAM zocantau sahitAvubhau .
uvAca sahadevastu tatra mAM vismayanniva . idaM dvAramito gaccha rAjaniti punaH punaH .
bhImasenena tatrokto dhRtarASTAtmajeti ca . sambodhya prahasitvA ca ito dvAraM narAdhipa .
nAmadheyAni ratnAnAM purastAnna zrutAni me . yAni dRSTAni me tasyAM manastapati tacca me .
vaizampAyana uvAca zrutvA tu rAjA rAjarSerindradyumnasya tat tathA . mArkaNDeyAnmahAbhAgAt svargasya pratipAdanam . yudhiSThiro mahArAja papraccha bharatarSabha . mArkaNDeyaM tapovRddhaM dIrghAyuSamakalmaSam .
viditAstava dharmajJa devadAnavarAkSasAH . rAjavaMzAzca vividhA RSivaMzAzca zAzvataH .
na te ' styaviditaM kiJcidasmaॅilloke dvijottam kathAM vetsi mune divyAM manuSyoragarakSasAm . devagandharvayakSANAM kinnarApsarasAM tathA .
idamicchAmyahaM zrotuM tattvena dvijasattama . kuvalAzva iti khyAta ikSvAkuraparAjitaH . kathaM nAmaviparyAsAd dhundhumAratvamAgataH .
etadicchAmi tattvena jJAtuM bhArgavasattama . viparyastaM yathA nAma kuvalAzvasya dhImataH .
vaizampAyana uvAca yudhiSThireNaivamukto mArkaNDeyo mahAmuniH . dhaundhumAramupAkhyAnaM kathayAmAsa bhArata .
mArkaNDeya uvAca hanta te kathayiSyAmi zRNu rAjan yudhiSThira . dharmiSThamidamAkhyAnaM dhundhumArasya tacchRNu .
yathA sa rAjA ikSvAkuH kuvalAzvo mahIpatiH . dhundhumAratvamagamat tacchRNuSva mahIpate .
maharSirvizrutastAta uttaGka iti bhArata . marudhanvasu ramyeSu Azramastasya kaurava .
uttaGkastu mahArAja tapo ' tapyat suduzcaram . ArirAdhayiSurviSNuM bahUn varSagaNAn vibhuH .
tasya prItaH sa bhagavAn sAkSAd darzanameyivAn . dRSTvaiva carSiH prahvastaM tuSTAva vividhaiH stavaiH .
uttaGkaM uvAca tvayA devA prajAH sarvAH sasurAsuramAnavAH . sthAvarANi ca bhUtAni jaGgamAni tathaiva ca . .
brahma vedAzca vedyaM ca tvayA sRSTaM mahAdyute . ziraste gaganaM deva netre zazidivAkarau .
niHzvAsaH pavanazcApi tejo ' gnizca tavAcyuta . bAhavaste dizaH sarvAH kukSizcApi mahArNavaH .
UrU te parvatA deva khaM nAbhirmadhusUdana . pAdau te pRthivI devI romANyoSadhayastathA .
indrasomAgnivaruNA devAsuramahoragAH . prahvAstvAmupatiSThanti stuvanto vividhaiH stavaiH .
tvayA vyAptAni sarvANi bhUtAni bhuvanezvara . yoginaH sumahAvIryAH stuvanti tvAM maharSayaH .
tvayi tuSTe jagat svAsthyaM tvayi kruddha mahad bhayam . bhayAnAmapanetAsi tvamekaH puruSottama . .
devAnAM mAnuSANAM ca sarvabhUtasukhAvahaH . tribhirvikramaNairdeva trayo lokAstvayA hRtAH .
asurANAM samRddhAnAM vinAzazca tvayA kRtaH . tava vikramaNairdevA nirvANamagaman param .
parAbhUtAzca daityendrAstvayi kruddhe mahAdyute . tvaM hi kartA vikartA ca bhUtAnAmiha sarvazaH . ArAdhayitvA tvAM devAH sukhamedhanti sarvazaH .
evaM stuto hRSIkeza uttaGkena mahAtmanA . uttaGkamabravId viSNuH prItaste ' haM varaM vRNu .
uttaGka uvAca paryApto me varo hyeSa yadahaM dRSTavAn harim . puruSaM zAzvataM divyaM sraSTAraM jagataH prabhum .
viSNuruvAca prItaste ' hamalaulyena bhaktyA tava ca sattama . avazyaM hi tvayA brahman matto cAhyo varo dvija .
mArkaNDeya uvAca evaM sa chandyamAnastu vareNa hariNA tadA . uttaGkaH prAJjalirvave varaM bharatasattama .
yadi me bhagavan prItaH puNDarIkanibhekSaNa . dharme satye dame caiva buddhirbhavatu me sadA . abhyAsazca bhaved bhaktyA tvayi nityaM mamezvara .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca sarvametaddhi bhavitA matprasAdAt tava dvija . pratibhAsyati yogazca yena yukto divaukasAm . trayANAmapi lokAnAM mahat kAryaM kariSyasi .
utsAdanArthaM lokAnAM dhundhurnAma mahAsuraH . tapasyati tapo ghoraM zRNu yastaM haniSyati .
rAjA hi vIryavAMstAta ikSvAkuraparAjitaH . bRhadazva iti khyAto bhaviSyati mahIpatiH . tasya putraH zucirdAntaH kuvalAzva iti zrutaH .
sa yogabalamAsthAya mAmakaM pArthivottamaH . zAsanAt tava viprarSe dhundhumAro bhaviSyati . evamuktvA tu taM vipraM viSNurantaradhIyata .
mArkaNDeya uvAca evamuktaH sa viprastu dharmavyAdhena bhArata . kathAmakathayad bhUyo manasaH prItivadhanIm .
brAhmaNa uvAca mahAbhUtAni yAnyAhuH paJca dharmabhRtAM vara . ekaikasya guNAn samyak paJcAnAmapi me vada .
