zarmArthaM te vizeSaNa sAnubandhasya bhArata . mahAprAjJakule jAtaH sAdhvetat kartumarhasi .
zrutavRttopasampannaH sarvaiH samudito guNaiH . dauSkuleyA durAtmAno nRzaMsA nirapatrapAH .
ta etadIdRzaM kuryuryathA tvaM tAta manyase . dharmArthayuktA loke ' smin pravRttirlakSyate satAm .
asatAM viparItA tu lakSyate bharatarSabha . viparItA tviyaM vRttirasakRllakSyate tvayi .
adharmazcAnubandho ' tra ghoraH prANaharo mahAn . aniSTazcAnimittazca na ca zakyazca bhArata . .
tamanarthaM pariharannAtmazreyaH kariSyasi . bhrAtRRNAmatha bhRtyAnAM mitrANAM ca paraMtapa .
adhAdayazasyAcca karmaNastvaM pramokSyase . prAjJaiH zUrairmahotsAhairAtmavadbhirbahuzrutaiH .
saMdhatsva puruSavyAghra pANDavairbharatarSabha . taddhitaM ca priyaM caiva dhRtarASTrasya
pitAmahasya droNasya vidurasya mahAmateH . kRpasya somadattasya bAhrIkasya ca dhImataH .
azvatthAmno vikarNasya saMjasya viviMzateH . jJAtInAM caiva bhUyiSThaM mitrANAM ca paraMtapa .
zame zarma bhavet tAta sarvasya jagatastathA . hrImAnasi kule jAtaH zrutavAnanRzaMsavAn . dhImataH . tiSTha tAta pituH zAstre mAtuzca bharatarSabha .
etacchreyo hi manyante pitA yacchAsti bhArata . uttamApadgataH sarvaH pituH smarati zAsanam .
rocate te pitustAta pANDavaiH saha saMgamaH . sAmAtyasya kuruzreSTha tat tubhyaM tAta rocatAm .
zrutvA yaH suhRdAM zAstraM maryo na pratipadyate . vipAkAnte dahatyenaM kimpAkamiva bhakSitam .
yastu niHzreyasaM vAkyaM mohAnna pratipadyate . sa dIrghasUtro hInArthaH pazcAttApena yujyate .
yastu niHzreyasaM zrutvA prAk tadevAbhipadyate . Atmano matamutsRjya sa loke sukhamedhate .
yo ' rthakAmasya vacanaM prAtikUlyAna mRSyate . zRNoti pratikUlAni dviSatAM vazameti saH .
satAM matamatikramya yo ' satAM vartate mate . zocante vyasane tasya suhRdo na cirAdiva .
mukhyAnamAtyAnutsRjya yo nihInAn niSevate . sa ghorAmApadaM prApya nottAramadhigacchati .
yo ' satsevIvRthAcAro na zrotA suhRdAM satAm . parAn vRNIte svAn dveSTi taM gaustyajati bhArata .
sa tvaM virudhya taivIrairanyebhyastrANamicchasi . aziSTebhyo ' samarthebhyo mUDhebhyo bharatarSabha . .
ko hi zakrasamAn jJAtInatikramya mahArathAn . anyebhyastrANamAzaMset tvadanyo bhuvi mAnavaH .
janmaprabhRti kaunteyA nityaM vinikRtAstvayA . na ca te jAtu kupyanti dharmAtmAno hi pANDavA .
mithyopacaritAstAta janmaprabhRti bAndhavAH . tvayi samyaGmahAbAho pratipannA yazasvinaH .
tvayApi pratipattavyaM tathaiva bharatarSabha . sveSu bandhuSu mukhyeSu mA manyuvazamanvagAH .
trivargayuktaH prAjJAnAmArambho bhatarSabha . dharmArthAvanurudhyante trivargAsambhave narAH .
pRthak ca viniviSTAnAM dharmaM dhIro ' nurudhyate . madhyamo ' rthaM kaliM bAlaH kAmamevAnurudhyate .
indriyaiH prAkRto lobhAd dharmaM viprajahAti yaH . kAmArthAvanupAyena lipsamAno vinazyati .
kAmArthoM lipsamAnastu dharmamevAditazcaret . na hi dharmAdapaityarthaH kAmo vA ' pi kadAcana .
upAyaM dharmamevAhustrivargasya vizAmpate . lipsamAno hi tenAzu kakSe ' gniriva vardhate .
sa tvaM tAtAnupAyena lipsase bharatarSabha . AdhirAjyaM mahad dApitaM prathitaM sarvarAjasu .
AtmAnaM takSati hyeSa vanaM parazunA yathA . yaH samyagvartamAneSu mithyA rAjan pravartate .
na tasya hi matiM chindyAd yasya necchet parAbhavam . avicchinnamaterasya kalyANe dhIyate matiH . AtmavAn nAvamanyeta triSu lokeSu bhArata .
apyanyaM prAkRtaM kiMcit kimu tAn pANDavarSabhAn . amarSavazamApanno na kiMcid budhyate janaH .
chidyate hyAtataM sarvaM pramANaM pazya bhArata . zreyaste durjanAt tAta pANDavaiH saha saMgatam .
tairhi samprIyamANastvaM sarvAn kAmAnavApsyasi . pANDavainirmitAM bhUmi bhuJjAno rAjasattama .
pANDavAn pRSThataH kRtvA trANamAzaMsase ' nyataH . duHzAsane durviSahe karNe cApi sasaubale .
eteSvaizvaryamAdhAya bhUtimicchasi bhArata . na caite tava paryAptA jJAne dharmArthayostathA .
vikrame cApyaparyAptAH pANDavAn prati bhArata . na hIme sarvavarAjAnaH paryAptAH sahitAstvayA .
kruddhasya bhImasenasya prekSituM mukhamAhave . idaM saMnihitaM tAta samagraM pArthivaM balam .
ayaM bhISmastathA droNaH karNazcAyaM tathA kRpaH . bhUrizravAH saumadattirazvatthAmA jayadrathaH .
azaktAH sarvaM evaite pratiyoddhaM dhanaMjayam . ajeyo hyarjunaH saMkhye sarvairapi surAsuraiH . mAnuSairipa gandharvairmA yuddhe ceta AdhithAH .
dRzyatAM vA pumAn kazcitaM samagre pArthive bale . yo ' rjunaM samare prApya svastimAnAvrajed gRhAn .
kiM te janakSayeNeha kRtena bharatarSabha . yasmiJjite jitaM tat syAt pumAnekaH sa dRzyatAm .52
yaH sa devAn sagandharvAn sayakSAsurapannagAn . ajayat khANDavaprasthe kastaM yudhyeta mAnavaH .
tathA virATanagare zrUyate mahadadbhutam . ekasya ca bahUnAM ca paryAptaM tannidarzanam .
yuddhe yena mahAdevaH sAkSAt saMtoSitaH zivaH . tamajeyamanAdhRSyaM vijetuM jiSNumacyutam . AzaMsasIha samare vIramarjunamUrjitam .
mad dvitIyaM punaH pArthaM kaH prArthayitumarhati . yuddhe pratIpamAyAntamapi sAkSAt puraMdaraH .
bAhubhyAmudvahed bhUmi dahet kruddha imAH prajAH . pAtayet tridivAd devAn yo ' rjunaM samare jayet .
pazya putrAMstathA bhrAtRjJAtIn sambandhinastathA . tvatkRte na vinazyeyurime bharatasattamAH .
astu zeSaM kauravANAM mA parAbhUdidaM kulam . kulana iti nocyethA naSTakIrtinarAdhipa .
tvAmeva sthApayiSyanti yauvarAjye mahArathAH . mahArAjye ' pi pitaraM dhRtarASTraM janezvaram .
mA tAta zriyamAyAntImavamaMsthAH samudyatAm . ardhaM pradAya pArthebhyo mahatIM zriyamApnuhi .
pANDavaiH saMzamaM kRtvA kRtvA ca suhRdAM vacaH . samprIyamANomitraizca ciraM bhadrANyavApsasyasi .
saMjaya uvAca kRtavarmA kRpo drauNiH sUtaputrazca mAriSa . ulUkaH saubalazcaiva rAjA ca saha sodaraiH . sIdamAnAM camUM dRSTvA pANDuputrabhayArditAm . samuhuH sma vegena bhinnAM nAvamivArNave .
tato yuddhamatIvAsInmuhUrtamiva bhArata . bhIrUNAM trAsajananaM zUrANAM harSavardhanam .
kRpeNa zaravarSANi pratimuktAni saMyuge . sRJjayAMzchAdayAmAsuH zalabhAnAM vrajA iva .
zikhaNDI ca tataH kruddho gautamaM tvarito yayau . vavarSa zaravarSANi samantAd dvijapuGgavam .
kRpastu zaravarSaM tad vinihatya mahAstravit . zikhaNDinaM raNe kraddho vivyAdha dazabhiH zaraiH .
tataH zikhaNDI kupitaH zaraiH saptabhirAhave . kRpaM vivyAdha kupitaM kaGkapatrairajihmagaiH .
tataH kRpaH zaraistIkSNaiH so ' tividdho mahArathaH . vyazvasUtarathaM cakre zikhaNDinamatho dvijaH .
hatAzcAt tu tato yAnAdavaplutya mahArathaH . khaGgaM carma tathA gRhya satvaM brAhmaNaM yayau .
tamApatantaM sahasA zaraiH saMnataparvabhiH . chAdayAmAsa samare tadadbhutamivAbhavat . tatrAdbhutamapazyAma zilAnAM plavanaM yathA . nizceSTastad raNe rAjaJchikhaNDI samatiSThata .
kRpeNacchAditaM dRSTvA nRpottama zikhaNDinam . pratyudyAyau kRpaM tUrNaM dhRSTadyumno mahArathaH .
dhRSTadyumnaM tato yAntaM zAradvatarathaM prati . pratijagrAha vegena kRtavarmA mahArathaH .
yudhiSThiramathAyAntaM zAradvatarathaM prati . saputraM sahasainyaM ca drauNaputro nyavArayat .
nakulaM sahadevaM ca tvaramANau mahArathau . pratijagrAha te putraH zaravarSeNa vArayan .
bhImasena karUSAMzca kekayAn saha saMjayaiH . karNo vaikartano yuddhe vArayAmAsa bhArata .
zikhaNDinastatau bANAn kRpaH zAradvato yudhi . prAhiNot tvarayA yukto didhakSuriva mAriSa . .
tAJcharAn preSitAstena samantAt svarNabhUSitAn . cicchadena khaGgamAvidhya bhrAmayaMzca punaH punaH .
zatacandraM ca tacarma gautamastasya bhArata . vyadhamat sAyakaistUrNaM tata ucukruzurjanAH .
sa vicarmA mahArAja khaGgapANirupAdravat . kRpasya vazamApanno mRtyorAsyamivAturaH .
zAradvatazarairgrastaM vizyamAnaM mahAbalaH . citraketusuto rAjan suketustvarito yayau .
vikiran brAhmaNaM yuddhe bahubhirnizitaiH zarai . abhyApatadameyAtmA gautamasya rathaM prati .
dRSTvA ca yuktaM ta yuddhe brAhmaNaM caritavratam . apayAtastastUrNaM zikhaNDI rAjasattama . .
suketustu tato rAjan gautamaM navabhiH zaraiH . viddhvA vivyAdha saptatyA punazcainaM tribhiH zaraiH .
athAsya sazaraM cApaM punazciccheda mAriSa . sArathiM ca zareNAsya bhRzaM marmasvatADayat .
gautamastu tataH kruddho dhanurgRhya navaM dRDham . suketuM triMzatA bANaiH sarvamarmasvatADayat .
sa vihvalitasarvAGgaH pracacAla rathottame . bhUmikampe yathA vRkSazcacAla kampito bhRzam .
calatastasya kAyAt tu ziro jvalitakuNDalam . soSNIyaM sazirastrANaM kSurapreNa tvapAtayad .
tacchiraMH prApatad bhUmau zyenAhatamivAmiSam . tato ' sya kAyo vasudhAM pazcAt prApatadacyuta .
tasmin hate mahArAja trastAstasya purogamAH . gautamaM hare tyaktvA duduvuste dizo daza .
dhRSTadyumnaM tu samare saMnivArya mahArathaH . kRtavarmAbravIddhRSTastiSTha tiSTheti bhArata .
tadabhUt tumulaM yuddhaM vRSNipArSatayo raNe . AmiSArthe yathA yuddhaM zyenayoH kruddhayopa .
dhRSTadyumnastu samare hArdikya navabhiH zaraiH . AjadhAnorasi kruddhaH pIDayan hRdikAtmajam .
kRtavarmA tu samare pArSatena dRDhAhataH . pArSataM sarathaM chAdayAmAsa sAyakaiH .
sarathazchAdito rAjan dhRSTadyumno na dRzyate . medhairiva paricchanno bhAskaro jaladhAribhiH .
vidhUya taM bANagaNaM zaraiH kanakabhUSaNaiH . vyarocata raNe rAjan dhRSTadyumnaH kRtavraNaH .
tatastu pArSataH kruddhaH zastravRSTiM sudAruNAm . kRtavarmANamAsAdya vyasRjat pRtanApatiH .
tAmApatantIM sahasA zastravRSTiM sudAruNAm . zarairanekasAhastrairhArdikyo ' vArayad yudhi .
dRSTvA tu vAritAM yuddhe zastravRSTiM durAsadAm . kRtavarmANamAsAdya vArayAmAsa pArSataH .
sArathiM cAsya tarasA prAhiNod yamasAdanam . bhallena zitadhAreNa sa hataH prApatad rathAt .
dhRSTadyumnastu balavAJjitvA zatru mahAbalam . kauravAn samare tUrNaM vArayAmAsa sAyakaiH .
tataste tAvakA yodhA dhRSTadyumnamupAdravan . siMhanAdaravaM kRtvA tato yuddhamavartata .
manuruvAca yadA taiH paJcabhiH paJca yuktAni manasA saha . atha tad rakSyate brahma maNau sUtramivApitam .
tadeva ca yathA sUtraM suvarNe vartate punaH . muktAsvatha pravAleSu mRnmaye rAjate tathA . tadvad go ' zvamanuSyeSu tadvaddhastimRgAdiSu . tadvat kITapataGgeSu prasaktAtmA svakarmabhiH .
yena yena zarIreNa yadyatkarma karotyayam . tena tena zarIreNa tat tat phalamupAznute .
yathA hyekarasA bhUmiroSadhyarthAnusAriNI . tathA karmAnugA buddhirantarAtmAnudarzinI .
jJAnapUrvA bhavellipsA lipsApUrvAbhisaMdhitA . abhisadhipUrvakaM karma karmamUlaM tataH phalam .
phalaM karmAtmakaM vidyAt karma jJeyAtmakaM tathA . jJeyaM jJAnAtmakaM vidyAjAnaM sadasadAtmakam .
jJAnAnAM ca phalAnAM ca jJeyAnAM karmaNAM tathA . kSayAnte yat phalaM vidyAjjJAnaM jJeyapratiSThitam .
mahaddhi paramaM bhUtaM yat prapazyanti yoginaH . abudhAstaM na pazyanti hyAtmasthaM guNabuddhayaH .
pRthivIrUpato rUpamapAmiha mahattaram . adbhayo mahattaraM tejastejasaH pavano mahAn .
pavanAcca mahad vyoma tasmAt parataraM manaH . manaso mahatI buddhirbuddheH kAlo mahAn smRtaH .
kAlAt sa bhagavAn viSNuryasya sarvamidaM jagat . nAdirna madhyaM naivAntastasya devasya vidyate .
anAditvAdamadhyatvAdanantatvAcca so ' vyayaH . atyeti sarvaduHkhAni duHkhaM hyantavaducyate .
tad brahma paramaM proktaM taddhAma paramaM padam . tad gatvA kAlaviSayAd vimuktA mokSamAzritAH .
guNeSvete prakAzante nirguNatvAt tataH param . nivRttilakSaNo dharmastathA ' ' nantyAya kalpate .
Rco yajUMSi sAmAni zarIrANi vyapAzritAH . jihvAgreSu pravartante yatnasAdhyA vinAzinaH .
na caivamiSyate brahma zarIrAzrayasambhavam . na yatnasAdhyaM tad brahma nAdimadhyaM na cAntavat . .
RcAmAdistathA sAmnAM yajuSAmAdirucyate . antazcAdimatAM dRSTo na tvAdibrahmaNaH smRtaH .
anAdinvAdanantatvAttadantamathAvyayam . avyayatvAcca nirduHkhaM dvandvAbhAvastataH param .
adRSTato ' nupAyAcca pratisaMdhezca karmaNaH . na tena mAH pazyanti yena gacchanti tat padam .
viSayeSu ca saMsargAcchAzvatasya ca darzanAt . manasA cAnyadAkAGkSan paraM na pratipadyate .
guNAn yadiha pazyanti tadicchantyapare janAH . paraM naivAbhikAGkSanti nirguNatvAd guNArthinaH .
guNairyastvavarairyuktaH kathaM vidyAt parAn guNAn . anumAnAddhi gantavyaM guNairavayavaiH param .
sUkSmeNa manasA vidyo vAcA vaktuM na zaknumaH . mano hi manasA grAhyaM darzanena ca darzanam .
jJAnena nirmalIkRtya buddhiM buddhyA manastathA . manasA cendriyagrAmamakSaraM pratipadyate .
buddhipravINo manasA samRddho nirAziSaM nirguNamabhyupaiti . paraM tyajantIha viloDyamAnA hutAzanaM vAyurivendhanastham .
guNAdAne viprayoge ca teSAM manaH sadA buddhiparAvarAbhyAm . anenaiva vidhinA sampravRtto guNApAye brahma zarIra meti .
