sarvairayaM cendriyaiH samprayukto dehaM prAptaH paJcabhUtAzrayaH syAt . nAsAmarthyAd gacchati karmaNeha hInastena parameNAvyayena .
pRthvyAM naraH pazyati nAntamasyA hyantazcAsyA bhavitA ceti viddhi . paraM nayantIha viloDyamAnaM yathA plavaM vAyurivArNavastham .
