jihmAkSAH pralalATAzca nirmAMsahanavo ' pi ca . vajrabAhaGgulIcakrAH kRzA dhamanisaMtatAH . pravizanti ca vegena sAmparAye chupasthite . vAraNA iva sammattAste bhavanti durAsadAH .
dIptasphuTitakezAntA : sthUlapArzvahanUmukhAH . unnatAMsAH pRthugrIvA vikaTAH sthUlapiNDikAH . uddhatA iva sugrIvA vinatAvihagA iva . . piNDazIrSAtivaktrAzca vRSadaMzamukhAstathA . ugrasvarA manyumanto yuddheSvArAvasariNaH . adharmajJAvaliptAzca ghorA raudrapradarzanAH . tyaktAtmAnaH sarva ete antyajA hyanivartinaH . puraskAryAH sadA sainye hanyante manti cApi ye .
adhArmikA bhinnavRttAH sAntvenaiSAM parAbhavaH . evameva prakupyanti rAjJo ' pyete hyabhIkSNazaH .
nArAyaNaM namaskRtya naraM caiva narottamam . devI sarasvatI vyAsaM tato jayamudIrayet . .
yuSThira uvAca zamo bahuvidhAkAraH sUkSma uktaH pitAmaha . na ca me hRdaye zAntirasti zrutvedamIdRzam .
asminnarthe bahuvidhA zAntiruktA pitAmaha . svakRte kA nu zAntiH syAcchamAd bahuvidhAdapi .
zarAcitazarIraM hi tIvravraNamudIkSya ca . zarma nopalabhe vIra duSkRtAnyeva cintayan .
rudhireNAvasiktAGgaM prasravantaM yathAcalam . tvAM dRSTvA puruSavyAghra sIde varSAsvivAmbujam .
ataH kaSTataraM kiM nu matkRte yat pitAmahaH . imAmavasthAM gamitaH pratyamitrai raNAjire .
tathA cAnye nRpatayaH sahaputrAH sabAndhavAH . matkRte nidhanaM prAptAH kiM nu kaSTataraM tataH .
vayaM hi dhArtarASTrAzca kAlamanyuvaMzagatAH . kRtvedaM ninditaM karma prApsyAmaH kAM gatiM nRpa . .
idaM tu dhArtarASTrasya zreyo manye janAdhipa . imAmavasthAM samprAptaM yadasau tvAM na pazyati .
so ' haM tava hyantakaraH suhRdvadhakarastathA . na zAntimadhigacchAmi pazyaMstvAM duHkhitaM kSitau .
duryodhano hi samare sahasainyaH sahAnujaH . nihataH kSatradharme ' smin durAtmA kulapAMsanaH .
na sa pazyati duSTAtmA tvAmadya patitaM kSitau . ataH zreyo mRtaM manye neha jIvitamAtmanaH .
ahaM hi samare vIra gamitaH zatrubhiH kSayam . abhaviSyaM yadi purA saha bhrAtRbhiracyuta . na tvAmevaM suduHkhArtamadrAkSaM sAyakArditam . nUnaM hi pApakarmANo dhAtrA sRSTAH sma he nRpa .
anyasminnapi loke vai yathA mucyema kilbiSAt . tathA prazAdhi mAM rAjan mama cedicchasi priyam .
bhISma uvAca paratantraM kathaM hetumAtmAnamanupazyasi . karmaNAM hi mahAbhAga sUkSmaM hyetadatAndriyam .
atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . saMvAdaM mRtyugautamyoH kAlalubdhakapannagaiH .
gautamI nAma kaunteya sthavirA zamasaMyutA . sarpaNa daSTaM svaM putramapazyadgatacetanam .
atha taM snAyupAzena baddhvA sarpamamarSitaH . lubdhako ' rjunako nAma gautamyAH samupAnayat .
sa cAbravIdayaM te sa putrahA pannagAdhamaH . brUhi kSipraM mahAbhAge vadhyatAM kena hetunA .
agnau prakSipyatAmeSa cchidyatAM khaNDazo ' pi vA . na hyayaM bAlahA pApazciraM jIvitumarhati .
gautamyuvAca visRjainamabuddhistvamavadhyo ' rjunaka tvayA . ko hyAtmAnaM guruM kuryAt prAptavyamavicintayan .
plavante dharmalaghavo loka ' mbhasi yathA plavAH . majjanti pApaguravaH zastraM skannamivodake .
hatvA cainaM nAmRta : syAdayaM me jIvatyasmin ko ' tyayaH syAdayaM te . asyotsarge prANayuktasya jantormRtyorlokaM ko nu gacchedanantam .
lubdhaka uvAca jAnAmyahaM devi guNAguNajJe sarvArtiyuktA guravo bhavanti . svasthasyaite tUpadezA bhavanti tasmAt kSudraM sarpamenaM haniSye . .
zamArthinaH kAlagatiM vadanti sadyaH zucaM tvarthavidastyajanti . zreyaHkSayaM zocati nityamohAt tasmAcchucaM muJca hate bhujaGge .
gautamyuvAca AtinaivaM vidyate ' smadvidhAnAM dharmAtmAnaH sarvadA sajjanA hi . dIze nAhaM pannagasya pramAthe .
na brAhmaNAnAM kopo ' sti kutaH kopAcca yAtanAm . mArdavArakSamyatAM sAdho mucyatAmeSa pannagaH .
lubdhaka uvAca llabhyo lAbhyaH syAd balibhyaH prazastaH . kAlAllAbho yastu satyo bhaveta zreyolAbhaH kutsite ' sminna te syAt .
gautamyuvAca kA nu prAptirgRhya zatru nihatya kA kAmAptiH prApya zatru na muktvA . kasmAt saumyAhaM na kSame no bhujaGge mokSArthaM vA kasya hetorna kuryAm .
lubdhaka uvAca asmAdekAd bahavo rakSitavyA naiko bahubhyo gautami rakSitavyaH . kRtAgasaM dharmavidastyajanti sarIsRpaM pApamimaM jahi tvam .
gautamyuvAca nAsmin hate pannage putrako me samprApsyate lubdhaka jIvitaM vai . guNaM cAnyaM nAsya vadhe prapazye tasmAt sarpa lubdhaka muJca jIvam .
lubdhaka uvAca vRtraM hatvA devarAT zreSThabhAga vai yajJaM hutvA bhAgamavApa caiva . zUlI devo devavRttaM cara tvaM kSipraM sarpa jahi mA bhUtte vizaGkA .
bhISma uvAca asakRt procyamAnApi gautamI bhujagaM prati . lubdhakena mahAbhAgA pApe naivAkaronmatim . ISaducchvasamAnastu kRcchrAt saMstabhya pannagaH . utsasarja giraM mandAM mAnuSIM pAzapIDitaH .
sarpa uvAca konvarjunaka doSo ' tra vidyate mama bAliza . asvatantraM hi mAM mRtyurvivazaM yadacUcudat .
tasyAyaM vacanAd daSTo na kopena na kAmyayA . tasya tatkilbiSaM lubdha vidyate yadi kilbiSam .
lubdhaka uvAca yadyanyavazagenedaM kRtaM te pannagAzubham . kAraNaM vai tvamapyatra tasmAt kilbiSI .
mRtpAtrasya kriyAyAM hi daNDacakrAdayo yathA . kAraNatve prakalpyante tathA tvamapi pannaga .
sarpa uvAca kilviSI cApi me vadhyaH kilbiSI cAsi pannaga . AtmAnaM kAraNaM hyatra tvamAkhyAsi bhujaGgama . sarva ete hyasvavazA daNDacakrAdayo yathA . tathA ' hamapi tasmAnme naiSa doSo matastava .
athavA matametatte te ' pyanyonyaprayojakAH . kAryakAraNasandeho bhavatyanyonyacodanAt .
evaM sati na doSo me nAsmi vadhyo na kilbiSI . kilviSaM samavAye syAnmanyase yadi kilviSam .
lubdhaka uvAca kAraNaM yadi na syAd vai na kartA syAstvamapyuta . vinAzakAraNaM tvaM ca tasmAd vadhyo ' si me mataH .
asatyapi kRte kAryaM neha pannaga lipyate . tasmAnnAtraiva hetuH syAd vadhyaH kiM bahu manyase .
sarpa uvAca kAryAbhAve kriyA na syAt satyasatyapi kAraNe . tasmAt same ' smin hetau me vAcyo heturvizeSataH .
anyaH prayoge syAdatra kilbiSI jantunAzane . . yadyahaM kAraNatvena mato lubdhaka tattvataH .
lubdhaka uvAca vadhyastvaM mama durbuddhe bAlaghAtI nRzaMsakRt . bhASase kiM bahu punarvadhyaH san pannagAdhama .
sarpa uvAca yathA havIMSi juhvAnA makhe vai lubdhakarvijaH . na phalaM prApnuvantyatra phalayoge tathA hyaham .
bhISma uvAca tathA bruvati tasmiMstu pannage mRtyucodite . AjagAma tato mRtyuH pannagaM cAbravIdidam .
mRtyuruvAca pracodito ' haM kAlena pannaga tvAmacUcudam . vinAzaheturnAsya tamahaM na prANinaH zizoH .
yathA vAyurjaladharAn vikarSati tatastataH . tadvajjaladavat sarpa kAlasyAhaM vazAnugaH .
sAttvikA rAjasAzcaiva tAmasA ye ca kecana . bhAvAH kAlAtmakAH sarve pravartante ha jantuSu .
jaGgamAH sthAvarAzcaiva divi vA yadi vA bhuvi . sarve kAlAtmakAH sarpa kAlAtmakamidaM jagat .
pravRttayazca loke ' smiMstathaiva ca nivRttayaH . tAsAM vikRtayo yAzca sarvaM kAlAtmakaM smRtam .
AdityazcandramA viSNurApo vAyuH zatakratuH . agni : svaM pRthivI mitraH parjanyo vasavo ' ditiH . .55
saritaH sAgarAcaiva bhAvAbhAvau ca pannaga . sarva kAlena sRjyante hriyante ca punaH punaH . evaM jJAtvA kathaM mAM tvaM sadoSaM sarpa manyase . atha caivaMgate doghe mayi tvamapi doSavAn .
sarpa uvAca nirdoSaM doSavantaM vA na tvAM mRtyo bravImyaham . tvayAhaM codita iti bravImyetAvadeva tu .
yadi kAle tu doSo ' sti yadi tatrApi neSyate . doSo naiva parIkSyo me na hyatrAdhikRtA vayam .
nirmokSastvasya doSasya mayA kAryA yathA tathA . mRtyorapi na doSaH syAditi me ' tra prayojanam .
bhISma uvAca sarpo ' thArjunakaM prAha zrutaM te mRtyubhASitam . nAnAgasaM mAM pAzena saMtApayitumarhasi .
lubdhaka uvAca mRtyoH zrutaM me vacanaM tava caiva bhujaGgama . naiva tAvadadoSatvaM bhavati tvayi pannaga .
mRtyustvaM caiva heturhi bAlasyAsya vinAzane . ubhayaM kAraNaM manye na kAraNamakAraNam .
dhimRtyuM ca durAtmAnaM krUraM duHkhakaraM satAm . tvAM caivAhaM vadhiSyAmi pApaM pApasya kAraNam .
mRtyuruvAca vivazau kAlavazagAvAvAM nirdiSTakAriNau . nAvAM doSeNa gantavyau yadi samyak prapazyasi .
lubdhaka uvAca yuvAmubhau kAlavazau yadi me mRtyupannagau . harSakrodhau yathA syAtAmetadicchAmi veditum .
mRtyuruvAca yA kAcideva ceSTA syAt sarvA kAlapracoditA . pUrvamevaitaduktaM hi mayA lubdhaka kAlataH . tasmAdubhau kAlavazAvAvAM nirdiSTakAriNau . nAvAM doSeNa gantavyau tvayA lubdhaka karhicit .
bhISma uvAca athopagamya kAlastu tasmin dharmArthasaMzaye . abravIt pannagaM mRtyu lubdhaM cArjunakaM tathA .
kAla uvAca na hyahaM nApyayaM mRtyu yaM lubdhaka pannagaH . kilbiSI jantumaraNe na vayaM hi prayojakAH .
akarod yadayaM karma tanno ' rjunaka codakam . vinAzaheturnAnyo ' sya vadhyate ' yaM svakarmaNA .
yadanena kRtaM karma tenAyaM nidhanaM gataH . vinAzahetuH karmAsya sarve karmavazA vayam .
karmadAyAdavA~llokaH karmasambandhalakSaNaH . karmANi codayantIha yathAnyonyaM tathA vayam .
yathA mRtpiNDataH kartA kurute yad yadicchati . evamAtmakRtaM karma mAnavaH pratipadyate .
yathAcchAyAtayau nityaM susambaddhau nirantaram . tathA karma ca kartA ca sambaddhAvAtmakarmabhiH .
evaM nAhaM na vai mRtyu sarpo na tathA bhavAn . na ceyaM brAhmaNI vRddhA zizurevAtra kAraNam .
tasmiMstathA bruvANe tu brAhmaNI gautamI nRpa . svakarmapratyayA~llokAn matvA ' rjunakamabravIt .
gautamI uvAca naiva kAlo na bhujago na mRtyuriha kAraNam . svakarmabhirayaM bAlaH kAlena nidhanaM gataH .
mayA ca tat kRtaM karma yenAyaM me mRtaH sutaH . yAtu kAlastathA mRtyurmuJcArjunaka pannagam .
bhISma uvAca tato yathAgataM jagmurmRtyuH kAlo ' tha pannagaH . abhUd vizoko ' rjunako vizokA caiva gautamI .
etacchutvA zamaM gaccha mA bhUH zokaparo nRpa . svakarmapratyayA~llokAn sarve gacchanti vai nRpa .
naiva tvayA kRtaM karma nApi duryodhanena vai . kAlenaitat kRtaM viddhi nihatA yena pArthivAH .
vaizampAyana uvAca ityetad vacanaM zrutvA babhUva vigatajvaraH . yudhiSThiro mahAtejAH papracchedaM ca dharmavit .
avazyaM kathanIyaM me tavaitannarapuGgava . yadarthaM tvAhamucchettuM samprApto manujAdhipa .
bhRgUNAM kSatriyA yAjyA nityametajjanAdhipa . te ca bhedaM gamiSyanti daivayuktena hetunA .
kSatriyAzca bhRgUn sarvAn vadhiSyanti narAdhipa . A garbhAdanukRntanto daivadaNDanipIDitAH .
tata utpatsyate ' smAkaM kule gotravivardhanaH . urvo nAma mahAtejA jvalanArkasamadyutiH .
sa trailokyavinAzAya kopAgniM janayiSyati . mahIM saparvatavanAM yaH kariSyati bhasmasAt .
kaMcit kAlaM tu vahniM ca sa eva zamayiSyati . samudre vaDavAvako prakSipya munisattamaH .
putraM tasya mahArAja RcIkaM bhRgunandanam . sAkSAt kRtsno dhanurvedaH samupasthAsyate ' nagha . . kSatriyANAmabhAvAya daivayuktena hetunA . sa tu taM pratigRhmaiva putre saMkrAmayiSyati . jamadagnau mahAbhAge tapasA bhAvitAtmani . sa cApi bhRguzArdUlastaM vedaM dhArayiSyati .
kulAt tu tava dharmAtman kanyAM so ' dhigamiSyati . udbhAvanArthaM bhavato vaMzasya nRpasattama .
gAdherduhitaraM prApya pautrIM tava mahAtapAH . brAhmaNaM kSatradharmANaM putramutpAdayiSyati .
kSatriyaM viprakarmANaM bRhaspatimivaujasA . vizvAmitraM tava kule gAdheH putraM sudhArmikam .
tapasA mahatA yuktaM pradAsyati mahAdyute . striyau ta kAraNaM tatra parivarte bhaviSyataH .
pitAmahaniyogAd vai nAnyathaitad bhaviSyati . tRtIye puruSe tubhyaM brAhmaNatvamupaiSyati . bhavitA tvaM ca sambandhI bhRgUNAM bhAvitAtmanAm .
bhISma uvAca kuzikastu munervAkyaM cyavanasya mahAtmanaH . zrutvA hRSTo ' bhavad rAjA vAkyaM cedamuvAca ha .
punareva narAdhipam . varArthaM codayAmAsa tamuvAca sa pArthivaH . bADhamevaM kariSyAmi kAmaM tvatto mahAmune .
cyavanastu mahAtejAH brahmabhUtaM kulaM me ' stu dharme cAsya mano bhavet . evamuktastathetyevaM pratyuktvA cyavano muniH . abhyanujJAya nRpati tIrthayAtrA yayau tadA . etat te kathitaM sarvamazeSeNa mayA nRpa . bhRgUNAM kuzikAnAM ca abhisambandhakAraNam .
yathoktamRSiNA cApi tadA tadabhavannRpa . janma rAmasya ca munervizvAmitrasya caiva hi .
yudhiSThira uvAca bhavAnetAdRzo loke vedavedAGgapAragaH . brUhi kiM kurvataH karma bhaved gatiranuttamA .
sarpa uvAca pAtre dattvA priyANyuktvA satyamuktvA ca bhArata . ahiMsAnirataH svarga gacchediti matirmama .
yudhiSThira uvAca dAnAd vA sarpa satyAd vA kimato guru dRzyate . ahiMsApriyayozcaiva gurulAghavamucyatAm .
sarpa uvAca dAnaM ca satyaM tattvaM vA ahiMsA priyameva ca . eSAM kAryagarIyastvAd dRzyate gurulAghavam .
kasmAccid dAnayogAddhi satyameva viziSyate . satyavAkyAcca rAjendra kiMcid dAnaM viziSyate .
evameva maheSvAsa priyavAkyAnmahIpate . ahiMsA dRzyate gurvI tatazca priyamiSyate .
evametad bhaved rAjan kAryApekSamanantaram . yadabhipretamanyat te brUhi yAvad bravImyaham .
yudhiSThira uvAca kathaM svarge gati : sarpa karmaNAM ca phalaMdhruvam . azarIrasya dRzyeta prabrUhi viSayAMzca me .
sarpa uvAca tige vai gatayo rAjan paridRSTAH svakarmabhiH . mAnuSaM svargavAsazca tiryagyonizca tat tridhA .
tatra vai mAnuSAllokAd dAnAdibhiratandritaH . ahiMsArthasamAyuktaiH kAraNaiH svargamaznute .
viparItaizca rAjendra kAraNairmAnuSo bhavet . tiryagyonistathA tAta vizeSazcAtra vakSyate .
kAmakrodhasamAyukto hiMsAlobhasamanvitaH . manuSyatvAt paribhraSTastiryagyonau prasUyate .
tiryagyonyAH pRthagbhAvo manuSyArthe vidhIyate . gavAdibhyastathAzvebhyo devatvamapi dRzyate .
so ' yametA gatIstAta jantuzcarati kAryavAn . nitye mahati cAtmAnamavasthApayate dvijaH .
jAto jAtazca balavad bhuGkte cAtmA sa dehavAn . phalArthastAta niSpRktaH prajApAlanabhAvanaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca zabde sparza ca rUpe ca tathaiva rasagandhayoH . tasyAdhiSThAnamavyaco brUhi sarpa yathAtatham .
kiM na gRhaNAti viSayAn yugapacca mahAmate . etAvaducyatAM coktaM sarvaM pannagasattama . .
sarpa uvAca yadAtmadravyamAyuSman dehasaMzrayaNAnvitam . karaNAdhiSThitaM bhogAnupabhuGkte yathAvidhi .
jJAnaM caivAtra buddhizca manazca bharatarSabha . tasya bhogAdhikaraNe karaNAni nibodha me .
manasA tAta paryeti kramazo viSayAnimAn . viSayAyatanastho hi bhUtAtmA kSetramAsthitaH .
tatra cApi naravyAghra mano jantorvidhIyate . tasmAd yugapadatrAsya grahaNaM nopapadyate .
sa AtmA puruSavyAghra bhruvorantaramAzritaH . buddhiM dravyeSu sRjati vividheSu parAvarAm .
vuddhezttarakAlA ca vedanA dRzyate budhaiH . eSa vai rAjazArdUla vidhiH kSetrajJabhAvanaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca manasazcApi buddhezca brUhi me lakSaNaM param . etadadhyAtmaviduSAM paraM kAryaM vidhIyate .
sarpa uvAca buddhirAtmAnugA tAta utpAtena vidhIyate . tadAzritA hi saMjJaiSA buddhistasyaiSiNI bhavet .
buddhirutpadyate kAryAnmanastUtpannameva hi . buddherguNavidhAnena manastahaguNavad bhavet .
etad vizeSaNaM tAta manobuddhyoryadantaram . tvamapyatrAbhisambuddhaH kathaM vA manyate bhavAn .
yudhiSThira uvAca aho buddhimatAM zreSTha zubhA buddhiriyaM tava . viditaM veditavyaM te kasmAt samanupRcchasi .
sarvajJaM tvAM kathaM moha Avizat svargavAsinam . evamadbhutakarmANamiti me saMzayo mahAn .
sarpa uvAca suprajJamapi cecchUramRddhirmohayate naram . vartamAnaH sukhe sarvo muhyatIti matirmama .
so ' hamaizvaryamohena madAviSTo yudhiSThira . patitaH pratisambuddhastvAM tu sambodhayAmyaham .
kRtaM kArya mahArAja tvayA mama paraMtapa . kSINa : zApaH sukRcchro me tvayA sambhASya sAdhunA . .
ahaM hi divi divyena vimAnena caran purA . abhimAnena mattaH san kaMcinnAnyamacintayam .
brahmarSidevagandharvayakSarAkSasapannagAH . karAn mama prayacchanti sarve trailokyavAsinaH .
cakSuSA yaM prapazyAmi prANinaM pRthivIpate . tasya tejo harAmyAzu taddhi dRSTerbalaM mama .
brahmarSINAM sataraM hi uvAha zibikAM mama . sa mAmapanayo rAjan bhraMzayAmAsa vai zriyaH .
tatra hyagastyaH pAdena vahan spRSTo mayA muniH . agastayena tato ' smyuktaH sarpastvaM ca bhaveti ha .
tatastasmAd vimAnAvayAt pracyutazcyutalakSaNaH . prapatan bubudhe ' ' tmAnaM vyAlIbhUtamadhomukham . anyAcaM tamahaM vipraM zApasyAnto bhavediti .
sarpa uvAca pramAdAt sampramUDhasya bhagavan kSantumarhasi . tataH sa mAmuvAcedaM prapatantaM kRpAnvitaH .
yudhiSThirodharmarAjaH zApAt tvAM mokSayiSyati . abhimAnasya ghorasya pApasya ca narAdhipa .
phale kSINe mahArAja phalaM puNyamavApsyasi . tato me vismayo jAtastad dRSTvA tapaso balam .
brahma ca brAhmaNatvaM ca yena tvAhamacUcudam . satyaM damastapo dAnAhiMsAdharmanityatA . .
sAdhakAni sadA puMsAM na jAtirna kulaM nRpa . ariSTa eSa bhrAtA bhImaseno mahAbalaH . svasti te ' stu mahArAja gamiSyAmi divaM punaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca ityuktvA ' ' jagaraM dehaM muktvA sa nahuSo nRpaH . divyaM vapuH samAsthAya gatastridivameva ha .
yudhiSThiro ' pidharmAtmA bhrAtrA bhImena saMgataH . dhaumyena sahitaH zrImAnAzramaM punarAgamat .
te tato dvijebhyaH sarvebhyaH sametebhyo yathAtatham . kathayAmAsa tat sarvadharmarAjo yudhiSThiraH .
tacchrutvA te dvijAH sarve bhrAtazcAsya te trayaH . Asan suvrIDitA rAjan draupadI ca yazasvinI .
te tu sarve dvijazreSThAH pANDavAnAM hitepsayA . maivamityabruvan bhImaM garhayanto ' sya sAhasam .
pANDavAstu bhayAnmuktaM prekSya bhImaM mahAbalam . harSamAhArayAMcakrurvijahvazca mudA yutAH .
saMjaya uvAca samaM vyUDheSvanIkeSu bhUyiSTheSvanivartinaH . brahmalokaparAH sarve samapadyanta bhArata . na hyanIkamanIkena samasajjata saMkule . rathA na rathibhiH sArdha pAdAtA na padAtibhiH .
azvA nAzvairayudhyanta gajA na gajayodhibhiH . unmattavanmahArAja yudhyante tatra bhArata . mahAn vyatikaro raudraH senayoH samapadyatA naranAgagaNeSveva vikIrNeSu ca sarvazaH .
kSaye tasmin mahAraudre nirvizeSamajAyata . tataH zalyaH kRpazcaiva citrasenazca bhArata . duHzAsano vikarNazca rathAnAsthAya bhAsvarAn . pANDavAnAM raNe zUrA dhvajinIM samakampayan .
sA vadhyamAnA samare pANDusenA mahAtmabhiH . bhrAmyate bahudhA rAjan mAruteneva naurjale .
yatA hi zaiziraH kAlo gavAM marmANi kRntati . tathA pANDusutAnAM vai bhISmo marmANi kRntati . tathaiva tava sainyasya pArthena ca mahAtmanA . navameghapratIkAzA : pAtitA bahudhA gajAH .
mRdyamAnAzca dRzyante pArthena narayUthapAH . iSubhistAGyamAnAzca nArAcaizca sahasrazaH .
peturArtasvaraM ghoraM kRtvA tatra mahAgajAH . AnaddhAbharaNaiH kAryenihatAnAM mahAtmanAm . channamAyodhanaM reje zirobhizca sakuNDalaiH . tasminneva mahArAja mahAvIravarakSaye .
bhISme ca yudhi vikrAnte pANDave ca dhanaMjaye . te parAkrAntamAlokya rAjan yudhi pitAmaham . abhyavartanta te putrAH sarve sainyapuraskRtAH . icchanto nidhanaM yuddhe svargaM kRtvA parAyaNam .
pANDavAnabhyavartanta tasmin vIravarakSaye . pANDavA ' pi mahArAja smaranto vividhAn bahUn .
klezAn kRtAn saputreNa tvayA pUrvaM narAdhipa . bhaya tyaktvA raNe zUrA brahmalokAya tatparAH .
tAvakAMstava putrAMzca yodhayanti prahRSTavat . senApatistu samare prAha senAM mahArathaH .
abhidravata gAGgeyaM somakAH sRJjayaiH saha . senApativacaH zrutvA samokAH sRJjayAzca te .
abhyadravanta gAGgeyaM zaravRSTyA samAhatAH . vadhyamAnastato rAjan pitA zAntanavastava .
amarSavazamApanno yodhayAmAsa sRJjayAn . tasya kIrtimatastAta purA rAmeNa dhImatA .
sampradattAstrazikSA vai parAnIkavinAzanI . sa tA zikSAmadhiSThAya kurvan parabalakSayam .
ahanyahani pArthAnAM vRddhaH kurupitAmahaH . bhISmo daza sahasrANi jaghAna paravIrahA . .
tasmiMstu dazame prApte divase bharatarSabha . bhISmeNaikena matsyeSu paJcAleSu ca saMyuge .
gajAzvamimitaM hatvA hatAH sapta mahArathAH . hatvA paJca sahasrANi rathAnAM prapitAmahaH .
narANAM ca mahAyuddhe sahasrANi caturdazaH . dantinAM ca sahasrANi hayAnAmayutaM punaH .
zikSAbalena nahitaM pitrA tava vizAmpate . tataH sarvamahIpanAM kSapayitvA varUthinIm .
virATasya priyo bhrAtA zatAnIko nipAtitaH . zatAnIkaM ca samare hatvA bhISmaH pratApavAn .
sahasrANi mahArAja rAjJA bhallairapAtayat . udvignAH samare yodhA vikrozanti dhanaMjayam .
ye ca kecana pArthAnAmabhiyAtA dhanaMjayam . rAjAno bhISmamAsAdya gatAste yamasAdanam . evaM daza dizo bhISmaH zarajAlaiH samantataH . atItya senAM pArthAnAmavatasthe camUmukhe .
sa kRtvA sumahat karma tasmin vai dazame ' hani . senayorantare tiSThan pragRhItazarAsanaH . na cainaM pArthivAH kecicchaktA rAjan nirIkSitum .
madhyaM prAptaM yathA grISme tapantaM bhAskaraM divi . yathA daityacamUM zaktastApayAmAsa saMyuge .
tathA bhISmaH pANDaveyAstApayAmAsa bhArata . tathA cainaM parAkrAntamAlokya madhusUdanaH .
uvAca devakIputraH prIyamANo dhanaMjayam . eSa zAntanavo bhISmaH senayorantare sthitaH .
saMnihatya balAdena vijayaste bhaviSyati . balAt saMstambhayasvainaM yatraiSA bhidyate camUH .
na hi bhISmazarAnanyaH soDhumutsahate vibho . tatastasmin kSaNe rAjaMzcodito vAnaradhvajaH .
sadhvajaM sarathaM sAzvaM bhISmamantardadhe zaraiH . sa cApi kurumukhyAnamRSabhaH pANDaveritAn . . zaravrAtaiH zaravrAtAn bahudhA vidudhAva tAn . tataH paJcAlarAjazca dhRSTaketuzca vIryavAn .
pANDavo bhImasenazca dhRSTadyumnazca pArSataH . yamau ca cekitAnazca kekayA : paJca caiva ha .
sAtyakizca mahAbAhuH saubhadro ' tha ghaTotkacaH . draupadeyAH zikhaNDI ca kuntibhojazca vIryavAn . suzarmA ca virATazca pANDaveyA mahAbalAH . ete cAnye ca bahavaH pIDitA bhISmasAyakaiH .
samuddhRtAH phAlgunena nimagnAH zokasAgare . tataH zikhaNDI vegena pragRhya paramAyudham . bhISmamevAbhidudrAva rakSyamANaH kirITinA .
