virATo drupadazcaiva mAdrIputrau ca pANDavau . dudruvurbhISmamevAjau rakSitA dRDhadhanvanA .
abhimanyuzca samare draupadyAH paJca cAtmajAH . dudruvuH samare bhISmaM samudyatamahAyudhAH .
te sarve dRDhadhanvAnaH saMyugeSvapalAyinaH . bahudhA bhISmamAnachurmArgaNaiH kSatamArgaNaiH .
vidhUya tAn bANagaNAn ye muktAH pArthivottamaiH . pANDavAnAmadInAtmA vyagAhata varUthinIm .
cakre zaravighAtaM cakrIDanniva pitAmahaH . nAbhisaMdhatta pAJcAlye smayamAno muhurmuhaH .
strItvaM tasyAnusaMsmRtya bhISmo bANAzikhaNDine . jagAna drupadAnIke rathAn sapta mahArathaH .
tata : kilakilAzabdaH kSaNena samabhUt tadA . matsyapAJcAlacedInAM tamekamabhidhAvatAm .
te narAzvarathavrAtairmArgaNaizca paraMtapa . tamekaM chAdayAmAsurmeghA iva divAkaram .
bhISmaM bhAgIrathIputraM pratapantaM raNe ripUn . tatastamya ca teSAM ca yuddhe devAsuropame . kirITIbhISmamAgacchat puraskRtya zikhaNDinam .
dhRtarASTra uvAca keSAM prahRSTAstatrAgre yodhA yudhyanti saMjaya . udagramanasaH ke vA ke vA dInA vicetasaH .
ke pUrvaM prAharaMstatra yuddhe hRdayakampane . mAmakAH pANDaveyA vA tanmamAcakSva saMjaya .
kasya senAsamudaye gandhamAlyasamudbhavaH . vAcaH pradakSiNAzcaiva yodhAnAmabhigarjatAm .
saMjaya uvAca vyUDhAnAM ubhayoH senayostatra yodhA jahaSire tadA . srajaH samAH sugandhAnAmubhayatra samudbhavaH . saMhatAnAmanIkAnAM bharatarSabha . saMsargAt samudIrNAnAM vimardaH sumahAnabhUt .
vAditrazabdastumulaH zaGkhabherIvimizritaH . zUrANAM raNazUrANAM garjatAmitaretaram . ubhayoH senayo rAjan mahAn vyatikaro ' bhavat .
anyonyaM vIkSyamANAnAM yodhAnAM bharatarSabha . kuJjarANAM ca nadatAM sainyAnAM ca prahRSyatAm .
vaizampAyana uvAca etasminneva kAle tu bhImaseno ' pi vIryavAn . dharmarajamanuprApya yayau prAcI dizaM prati .
mahatA balacakreNa pararASTrAvamardinA . hastyazvarathapUrNena daMzitena pratApavAn . vRto bharatazArdUlo dviSacchokavivarddhanaH . sa gatvA narazArdUla : paJcAlAnAM puraM mahat .
paJcAlAn vividhepAyaiH sAntvayAmAsa pANDavaH . tataH sa gaNDakAJchUro videhAn bharatarSabhaH . vijityAlpena kAlena dazArNAnajayat prabhuH . tatra dAzArNako rAjA sudharmA lomaharSaNam . kRtavAn bhImasenena mahad yuddhaM nirAyudham .
bhImasenastu tad dRSTvA tasya karma mahAtmanaH . adhisenApatiM cakre sudharmANaM mahAbalam .
tataH prAcI dizaM bhImo yayau bhImaparAkramaH . sainyena mahatA rAjan kampayanniva medinIm .
so ' zvamedhezvaraM rAjan rocamAnaM sahAnugam . jigAya samare vIro balena balinAM varaH .
sa taM nirjitya kaunteyo nAtitIvraNa karmaNA . pUrvadezaM mahAvIryo vijigye kurunandana .
tato dakSiNamAgamya pulindanagaraM mahat . sukumAraM vaze cakre sumitraM ca narAdhipam .
tatastu dharmarAjasya zAsanAd bharatarSabhaH . zizupAlaM mahAvIryamabhyagAjjanamejaya .
cedirAjo ' pi tacchrutvA pANDavasya cikIrSitam . upaniSkramya nagarAt pratyagRhaNAt paraMtapa .
tau sametya mahArAja kurucedivRSau tadA . ubhayorAtmakulayoH kauzalyaM paryapRcchatAm .
tato nivedya tad rASTra cedirAjo vizAmpate . uvAca bhImaM prahasan kimidaM kuruSe ' nagha .
tasya bhImastadA ' cakhyau dharmarAjacikIrSitam . sa ca taM pratigRhyeva tathA cakre narAdhipaH .
tato bhImastatra rAjannuSitvA tridaza kSapAH . satkRta : zizupAlena yayau sabalavAhanaH .
nArAyaNaM namaskRtya naraM caiva narottamam . devI sarasvatI vyAsaM tato jayamudIrayet .
saMjaya uvAca tataste sahitA vIrAH prayAtA dakSiNAmukhAH . upAstamanavelAyAM zivirAbhyAzamAgatAH .
vimucya vAhAMstvaritA bhItA samabhavaMstadA . gahanaM dezamAsAdya pracchannA nyavizanta te .
senAnivezamabhito nAtidUramavasthitAH . nikRttA nizitaiH zastraiH samantAt kSatavikSatAH . dIrghamuSNaM ca niHzvasya pANDavAneva cintayatan .
zrutvA ca ninadaM ghoraM pANDavAnAM jayaiSiNAm . anusArabhayAd bhItAH prAGmukhAH prAdravan punaH .
te muhUrtAt tato gatvA zrAntavAhAH pipAsitAH . nAmRSyanta maheSvAsAH krodhAmarSavazaM gatAH . rAjJo vadhena saMtaptA muhUrtaM samavasthitAH .
dhRtarASTra uvAca azraddheyamidaM karma kRtaM bhImena saMjaya . yat sa nAgAyutaprANaH putro mama nipAtitaH .
avadhyaH sarvabhUtAnAM vajrasaMhanano yuvA . pANDavaiH samare putro nihato mama saMjaya . na diSTamabhyatikrAntuM zakyaM gAvalgaNe naraiH . yat sametya raNe pAthaiH putro mama nipAtitaH . adrisAramayaM nUnaM hRdayaM mama saMjaya . hataM putrazataM zrutvA yanna dIrNaM sahasradhA . kathaM hi vRddhamithunaM hataputraM bhaviSyati . na hyahaM pANDaveyasya viSaye vastumutsahe .
kathaM rAjJaH pitA bhUtvA svayaM rAjA ca saMjaya . preSyabhUtaH pravarteyaM pANDaveyasya zAsanAt .
AjJApya pRthivIM sarvAM sthitvA mUrdhni ca saMjaya . kathamadya bhaviSyAmi preSyabhUto durantakRt .
kathaM bhImasya vAkyAni zrotuM zakSyAmi saMjaya . yena putrazataM pUrNamekena nihataM mama .
kRtaM satyaM vacastasya vidurasya mahAtmanaH . akurvatA vacastena mama putreNa saMjaya .
adharmeNa hate tAta putre duryodhane mama . kRtavarmA kRpo drauNiH kimakurvata saMjaya .
saMjaya uvAca gatvA tu tAvakA rAjan nAtidUramavasthitAH . apazyanta vanaM ghoraM nAnAdrumalatAvRtam .
te muhUrtaM tu vizramya labdhatoyaihayottamaiH . sUryAstamanavelAyAM samAsedurmahad vanam .
nAnAmRgagaNairjuSTaM nAnApakSigaNAvRtam . nAnAdrumalatAcchannaM nAnAvyAlaniSevitam .
nAnAtoyaiH samAkIrNaM nAnApuSpopazobhitam . padminIzatasaMchannaM nIlotpalasamAyutam .
pravizya tad vanaM ghoraM vIkSamANAH samantataH . zAkhAsahasrasaMchannaM nyagrodhaM dadRzustataH .
upetya tu tadA rAjan nyagrodhaM te mahArathAH . dadRzurdvipadAM zreSThAH zreSThaM taM vai vanaspatim .
te ' vatIrya rathebhyazca vipramucya ca vAjinaH . upaspRzya yathAnyAyaM saMdhyAmanvAsata prabho .
tato ' staM parvatazreSThamanuprApte divAkare . sarvasya jagato dhAtrI zarvarI samapadyata . grahanakSatratArAbhiH sampUrNAbhiralaMkRtam . nabhoM ' zukamivAbhAti prekSaNIyaM samantataH .
icchayA te pravalganti ye sattvA rAtricAriNaH divAcarAzca ye sattvAste nidrAvazamAgatAH .
rAtriMcarANAM sattvAnAM nirghoSo ' bhUt sudAruNaH . kravyAdAzca pramuditA ghorA prAptA ca zarvarI .
tasmin rAtrimukhe ghore duHkhazokasamanvitAH . kRtavarmA kRpo drauNirupopavivizuH samam .
tatropaviSTAH zocanto nyagrodhasya samIpataH . tamevArthamatikrAntaM kurupANDavayoH kSayam .
nidrayA ca parItAGgA niSedurdharaNItale . zrameNa sudRDhaM yuktA vikSatA vividhaiH zaraiH .
tato nidrAvazaM prAptau kRpabhojau mahArathau . sukhocitAvaduHkhArhI niSaNNau dharaNItale .
tau tu suptau mahArAja zramazokasamanvitau . mahArhazayanopetau bhUmAveva hyanAthavat .
krodhAmarSavazaM prApto droNaputrastu bhArata . na vai sma sa jagAmAtha nidrAM sarpa iva zvasan .
na lebhe sa tu nidrAM vai dahyamAno hi manyunA . vIkSAJcakre mahAbAhustad vanaM ghoradarzanam .
vIkSamANo vanoddezaM nAnasattvairniSevitam . apazyata mahAbAhuryagrodhaM vAyasairyutam .
tatra kAkasahasrANi tAM nizAM paryaNAmayan . sukhaM svapanti kauravya pRthak pRthagupAzrayAH .
supteSu teSu kAkeSu vizravyeSu samantataH . so ' pazyat sahasA yAntamulUkaM ghoradarzanam .
mahAsvanaM mahAkAyaM haryakSaM babhrupiGgalam . sudIrghaghoNAnakharaM suparNamiva vegitam .
so ' tha zabdaM mRduM kRtvA lIyamAna ivANDajaH . nyagrodhasya tataH zAkhAM prArthayAmAsa bhArata .
saMnipatya tu zAkhAyAM nyagrodhasya vihaGgamaH . suptAJjadhAna subahUn vAyasAn vAyasAntakaH .
keSAMcidacchinat pakSAzirAMsi ca cakarta ha . caraNAMzcaiva keSAMcid babhaJja caraNAyudhaH . kSaNenAhan sa balavAn ye ' sya dRSTipathe sthitAH .
teSAM zarIrAvayavaiH zarIraizca vizAmpate . nyagrodhamaNDalaM sarvaM saMchannaM sarvato ' bhavat .
tAMstu hatvA tataH kAkAn kauziko mudito ' bhavat . .43 pratikRtya yathAkAmaM zatrUNAM zatrusUdanaH .
tad dRSTvA sopadhaM karma kauzikena kRtaM nizi . tadbhAvakRtasaMkalpo droNireko ' nvacintayat .
upadezaH kRto ' nena pakSiNA mama saMyuge . zatrUNAM kSapaNe yuktaH prAptaH kAlazca me mataH .
nAdya zakyA mayA hantuM pANDavA jitakAzinaH . balavantaH kRtotsAhAH prAptalakSyAH prahAriNaH .
rAjJaH sakAzAt teSAM tu pratijJAto vadho mayA . pataGgAgnisamAM vRttimAsthAyAtmavinAzinIm .
nyAyato yudhyamAnasya prANatyAgo na saMzayaH . chadmanA ca bhavet siddhiH zatrUNAM ca kSayo mahAn . tatra saMzayitAdAd yo ' rtho niHsaMzayo bhavet .
taM janA bahuH manyante ye ca zAstravizAradAH . yacApyatra bhaved vAcyaM garhitaM lokaninditam . kartavyaM tanmanuSyeNa kSatradharmeNa vartatA . ninditAni ca sarvANi kutsitAni pade pade . sopadhAni kRtAnyeva pANDavairakRtAtmabhiH .
asminnarthe purA gItA zrUyante dharmacintakaiH . zlokA nyAyamavekSadbhistattvArthAstattvadarzibhiH .
parizrAnte vidIrNe vA bhuJjAne vApi zatrubhiH . prasthAne vA praveze vA prahartavyaM riporbalam .
nidrArtamardharAtre ca tathA naSTapraNAyakam . bhinnayodhaM balaM yacca dvidhA yuktaM ca yad bhavet . ityevaM nizcayaM cakre suptAnAM nizi mAraNe . pANDUnAM saha paJcAlaioNaputraH pratApavAn .
sa krUrAM matimAsthAya vinizcitya muhurmuhuH . suptau prAbodhayat tau tu mAtulaM bhojameva ca .
tau prabuddhau mahAtmAnau kRpabhojau mahAbalau . nottaraM pratipadyetAM tatra yuktaM hriyA vRtau .
sa muhUrtamiva dhyAtvA bASyavihvalamabravIt . hato duryodhano rAjA ekavIro mahAbalaH . yasyArthe vairamasmAbhirAsaktaM pANDavaiH saha . ekAkI bahubhiH kSudairAhave zuddhavikramaH . pAtito bhImasenena ekAdazacamUpatiH .
vRkodareNa kSudreNa sunRzaMsamidaM kRtam . mUrdhAbhiSiktasya ziraH pAdena parimRdnatA .
vinardanti ca paJcAlA : zvelanti ca hasanti ca . dhamanti zaGkhAzatazo hRSTA janti ca dundubhIn .
vAditraghoSastumulo vimizraH zaGkhaniHsvanaiH . anilenerito ghoro dizaH pUrayatIva ha .
azvAnAM heSamANAnAM gajAnAM caiva buMhatAm . siMhanAdazca zUrANAM zrUyate sumahAnayam .
dizaM prAcI samAzritya hRSTAnAM gacchatAM bhRzam . rathanemisvanAzcaiva zrUyante lomaharSaNAH .
pANDavairdhArtarASTrANAM yadidaM kadanaM kRtam . vayameva trayaH ziSTA asmin mahati vaizase .
kecinnAgazataprANAH kecit sarvAstrakovidAH . nihatAH pANDaveyaiste manye kAlasya paryayam .
evametena bhAvyaM hi nUnaM kArveNa tattvataH . yathA hyasyedRzI niSThA kRtakArye ' pi duSkare .
bhavetAstu yadi prajJA na mohAdapanIyate . vyApanne ' smin mahatyarthe yannaH zreyastaducyatAm .
vaizampAyana uvAca svargataH sa tu rAjendro nivasan devavezmani . pUjitastridazaiH sAdhyairmarudbhirvasubhistathA .
devalokaM brahmalokaM saMcaran puNyakRd vazI . avasat pRthivIpAlo dIrghakAlamiti zrutiH .
sa kadAcinRpazreSTho yayAtiH zakramAgamat . kathAnte tatra zakreNa sa pRSTaH pRthivIpatiH .3 .
zakra uvAca yadA sa pUrustava rUpeNa rAjan jarAM gRhItvA pracacAra bhUmau . tadA ca rAjyaM sampradAyaiva tasmai tvayA kimuktaH kathayeha satyam .
yayAtiruvAca gaGgAyamunayormadhye kRtsno ' yaM viSayastava . madhya pRthivyAstvaM rAjA bhrAtaro ' ntyAdhipAstava .
stathA titikSuratitikSorviziSTaH . amAnuSebhyo mAnuSAzca pradhAnA vidvAMstathaivAviduSaH pradhAnaH .
AkruzyamAno nAkrozenmanyureva titikSataH . AkroSTAraM nirdahati sukRtaM cAsya vindati .
nAruntudaH syAnna nRzaMsavAdI na hInataH paramabhyAdadIt . yayAsya vAcA para udvijeta na tAM vadeduSatI pApalokyAm .
aruntudaM paruSaM tIkSNavAcaM vAkkaNTakairvitudantaM manuSyAn . vidyAdalakSmIkatamaM janAnAM mukhe nibaddhAM nirRtiM vahantam .
sadbhiH purastAdabhipUjita : syAt sadbhistathA pRSThato rakSitaH syAt . sadAsatAmativAdAMstitikSet satAM vRttaM cAdadItAryavRttaH .
vAksAyakA vadanAnniSpatanti yairAhataH zocati rAtryahAni . parasya nAmarmasu te patanti tAn paNDito nAvasRjet pareSu .
na hIdRzaM saMvananaM triSu lokeSu vidyate . dayA maitrI ca bhUteSu dAnaM ca madhurA ca vAk .
tasmAt sAntvaM sadA vAcyaM na vAcyaM paruSaM kvacit . pUjyAn sampUjayed dadyAnna ca yAcet kadAcana .
saMjaya uvAca rAjan zatasahasrANi tatra tatra padAtinAm . nirmaryAdaM prayuddhAni tat te vakSyAmi bhArata .
na putraH pitaraM jajJe pitA vA putramaurasam . na bhrAtA bhrAtaraM tatra svasrIyaM na ca mAtulaH .
na mAtulaM ca svasrIyo na sakhAyaM sakhA tathA . AviSTA iva yuddhayante pANDavAH kurubhiH saha .
sthAnIkaM naravyAghrAH kecidabhyapatana rathaiH . abhajyanta yugaireva yugAni bharatarSabha .
ratheSAzca ratheSAbhiH kUbarA rathakUbaraiH . saMgataiH sahitAH kecit parasparajighAMsavaH .
na zekuzcalituM kecit saMnipatya sthA rathaiH . prabhinnAstu mahAkAyaH saMnipatya gajA gajaiH . bahudhAdArayan kruddhA viSANairitaretaram . satoraNapatAkaiza vAraNA varavAraNaiH . abhisRtya mahArAja vegavadbhirmahAgajaiH . dantairabhihatAstatra cukruzuH paramAturAH .
abhinItAzca zikSAbhistotrAMkuzasamAhatAH . aprabhinnAH prabhinnAnAM sammukhAbhimukhA yayuH .
prabhinnairapi saMsaktAH kecit tatra mahAgajAH . krauJcavanninadaM kRtvA durduvuH sarvato dizam .
samyak praNItA nAgAzca prabhinnakaraTAmukhAH . RSTitomaranArAcairnirviddhA varavAraNAH . praNedurbhinnamarmANo nipetuzca gatAsavaH . prAdravanta dizaH kecinnadanto bhairavAn ravAn . .
gajAnAM pAdarakSAstu vyUDhoraskAH prahAriNaH . RSTibhizca dhanurbhizca vimalaizca parazvadhaiH . gadAbhirmusalaizcaiva bhindipAlaiH satomaraiH . AyasaiH paripaizcaiva nistriMzaivimalaiH zitaiH . pragRhItaiH susaMrabdhA dravamANAstatastataH . vyadRzyanta mahArAja parasparajighAMsavaH .
rAjamAnAzca nistriMzAH saMsiktA narazoNitaiH . pratyadRzyanta zUrANAmanyonmabhidhAvatAm .
avakSiptAvadhUtAnAmasInAM vIrabAhubhiH . saMjajJe tumulaH zabdaH patatAM paramarmasu .
gadAmusalarugNAnAM bhinnAnAM ca varAsibhiH . dantidantAvabhinnAnAM mRditAnAM ca dantibhiH . tatra tatra naraughANAM krozatAmitaretaram . zuzruvurdAruNA vAcaH pretAnAmiva bhArata .
hayairapi hayArohAzcAmarApIDadhAribhiH . haMsairiva mahAvegairanyonyamabhividrutAH .
taivimuktA mahAprAsA jAmbUnadavibhUSaNAH . AzugA vimalAstIkSNAH sampeturbhujagopamAH .
azvairacyajavaiH kecidAplutya mahato sthAn . zirAMsyAdadire vIrA rathinAmazvasAdinaH .
bahUnapi hayArohAn bhallaiH saMnataparvabhiH . rathI jaghAna samprApya bANagocaramAgatAn .
navameghapratIkAzAzcAkSipya turagAn gajAH . pAdaireva vimRdnanti mattAH kanakabhUSaNAH .
pATyamAneSu kumbheSu pArzveSvapi ca vAraNAH . prAsairvinihatAH kecid vineduH paramAturAH .
sAzvArohAn hayAn kAMzcidunmathya varavAraNAH . sahasA cikSipustatra saMkule bhairave sati .
sAzvArohAn viSANApraikSipya turagAn gajAH . rathaughAnabhimRdnantaH sadhvajAnabhicakramuH .
puMstvAdatimadatvAcca kecit tatra mahAgajAH . sAzvArohAn hayAJjaghnuH karaiH sacaraNaistathA . azvArohaizca samare hastisAdibhireva ca .
pratimAneSu gAtreSu pArzveSvabhi ca vAraNAn . AzugA vimalAstIkSNAH sampeturbhujagopamAH .
narAzvakAyAn nirbhidya lauhAni kavacAni ca . nipeturvimalAH zaktyo vIrabAhubhirarpitAH . maholkApratimA ghorAstatra tatra vizAmpate . dvIpicarmAvanaddhaizca vyAghracarmacchadairapi . vikozaivimalaiH khaGgairabhijagmuH parAn raNe .
abhiplutamabhikruddhamekapAvidAritam . vidarzayantaH sampetuH khagacarmaparazvadhaiH .
kecidAkSipya kariNaH zAzvAnapi rathAn karaiH . vikarSanto dizaH sarvAH sampetuH sarvazabdagAH .
zaGkubhirdAritAH kecit sambhinnAzca parazvadhaiH . hastibhirmuditAH kecit kSuNNAzcAnye turaMgamaiH . rathaneminikRttAzca nikRttAzca parazvadhaiH . vyAkrozanta narA rAjaMstatra tatra sma bAndhavAn . putrAnanye pitRnanye bhrAtR/zca saha bandhubhiH . mAtulAn bhAgineyAMzca parAnapi ca saMyuge .
vikIrNAntrAH subahavo bhagnasakthAzca bhArata . bAhubhizcApare chinnaiH pArtheSu ca vidAritAH .
krandantaH samadRzyanta tRSitA jIvitepsavaH . tRSA parigatAH kecidalpasattvA vizAmpate .
bhUmau nipatitAH saMkhye mRgayAMcakrire jalam . rudhiraughapariklinnAH klizyamAnAzca bhArata . vyanindana bhRzamAtmAnaM tava putrAMzca saMgatAn .
apare kSatriyAH zUrAH kRtavairAH parasparam . naiva zastraM vimuJcanti naiva krandanti mAriSa .
tarjayanti ca saMhRSTAstatra tatra parasparam . Adazya dazanaizcApi krodhAt saradanacchadam . bhRkuTIkuTilairvaktraiH prekSanti ca parasparam . apare klizyamAnAstu zarArtA vraNapIDitAH . niSkUjAH samapadyanta dRDhasattvA mahAbalAH . anye ca visthAH zUrA sthamanyasya saMyuge . . prArthayAnA nipatitAH saMkSuNNA varavAraNaiH . azobhanta mahArAja sapuSpA iva kiMzukAH .
sambabhUvuranIkeSu bahavo bhairavasvanAH . vartamAne mahAbhIme tasmin vIravarakSaye . . nijaghAna pitA putraM putrazca pitaraM raNe . svasrIyo mAtulaM cApi svasrIyaM cApi mAtulaH .
sakhA sakhAyaM ca tathA sambandhI bAndhavaM tathA . evaM yuyudhire tatra kuravaH pANDavaiH saha .
vartamAne tathA tasmin nirmaryAde bhayAnake . bhISmamAsAdya pArthAnAM vAhinI samakampata .
ketunA paJcatAreNa tAlena bharatarSabha . rAjatena mahAbAhurucchritena mahArathe . babhau bhISmastadA rAjazcandramA iva meruNA .
dhRtarASTra uvAca merorathottaraM pArzva pUrvaM cAcakSva saMjaya . nikhilena mahAbuddhe mAlyavantaM ca parvatam .
saMjaya uvAca dakSiNena tu nIlasya meroH pArzve tathottare . uttarAH kuravo rAjan puNyAH siddhaniSevitAH .
tatra vRkSA madhuphalA nityapuSpaphalopagAH . puSpANi ca sugandhIni rasavanti phalAni ca .
sarvakAmaphalAstatra kecid vRkSA janAdhipa . apare kSIriNo nAma vRkSAstatra narAdhipa .
ye kSaranti sadA kSIraM SaDrasaM cAmRtopamam . vastrANi ca prasUyante phaleSvAbharaNAni ca .
sarvA maNimayI bhUmiH sUkSmakAJcanavAlukA . sarvartusukhasaMsparzA niSpaGkA ca janAdhipa .
pudhyakariNyaH zubhAstatra sukhasparzA manoramAH . devalokacyutAH sarve jAyante tatra mAnavAH .
zuklAbhijanasampannAH sarve supriyadarzanAH . mithunAni ca jAyante striyazcApsarasopamAH .
teSAM te kSIriNAM kSIraM pibantyamRtasaMnibham . mithunaM jAyate kAle samaM tacca pravardhate .
tulyarUpaguNopetaM samaveSaM tathaiva ca . ekaikamanuraktaM ca cakravAkasamaM vibho .
nirAmayAzca te lokA nityaM muditamAnasAH . daza varSasahasrANi daza varSazatAni ca . jIvanti te mahArAja na cAnyonyaM jahatyuta . bhAruNDA nAma zakunAstIkSNatuNDA mahAbalAH . tAn nirharantIha mRtAn darISu prakSipanti ca . uttarAH kuravo rAjan vyAkhyAtAste samAsataH .
meroH pArzvamahaM pUrvaM vakSyAmyatha yathAtatham . tasya mUrdhAbhiSekastu bhadrAzvasya vizAmpate .
bhadrasAlavanaM yatra kAlAmrazca mahAdrumaH . kAlAmrastu mahArAja nityapuSpaphalaH zubhaH .
dumazca yojanotsedhaH siddhacAraNasevitaH . tatra te puruSAH zvetAstejoyuktA mahAbalAH .
striyaH kumudavarNAzca sundaryaH priyadarzanAH . candraprabhAzcandravarNAH pUrNacandranibhAnanAH .
candrazItalagAyazca nRtyagItavizAradAH . daza varSasahasrANi tatrAyurbharatarSabha .
kAlAmrarasapItAste nityaM saMsthitayauvanAH . dakSiNena tu nIlasya niSadhasyottareNa tu .
sudarzano nAma mahAJjambUvRkSaH sanAtanaH . sarvakAmaphalaH puNyaH siddhacAraNasevitaH .
tasya nAmnA samAkhyAto jambUdvIpa : sanAtanaH . yojanAnAM sahasraM ca zataM ca bharatarSabha . utsedho vRkSarAjasya divaspRGmanujezvaraH . aratnInAM sahasraM ca zatAni daza paJca ca . pariNAhastu vRkSasya phalAnAM rasabhedinAm . patamAnAni tAnyurvI kurvanti vipulaM svanam .
muJcanti ca rasaM rAjestasmin rajatasaMnibham . tasyA jambvAH phalaraso nadI bhUtvA janAdhipa .
meruM pradakSiNaM kRtvA samprayAtyuttarAn kurUn . . tatra teSAM mana : zAntina pipAsA janAdhipa . tasmin phalarase pIte na jarA bAdhate ca tAn . tatra jAmbUnadaM nAma kanakaM devabhUSaNam . indragopakasaMkAzaM jAyate bhAsvaraM tu tat . taruNAdityavarNAzca jAyante tatra mAnavAH .
tathA mAlyavataH zRGge dRzyate havyavAT sadA . nAmnA saMvartako nAma kAlagnirbharatarSabha .
tathA mAlyavataH zRGge pUrvapUrvAnugaNDikA . yojanAnAM sahasrANi paJcaSaNmAlyavAnatha .
mahArajatasaMkAzA jAyante tatra mAnavAH . brahmalokacyutAH sarve sarve sarveSu sAdhavaH .
tapastapyanti te tIvra bhavanti jhUrdhvaretasaH . rakSaNArthaM tu bhUtAnAM pravizante divAkaram .
SaSTistAni sahasrANi SaSTireva zatAni ca . aruNasyAgrato yAnti parivArya divAkaram .
SaSTi varSasahasrANi SaSTimeva zatAni ca . AdityatApataptAste vizanti zazimaNDalam .
sautiruvAca spRSTamAtrA tu padbhyAM sA garuDena balIyasA . abhajyata taroH zAkhAM bhagnAM caikAmadhArayat .
tAM bhaktvA sa mahAzAkhAM smayamAno vilokayan . athAtra lambato ' pazyadvAlakhilyAnadhomukhAn . .
RSayo hyatra lambante na hanyAmiti tAnRSIn . taporatAnlambamAnAnbrahmarSInabhivIkSya saH .
hanyAdetAnsaMpatantI zAkhetyatha vicintya saH . nakhaidUMDhataraM vIraH saMgRhya gajakacchapau .
sa tadvinAzasaMtrAsAdabhipatya khagAdhipaH . zAkhAmAsyena jagrAha teSAmevAnvavekSayA .
atidaivaM tu tattasya karma dRSTvA maharSayaH . vismayotkampahRdayA nAma cakrurmahAkhage .
guruM bhAraM samAsAdyaDDIna eSa vihaMgamaH . garuDastu khagazreSThastasmAtpannagabhojanaH .
tataH zanaiH paryapatatpakSaiH zailAprakampayan . evaM so ' bhyapataddezAnbahUnsagajakacchapaH .
dayArthaM bAlakhilyAnAM na ca sthAnamavindata . sa gatvA parvatazreSThaM gandhamAdanamaJjasA .
dadarza kazyapaM tatra pitaraM tapasi sthitam . dadarza taM pitA cApi divyarUpaM vihaMgamam .
tejovIryabalopetaM manomArutaraMhasam . zaila , GgapratIkAzaM brahmadaNDamivodyatam .
acintyamanabhidhyeyaM sarvabhUtabhayaMkaram . mahAvIryadharaM raudraM sAkSAdagnimivodyatam .
apradhRSyamajeyaM ca devadAnavarAkSasaiH . bhettAraM girizRGgANAM samudrajalazoSaNam .
lokasaMloDanaM ghoraM kRtAntasamadarzanam . tamAgatamabhiprekSya bhagavAnkazyapastadA . viditvA cAsya saMkalpamidaM vacanamabravIt .
kazyapa uvAca putra mA sAhasaM kArSIrmA sadyo lapsyase vyathAm . mA tvAM daheyuH saMkruddhA vAlakhilyA marIcipAH .
sautiruvAca tataH prasAdayAmAsa kazyapaH putrakAraNAt . vAlakhilyAnmahAbhAgAMtapasA hatakalmaSAn .
kazyapa uvAca prajAhitArthamArambho garuDasya tapodhanAH . cikIrSati mahatkarma tadanujJAtumarhatha .
sautiruvAca evamuktA bhagavatA munayaste samabhyayuH . muktvA zAkhAM giriM puNyaM himavantaMtapo ' rthinaH .
tatasteSvapayAteSu pitaraM vinatAsutaH . zAkhAvyAkSiptavadanaH paryapRcchata kazyapam .
bhagavankva vimuJcAmi taroH zAkhAmimAmaham . varjitaM mAnuSairdezamAkhyAtu bhagavAnmama .
tato niHpuruSaM zailaM himasaMruddhakandaram . agamyaM manasApyanyaistasyAcakhyau sa kazyapaH .
taM parvataM mahAkukSimuddizya sa mahAkhagaH ! javenAbhyapatattArkSya : sazAkhAgajakacchapaH .
na tAM vadhrI pariNahecchatacarmA mahAtanum . zAkhino mahatIM zAkhAM yAM pragRhya yayau khagaH .
sa tataH zatasAhasraM yojanAntaramAgataH . kAlena nAtimahatA garuDaH patagezvaraH .
sa taM gatvA kSaNenaiva parvataM vacanApituH . amuJcanmahatIM zAkhAM sasvanaM tatra khecaraH .
pakSAnilahatazcAsya prAkampata sa zailarAT . mumoca puSpavarSaM ca samAgalitapAdapaH .
zRGgANi ca vyazIryanta girestasya samantataH . maNikAJcanacitrANi zobhayanti mahAgirim .
zAkhino bahavazcApi zAkhAyA ' bhihatAstayA . kAJcanaiH kusumairbhAnta vidyuttvanta ivAmbudAH .
te hemavikacA bhUmau yutAH parvatadhAtubhiH . vyarAjaJchAkhinastatra sUryAMzupratiraJjitAH .
tatastasya gireH zRGgamAsthAya sa khagottamaH . bhakSayAmAsa garuDastAvubhau gajakacchapau .
tAvubhau bhakSayitvA tu sa tAyaH kUrmakuJjarau . tataH parvatakUTAgrAdutpapAta mahAjavaH .
prAvartantAtha devAnAmutpAtAbhayazaMsinaH . indrasya vajraM dayitaM prajajvAla bhayAttataH .
sadhUmA nyapatatsArcirdivolkA nabhasazcyutA . tathA vasUnAM rudrANAmAdityAnAM ca sarvazaH . sAdhyAnAM marutAM caiva ye cAnye devatAgaNAH . svaM svaM praharaNaM teSAM parasparamupAdravat .
abhUtapUrvaM saMgrAme tadA devAsure ' pi ca . vadurvAtAH sanirghAtA : peturulkAH sahasrazaH .
nirabhrameva cAkAzaM prajagarna mahAsvanam . devAnAmapi yo devaH so ' pyavarSata zoNitam .
mamlurmAlyAni devAnAM nezustejAMsi caiva hi . utpAtameghA raudrAzca vavRSuH zoNitaM bahu .
rajAMsi mukuTAnyeSAmutthiAni vyagharSayan . tatastrAsasamudvignaH saha devaiH zataRtuH . utpAtAndAruNAnpazyannityuvAca bRhaspatim .
indra uvAca kimarthaM bhagavanyorA utpAtAH sahasosthitAH . na ca zatru prapazyAmi yudhi yo naH pradharSayet .
bRhaspatiruvAca tavAparAdhAddevendra pramAdAcca zatakrato . tapasA bAlakhilyAnAM maharSINAM mahAtmanAm .
kazyapasya muneH putro vinatAyAzca khecaraH . hartuM somamabhiprApto balavAnkAmarUpadhRk .
samartho balinA zreSTho hartuM somaM vihaMgamaH . sarvaM saMbhavAyAmyasminnasAdhyamapi sAdhayet .
sautiruvAca zrutvaitadvacanaM zakraH provAcAmRtarakSiNaH . mahAvIryabala : pakSI hartuM somamihodyataH .
yuSmAnsaMbodhayAmyeSa yayA na sa harebalAt . atulaM hi balaM tasya bRhaspatiruvAca ha .
tacchrutvA vibudhA vAkyaM vismitA yatnamAsthitAH . parivAryAmRtaM tasthurvajrI cendraH pratApavAn .
dhArayanto vicitrANi kAJcanAni manasvinaH . kavacAni mahArhANi vaidUryavikRtAni ca .
carmANyapi ca gAtreSu bhAnumanti dRDhAni ca . vividhAni ca zastrANi ghorarUpANyanekazaH .
zitatIkSNAgradhArANi samudyamya surottamAH . savisphuliGgajvAlAni sadhUmAni ca sarvazaH .
cakrANi parighAMzcaiva trizUlAni parazvadhAn . zaktIzca vividhAstIkSNA : karavAlAMzca nirmalAn . svadeharUpANyAdAya gadAzcograpradarzanAH .
taiH zastrairbhAnumadbhiste divyAbharaNabhUSitAH . bhAnumantaH suragaNAstasthurvigatakalmaSAH .
anupamabalavIryatajeso dhRtamanasaH parirakSaNe ' mRtasya . asurapuravidAraNAH surA jvalanasamiddhavapu : prakAzinaH .
iti samaravaraM surAH sthitAste parighasahasrazataiH samAkulam . vigalitamiva cAmbarAntaraM tapanamarIcivikAzitaM babhAse .
vaizampAyana uvAca matamAjJAya putrasya dhRtarASTro narAdhipaH . matvA ca dustaraM daivametad rAjazcakAra ha .
anyAyena tathoktastu viduro viduSAM varaH . nAbhyanandad vaco bhrAturvacanaM cedamabravIt .
vidura uvAca nAbhinande nRpate praiSametaM maivaM kRthAH kulanAzAd bibhemi . detacchaGke dyUtakRte narendra .
dhRtarASTra uvAca neha kSattaH kalahastapsyate mAM na ced daivaM pratilomaM bhaviSyat . dhAga tu diSTasya vaze kiledaM sarvaM jagacceSTati na svatantratam .
nArada uvAca kathayiSye sabhAM yAmyAM yudhiSThira nibodha tAm . vaivasvatasya yAM pArtha vizvakarmA cakAra ha .
taijasI sA sabhA rAjan babhUva zatayojanA . vistArAyAmasampannA bhUyasI cApi pANDava . arkaprakAzA bhrAjiSNuH sarvataH kAmarUpiNI . nAtizItA ca cAtyuSNA manasazca praharSiNI .
na zoko na jarA tasyAM kSutpipAse na cApriyam . na ca dainyaM klamo vApi pratikUlaM na cApyuta . .4 .
sarve kAmAH sthitAstasyAM ye divyA ye ca mAnuSAH . sAravacca prabhUtaM ca bhakSyaM bhojyamariMdama . lehyaM coSyaM ca peyaM ca hRdyaM svAdu manoharam . puNDagandhAH srajastasya nityaM kAmaphalA dumAH .
rasavanti ca toyAni zItAnyuSNAni caiva hi . tasyAM rAjarSayaH puNyAstathA brahmarSayo ' malAH .
yamaM vaivasvataM tAta prahRSTAH paryupAsate . yayAtinahuSaH pUrurmAndhAtA somako nRgaH .
trasadasyuzca rAjarSiH kRtavIryaH zrutazravAH . ariSTanemiH siddhazca kRtavegaH kRtirnimiH . pratardanaH zibirmatsyaH pRthulAkSo bRhadrathaH . vArto maruttaH kuzikaH sAMkAzyaH sAMkRtiv\avaH . caturazvaH sadazvormi : kArtavIryazca pArthivaH . bharataH surathazcaiva sunItho nizaddo nalaH . divodAsazca sumanA ambarISo bhagIrathaH . vyazvaH sadazvo vadhyazvaH pRthuvegaH pRthuzravAH . pRSadazvo vasumanAH kSupazca sumahAbalaH . ruSadurvRSasenazca purukutso dhvajI rathI . ArTiSeNo dilIpazca mahAtmA cApyuzInaraH . auzInariH puNDarIkaH zaryAtiH zarabhaH zuciH . aGgo ' riSTazca venazca duSyantaH sRJjayo jayaH . bhAGgAsuriH sunIthazca niSadho ' tha vahInaraH . karandhamo bAhnikzca sudyumno balavAn madhuH . ailo maruttazca tathA balavAn pRthivIpatiH . kapotaromA tRNakaH sahadevArjunau tathA . vyazvaH sAzvaH kRzAzvazca zazAbinduzca pArthivaH . rAjA dazarathazcaiva kakutstho ' tha pravardhanaH . alarkaH kakSasenazca gayo gaurAzva eva ca . jAmadagnayazca rAmazca nAbhAgasagarau tathA . bhUridyumno mahAzvazca pRthAzvo janakastathA . rAjA vainyo vArisenaH purujijjanamejayaH . brahmadattastrigartazca rAjoparicarastathA . . indradyumno bhImajAnulrapRSTho ' nagho layaH . padmo ' tha mucukandazca bhUridyumnaH prasenajit . ariSTanemiH sudyumnaH pRthulAzvo ' STakastathA . zataM matsyA nRpatayaH zataM nIpAH zataM gayAH .
dhRtarASTrAzcaikazatamazItirjanamejayAH . zataM ca brahmadattAnAM vIriNAmIriNAM zatam .
bhISmANAM dve zate ' pyatra bhImAnAM tu tathA zatam . zataM ca prativindhyAnAM zataM nAgAH zataM hayAH .
palAzAnAM zataM jJeyaM zataM kAzakuzAdayaH . zAntanuzcaiva rAjendra pANDuzcaiva pitA tava .
uzaGgavaH zataratho devarAjo jayadrathaH . vRSadarbhazca rAjarSirbuddhimAn saha mantribhiH .
athApare sahasrANi ye gatAH zazabindavaH . iSTavAzvamedhairbahubhirmahadbhirbhUridakSiNaiH .
ete rAjarSayaH puNyAH kIrtimanto bahuzrutAH . tasyAM sabhAyAM rAjendra vaivasvatamupAsate .
agastyo ' tha mataGgazca kAlo mRtyustathaiva ca . yajvAnazcaiva siddhAzca ye ca yogazarIriNaH . agniSvAttAzca pitaraH phenapAzcoSmapAzca ye . svadhAvanto barhiSado mUrtimantastathApare .
kAlacakraM ca sAkSAcca bhagavAn havyavAhanaH . narA duSkRtakarmANo dakSiNAyanamRtyavaH .
kAlasya nayane yuktA yamasya puruSAzca ye . tasyAM ziMzapapAlAzAstathA kAzakuzAdayaH . upAsate dharmarAjaM mUrtimanto janAdhipa . ete cAnye ca bahavaH pitRrAjasabhAsadaH . na zakyAH parisaMkhyAtuM nAmabhiH karmabhistathA .
asambAdhA hi sA pArtha ramyA kAmagamA sabhA . dIrghakAlaM tapastatvA nirmitA vizvakarmaNA .
jvalantI bhAsamAnA ca tejasA svena bhArata . tAmugratapaso yAnti suvratAH satyavAdinaH . zAntAH saMnyAsinaH zuddhAH pUtAH puNyena karmaNA . sarve bhAsvaradehAzca sarve ca virajo ' mbarAH .
citrAGgadAcitramAlyAH sarve jvalitakuNDalAH . sukRtaiH karmabhiH puNyaiH pAribaheca bhUSitAH .
gandharvAzca mahAtmAnaH saGghazazcApsarogaNAH . vAditraM nRtyagItaM ya hAsyaM lAsyaM ca sarvazaH .
puNAyazca gandhAH zabdAzca tasyAM pArtha samantataH . divyAni caiva mAlyAni upatiSThanti nityazaH .
zataM zatasahasrANi dharmiNAM taM prajezvaram . upAsate mahAtmAnaM rUpayuktA manasvinaH .
IdRzI sA sabhA rAjan pitRrAjJo mahAtmanaH . varuNasyApi vakSyAmi sabhAM puSkaramAlinIm .
arjuna uvAca ye zAstravidhimutsRjya yajante zraddhayA ' nvitAH . teSAM niSThA tu kA kRSNa sattvamAho rajastamaH .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca trividhA bhavati zraddhA dehinAM sA svabhAvajA . sAttvikI rAjasI caiva tAmasI cetitAM zRNu .
sattvAnurUpA sarvasya zraddhA bhavati bhArata . zraddhAmayo ' yaM puruSo yo yacchraddhaH sa eva saH .
yajante sAttvikA devAn yakSarakSAMsi rAjasAH . pretAn bhUtagaNAMzcAnye yajante tAmasA janAH .
azAstravihitaM ghoraM tapyante ye tapo janAH . dambhAhaMkArasaMyuktaH kAmarAgabalAnvitAH .
karzayantaH zarIrasthaM bhUtagrAmamacetasaH . mAM caivAntaH zarIrasthaM tAn viddhyAsuranizcayAn .
AhArastvapi sarvasya trividho bhavati priyaH . yajJastapastathA dAnaM teSAM bhedamimaM zRNu . .
AyuH sattvavalArogyasukhaprItivivardhanAH . rasyAH snigdhAH sthirA hRdyA AhArAH sAttvikapriyAH . .
kaTvAlalavaNAtyuSNatIkSNarUkSavidAhinaH . AhArA rAjasasyeSTA duHkhazokAmayapradAH .
yAtayAmaM gatarasaM pUti paryuSitaM ca yat . ucchiSTamapi cAmedhyaM bhojanaM tAmasapriyam .
aphalAkAkSibhiryajJo vidhidRSTo ya ijyate . yaSTavyameveti mana : samAdhAya sa sAttvikaH .
abhisaMdhAya tu phalaM dambhArthamapi caiva yat . ijyate bharatazreSTha taM yajJaM viddhi rAjasam .
vidhihInamasRSTAnnaM mantrahInamadakSiNam . zraddhAvirahitaM yajJaM tAmasaM paricakSate .
devadavijaguruprAjJapUjanaM zaucamArjavam . brahmacaryamahiMsA ca zArIraM tapa ucyate .
anudvegakaraM vAkyaM satyaM priyahitaM ca yat . svAdhyAyAbhyasanaM caiva vAraDmayaM tapa ucyate .
manaHprasAdaH saumyatvaM maunamAtmavinigrahaH . bhAvasaMzuddhirityetat tapo mAnasamucyate .
zraddhayA parayA taptaM tapastat trividhaM naraiH . aphalArkAkSibhiryuktaiH sAttvikaM paricakSate .
satkAramAnapUjArthaM tapo dambhena caiva yat . kriyate tadiha proktaM rAjasaM calamadhruvam .
mUDhagrAheNAtmano yat pIDayA kriyate tapaH . parasyotsAdanArthaM vA tat tAmasamudAhRtam .
dAtavyamiti yad dAnaM dIyate ' nupakAriNe . deze kAle ca pAtre ca tad dAnaM sAttvikaM smRtam .
yattu pratyupakArArthaM phalamuddizya vA punaH . dIyate ca parikliSTaM tad dAnaM rAjasaM smRtam .
adezakAle yad dAnamapAtrebhyazca dIyate . zraUsatkRtamavajJAtaM tat tAmasamudAhRtam .
OM tatsaditi nirdezo brahmaNastrividhaH smRtaH . brAhmaNAstena vedAzca yajJAzca vihitAH purA .
tasmAdomityudAhRtya yajJadAnatapaH kriyAH . pravartante vidhAnoktAH satataM brahmavAdinAm .
tadityanabhisaMdhAya phalaM yajJatapa : kriyAH . dAnakriyAzca vividhA kriyante mokSakAkSibhiH .
sadbhAve sAdhubhAve ca sadityetat prayujyate . prazaste karmaNi tathA sacchabdaH pArtha yujyate .
yajJe tapasi dAne ca sthitiH saditi cocyate . karma caiva tadarthIyaM sadityevAbhidhIyate .
azraddhayA hutaM dattaM tapastaptaM kRtaM ca yat . asadityucyate pArtha na ca tat pretya no iha .
bhISma uvAca cedirAjakule jAtastryakSa eSa caturbhujaH . rAsabhArAvasadRzaM rarAsa ca nanAda ca .
tenAsya mAtApitarau tresatustau sabAndhavau . vaikRtaM tasya tau dRSTvA tyAgAyAkurutAM matim .
tataH sabhAryaM nRpatiM sAmAtyaM sapurohitam . cintAsammUDhahRdayaM vAguvAcAzarIriNI .
eSa te nRpateH putraH zrImAJjAto balAdhikaH . tasmAdasmAnna bhetavyamavyagaH pAhi vai zizum .
na ca vai tasya mRtyurvai na kAlaH pratyupasthitaH . mRtyuhantAsya zastreNa sa cotpanno narAdhipa . .
saMzrutyodAhRtaM vAkyaM bhUtamantarhitaM tataH . putrasnehAbhisaMtaptA jananI vAkyamabravIt .
yenedamIritaM vAkyaM mamaitaM tanayaM prati . prAJjalistaM namasyAmi bravItu sa punarvacaH . yAthAtathyena bhagavAn devo vA yadi vetaraH . zrotumicchAmi putrasya ko ' sya mRtyubhaviSyati .
antarbhUtaM tato bhUtamuvAcedaM punarvacaH . yasyotsaGge gRhItasya bhujAvabhyadhikAvubhau . patiSyataH kSititale paJcazIrSAvivoragau . tRtIyametad bAlasya lalATasthaM tu locanam . nimajjiSyati yaM dRSTvA so ' sya mRtyubhaviSyati . tryakSaM caturbhujaM zrutvA tathA ca samudAhRtam .
pRthivyAM pArthivAH sarve abhyAgacchan didRkSavaH . tAn pUjayitvA samprAptAn yathArha sa mahIpatiH .
