bhRzaM kruddhazca tejasvI nArAcena samArpayat . citrasenaM mahArAja tava putraM mahAyazAH .
tathetarAMstava sutAMstanADayAmAsa bhArata . zarairbahuvidhaiH saMkhye rukmaputraiH sutejanaiH .
tata : saMsthApya samare tAnyanIkAni sarvazaH . abhimanyuprabhRtayaste dvAdaza mahArathAH .
preSitA dharmarAjena bhImasenapadAnugAH . pratijagmurmahArAja tava putrAn mahAbalAn .
dRSTvA rathasthAMstAzUrAn sUryAgnisamatejasaH . sarvAneva maheSvAsAn bhrAjamAnAzriyA vRtAn .
mahAhave dIpyamAnAn suvarNamukuTojjvalAn . tatyajuH samare bhImaM tava putrA mahAbalAH . tAn nAmRSyata kaunteyo jIvamAnA gatA iti .
dhRtarASTra uvAca samapramRdya mahat sainyaM yAntaM zaineyamarjunam . nihrIMkA mama te putrAH kimakurvata saMjaya .
kathaM veSAM tadA yuddhe dhRtirAsInmumUrSatAm . zaineyacaritaM dRSTvA yAdRzaM savyasAcinaH .
kiM nu vakSyanti te kSAtraM sainyamadye parAjitAH . kathaM nu sAtyakiryuddhe vyatikrAnto mahAyazAH .
kathaM ca mama putrANAM jIvatAM tatra saMjaya . zaineyo ' bhiyayau yuddhe tanmamAcakSva saMjaya .
atyadbhutamidaM tAta tvatsakAzAcchraNomyaham . ekasya bahubhiH sArdhe zatrubistairmahArathaiH .
viparItamahaM manye mandabhAgyaM sutaM prati . yatrAvadhyanta samare sAtvatena mahArathAH .
ekasya hi na paryAptaM yatsainyaM tasya saMjaya . kruddhasya yayudhAnasya sarve tiSThantu pANDavAH .
nirjitya samare droNaM kRtinaM citrayodhinam . yathA pazugaNAn siMhastaddhaddhantA sutAn mama .
kRtavarmAdibhiH zUrairyattairbahubhirAhave . yuyudhAno na zakito hantuM yat puruSarSabhaH .
naitadIdRzakaM yuddhaM kRtavAMstatra phAlgunaH . yAdRzaM kRtavAn yuddhaM zinernaptA mahAyazAH .
saMjaya uvAca tava durmantrite rAjan duryodhanakRtena ca . zRNuSvAvahitobhUtvA yat te vakSyAmi bhArata .
punaH saMnyavartanta kRtvA saMzaptakAn mithaH . parAM yuddhe matiM krUrAM tava putrasya zAsanAt .
te
trINi sAdisahasrANi duryodhanapurogamAH . zakakAmbojabAhrIkA yavanAH pAradAstathA .
kulindAstaGgaNAmbaSThA paizAcAzca sabarbarAH . parvatIyAzca rAjendra kruddhA : pASANapANayaH .
abhyadravanta zaineyaM zalabhAH pAvakaM yathA . yuktAzca parvatIyAnAM rathAH pASANayodhinAm .
zUrAH paJcazatA rAjan zaineyaM samupAdravan . tato rathasahasreNa mahArathazatena ca . . dviradAnAM sahasreNa dvisAhanaizca vAjibhiH . zaravarSANi muJcanto vividhAni mahArathAH .
abhyadravanta zaineyamasaMkhyeyAzca pattagaH . tAMzca saMcodayan sarvAn natainamiti bhArata .
duHzAsano mahArAja sAtyakiM paryavArayat . tatrAdbhutamapazyAma zaineyacaritaM mahat .
yadeko bahubhiH sArdhamasambhrAntamayudhyata . avadhIca rathAnIkaM dviradAnAM ca tad balam .
sAdinazcaiva tAn sarvAn dasyUnapi ca sarvazaH . tatra cakrairvimathitairbhagnaizca paramAyudhaiH . akSaizca bahudhA bhagnairISAdaNDakabandhuraiH . kuJjarairmathitaizcApi dhvajaizca vinipAtitaH . varmabhizca tathAnIkairvyavakIrNA vasuMdharA . sragbhirAbharaNairvastrairanukapaizca mAriSa .
saMchannA vasudhA tatra dyauryahairiva bhArata . girirUpadharAzcApi patitAH kuJjarottamAH . aJjanasya kule jAtA vAmanasya ca bhArata . supratIkakule jJAtA mahApadmakule tathA . erAvatakule caiva tathAnyeSu kuleSu ca . jAtA dantivarA rAjazerate bahavo hatAH . vanAjAn parvatIyAn kAmbojAn bAlikAnapi . tathA hayavarAn rAjan nijaghne tatra sAtyakiH . nAnAdezasamutthAMzca nAnAjAtIMzca dantinaH . nijamne tatra zaineyaH zatazo ' tha sahasrazaH .
teSu prakAlyamAneSu dasyUn duHzAsano ' brarIt . nivartadhvamadharmajJA yudhyadhvaM kiM sRtena vaH .
tAMzcAtibhagnAn samprekSya putro duHzAsanastava . pASANayodhinaH zUrAn parvatIyAnacodayat .
azmayuddheSu kuzalA naitajAnAti sAtyakiH . azmayuddhamajAnantaM natainaM yuddhakArmukam .
tathaiva kuravaH sarve nAzmayuddhavizAradAH . abhidravata mAbhaiSTa na vaH prApsyati sAtyakiH .
te parvatIyA rAjAnaH sarve pASANayodhinaH . abhyadravanta zaineyaM rAjAnamiva mantriNaH .
tato gajaziraHprakhyairupalaiH zailavAsinaH . udyatairyuyudhAnasya puratastasthurAhave .
kSepaNIyaistathApyanye sAtvatasya vadhaiSiNaH . coditAstava putreNa sarvato rurudhurdizaH .
teSAmApatatAmeva zilAyuddhaM cikIrSatAm . sAtyakiH pratisaMdhAya nizitAn prAhiNoccharAn .
tAmazmavRSTiM tumulAM parvatIyaiH samIritAm . cicchedoragasaMkAzairnArAcaiH zinipuGgavaH .
tairazmacUrNairdIpyadbhiH khadyotAnAmiva vrajaiH . prAya : sainyAnyahanyanta hAhAbhUtAni mAriSa .
tataH paJcazataM zUrAH samudyatamahAzilAH . nikRttabAhavo rAjan nipeturdharaNItale .
punardazazatAzcAnye zatasAhastriNastathA . sopalairbAhubhizchinnaiH peturaprApya sAtyakim .
pASANayodhinaH zUrAn yatamAnAvasthitAn . nyavadhId bahusAhastrAMstadadbhutamivAbhavat .
tataH punAttamukhAste ' zmavRSTIH samantataH . ayohastAH zUlahastA daradAstaGgaNAH khasAH .
lampAkAzca kulindAzca cikSipustAMzca sAtyakiH . nArAcaiH praticiccheda pratipattivizAradaH .
adrINAM bhidyamAnAnAmantarikSe zitaiH zaraiH . zabdena prAdvan saMkhye rakSAzvagajapattayaH .
azmacUrNairavAkIrNA manuSyagajavAjinaH . nAzaknuvannasthAtuM bhramarairiva daMzitAH .
hataziSTAH sarudhirA bhinnamastakapiNDikAH . kuJjarA varjayAmAsusuyudhAnarathaM tathA .
tataH zabdaH samabhavat tava sainyasya mAriSa . mAdhavenArdhamAnasya sAgarasyeva parvaNi .
taM zabdaM tumulaM zrutvA droNo yantAramabravIt . kruddhaH sAtvatAnAM mahArathaH .
dArayan bahudhA sainyaM raNe carati kAlavat . yatraiSa zabdastumulastatra sUta rathaM naya .
eSa sUte raNe pASANayodhibhirnUnaM yuyudhAnaH samAgataH . tathA hi rathinaH sarve hriyante vidrutairhayaiH .
vizastrakavacA rugNAstatra tatra patanti ca . na zaknuvanti yantAraH saMyantuM tumule hayAn .
ityetad vacanaM zrutvA bhAradvAjasya sArathiH . pratyuvAca tato droNaM sarvazastrabhRtAM varam .
sainyaM dravati cAyuSman kauraveyaM samantataH . pazya rodhAn raNebhagnAn dhAvato vai tatastataH .
ime ca saMhatAH zUrAH paJcAlA : pANDavaiH saha . tvAmeva hi jighAMsanta Adravanti samantataH .
atra kArya samAdhatsva prAptakAlamariMdama . sthAne vA gamane vApi dUraM yAtazca sAtyakiH .
tathaivaM vadatastasya bhAradvAjasya sAratheH . pratyadRzyata zaineyo nighnan bahuvidhAn rathAn .
te vadhyamAnAH samare yuyudhAnena tAvakAH . yuyudhAnarathaM tyaktvA droNAnakAya dudruvuH . yaistu duHzAsanaH sArdha rathaiH pUrva nyavartata . te bhItAstvabhyadhAvanta sarve droNarathaM prati .
brAhmaNa uvAca saMkalpadaMzamazakaM zokaharSahimAtapam . mohAndhakAratimiraM lobhavyAdhisarIsRpam . viSayaikAtyayAdhvAnaM kAmakrodhavirodhakam . tadatItya mahAdurga praviSTo ' smi mahad vanam .
brAhmaNyuvAca kva tad vanaM mahAprAjJa ke vRkSAH saritazca kAH . girayaH parvatAzcaiva kiyatyadhvani tad vanam .
brAhmaNa uvAca naitadasti pRthagbhAva : kiMcidanyat tataH sukham . naitadastyapRthagbhAvaH kiMcid duHkhataraM tataH .
tasmAddhasvataraM nAsti na tato ' sti mahattaram . nAsti tasmAt sUkSmataraM nAstyanyat tatsamaM sukham .
na tatrAvizya zocanti na prahaSyanti ca dvijAH . na ca bibhyati keSAMcit tebhyo bibhyati kecana .
tasmin vane sapta yahAdumAzca phalAni saptAtithayazca sapta . saptAzramAH sapta samAdhayazca dIkSAzca saptaitadaraNyarUpam . .7 .
paJcavarNAni divyAni puSpANi ca phalAni ca . sRjantaH pAdapAstatra vyApya tiSThanti tad vanam .
suvarNAni dvivarNAni puSpANi ca phalAni ca . sRjantaH pAdapAstatra vyApya tiSThanti tad vanam .
surabhINi dvivarNAni puSpANi ca phalAni ca . sRjantaH pAdapAstatra vyApya tiSThanti tad vanam .
surabhINyekavarNAni puSpANi ca phalAni ca . sRjantaH pAdapAstatra vyApya tiSThanti tad vanam .
bahUnyavyaktavarNAni puSpANi ca phalAni ca . visRjantau mahAvRkSau tad vanaM vyApya tiSThataH .
eko vahniH sumanA brAhmaNo ' tra paJcendriyANi samidhazcAtra santi . tebhyo mokSAH sapta phalanti dIkSA guNAH phalAnyatithayaH phalAzAH .
AtithyaM pratigRhNanti tatra tatra maharSayaH . arciteSu pralIneSu teSvanyad rocate vanam .
prajJAkSaM mokSaphalaM zAnticchAyAsamanvitam . jJAnAzrayaM tRptitoyamantaHkSetrajJabhAskaram .
ye ' dhigacchanti taM santa steSAM nAsti bhayaM punaH . Urve cAdhazca tiryak ca tasya nAnto ' dhigamyate .
stvavAGmukhA bhAnumatyo janitryaH . ardhvaM rasAnAdadate prajAbhyaH . sarvAn yathA satyamanityatA ca .
tatraiva pratitiSThanti punastatropayanti ca . sapta saptarSayaH siddhA vasiSThapramukhaiH saha .
yazo vartho bhagazcaiva vijayaH siddhatejasaH . evamevAnuvartante sapta jyotIMSi bhAskaram .
girayaH parvatAzcaiva santi tatra samAsataH . nadyazca sarito vAri vahantyo brahmasambhavam .
nadInAM saGgamazcaiva vaitAne samupahvare . svAtmatRptA yato yAnti sAkSAdeva pitAmaham .
kRzAzAH suvratAzAzca tapasA dagdhakilbiSA : . AtmanyAtmAnamAvizya brahmANaM samupAsate .
zamamapyatra zaMsanti vidyAraNyavido janAH . tadAraNyamabhipretya yathAdhIrabhijAyata .
etadevedRzaM puNyamaraNyaM brAhmaNA viduH . viditvA cAnutiSThanti kSetrajJenAnudarzinA .
bhISma uvAca evamuktastadA rAmo jahi bhISmamiti prabho . uvAca rudatI kanyAM codayantIM punaH punaH .
kAzye na kAmaM gRhNAmi zastraM vai varavarNini . Rte brahmavidAM hetoH kimanyat karavANi te .
vAcA bhISmazca zAlvazca mama rAjJi vasAnugau . bhaviSyato ' navadyAGgi tat kariSyAmi mA zucaH .
na tu zastraM grahISyAmi kathaMcidapi bhAvini . Rte niyogAd viprANAmeSa me samayaH kRtaH .
ambovAca mama duHkhaM bhagavatA vyapaneyaM yatastataH . tacca bhISmaprasUtaM me taM jahIzvara mA ciram .
rAma uvAca kAzikanye punarbaMhi bhISmaste caraNAvubhau . zirasA vandanA. ' pi grahIyaSyati girA mama .
ambovAca jahi bhISmaM raNe rAma garjantamasuraM yathA . samAhUto raNe rAma mama cedicchasi priyam . pratizrutaM ca yadapi tat satyaM kartumarhasi .
bhISma uvAca tayoH saMvadatorevaM rAjan rAmAmbayostadA . RSiH paramadharmAtmA idaM vacanamabravIt .
zaraNAgatAM mahAbAho kanyAM na tyaktumarhasi . yadi bhISmo raNe rAma samAhUtastvayA mRdhe .
nirjito ' smIti vA brUyAt kuryAd vA vacanaM tava . kRtamasyA bhavet kAryaM kanyAyA bhRgunandana .
vAkyaM satyaM ca te vIra bhaviSyati kRtaM vibho . iyaM cApi pratijJA te tadA rAma mahAmune .
jitvA vai kSatriyAn sarvAn brAhmaNeSu pratizrutA . brAhmaNaH kSatriyo vaizyaH zUdrazcaiva raNe yadi .
brahmadviDa bhavitA taM vai haniSyAmIti bhArgava . zaraNArthaM prapannAnAM bhItAnAM zaraNArthinAm .
na zakSyAmi parityAgaM kartuM jIvan kathaMcana . yazca kRtsnaM raNe kSatraM vijeSyati samAgatam .
dIptAtmAnamahaM taM ca haniSyAmIti bhArgava . sa evaM vijayI rAma bhISmaH kurukulodvahaH . tena yudhyasva saMgrAme sametya bhRgunandana . .
rAma uvAca smarAmyahaM pUrvakRtAM pratijJAmRSisattama . tathaiva ca cariSyAmi yathA sAmnaiva lapsyate .
kAryametanmahad brahman kAzikanyAmanogatam . gamiSyAmi svayaM tatra kanyAmAdAya yatra saH .
yadi bhISmo raNazlAghI na kariSyati me vacaH . haniSyAmyenamudriktamiti me nizcitA matiH .
na hi bANA mayotsRSTAH sajjantIha zarIriNAm . kAyeSu viditaM tubhyaM purA kSatriyasaMgare .
evamuktvA tato rAmaH saha tairbrahmavAdibhiH . prayANAya matiM kRtvA samuttasthau mahAtapAH .
tataste tAmuSitvA tu rajanIM tatra tApasAH . hutAgnayo japtajapyAH pratasthurmajjighAMsayA .
abhyagacchat tato rAmaH saha taibrahmavAdibhiH . kurukSetraM mahArAja kanyayA saha bhArata .
nyavizanta tataH sarve parigRhya sarasvatIm . tApasAste mahAtmAno bhRguzreSThapuraskRtAH .
bhISma uvAca tatastRtIye divase saMdideza vyavasthitaH . kuru priyaM sa me rAjan prApto ' smIti mahAvrataH .
tamAgatamahaM zrutvA viSayAntaM mahAbalam . abhyagacchaM javenAzu prItyA tejonidhiM prabhum .
gAM puraskRtya rAjendraM brAhmaNaiH parivAritaH . Rtvibhirdevakalpaizca tathaiva ca purohitaiH .
sa mAmabhigataM dRSTvA jAmadagnyaH pratApavAn . pratijagrAha tAM pUjAM vacanaM cedamabravIt .
rAma uvAca bhISma kAM buddhimAsthAya kAzirAjasutA tadA . akAmena tvayA ' ' nItA punazcaiva visarjitA .
vibhraMzitA tvayA hIyaM dharmAdAste yazasvinI . parAmRSTAM tvayA hImAM ko hi gantumihArhati .
pratyAkhyAtA hi zAlvena tvayA ' ' nIteti bhArata . tasmAdimA manniyogAt pratigRhNISva bhArata .
svadharmaM puruSavyAghra rAjaputrI labhatviyam . na yuktastvavamAno ' yaM rAjJAM kartuM tvayAnagha .
tatastaM vai vimanasamudIkSyAhamathAbruvam . nAhamenAM punardadyAM brahman bhrAtre kathaMcana .
zAlvasyAhamiti prAha purA mAmeva bhArgava . mayA caivAbhyanujJAtA gateyaM nagaraM prati .
na bhayAnnApyanukrozAnnArthalobhAnna kAmyayA . kSAtraM dharmamahaM jahyAmiti me vratamAhitam .
atha mAmabravId rAmaH krodhaparyAkulekSaNaH . na kariSyasi cedetad vAkyaM me narapuGgava .
haniSyAmi sahAmAtyaM tvAmadyeti punaH punaH . saMrambhAdabravId rAmaH krodhaparyAkulekSaNaH .
tamahaM gIIriSTAbhi punaH punarariMdama . ayAcaM bhRguzArdUlaM na caiva prazazAma saH .
praNamya tamahaM mUrdhA bhUyo brAhmaNasattamam . abrUvaM kAraNaM kiM tad yat tvaM yuddhaM mayecchasi .
iSvastraM mama bAlasya bhavataiva caturvidham . upadiSTaM mahAbAho ziSyo ' smi tava bhArgava .
tato mAmabravId rAmaH krodhasaMraktalocanaH . jAnI mAM guruM bhISma gRhNAsImAM na caiva ha .
sutAM kAzyasya kauravya matpriyArthaM mahAmate . na hi te vidyate zAntiranyathA kurunandana .
gRhANemAM mahAbAho rakSasva kulamAtmanaH . tvayA vibhraMzitA hIyaM bhartAraM nAdhigacchati .
tathA brUvantaM tamahaM rAmaM purapuraMjayam . naitadevaM punarbhAvi brahmarSe kiM zrameNa te .
gurutvaM tvayi samprekSya jAmadagnya purAtanam . prasAdaye tvAM bhagavastyaktaiSA tu purA mayA .
ko jAtu parabhAvAM hi nArI vyAlImava sthitAm . vAsayeta gRhe jAnan strINAM doSo mahAtyayaH .
na bhayAd vAsavasyApi dharma jahyAM mahAvrata . prasIda mA vA yadvA te kAryaM tatkuru mA ciram .
ayaM cApi vizuddhAtman purANe zrUyate vibho . maruttena mahAbuddhe gItaH zloko mahAtmanA .
gurorapyavaliptasya kAryAkAryamajAnataH . utpathapratipannasya parityAgo vidhIyate .
sa tva gururiti premNA mayA sammAnito bhRzam . guruvRttiM na jInIghe tasmAda yotsyAmi vai tvayA .
guruM na hanyAM samare brAhmaNaM ca vizeSataH . vizeSatastapovRddhamevaM kSAntaM mayA tava .
udyateSumatho dRSTvA brAhmaNaM kSatrabandhuvat . yo hanyAt samare kruddhaM yudhyantamapalAyinam .
brahmahatyA na tasya syAditi dharmeSU nizcayaH . kSatriyANAM sthito dharmaM kSatriyo ' smi tapodhana .
yo yathA vartate yasmiMstasminneva pravayartayan . nAdharmaM samavApnoti na cAzreyazca vindati .
arthaM vA yadi vA dharma samartho dezakAlavit . arthasaMzayamApannaH zreyAnniH saMzayo naraH .
yasmAt saMzayite ' pyarthe ' yathAnyAyaM pravartase . tasmAd yotsyAmi sahitastvayA rAma mahAhave .
pazya me bAhuvIryaM vikramaM cAtimAnuSam . evaM gate ' pi tu mayA yacchakyaM bhRgunandana . .
tat kariSye kurukSetre yotsye vipra tvayA saha . dvandve rAma yatheSTaM me sajjIbhava mahAdyute .
tatra tvaM nihato rAma mayA zarazatArditaH . prApsyase nirjitA~llokAn zastrapUto mahAraNe .
sa gaccha vinivartasva kurukSetraM raNapriya . tatraiSyAmi mahAbAho yuddhAya tvAMta podhana .
api tatra tvayA rAma kRtaM zaucaM purA pituH . tatrAhamapi hatvA tvAM zaucaM kartA ' smi bhArgava .
tatra rAma samAgaccha tvaritaM yuddhadurmadA vyapaneSyAmi te darthaM paurANaM brAhmaNabruva . rAma bahuzaH
yaccApi katthase parivatsare . nirjitAH kSatriyA loke mayaikeneti tacchRNu .
na tadA jAtavAn bhISmaH kSatriyo vApi madvidhaH . pazcAjjAtAni tejAMsi tRNeSu jvalitaM tvayA . .
yaste yuddhamayaM dadhaiM kAmaM ca vyapanAzayet . so ' haM jAto mahAbAho bhISmaH parapuraMjayaH . vyapaneSyAmi te darpa yuddhe rAma na saMzayaH .
bhISma uvAca tato mAmabravId rAmaH prahasanniva bhArata . diSTyA bhISma mayA sAdhU yoddhumicchasi saMgare .
ayaM gacchAmi kauravya kurukSetraM tvayA saha . bhASitaM te kariSyAmi tatrAgaccha paraMtapa .
tatra tvAM nihataM mAtA mayA zarazatAcitam . jAhnavI pazyatAM bhISma gRdhrakaGkabalAzanam .
kRpaNaM tvAmabhiprekSya siddhacAraNasevitA . mayA vinihataM devI rodatAmadya pArthiva .
atadarhA mahAbhAgA bhagIrathasutA ' dhA . yA tvAmajIjananmandaM yuddhakAmukamAturam .
ehi gaccha mayA bhISma yuddhakAmuda durmada . gRhANa sarvaM kauravya rathAdi bharatarSabha .
iti bravANAM tamahaM rAmaM parapuraMjayam . praNamya zirasA rAmamevamastvityathAbruvam .
evamuktvA yayau rAmaH kurukSetraM yuyutsayA . pravizya nagaraM cAhaM satyavatyai nyavedayam .
tataH kRtasvastyayano mAtrA ca pratinanditaH . dvijAtIn vAcya puNyAhaM svasti caiva mahAdyute .
rathamAsthAya ruciraM rAjataM pANDurairhayaiH . sUpaskaraM svadhiSThAnaM vaiyAghraparivAraNam .
upapannaM mahAzastraiH sarvopakaraNAnvitam . tatkulInena vIreNa hayazAstravidANe .
yattuM sUtena ziSTena bahuzo dRSTakarmaNA . daMzitaH pANDureNAhaM kavacena vapuSmatA .
pANDuraM kArmukaM gRhya prAyA bharatasattama . pANDureNAtapatreNa dhriyamANena mUrdhani .
pANDuraizcApi vyajanairvIjyamAno narAdhipa . zuklavAsAH sitoSNISaH sarvazuklavibhUSaNaH .
stUyamAno jayAzIbhiniSkramya gajasAhvayAt . kurukSetraM raNakSetramupAyAM bharatarSabha .
te hayAzcoditAstena sUtena paramAhave . avahan mAM bhRzaM rAjan manomArutaraMhasaH .
gatvAhaM tat kurukSetraM sa ca rAmaH pratApavAn . yuddhAya sahasA rAjan parAkrAntau parasparam .
tataH saMdarzane ' tiSThaM rAmasyAtitapasvinaH . pragRhya zaGkhapravaraM tataH prAdhamamuttamam .
tatastatra dvijA rAjaMstApasAzca vanaukasaH . apazyanta raNaM divyaM devAH sendragaNAstadA .
tato divyAni mAlyAni prAdurAsaMstatastataH . vAditrANi ca divyAni meghavRndAni caiva ha .
tataste tApasAH sarve bhArgavasyAnuyAyinaH . prekSakAH samapadyanta parivArya raNAjiram .
tato mAmabravId devI sarvabhUtahitaiSiNI . mAtA svarUpiNI rAjan kimidaM te cikIrSitam .
gatvAhaM jAmadagnyaM tu prayAciSye kurUdvaha . bhISmeNa saha mA yotsI : ziSyeNeti punaH punaH .
