avairA ye tvanAyAsA maitrIcittaratAH sadA . sarvabhUtadayAvantaste narAH svargagAminaH .
zraddhAvanto dayAvantazcokSAzcokSajanapriyAH . dharmAdharmavido nityaM te narAH svargagAminaH .
zubhAnAmazubhAnAM ca karmaNAM phalasaMcaye . vipAkajJAzca ye devi te narAH svargagAminaH .
nyAyopetA guNopetA devadvijaparAH sadA . samutthAnamanuprAptAste narAH svargagAminaH .
zubhaiH karmaphalairdevi mayaite parikIrtitAH . svargamArgaparA bhUyaH kiM tvaM zrotumihecchasi .
umovAca mahAn me saMzayaH kazcanmAn prati mahezvara . tasmAt tvaM naipuNenAdya mama vyAkhyAtumarhasi .
kenAyurlabhate dIrgha karmaNA puruSaH prabho . tapasA vApi deveza kenAyurlabhate mahat .
kSINAyuH kena bhavati karmaNA bhuvi mAnavaH . vipAkaM karmaNAM deva vaktumarhasyanindita .
apare ca mahAbhAgyA mandabhAgyAstathApare . akulInAstathA cAnye kulInAzca tathApare .
durdarzAH kecidAbhAnti narA : kASThamayA iva . priyadarzAstathA cAnye darzanAdeva mAnavAH .
duSprajJAH kecidAbhAnti kecidAbhAnti paNDitAH . mahAprAjJAstathaivAnye jJAnavijJAnabhAvinaH .
alpAbAdhAstathA kecinmahAbAdhAstathApare . dRzyante puruSA deva tanme vyAkhyAtumarhasi .
zrImahezvara uvAca hanta te ' haM pravakSyAmi devi karmaphalodayam . martyaloke naraH sarvo yena svaphalamaznute .
prANAtipAte yo raudro daNDahastodyataH sadA . nityamudyatazastrazca hanti bhUtagaNAn naraH . nirdayaH sarvabhUtAnAM nityamudvegakArakaH . api kITapipIlAnAmazaraNyaH sunighRNaH . evaMbhUto naro devi nirayaM pratipadyate . viparItastu dharmAtmA rUpavAnabhijAyate .
pApena karmaNA devi vadhyo hiMsAratirnaraH . apriyaH sarvabhUtAnAM hInAyurupajAyate .
nirayaM yAti hiMsAtmA yAti svargamahiMsakaH . yAtanAM niraye raudrAM sa kRcchrAM labhate naraH .
yaH kazcinnirayAt tasmAt samuttarati karhicit . mAnuSyaM labhate cApi hInAyustatra jAyate . pApena karmaNA devi baddho hiMsAratirnaraH . apriyaH sarvabhUtAnAM hInAyurupajAyate . yastu zuklAbhijAtIyaH prANighAtavivarjakaH . nikSiptazastro nirdaNDo na hiMsati kadAcana . na ghAtayati nA hanti naMnta naivAnumodate . sarvabhUteSu sasneho yathA ' ' tmani tathApare . IdRzaH puruSotkarSo devi devatvamaznute . upapannAn sukhAn bhogAnupAznAti mudA yutaH .
atha cenmAnuSe loke kadAcidupapadyate . tatra dIrghAyurutpanna : sa naraH sukhamedhate .
eSa dIrghAyuSAM mArgaH suvRttAnAM sukarmiNAm . prANihiMsAvimokSeNa brahmaNA samudIritaH .
bhISma uvAca ityukto ' bhiprazasyaitat paramarSastu zAsanam . mokSadharmArthasaMyuktamidaM praSTuM pracakrame .
zuka uvAca prajJAvAzrotriyo yajvA kRtaprajJo ' nasUyakaH . anAgatAmanaiticaM kathaM brahmAdhigacchati .
tavayasa brahmacaryeNa sarvatyAgena medhayA . sAMkhye vA yadi vA yoga etat pRSTo vadasva me .
manasazcendriyANAM ca yathaikAmyamavApyate . yenopAyena puruSaistat tvaM vyAkhyAtumarhasi .
vyAsa uvAca nAnyatra vidyAtapasornAnyatrendriyanigrahAt . nAnyatra sarvasaMtyAgAt siddhiM vindati kazcana .
mahAbhUtAni sarvANi pUrvasRSTiH svayambhuvaH . bhUyiSThaM prANabhRdagnAme niviSTAni zarIriSu .
bhUmedeho jalAt sneho jyotiSazcakSuSI smRte . prANApAnAzrayo vAyu : kheSvAkAzaM zarIriNAm .
krAnte viSNurbale zakraH koSThe ' gnirbhoktumicchati . karNayoH pradizaH zrotraM jihvAyAM vAk sarasvatI .
karNI tvak cakSuSI jihvAra nAsikA caiva paJcamI . darzanIyendriyoktAni dvArANyAhArasiddhaye .
zabdaH sparzastathA rUpaM raso gandhazca paJcamaH . indriyArthAn pRthagvidyAdindriyebhyastu nityadA .
indriyANi manoyuGkte vazyAn yanteva vAjinaH . panazcApi sadA yuGkte bhUtAtmA hRdayAzritaH .
indriyANAM tathaivaiSAM sarveSAmIzvaraM manaH . niyame ca visarge ca bhUtAtmA mAnasastathA .
indriyANIndriyArthAzca svabhAvazcetanA manaH . prANApAnau ca jIvazca nityaM deheSu dehinAm .
Azrayo nAsti sattvasya guNAH zabdo na cetanA . sattvaM hi tejaH sRjati na guNAn vai kathaMcana .
evaM saptadazaM dehe vRtaM SoDazabhirguNaiH . manISI manasA vipraH pazyatyAtmAnamAtmani .
na hyayaM cakSuSA dRzyo na ca sarvairapIndriyaiH . manasA tu pradIpena mahAnAtmA prakAzate .
azabdasparzarUpaM tadarasAgandhamavyayam . azarIraM zarIreSu nirIkSeta nirindriyam .
avyaktaM sarvadeheSu maryeSu paramAzritam . yo ' nupazyati sa pretya kalpate brahmabhUyase .
vidyAbhijanasampanne brAhmaNe gavi hastini . zuci caiva zvapAke ca paNDitAH samadarzinaH .
sa hi sarveSu bhUteSu jaGgameSu dhruveSu ca . vasatyeko mahAnAtmA yena sarvamidaM tatam .
sarvabhUteSu cAtmAnaM sarvabhUtAni cAtmani . yadA pazyati bhUtAtmA brahma sampadyate tadA .
yAvAnAtmani vedAtmA tAvAnAtmA parAtmani . ya evaM satataM veda so ' mRtatvAya kalpate .
sarvabhUtAtmabhUtasya vibhorbhUtahitasya ca . devA ' pi mArge muhyanti apadasya padaiSiNaH .
zakuntAnAmivAkAze matsyAnAmiva codake . yathA gatirna dRzyeta tathA jJAnavidAM gatiH .
kAla : pacati bhUtAni sarvANyevAtmanAtmani . yasmistu pacyate kAlastaM vedeha na kazcana .
na tadUrdhvaM na tiryak ca nAdho na ca punaH punaH . na madhye pratigRhNIte naiva kiMcit kutazcana .
sarve ' ntaHsthA ime lokA bAhmameSAM na kiMcana . yadyajasraM samAgacched yathA bANo guNacyutaH . naivAntaM kAraNasyeyAd yadyapi syAnmanojavaH . tasmAt sUkSmAt sUkSmataraM nAsti sthUlataraM tataH .
sarvataH pANipAdaM tat sarvato ' kSiziromukham . sarvataHzrutimalloke sarvamAvRtya tiSThati .
tadevANoraNutaraM tanmahadbhyo mahattaram . tadantaHsarvabhUtAnAM dhruvaM tiSThanna dRzyate .
akSaraM ca kSaraM caiva dvaidhIbhAvo ' yamAtmanaH . kSaraH sarveSu bhUteSa divyaM tamRtamakSaram .
navadvAraM puraM gatvA haMso hi niyato vazI . IzaH sarvasya bhUtasya sthAvarasya carasya ca .
hAnibhaGgavikalpAnAM navAnAM saMcayena ca . zarIrANAmajasyAhuha~satvaM pAradarzinaH .
haMsoktaM cAkSaraM caiva kUTasthaM yat tadakSaram . tad vidvAnakSaraM prApya jahAti prANajanmanI .
nakula uvAca uktaM bahuvidhaM vAkyaM dharmarAjena mAdhava . dharmajJena vadAnyena zrutaM caiva hi tat tvayA .
matamAjJAya rAjJazca bhImasenena mAdhava . saMzamo bAhuvIryaM ca khyApitaM mAdhavAtmanaH .
tathaiva phAlgunenApi yaduktaM tat tvayA zrutam . Atmanazca mataM vIraM kathitaM bhavatA sakRt .
sarvametadatikramya zrutvA paramataM bhavAn . yat prAptakAlaM manyethAstataM kuryAH puruSottama .
tasmiMstasmin nimittaM hi mataM bhavati kezava . prAptakAla manuSyeNa kSamaM kAryamarindama .
anyathA cintito hyarthaH punarbhavati so ' nyathA . anityamatayo loke narAH puruSasattama .
anyathA buddhayA hyAsannasmAsu vanavAsiSu . adRzyeSvanyathA kRSNa dRzyeSu punaranyathA .
asmAkamapi vArSNeya vane vicaratAM tadA . na tathA praNayo rAjye yathA samprati vartate .
nivRttavanavAsAn naH zrutvA vIra samAgatAH . akSauhiNyo hi saptemAstvatprasAdAjjanArdana .
imAn hi puruSavyAghrAnacintyabalapauruSAn . AttazastrAn raNe dRSTvA na vyathediha kaH pumAn .
sa bhavAn kurumadhye taM sAntvapUrvaM bhayottaram . brUyAd vAkyaM yathA mando na vyatheta suyodhanaH .
yudhiSThiraM bhImasenaM bIbhatsuM cAparAjitam . sahadevaM ca mAM caiva tvAM ca rAmaM ca kezava . . sAtyakiM ca mahAvIryaM virATaM ca sahAtmajam . dupadaM ca sahAmAtyaM dhRSTadyumnaM ca mAdhava . kAzirAjaM ca vikrAntaM dhRSTaketuM ca cedipam . mAMsazoNitabhRnmartyaH pratiyudhyeta ko yudhi .
sa bhavAn gamanAdeva sAdhayiSyatyasaMzayam . iSTamarthaM mahAbAho dharmarAjasya kevalam .
vidurazcaiva bhISmazca droNazca sahabAhnikaH . zreyaH samarthA vijJAtumucyamAnAstvayAnagha .
te cainamanuneSyanti dhRtarASTraM janAdhipam . taM ca pApasamAcAraM sahAmAtyaM suyodhanam .
zrotA cArthasya vidurastvaM ca vaktA janArdana . kamivArthaM nivartantaM sthApayetAM na varmani .
bRhadazva uvAca sa nadI : parvatAMzcaiva vanAni ca sarAMsi ca . acireNAticakrAma khecaraH khe caraniva .
tathA prayAte tu rathe tadA bhAGgAsurirnRpaH . uttarIyamadho ' pazyad bhraSTaM parapurajayaH .
tataH sa tvaramANastu paTe nipatite tadA . grahISyAmIti taM rAjA nalamAha mahAmanAH . nigRhaNeSva mahAbuddhe hayAnetAn mahAjavAn . vArSNeyo yAvadenaM me paTamAnayatAmiha .
nalastaM pratyuvAcAtha dUre bhraSTaH paTastavA yojanaM samatikrAnto nAhartuM zakyate punaH .
evamukto nalenAtha tadA bhAGgAsurirnRpaH . AsasAda vane rAjan phalavantaM bibhItakam .
taM dRSTvA bAhukaM rAjA tvaramANo ' bhyabhASata . mamApi sUta pazya tvaM saMkhyAne paramaM balam .
sarvaH sarvaM na jAnAti sarvajJo nAsti kazcana . naikatra pariniSThAsti jJAnasya puruSe kvacit .
vRkSe ' smin yAni parNAni phalAnyapi ca bAhuka . patitAnyapi yAnyatra tatraikamadhikaM zatam . ekapatrAdhikaM cAtra phalamekaM ca bAhukA paJcakoTyo ' tha patrANAM dvayorapi ca zAkhayoH . pracinuguhyasya zAkhe dve yAzcApyanyAH prazAkhikAH . AbhyAM phalasahasre dve paJconaM zatameva ca .
tato rathamavasthApya rAjAnaM bAhuko ' bravIt . parokSamiva me rAjan katthase zatrukarzana . pratyakSametat kartAsmi zAtayitvA vibhItakam . athAtra gaNite rAjan vidyate na parokSatA . pratyakSaM te mahArAja zAtayiSye bibhItakam . ahaM hi nAbhijAnAmi bhavedevaM na veti vA .
saMkhyAsyAmi phalAnyasya pazyataste janAdhipa . muhUrtamapi vArSNeyo razmIn yacchatu vAjinAm .
tamabravInRpaH sUtaM nAyaM kAlo vilambitum . bAhukastvabravIdenaM paraM yatnaM samAsthitaH . pratIkSasva muhUrtaM tvamathavA tvarate bhavAn . eSa yAti zivaH panthA yAhi vArSNeyasArathiH .
abravIdUtuparNastu sAntvayan kurunandana . tvameva yantA nAnyo ' sti pRthivyAmapi bAhuka .
tvatkRte yAtumicchAmi vidarbhAn hayakovidA zaraNaM tvAM prapanno ' smi na vighnaM kartumarhasi .
kAmaM ca te kariSyAmi yanmAM vakSyasi bAhuka . vidarbhAn yadi yAtvAdya sUryaM darzayitAsi me .
athAbravId bAhukastaM saMkhyAya me bibhItakam . tato vidarbhAn yAsyAmi kuruSvaivaM vaco mama .
akAma iva taM rAjA gaNayasvetyuvAca ha . ekadezaM ca zAkhAyAH samAdiSTaM mayAnagha . gaNayasvAzvatattvajJa tatastvaM prItimAvaha . so ' vatIrya rathAt tUrNaM zAtayAmAsa taM dumam .
tataH sa vismayAviSTo rAjAnamidamabravIt . gaNayitvA yathoktAni tAvantyeva phalAni tu .
atyadbhutamidaM rAjan dRSTavAnasmi te balam . zrotumicchAmi tAM vidyAM yayaitajjJAyate nRpa . tamuvAca tato rAjA tvarito gamane nRpa . viddhyakSahadayajJaM mAM saMkhyAne ca vizAradam .
bAhukastamuvAcAtha dehi vidyAmimAM mama . matto ' pi cAzcahRdayaM gRhANa puruSarSabha .
RtuparNastato rAjA bAhukaM kAryagauravAt . hayajJAnasya lobhAcca taM tathetyabravId vacaH .
yathoktaM tvaM gRhANedamakSANAM hRdayaM param . nikSepo me ' zvahRdayaM tvayi tiSThatu bAhukA evamuktvA dadau vidyAmRtuparNo nalAya vai .
tasyAkSahRdayajJasya zarIrAni : sRtaH kaliH . karkoTakaviSaM tIkSNaM mukhAt satatamudvaman . kalestasya tadArtasya zApAgniH sa viniHsRtaH . sa tena karzitA rAjA dIrghakAlamanAtmavAn .
tato viSavimuktAtmA svaM rUpamakarot kaliH . taM zaptumaicchat kupito niSadhAdhipatirnalaH .
tamuvAca kali to vepamAnaH kRtAJjaliH . kopaM saMyaccha nRpate kIrtiM dAsyAmi te parAm .
indrasenasya jananI kupitA mAzapat purA . yadA tvayA parityaktA tato ' haM bhRzapIDitaH .
avasaM tvayi rAjendra suduHkhamaparAjita . viSeNa nAgarAjasya dahyamAno divAnizam .
zaraNaM tvAM prapanno ' smi zRNu cedaM vaco mama ! ye ca tvAM manujA loke kIrtayiSyantyatandritAH . matprasUtaM bhayaM teSAM na kadAcid bhaviSyati . bhayArtaM zaraNaM yAtaM yadi mAM tvaM na zapsyase . evamukto nalo rAjA nyayacchat kopamAtmanaH .
tato bhItaH kaliH kSipraM praviveza bibhItakam . kalistvanyaistadAdRzyaH kathayan naiSadhena vai .
tato gatajvaro rAjA naiSadhaH paravIrahA . sampraNaSTe kalau rAjA saMkhyAyAsya phalAnyuta . mudA paramayA yuktastejasAtha pareNa vai . rathamAruhya tejasvI prayayau javanairhayaiH .
bibhItakazcAprazastaH saMvRttaH kalisaMzrayAt . hayottamAnutpatato dvijAniva punaH punaH . nalaH saMcodayAmAsa prahRSTenAntarAtmanA . vidarbhAbhimukho rAjA prayayau sa mahAyazAH .
nale ta samatikrAnte kalirapyagamad gRham . tato gatajvaro rAjA nalo ' bhUt pRthivIpatiH . vimuktaH kalinA rAjan rUpamAtraviyojitaH .
pulastya uvAca tato gaccheta rAjendra kurukSetramabhiSTutam . pApebhyo yatra mucyante darzanAt sarvajantavaH .
kurukSetraM gamiSyAmi kurukSetre vasAmyaham . ya evaM satataM brUyAt sarvapApaiH pramucyate .
pAMsavo ' pi kurukSetre vAyunA samudIritAH . api duSkRtakarmANaM nayanti paramAM gatim .
dakSiNena sarasvatyA dRSadvatyuttareNa ca . ye vasanti kurukSetre te vasanti triviSTape .
tatra mAsaM vaseddhIraH sarasvatyAM yudhiSThira . yatra brahmAdayo devA RSayaH siddhacAraNAH .
gandharvApsaraso yakSAH pannagAzca mahIpate . brahmakSetraM mahApuNyamabhigacchanti bhArata .
manasApyabhikAmasya kurukSetraM yudhiSThira . pApAni vipraNazyanti brahmalokaM ca gacchati .
gatvA hi zraddhayA yuktaH kurukSetraM kurUdvaha . phalaM prApnoti ca tadA rAjasUyAzvamedhayoH .
tato maGkhanakaM nAma dvArapAlaM mahAbalam . yakSaM samabhivAdyaiva gosahasraphalaM labhet .
tato gacchetadharmajJa viSNo : sthAnamanuttamam . satataM nAma rAjendra yatra saMnihito hariH .
tatra snAtvA ca natvA ca trilokaprabhavaM harim . azvamedhamavApnoti viSNulokaM ca gacchati . tataH pAriplavaM gacchet tIrthaM trailokyavizrutam . agniSTomAtirAtrAbhyAM phalaM prApnoti bhArata .
pRthivItIrthamAsAdya gosahasraphalaM labhet . tataH zAlUkinI gatvA tIrthasevI narAdhipa . . dazAzvamedhe snAtvA ca tadeva phalamApnuyAt . sarpadevIM samAsAdya nAgAnAM tIrthamuttamam . agniSTomamavApnoti nAgalokaM ca vindati . tato gacchetadharmajJa dvArapAlaM tarantukam . tatroSya rajanImekAM gosahasraphalaM labhet . tataH paJcanadaM gatvA niyato niyatAzanaH . koTitIrthamupaspRzya hayamedhaphalaM labhet . azvinostIrthamAsAdya rUpavAnabhijAyate .
tato gacchetadharmajJa vArAhaM tIrthamuttamam . viSNurvArAharUpeNa pUrvaM yatra sthito ' bhavat . tatra snAtvA narazreSTha agniSTomaphalaM labhet .
tato jayantyAM rAjendra somatIrthaM samAvizet . snAtvA phalamavApnoti rAjasUyasya mAnavaH .
ekahaMse naraH snAtvAH gosahasraphalaM labhet . kRtAzaucaM samAsAdya tIrthasevI narAdhipa . puNDarIkamavApnoti kRtazauto bhavecca saH .
tato muJjavaTaM nAma sthANoH sthAnaM mahAtmanaH . upoSya rajanImekAM gANapatyamavApnuyAt .
tatraiva ca mahArAja yakSiNI lokavizrutAm . snAtvAbhigamya rAjendra sarvAn kAmAnavApnuyAt .
kurukSetrasya tad dvAraM vizrutaM bharatarSabha . pradakSiNamupAvRtya tIrthasevI samAhitaH . sammitaM puSkarANAM ca snAtvArya pitRdevatAH . jAmadagnyena rAmeNa kRtaM tat sumahAtmanA . kRtakRtyo bhaved rAjannazvamedhaM ca vindati . tato rAmahradAna gacchet tIrthasevI samAhitaH .
tatra rAmeNa rAjendra tarasA dIptatejasA . kSatramutsAdya vIreNa hradAH paJca nivezitAH .
pUrayitvA naravyAghra rudhireNeti vizrutam . pitarastarpitAH sarve tathaiva prapitAmahAH .
tataste pitara : prItA rAmamUcurnarAdhipa .
pitara UcuH rAma rAma mahAbhAga prItAH sma tava bhArgava . anayA pitRbhaktyA ca vikrameNa ca te vibho . varaM vRNISva bhadraM te kimicchasi mahAdyute .
pulastya uvAca evamuktaH sa rAjendra rAmaH praharatAM varaH . abravIt prAJjalirvAkyaM pitRRn sa gagane sthitAn . bhavanto yadi me prItA yadyanucAhyatA mayi . pitRprasAdamiccheyaM tapa ApyAyanaM punaH .
yacca roSAbhibhUtena kSatramutsAditaM mayA . tatazca pApAnmucyeyaM yuSmAkaM tejasApyaham . hradAzca tIrthabhUtA me bhaveyurbhuvi vizrutAH .
etacchrutvA zubhaM vAkyaM rAmasya pitarastadA . pratyUcuH paramaprItA rAma harSasamanvitAH . tapaste vardhatAM bhUyaH pitRbhaktyA vizeSataH .
yacca roSAbhibhUtena kSatramutsAditaM tvayA . tatazca pApAnmuktastvaM patitAste svakarmabhiH .
hradAzca tava tIrthatvaM gamiSyanti na saMzayaH . hradeSu teSu yaH snAtvA pitRn saMtarpayiSyati . pitarastasya vai prItA dAsyanti bhuvi durlabham . IpsitaM ca mana : kAmaM svargalokaM ca zAzvatam .
evaM dattvA varAn rAjan rAmasya pitarastadA . Amantrya bhArgavaM prItyA tatraivAntarhitAstataH .
evaM rAmahadAH puNyA bhArgavasya mahAtmanaH . snAtvA hRdeSu rAmasya brahmacArI zubhavataH . rAmamabhyarcya rAjendra labhed bahusuvarNakam . vaMzamUlakamAsAdya tIrthasevI kurUdvaha .
svavaMzamuddhared rAjan snAtvA vai vaMzamUlake . kAyazodhanamAsAdya tIrthaM bharatasattama . zarIrazuddhiH snAtasya tasmiMstIrthe na saMzayaH . zuddhadehaca saMyAti zubhA~llokAnanuttamAn .
tato gacchetadharmajJa tIrthaM trailokyavizrutam . lokA yatroddhatAH pUrvaM viSNunA prabhaviSNunA . lokoddhAraM samAsAdya tIrthaM trailokyapUjitam . snAtvA tIrthavare rAjaillokAnuddharate svakAn .
zrItIrthaM ca samAmAdya snAtvA niyatamAnasaH . arcayitvA pitRRn devAn vindate zriyamuttamAm .
kapilAtIrthamAsAdya brahmacArI samAhitaH . tatra snAtvArcayitvA ca pitRn svAn daivatAnyapi . kapilAnAM sahasrasya phalaM vindati mAnavaH .
sUryatIrthaM samAsAdya snAtvA niyamAnasaH . arcayitvA pitRRn devAnupavAsaparAyaNaH . agniSTomamavApnoti sUryalokaM ca gacchati .
gavAM bhavanamAsAdya tIrthasevI yathAkramam . tatrAbhiSekaM kurvANo gosahasraphalaM labhet .
zaGkhinItIrthamAsAdya tIrthasevI kurUdvaha . devyAstIrthe naraH snAtvA labhate rUpamuttamam .
tato gaccheta rAjendra dvArapAlamarantukam . tacca tIrthaM sarasvatyAM yakSendrasya mahAtmanaH . tatra snAtvA naro rAjannagniSTomaphalaM labhet .
tato gaccheta rAjendra brahmAvartaM narottamaH . brahmAvarte naraH snAtvA brahmalokamavApnuyAt .
tato gaccheta rAjendra sutIrthakamanuttamam . tatra saMnihitA nityaM pitaro daivataiH saha . tatrAbhiSekaM kurvIta pitRdevArcane rataH . azvamedhamavApnoti pitRlokaM ca gacchati .
tato ' mbumatyAMdharmajJa sutIrthakamanuttamam .
kAzIzvarasya tIrtheSu snAtvA bharatasattama . sarvavyAdhivinirmukto brahmaloke mahIyate .
mAtRtIrthaM ca tatraiva yatra snAtasya bhArata . prajA vivardhate rAjannatanvIM zriyamaznute .
tataH sItavanaM gacchenniyato niyatAzanaH . tIrthaM tatra mahArAja mahadanyatra durlabham .
punAti gamanAdeva dRSTamekaM narAdhipa . kezAnabhyukSya vai tasmin pUto bhavati bhArata .
