dvijottama mahAbhAga pazyatAM vacanAnmama . samrAT rAjA vasurnAma dharmAtmA saMzitavrataH . brAhmaNAnAM prakopena praviSTo vasudhAtalam .
mAnitAste tu viprendrAstvaM tu gaccha dvijottama .
bhUmervivarasaMguptaM garuDeha mamAjJayA . adhazcaraM nRpazreSThaM khecaraM kuru mA ciram .
garutmAnatha vikSipya pakSau mArutavegavAn . viveza vivaraM bhUmeryatrAste pArthivo vasuH .
tata enaM samutkSipya sahasA vinatAsutaH . utpapAta nabhastUrNaM tatra cainamamuJcata .
asmin muhUrte saMjajJe rAjoparicaraH punaH . sazarIro gatazcaiva brahmalokaM nRpottamaH .
evaM tenApi kaunteya vAgdoSAd devatAjJayA . prAptA gatiravastAt tu dvijazApAnmahAtmanA .
kevalaM puruSastena sevito harirIzvaraH . tataH zIghraM jahau zApaM brahmalokamavApa ca .
bhISma uvAca etat te sarvamAkhyAtaM sambhUtA mAnavA yathA . nArado ' pi yathA zvetaM dvIpaM sa gatavAnRSiH . tat te sarvaM pravakSyAmi zRNuSvaikamanA nRpa . .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktastu kaunteyo guDAkezena pANDavaH . novAca kiMcit kauravyastato dvaipAyano ' bravIt .
vyAsa uvAca bIbhatsorvacanaM saumya satyametad yudhiSThira . zAstradRSTaH paro dharmaH sthito gArhasthyamAzritaH .
svadharmaM cara dharmajJa yathAzAstraM yathAvidhi . na hi gArhasthayamutsRjya tavAraNyaM vidhIyate .
gRhasthaM hi sadA devAH pitaro ' tithayastathA . bhRtyAzcaivopajIvanti tAn bharasva mahIpate .
vayAMsi pazavazcaiva bhUtAni ca janAdhipa . gRhasthaireva dhAryante tasmAccherUSTho gRhAzramI .
so ' yaM caturNAmeteSAmAzramANAM durAcaraH . taM carAdya vidhi pArtha duzcaraM durbalendriyaiH
vedajJAnaM ca te kRtsnaM tapazcAcaritaM mahat . pitRpaitAmahaM rAjyaM dhuryavad voDhumarhasi .
tapo yajJastathA vidyA bhakSyamindriyasaMyamaH . dhyAnamekAntazIlatvaM turjJAinaM ca zaktitaH . brAhmaNAnAM mahArAja ceSTA saMsiddhikArikA .
kSatriyANAM tu vakSyAmi tavApi viditaM punaH . yajJo vidyA samutthAnamasaMtoSaH zriyaM prati . daNDadhAraNamugratvaM prajAnAM paripAlanam . vedajJAnaM tathA kRtsnaM tapaH sucaritaM tathA . draviNopArjanaM bhUri pAtre ca pratipAdanam . etAni rAjJAM karmANi sukRtAni vizAmpate . imaM lokamamuM caiva sAdhayantIti naH zrutam .
eSAM jyAyastu kaunteya daNDadhAraNamucyate . balaM hi kSatriye nityaM bale daNDaH samAhitaH .
etA vidyAH kSatriyANAM rAjan saMsiddhikArikAH . api gAthAmimAM cApi bRhaspatiragAyata .
bhUmiretau nigirati sarpo bilazayAniva . rAjAnaM cAviroddhAraM brAhmaNaM cApravAsinam .15 . .
sudyumnazcApi rAjarSiH zrUyate daNDadhAraNAt . prAptavAn paramAM siddhiM dakSaH prAcetaso yathA .
yudhiSThira uvAca bhagavan karmaNA kena sudyumno vasudhAdhipaH . saMsiddhiM paramAM prAptaH zrotumicchAmi taM nRpam .
vyAsa uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . zaGkhaca likhitazcAstAM bhrAtarau saMzitavratau .
tayorAvasathAvAstAM ramaNIyau pRthak pRthak . nityapuSpaphalairvRkSarupetau bAhudAmanu .
tataH kadAcillikhitaH zaGkhasyAzramamAgataH . yadRcchayAthazaGkho ' pi niSkrAnto ' bhavadAzramAt .
so ' bhigamyAzramaM bhrAtuH zaGkhasya likhitastadA . phalAni pAtayAmAsa samyakpariNatAnyuta .
tAnyupAdAya visrabyo bhakSayAmAsa sa dvijaH . tasmiMzca bhakSayatyeva zaGkho ' pyAzramamAgataH .
bhakSayantaM tu taM dRSTvA zaGkho bhrAtaramabravIt . kutaH phalAnyavAptAni hetunA kena khAdasi .
so ' bravId bhrAtaraM jyeSThamupasRtyAbhivAdya ca . ita eva gRhItAni mayeti prahasanniva .
tamabravIt tathA zaGkhastIvraroSasamanvitaH . steyaM tvayA kRtamidaM phalAnyAdadatA svayam .
gaccha rAjAnamAsAdya svakarma kathayasva vai . adattAdAnamevaM hi kRtaM pArthivasattama .
stenaM mAM tvaM viditvA ca svadharmamanupAlaya . zIghraM dhAraya caurasya mama daNDaM narAdhipa .
ityuktastasya vacanAt sudyumnaM sa narAdhipam . abhyagacchanmahAbAho likhitaH saMzitavrataH .
sudyumnastvantapAlebhyaH : zrutvA likhitamAgatam . abhyagacchat sahAmAtyaH padbhyAmeva janezvaraH .
tamabravIt samAgamya sa rAjA dharmavittamam . kimAgamanamAcakSva bhagavan kRtameva tat . evamuktaH sa viprarSiH sudyumnamidamabravIt . pratizrutya kariSyeti zrutvA tat kartumarhasi .
sudyumna uvAca anisRSTAni guruNA phalAni manujarSabha . bhakSitAni mahArAja tatra mAM zAdhi mA ciram . pramANaM cenmato rAjA bhavato daNDadhAraNe . anujJAyAmapi tathA hetuH syAd brAhmaNarSabha . .
sa bhavAnabhyanujJAtaH zucikarmA mahAvrataH . brUhi kAmAnato ' nyAMstvaM kariSyAmi hi te vacaH .
vyAsa uvAca saMchandyamAno brahmaSiH pArthivena mahAtmanA . nAnyaM sa varayAmAsa tasmAd daNDAdRte varam .
tataH sa pRthivIpAlo likhitasya mahAtmanaH . karau pracchedayAmAsa dhRtadaNDo jagAma saH .
sa gatvA bhrAtaraM zaGkhamArtarUpo ' bravIdidam . dhRtadaNDasya durbuddherbhavAMstat kSantumarhati .
zaGkha uvAca na kupye tava dharmajJa na tvaM dUSayase mamA sunirmalaM kulaM brahmannasmiJjagati vizrutam . dharmastu te vyatakrAntastataste niSkRtiH kRtAH .
tvaM gatvA bAhudAM zIghraM tarpayasva yathAvidhi . devAnRSIn piDhezcaivaM mA cAdharme manaH kRthAH .
tasya tad vacanaM zrutvA zaGkhasya likhitastadA . avagAhyApagAM puNyAmudakArthaM pracakrame .
prAdurAstAM tatastasya karau jalajasaMnibhau . tataH sa vismito bhrAturdarzayAmAsa tau karau .
zaGkha uvAca tatastamabravIcchaGkhastapasedaM kRtaM mayA . mA ca te ' tra vizaGkAbhUd daivamatra vidhIyate .
likhita uvAca kiM tu nAhaM tvayA pUtaH pUrvameva mahAdyute . yasya te tapaso vIryamIdRzaM dvijasattama .
zaGkha uvAca evametanmayA kAryaM nAhaM daNDadharastava . sa ca pUto narapatistvaM cApi pitRbhiH saha .
vyAsa uvAca sa rAjA pANDavazreSTha zreyAn vai tena karmaNA . prAptavAn paramAM siddhiM dakSaH prAcetaso yathA .
eSa dharmaH kSatriyANAM prajAnAM paripAlanam . utpatho ' nyo mahArAja mA sma zoke manaH kRthAH .
bhrAturasya hitaM vAkyaM zRNu dharmajJa sattama . daNDa eva hi rAjendra kSatradharmo na muNDanam .
kuntyuvAca bhagavazvazuro me ' si daivatasyApi daivatam . sa me devAtidevastvaM zRNu satyA giraM mama .
tapasvI kopano vipro durvAsA nAma me pituH . bhikSAmupAto bhoktuM tamahaM paryatoSayam . zaucena tvAgasastyAgaiH zuddhena manasA tathA . kopasthAneSvapi mahatsvakuSyanna kadAcana . .
sa prIto varado me ' bhUt kRtakRtyo mahAmuniH . avazyaM te gRhItavyamiti mAM so ' bravId vacaH .
tataH zApabhayAd vipramavocaM punareva tam . evamastviti ca prAha punareva sa me dvijaH . dharmasya jananI bhadre bhavitrI tvaM zubhAnane . vaze sthAsyanti te devA yAMstvamAvAhayiSyasi .
ityuktvAntarhito viprastato ' haM vismitAbhavam . na ca sarvAsvavasthAsu ramRtirme vipraNazyati .
atha harmyatalasthAhaM ravimudyantamIkSatI . saMsmRtya tadRServAkyaM spRhayantI divAnizam .
sthitA ' haM bAlabhAvena tatra doSamabuddhyatI . atha devaH sahasrAMzumatsamIpagato ' bhavat .
dvidhA kRtvA ' ' tmano dehaM bhUmau ca gagane ' pi ca . tatApa lokAnekena dvitIyenAgamat sa mAm .
sa mAmuvAca vepantIM varaM matto vRNISva ha . gamyatAmiti taM cAhaM praNamya zirasA ' vadam .
sa mAmuvAca tigmAMzuvRthA ' ' hvAnaM na me kSamam . dhakSyAmi tvAM ca vipraM ca yena datto varastava .
tamahaM rakSatI vipraM zApAdanapakAriNam . putro me tvatsamo deva bhavediti tato ' bravam .
tato mAM tejasA ' ' vizya mohayitvA ca bhAnumAn . uvAca bhavitA putrastavetyabhyagamad divam .
tato ' hamantarbhavane piturvRttAntarakSiNI . gUDhotpannaM sutaM bAlaM jale karNamavAsRjam .
nUnaM tasyeva devasya prasAdAt punareva tu . kanyA ' hamabhavaM vipra yathA prAha sa mAmRSiH .
sa mayA mUDhayA putro jJAyamAno ' pyupekSitaH . tanmAM dahati viprarSe yathA suviditaM tava .
yadi pApamapApaM vA tavaitad vivRtaM mayA . tanme dahantaM bhagavan vyapanetuM tvamarhasi .
yaccAsya rAjJo viditaM hRdisthaM bhavato ' nagha . taM cAyaM labhatAM kAmamadyaiva munisattama .
ityuktaH pratyuvAcedaM vyAso vedavidAM varaH . sAdhu sarvamidaM bhAvyamevametad yathA ' ' tya mAm .
aparAdhazca te nAsti kanyAbhAvaM gatA hyasi . devAzcaizcaryavanto vai zarIrANyAvizanti vai .
santi devanikAyAzca saMkalpAjjanayanti ye . vAcA dRSTyA tathA sparzAt saMgharSeNeti paJcadhA . .
manuSyadharmo daivena dharmeNa hi na duSyati . iti kunti vijAnIhi vyetu te mAnaso jvaraH .
sarvaM balavatAM pathyaM sarvaM balavatAM zuci . sarvaM balavatAM dharmaH sarvaM balavatAM svakam .
saMjaya uvAca karNasya vacanaM zrutvA kezavaH paravIrahA . uvAca prahasan vAkyaM smitapUrvamidaM yathA .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca api tvAM na labhet karNa rAjyalambhopapAdanam . mayA dattAM hi pRthivIM na prazAsitumicchasi .
dhruvo jayaH pANDavAnAmitIdaM na saMzayaH kazcana vidyate ' tra . jayadhvayo dRzyate pANDavasya samucchrito vAnararAja ugraH .
divyA mayAyA vihitA bhaumanena samucchritA indraketuprakAzA . divyAni bhUtAni jayAvahAni dRzyanti caivAtra bhayAnakAni .
na sajjate zailavanaspatibhya UrdhvaM tiryagayojanamAtrarUpaH . zrImAn dhvajaH karNa dhanaMjayasya samucchritaH pAvakatulyarUpaH .
yadA drakSyasi saMgrAme zvetAzraM kRSNasArathim . aindramastraM vikurvANamubhe cApyagnimArute .
gANDIvasya ca nirghoSaM visphUrjitamivAzaneH . na tadA bhavitA tretA na kRtaM dvAparaM na ca .
yadA drakSyasi saMgrAme kuntIputraM yudhiSThiram . japahomasamAyuktaM svAM rakSantaM mahAcamUm .
Adityamiva durdharSaM tapantaM zatruvAhinIm . na tadA bhavitA tretA na kRtaM dvAparaM na ca .
yadA drakSyasi saMgrAme bhImasenaM mahAbalam . duHzAsanasya rudhiraM pItvA nRtyantamAhave .
prabhinnamiva mAtaGgaM pratidviradaghAtinam . na tadA bhavitA tretA na kRtaM dvAparaM na ca .
yadA drakSyasi saMgrAme droNaM zAntanavaM kRpam . suyodhanaM ca rAjAnaM saindhavaM ca jayadratham .
yuddhAyApatatastUrNaM vAritAn savyasAcinA . na tadA bhavitA tretA na kRtaM dvAparaM na ca .
yadA drakSyasi saMgrAme mAdrIputrau mahAbalau . vAhinIM dhArtarASTrANAM kSobhayantau gajAviva .
vigADhe zastrasampAte paravIrarathArujau . na tadA bhavitA tretA na kRtaM dvAparaM na ca .
brUyAH karNa ito gatvA droNaM zAntanavaM kRpam . saumyo ' yaM vartate mAsaH suprApayavasendhanaH .
sauSadhivanasphItaH phalavAnalpamakSikaH . niSpako rasavattoyo nAtyuSNaziziraH sukhaH .
saptamAccApi divasAdamAvAsyA bhaviSyati . saMgrAmo yujyatAM tasyAM tAmAhuH zakradevatAm .
tathA rAjJo vadeH sarvAn ye yuddhAyAbhyupAgatAH . yad vo manISitaM tad vai sarvaM sampAdayAmyaham .
rAjAno rAjaputrAzca duryodhanavazAnugAH . prApya zastreNa nidhanaM prApsyanti gatimuttamAm .
saMjaya uvAca manIkinInAM pramukhe mahAtmA . yayau sapatnAn prati jAtakopo vRtaH samagreNa balena bhISmaH .
taM droNaduryodhanabAlikAzca tathaiva durmarSaNacitrasenau . nRpAstathA ' nye prayayuH samantAt .
sa tairmahadbhizca mahArathaizca tejasvibhirvIryavaddhizca rAjan . vRtaH sa devairiva vajrapANiH .
tasminnanIkapramukhe viSaktA dodhUyamAnAzca mahApatAkAH . suraktapItAsitapANDurAbhA mahAgajaskandhagatA virejuH .
sA vAhinI zAntanavena guptA mahArathairvAraNavAjibhizca . babhau savidyutstanayilukalpA jalAgamai dyauriva jAtameghA .
tato raNAyAbhimukhI prayAtA pratyarjunaM zAntanavAbhiguptA . senA mahogrA sahasA kurUNAM vego yathA bhIma ivApagAyAH .
taM vyAlanAnAvidhagUDhasAraM gajAzvapAdAtarathaughapakSam . vyUhaM mahAmeghasamaM mahAtmA dadarza dUrAt kapirAjaketuH .
viniryayau ketumatA rathena nararSabhaH zvetahayena vIraH . varUthinA sainyamukhe mahAtmA vadhe dhRtaH sarvasapatnayUnAm .
sUpaskaraM sottarabandhureSaM yattaM yadUnAmRSabheNa saMkhye . kapidhvajaM prekSya viSedurAjau sahaiva putraistava kauraveyAH .
prakarSatA guptamudAyudhena kirITinA lokamahArathena . zcatuzcatuLalasahasrakarNam .
yathA hi pUrve ' hani dharmarAjJA vyUhaH kRtaH kauravasattamena . tathA na bhUto bhuvi mAnuSeSu na dRSTapUrvo na ca saMzrutazca .
tato yathAdezamupetya tasthuH pAJcAlamukhyAH saha cedimukhyaiH . tataH samAdezasamAhatAni bherIsahasrANi vinedurAjau .
zaGkhasvanAstUryarathasvanAzca sarveSvanIkeSu sasiMhanAdAH . tataH sabANAni mahAsvanAni visphAryamANAni dhanUMSi vIraiH .
kSaNena bherIpaNavapraNAdAnantardadhuH zaGkhamahAsvanAzca . tacchaGkhazabdAvRtamantarikSamudbhUtabImAdbhutareNujAlam .
mAlokya vIrAH sahasAbhipetuH . rathI rathenAbhihataH sasUtaH papAta sAzvaH sarathaH saketuH .
gajo gajenAbhihataH papAta padAtinA cAbhihataH padAtiH . ?rIkRtAnyadbhutadarzanAni . prAsaizca khaDDaizca samAhatAni sadazvavRndAni sadazvavRndaiH .
suvarNatArAgaNabhUSitAni sUryaprabhAbhAni zarAvarANi . vidAryamANAni parazvadhaizca prAsaizca khaDDaizca nipeturukm .
gajaiviSANairvarahastarugNAH kecit sasUtA rathinaH prapetuH . gajarSabhAzcApi ratharSabheNa nipAtitA bANahatAH pRthivyAm .
gajaughavegoddhatasAditAnAM zrutvA viSeduH sahasA manuSyAH . AsvinaM sAdipadAtiyUnAM viSANagAtrAvaratADitAnAm .
sambhrAntanAgAzvarathe muhUrte mahAkSaye sAdipadAtiyUnAm . mahArathaiH samparivAryamANo dadarza bhISmaH kapirAjaketum .
taM paJcatAlocchritatAlaketuH sadazvavegAdbhutavIryayAnaH . mahAstrabANAzanidIptimantaM kirITinaM zAntanavo ' bhyadhAvat .
mindrAtmajaM droNamukhA vimaH . kRpazca zalyazca viviMzatizca duryodhanaH saumadattizca rAjan .
tato rathAnAM pramukhAdupetya sarvAstravit kAJcanacitravarmA . stAnarjunasyAtmasuto ' bhimanyuH .
masahyakarmA vinihatya kArSNiH . babhau mahAmantrahutArcimAlI bhagavAnivAgniH . sadogataH san
tataH sa tUrNaM rudhirodaphenAM kRtvA nadImAzu raNe ripUNAm . jagAma saubhadramatItya bhISmo mahArathaM pArthamadInasattvaH .
tataH prahasyAdbhutavikrameNa gANDIvamuktena zilAzitenA vipAThajAlena mahAstrajAlaM vinAzayAmAsa kirITamAlI .
saktakarmA kapirAjaketuH . bhISmaM mahAtmAbhivavarSa tUrNaM zaraughajAlairvimalaizca bhallaiH .
tathaiva bhISmAhatamantarikSa mahAstrajAlaM kapirAjaketoH . vizIryamANaM dadRzustvadIyA divAkareNeva tamo ' bhibhUtam .
madInavat satpuruSottamAbhyAm . dadarza lokaH kurusuMjayAca tad dvairathaM bhISmadhanaMjayAbhyAm .
janamejaya uvAca astauSId yairimaM vyAsaH sa ziSyo madhusUdanam . nAmabhirvividhaireSAM niruktaM bhagavan mama . vaktumarhasi zuzrUSoH prajApatipaterhareH . zrutvA bhaveyaM yat pUtaH zaraccandra ivAmalaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca zRNu rAjana yathA ' ' caSTa phAlgunasya hariH prabhuH . prasannAtmA ' ' tmano nAmnAM niruktaM guNakarmajam .
nAmabhiH kIrtitaistasya kezavasya mahAtmanaH . pRSTavAn kezavaM rAjan phAlgunaH paravIrahA .
arjuna uvAca bhagavan bhUtabhavyeza sarvabhUtasRgavyaya . lokadhAma jagannAtha lokAnAmabhayaprada .
yAni nAmAni te deva kIrtitAni maharSibhiH . vedeSu sapurANeSu yAni guhyAni karmabhiH . teSAM niruktaM tvatto ' haM zrotumicchAmi kezava . na hyanyo varNa yennAmnAM niruktaM tvAmRte prabho .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca Rgvede sayajurvede tathaivAtharvasAmasu . purANe sopaniSade tathaiva jyautiSe ' rjuna . sAMkhye ca yogazAstre ca Ayurvede tathaiva ca . bahUni mama nAmAni kIrtitAni maharSibhiH . gauNAni tatra nAmAni karmajAni ca kAnicit . niruktaM karmajAnAM tvaM zRNuSva prayato ' nagha .
kathyamAnaM mayA tAta tvaM hi me ' rdhaM smRtaH purA . namo ' tiyazase tasmai dehinAM paramAtmane .
nArAyaNAya vizvAya nirguNAya guNAtmane . yasya prasAdajo brahmA rudrazca krodhasambhavaH .
yo ' sau yonirhi sarvasya sthAvarasya carasya ca . aSTAdazaguNaM yat tat sattvaM sattvavatAM vara . prakRtiH sA parA mahyaM rodasI yogadhAriNI .
RtA satyAmarAjayyA lokAnAmAtmasaMjJitA . tasmAt sarvAH pravartante sargapralayavikriyAH .
tapo yajJazca yaSTA ca purANaH puruSo virAT . aniruddha iti prokto lokAnAM prabhavApyayaH .
brAhme rAtrikSaye prApte tasya hyamitatejasaH . prasAdAt prAdurabhavat padmaM padmanibhekSaNa .
tato brahmA samabhavat sa tasyaiva prasAdajaH . ahnaH kSaye lalATAcca suto devasya vai tathA . krodhAviSTasya saMjajJe rudraH saMhArakArakaH . etau dvau vibudhazreSThau prasAdakrodhajAvubhau .
tadAdezitapanthAnau sRSTisaMhArakArakau . nimittamAtraM tAvatra sarvaprANivarapradau .
kapardI jaTilA muNDaH zmazAna gRhasevakaH . ugravratacaro rudro yogI paramadAruNaH .
dakSakratuharazcaiva bhaganetraharastathA . . nArAyaNAtmako jJeyaH pANDaveya yuge yuge .
tasmin hi pUjyamAne vai devadeve mahezvare . sampUjito bhavet pArtha devo nArAyaNaH prabhuH .
ahamAtmA hi lokAnAM vizveSAM pANDunandana . tasmAdAtmAnamevAgre rudraM sampUjayAmyaham .
yadyahaM nArcayeyaM vai IzAnaM varadaM zivam . AtmAnaM nArcayet kazciditi me bhAvitAtmanaH .
mayA pramANaM hi kRtaM lokaH samanuvartate . pramANAni hi pUjyAni tatastaM pUjayAmyaham .
yastaM vetti sa mAM vetti yo ' nu taM sa hi mAmanu . rudro nArAyaNazcaiva sattvamekaM dvidhAkRtam .
loke carati kaunteya vyaktisthaM sarvakarmasu . na hi me kenacid deyo varaH pANDavanandana .
iti saMcintya manasA purANaM rudramIzvaram . putrArthamArAdhitavAnahamAtmAnamAtmanA .
na hi viSNuH praNamati kasmaicid vibudhAya ca . Rte AtmAnameveti tato rudraM bhajAmyaham .
sabrahmakAH sarudrAzca sendrA devAH saharSibhiH . arcayanti surazreSThaM devaM nArAyaNaM harim .
bhaviSyatAM vartatAM ca bhUtAnAM caiva bhArata . sarveSAmagraNIviSNaH sevyaH pUjyazca nityazaH .
namasva havyadaM viSNuM tathA zaraNadaM nama . varadaM namasva kaunteya havyakavyabhujaM nama . caturvidhA mana janA bhaktA eva hi me zrutam .
teSAmekAntinaH zreSThA ye caivAnanyadevatAH . ahameva gatisteSAM nirAzI : karmakAriNAm .
