tataH prabhagnA sahasA mahAcamU : sA pANDavI tena narAdhipena . dizazcatasraH sahasA vidhAvitA gajendravegaM tamapArayantI .
dRSTvA ca tAM vegavatIM prabhagnAM sarve tvadIyA yudhi yodhamukhyAH . apUjayaste tu narAdhipaM taM dadhmuzca zaGkhAzazisaMnikAzAn .
zrutvA ninAdaM tvatha kauravANAM harSAd vimuktaM saha zaGkhazabdaiH . senApatiH pANDavasRJjayAnAM pAJcAlaputro mamRSe na kopAt .
tatastu taM vai dviradaM mahAtmA pratyudyayau tvaramANo jayAya . jambho yathA zakrasamAgame vai nAgendramairAvaNamindravAhyam .
tamApatantaM sahasA tu dRSTvA pAJcAlaputraM yudhi rAjasiMhaH . taM vai dvipaM preSayAmAsa tUrNaM vadhAya rAjan dupadAtmajasya .
mavidhyadagnipratimaiH pRSatkaiH karmAradhautairnizitairvvaladbhi ArAcamukhyaistribhirupavegaiH .
tato ' parAn paJcazatAn mahAtmA nArAcamukhyAn visasarja kumbhe . sa taistu viddhaH paramadvipo raNe tadA parAvRtya bhRzaM pradudruve .
taM nAgarAjaM sahasA praNunnaM vidrAvyamANaM vinivartya zAlvaH . totrAGkuzaiH preSayAmAsa tUrNaM pAJcAlarAjasya rathaM pradizya .
dRSTvA ' ' patantaM sahasA tu nAgaM dhRSTadyumnaH svarathAcchrIghrameva . gadAM pragRhyograjavena vIro bhUmiM prapanno bhayavihvalAGgaH .
sa taM rathaM hemavibhUSitAGgaM sAzvaM sasUtaM sahasA vimRdyA utkSipya hastena nadan mahAdvipo vipothayAmAsa vasundharAtale .
pAJcAlarAjasya sutaM ca dRSTvA tadArditaM nAgavareNa tenA tamabhyadhAvat sahasA javena bhImaH zikhaNDI ca zinezca naptA .
zaraizca vegaM sahasA nigRhya tasyAbhito vyApatato gajasya . sa saMgRhIto rathibhirgajo vai cacAla tairvAryamANAzca saMkhye .
tataH pRSatkAn pravavarSa rAjA sUryo yathA razmijAlaM samantAt . tairAzugairvadhyamAnA rathaudhAH pradudruvuH sahitAstatra tatra .
tat karma zAlvasya samIkSya sarve pAJcAlaputrA nRpa sRJjayAzca . hAhAkArairnAdayanti sma yuddhe dvipaM samantAd rurudhunarAgryAH .
pAJcAlaputrastvaritastu zUro gadAM pragRhyAcalazRGgakalpAm . sasambhramaM bhArata zatrughAtI javena vIro ' nusasAra nAgam .
tatastu nAgaM dharaNIdharAbhaM madaM sravantaM jaladaprakAzam . gadAM samAviddhya bhRzaM jaghAna pAJcAlarAjasya sutastarasvI . tu tadA gajendre
sa bhinnakumbhaH sahasA vinadya mukhAt prabhUtaM kSatajaM vimuJcan . papAta nAgo dharaNIdharAbhaH kSitiprakampAJcalito yathA ' dbhiH .
nipAtyamAne hAhAkRte tava putrasya sainye . sa zAlvarAjasya zinipravIro jahAra bhallena ziraH zitena .
hRtottamAGgo yudhi sAtvatena papAta bhUmau saha nAgarAjJA . yathAdrizRGgaM sumahat praNunnaM vajreNa devAdhipacoditena .
uttaGka uvAca brUhi kezava tatvena tvamadhyAtmamaninditam . zrutvA zreyo ' bhidhAsyAmi zApaM vA te janArdana .
vAsudeva uvAca tamo rajazca satvaM ca viddhi bhAvAn madAzrayAn . tathA rudAn vasUn vApi viddhi matprabhavAn dvija .
mayi sarvANi bhUtAni sarvabhUteSu cApyaham . sthita ityabhijAnIhi mA te ' bhUdatra saMzayaH .
tathA daityagaNAn sarvAn yakSagandharvarAkSasAn . nAgAnapsarasazcaiva viddhi matprabhavAn dvija .
sadasaccaiva yat prAhuravyaktaM vyaktameva ca . akSaraM ca kSaraM caiva sarvametanmadAtmakam .
ye cAzrameSu vai dharmAzcaturdhA viditA mune . vaidikAni ca sarvANi viddhi sarvaM madAtmakam .
asacca sadasaccaiva yad vizvaM sadasat param . mattaH parataraM nAsti devadevAt sanAtanAt .
oGkArapramukhAn vedAn viddhi mAM tvaM bhRgUdvaha . yUpaM somaM caruM homaM tridazApyAyanaM makhe . hotAramapi havyaM ca viddhi mAM bhRgunandana . adhvaryuH kalpakazcApi haviH paramasaMskRtam . udgAtA cApi mAM stauti gItaghoSairmahAdhvare . prAyazcitteSu mAM brahmazAntimaGgalavAcakAH . stuvanti vizvakarmANaM satataM dvijasattama .
mama viddhi sutaM dharmamagrajaM dvijasattama . mAnasaM dayitaM vipra sarvabhUtadayAtmakam .
tatrAhaM vartamAnaizca nivRttaizcaiva mAnavaiH . bahvIH saMsaramANo vai yonIrvAmi sattama . dharmasaMrakSaNArthAya dharmasaMsthApanAya ca .
taistairveSaizca rUpaizca triSu lokeSu bhArgava . ahaM viSNurahaM brahmA zakro ' tha prabhavApyayaH .
bhUtagrAmasya sarvasya sraSTA saMhAra eva ca . adharme vartamAnAnAM sarveSAmahamacyutaH .
dharmasya setuM banAmi calite calite yuge . tAstA yonIH pravizyAhaM prajAnAM hitakAmyayA . .
yadA tvahaM devayonau vartAmi bhRgunandanA tadAhaM devavat sarvamAcarAmi na saMzayaH .
yadA gandharvayonau vA vartAmi bhRgunandanA tadA gandharvavat sarvamAcarAmi na saMzayaH .
nAgayonau yadA caiva tathA vartAmi nAgavat . yakSarAkSasayonyostu yathAvad vicarAmyaham . .
mAnuSye vartamAne tu kRpaNaM yAcitA mayA . na ca te jAnasammohA vaco ' gRhanta me hitam .
bhayaM ca mahaduddizya trAsitAH kuravo mayA . kruddhena bhUtvA tu punaryathAvadanudarzitAH .
te ' dharmeNehaM saMyuktAH parItAH kAladharmaNA . dharmeNa nihatA yuddhe gatAH svargaM na saMzayaH .
lokeSu pANDavAzcaiva gatAH khyAti dvijottama . etat te sarvamAkhyAtaM yanmAM tvaM paripRcchasi .
saMjaya uvAca evamuktastato rAjA gautamena tapasvinA . niHzvasya dIrghamuSNaM ca tUSNImAsId vizAmpate .
tato muhUrtaM sa dhyAtvA dhArtarASTro mahAmanAH . kRpaM zAradvataM vAkyamityuvAca paraMtapaH .
yat kiJcit suhRdA vAcyaM tat sarvaM zrAvito hyaham . kRtaM ca bhavatA sarvaM prANAn saMtyajya yudhyatA .
gAhamAnamanIkAni yudhyamAnaM mahArathaiH . pANDavairatitejobhirlokastvAmanudRSTavAn .
suhRdAM yadidaM vAkyaM bhavatA zrAvito hyaham . na mAM prINAti tatsarvaM mumUrSoriva bheSajam .
hetukAraNasaMyuktaM hitaM vacanamuttamam . ucyamAnaM mahAbAho na me viprAya rocate .
rAjyAd vinikRto ' smAbhiH kathaM so ' smAsu vizvaset . akSayUte ca nRpatirjito ' smAbhirmahAdhanaH .
sa kathaM mama vAkyAni zraddadhyAd bhUya eva tu . tathA dautyena samprAptaH kRSNaH pArthahite rataH .
pralabdhazca hRSIkezastaca karmAvicAritam . sa ca me vacanaM brahman kathamevAbhimanyate .
vilalApa ca yat kRSNa sabhAmadhye sameyuSI . na tanmarSayate kRSNo na rAjyaharaNaM tathA .
ekaprANAvubhau kRSNAvanyonyamabhisaMzritau . purA yacchrutamevAsIdadya pazyAmi tat prabho . svasrIyaM nihataM zrutvA duHkhaM svapiti kezavaH . kRtAgaso vayaM tasya sa madarthaM kathaM kSamet .
AbhimanyorvinAzena na zarma labhate ' rjunaH . sa kathaM maddhite yatnaM prakariSyati yAcitaH .
madhyamaH pANDavastIkSNo bhImaseno mahAbalaH . pratijJAtaM ca tenograM bhajyetApi na saMnamet .
ubhau tau baddhanistriMzAvubhau cAbaddhakaGkaTau . kRtavairAbubhau vIrau yamAvapi yamopamau .
dhRSTadyumna : zikhaNDI ca kRtavairau mayA sahA tau kathaM maddhite yatnaM kuryAtAM dvijasattama .
duHzAsanena yat kRSNa ekavastrA rajasvalAH . parikliSTA sabhAmadhye sarvalokasya pazyataH .
tathA vivasanAM dInAM smaratvadyApi pANDavAH . na nivArayituM zakyAH saMgrAmAtte paraMtapAH .
yadA ca draupadI kliSTA madvinAzAya duHkhitA . sthaNDile nityadA zete yAvad vairasya yAtanam . . ugraM tepe tapaH kRSNA bhartRNAmarthasiddhaye .
nikSipya mAnaM darpa ca vAsudevasahodarA . kRSNAyAH preSyavad bhUtvA zuzrUSAM kurute sadA .
iti sarvaM samunnaddhaM na nirvAti kathaJcana . abhimanyorvinAzena sa saMdheyaH kathaM mayA .
kathaM ca rAjA bhuktvemAM pRthivIM sAgarAmbarAm . pANDavAnAM prasAdena bhokSye rAjyamahaM katham .
uparyupari rAjJAM vai jvalitvA bhAskaro yathA . yudhiSThiraM kathaM pazyAdanuyAsyAmi dAsavat .
kathaM bhuktvA svayaM bhogAn dattvA dAyAMzca yupkalAn . kRpaNaM vartayiSyAmi kRpaNaiH saha jIvikAm .
nAbhyasUyAmi te vAkyamuktaM snigdhaM hitaM tvayA . na tu sandhimahaM manye prAptakAlaM kathaJcana .
sunItamanupazyAmi suyuddhena paraMtapa . nAyaM kIbayituM kAlaH saMyoddhaM kAla eva naH .
iSTaM me buhabhiryajJairdattA vipreSu dakSiNAH . prAptA : kAmAH zrutA vedAH zatrUNAM mUrdhni ca sthitam .
bhRtyA me subhRtAstAta dInazcAbhyuddhato janaH . notsahe ' dya dvijazreSTha pANDavAn vaktumIdRzam .
jitAni pararASTrAni svarASTramanupAlitam . bhuktAzca vividhA bhogAstrivarga : sevito mayA . pitRRNAM gatamAnRNyaM kSatradharmasya cobhayoH .
na dhruvaM sukhamastIti kuto rASTraM kuto yazaH . iha kIrtirvidhAtavyA sA ca yuddhena nAnyathA .
gRhe yat kSatriyasyApi nidhanaM tad vigarhitam . adharmaH sumahAneSa yacchayyAmaraNaM gRhe .
araNye yo vimucyeta saMgrAme vA tanuM naraH . RtUnAdRtya mahato mahimAnaM sa gacchati .
kRpaNaM vilapannA " jarayAbhipariplutaH . mriyate rudratAM madhye jJAtInAM na sa pUruSaH .
tyaktvA tu vividhAn bhogAn prAptAnAM paramAM gatim . apIdAnIM suyuddhena gaccheyaM yatsalokatAm . zUrANAmAryavRttAnAM saMgrAmeSvanivartinAm . dhImatAM satyasaMghAnAM sarveSAM RtuyAjinAm . zastrAvabhRthapUtAnAM dhruvaM vAsastriviSTape . mudA nUnaM prapazyanti yuddhe hyapsarasAM gaNAH . pazyanti nUnaM pitaraH pUjitAn surasaMsadi . apsarobhiH parivRtAn modamAnAMstriviSTape .
panthAnamamarairyAntaM zUraizcaivAnivartibhiH . api tatsaMgataM mArga vayamadhyAruhemahi . pitAmahena vRddhena tathA ' ' cAryeNa dhImatA . jayadrathena karNena tathA duHzAsanena ca .
ghaTamAnA madarthe ' smin hatAH zUrA janAdhipAH . zerate lohitAktAGgA saMgrAme zaravikSataH .
uttamAstravidaH zUrA yathoktakratuyAjinaH . tyaktvA prANAn yathAnyAyamindrasAsvadhiSThitAH .
taiH svayaM racito mArgo durgamo hi punarbhavet . sampatadbhirmahAvegairyAsyadbhiriha sadgatim .
ye madarthe hatA zUrAsteSAM kRtamanusmaran . RNaM tat pratiyuJjAno na rAjye mana Adadhe .
ghAtayitvA vayasyAMzca bhrAtRnatha pitAmahAn . jIvitaM yadi rakSeyaM loko mAM garhayed dhruvam .
kIdRzaM ca bhaved rAjyaM mama hInasya bandhubhiH . sakhibhizca vizeSeNa praNipatya ca pANDavam .
so ' hametAdRzaM kRtvA jagato ' sya parAbhavam . suyuddhena tataH svargaM prApsyAmi na tadanyathA .
evaM duryodhanenoktaM sarve sampUjya tadvacaH . sAdhu sAdhviti rAjAnaM kSatriyAH sambabhASire .
parAjayamazocantaH kRtacittAzca vikrame . sarve sunizcitA yoddhamudagramanaso ' bhavan .
tato vAhAn samAzvasya sarve yuddhAbhinandinaH . Une dviyojane gatvA pratyatiSThanta kauravAH .
AkAze vidrume puNye prasthe himavataH zubhe . aruNAM sarasvatIM prApya papuH sasnuzca te jalam . tava putrakRtotsAhAH paryavartanta te tataH .
paryavasthApya cAtmAnamanyonyena punastadA . sarve rAjan nyavartanta kSatriyAH kAlacoditAH .
karNa uvAca duryodhana tava prajJA na samyagiti me matiH . na hyupAyena te zakyAH pANDavAH kuruvardhana .
pUrvameva hi te sUkSmairupAyairyatitAstvayA . nigrahItuM tadA vIra na caiva zakitAstvayA . .
ihaiva vartamAnAste samIpe tava pArthiva . ajAtapakSAH zizavaH zakitA naiva bAdhitum .
jAtapakSA videzasthA vivRddhAH sarvazo ' dya te . nopAyasAdhyAH kaunteyA mamaiSA matiracyuta .
na ca te vyasanairyoktuM zakyA diSTakRtena ca . zakitAzcepsavazcaiva pitRpaitAmahaM padam .
paraspareNa bhedazca nAdhAtuM teSu zakyate . ekasyAM ye ratAH panyAM na bhidyante parasparam .
na cApi kRSNA zakyeta tebhyo bhedayituM paraiH . pariyUnAn vRtavatI kimutAdya mRjAvataH .
Ipsitazca guNaH strINAmekasyA bahubhartRtA . taM ca prAptavatI kRSNA na sA bhedayituM kSamA .
Aryavratazca pAJcAlyo na sa rAjA dhanapriyaH . na saMtyakSyati kaunteyAn rAjyadAnairapi dhruvam .
yathAsya putro guNavAnanuraktazca pANDavAn . tasmAnno pAyasAdhyAMstAnahaM manye kathaMcana .
idaM tvadya kSamaM kartumasmAkaM puruSarSabha . yAvanna kRtamUlAste pANDaveyA vizAmpate . tAvat praharaNIyAste tat tubhyaM tAta rocatAm . asmatpakSo mahAn yAvad yAvat pAJcAlako laghuH . tAvat praharaNaM teSAM kriyatAM mA vicAraya .
vAhanAni prabhUtAni mitrANi ca kulAni ca . yAvanna teSAM gAndhAre tAvad vikrama pArthiva .
yAvacca rAjA pAJcAlyo nodyame kurute manaH . saha putrairmahAvIrya stAvad vikrama pArthiva .
yAvannAyAti vArSNeyaH karSan yAdavavAhinIm . rAjyArthe pANDaveyAnAM pAJcAlyasadanaM prati .
vasUni vividhAn bhogAn rAjyameva ca kevalam . nAtyAjyamasti kRSNasya pANDavArthaM kathaMcana .
vikrameNa mahI prAptA bharatena mahAtmanA . vikrameNa ca lokAMstrIJjitavAn pAkazAsanaH .
vikramaM ca prazaMsanti kSatriyasya vizAmpate . svako hi dharmaH zUrANAM vikramaH pArthivarSabha .
te balena vayaM rAjan mahatA caturaGgiNA . pramathya dupadaM zIghramAnayAmeha pANDavAn .
na hi sAmnA na dAnena na bhedena ca pANDavAH . zakyAH sAdhayituM tasmAd vikrameNaiva tAJjahi .
tAn vikrameNa jitvemAmakhilAM bhukSva medinIm . ato nAnyaM prapazyAmi kAryopAyaM janAdhipa .
vaizampAyana uvAca zrutvA tu rAdheyavaco dhRtarASTraH pratApavAn . abhipUjya tataH pazcAdidaM vacanamabravIt .
upapannaM mahAprAjJe kRtAstre sUtanandane . tvayi vikramasampannamidaM vacanamIdRzam .
bhUya eva tu bhISmazca droNo viduraeva ca . yuvAM ca kurutaM buddhiM bhaved yA naH sukhodayA .
tata AnAyya tAn sarvAn mantriNaH sumahAyazAH . dhRtarASTro mahArAja mantrayAmAsa vai tadA .
vaizampAyana uvAca darzanIyAMstataH putrAn pANDuH paJca mahAvane . tAn pazyan parvate ramye svabAhubalamAzritaH .
supuSpitavane kAle kadAcinmadhumAdhave . bhUtasammohane rAjA sabhAryo vyacarad vanam .
palAzaistilakaizcataizcampakaiH pAribhadrakaiH . anyaizca bahubhivRkSaiH phalapuSpasamRddhibhiH . jalasthAnaizca vividhaiH padminIbhizca zobhitam . pANDorvanaM tat samprekSya prajajJe hRdi manmathaH .
prahRSTamanasaM tatra vicarantaM yathAmaram . taM mAtyanujagAmaikA vasanaM bibhratI zubham . samIkSamANaH sa tu tAM vayaHsthAM tanuvAsasam . tasya kAmaH pravavRdhai gahane ' gnirivodgataH .
rahasyekAM tu tAM dRSTvA rAjA rAjIvalocanAm . na zazAka niyantuM taM kAmaM kAmavazIkRtaH .
tata enAM balAd rAjA nijagrAha raho gatAm . vAryamANastayA devyA visphurantyA yathAbalam .
sa tu kAmaparItAtmA taM zApaM nAnvabudhyata . mAdrI maithunadharmeNa so ' nvagacchad balAdiva . jIvitAntAya kauravya manmathasya vazaM gataH . zApajaM bhayamutsRjya vidhinA sampracoditaH .
tasya kAmAtmano buddhiH sAkSAt kAlena mohitA . sampramathyendriyagrAmaM praNaSTA saha cetasA .
sa tayA saha saMgamya bhAryayA kurunandanaH . pANDuH paramadharmAtmA yuyuje kAladharmaNA .
tato mAdrI samAliGgaya rAjAnaM gatacetasam . mumoca duHkhajaM zabdaM punaH punaratIva hi .
saha putraistataH kuntI mAdrIputrau ca pANDavau . AjagmuH sahitAstatra yatra rAjA tathAgataH .
tato mAyabravId rAjannArtA kuntImidaM vacaH . ekaiva tvamihAgaccha tiSThantvayaiva dArakAH .
tacchrutvA vacanaM tasyAstatraivAdhAya dArakAn . hatAhamiti vikruzya sahasaivAjagAma sA .
dRSTvA pANDaM ca mAdrIM ca zayAnau dharaNItale . kuntI zokaparItAGgI vilalApa suduHkhitA .
rakSyamANo mayA nityaM vIraH satatamAtmavAn . kathaM tvAmatyatikrAntaH zApaM jAnan vanaukasaH .
nanu nAma tvayA mAdri rakSitavyo narAdhipaH . sA kathaM lobhitavatI vijane tvaM narAdhipam .
kathaM dInasya satataM tvAmAsAdya rahogatAm . taM vicintayataH zApaM praharSaH samajAyata .
dhanyA tvamasi bAhrIki matto bhAgyatarA tathA . dRSTavatyasi yad vaktraM prahRSTasya mahIpateH .
mAnyuvAca vilapantyA mayA devi vAryamANena cAsakRt . AtmA na vArito ' nena satyaM diSTaM cikIrSaNA .
kuntyuvAca ahaM jyeSThA dharmapatnI jyeSThaM dharmaphalaM mama . avazyambhAvino bhAvAnmA mAM mAdri nivartaya . anviSyAmIha bhartAramahaM pretavazaM gatam . uttiSTha tvaM visRjyainamimAn pAlaya dArakAn . avApya putrA~llobdhAtmA vIrapatnItvamarthaye .
mAnyuvAca ahamevAnuyAsyAmi bhartAramapalAyinam . na hi tRptAsmi kAmAnAM jyeSThA mAmanumanyatAm .
mAM cAbhigamya kSINo ' yaM kAmAd bharatasattamaH . tamucchindyAmasya kAmaM kathaM nu yamasAdane .
na cApyahaM vartayantI nirvizeSaM suteSu te . vRttimArye cariSyAmi spRzedenastathA ca mAm .
tasmAnme sutayoH kunti vartitavyaM svaputravat . mAM ca kAmayamAno ' yaM rAjA pretavazaM gataH .
vaizampAyana uvAca rAjJaH zarIreNa saha mAmapIdaM kalevaram . dagdhavyaM supraticchannametadArye priyaM kuru .
dArakeSvapramattA ca bhavethAzca hitA mamA ato ' nyanna prapazyAmi saMdeSTavyaM hi kiMcana .
vaizampAyana uvAca ityuktvA taM citAgnisthaM dharmapatnI nararSabham . madrarAjasutA tUrNamanvArohad yazasvinI .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataH zAntanavo bhISmo duryodhanamamarSaNam . kezavasya vacaH zrutvA provAca bharatarSabha .
kRSNena vAkyamukto ' si suhRdAM zamamicchatA . anvapadyasva tat tAta mA manyuvazamanvagAH .
akRtvA vacanaM tAta kezavasya mahAtmanaH . zreyo na jAtu na sukhaM na kalyANamavApsyasi .
dharmyamarthya mahAbAhurAha tvAM tAta kezavaH . tadarthamabhipadyasva mA rAjan nInazaH prajAH .
jvalitAM tvamimAM lakSmI bhAratI sarvarAjasu . jIvato dhRtarASTrasya daurAtmyAd bhraMzayiSyasi .
AtmAnaM ca sahAmAtyaM saputrabhrAtRbAndhavam . ahamityanayA buddhyA jIvitAd bhraMzayiSyasi .
atikrAman kezavasya tathyaM vacanamarthavat . pituzca bharatazreSTha vidurasya ca dhImataH .
mA kulaghnaH kupuruSo durmatiH kApathaM gamaH . mAtaraM pitaraM caiva mA majjIH zokasAgare .
atha droNo ' bravIt tatra duryodhanamidaM vacaH . amarSavazamApannaM niHzvasantaM punaH punaH .
dharmArthayuktaM vacanamAha tvAM tAta kezavaH . tathA bhISmaH zAntanavastajjuSasva narAdhipa .
prAjJau medhAvinau dAntAvarthakAmau bahuzrutau . AhatustvAM hitaM vAkyaM tajjuSasva narAdhipa . .
anutiSTha mahAprAjJa kRSNabhISmau yadUcatuH . mAdhavaM buddhimohena mA ' vamaMsthAH paraMtapa .
ye tvAM protsAhayantyete naite kRtyAya karhicit . vairaM pareSAM grIvAyAM pratimokSyanti saMyuge . .
mA jIdhanaH prajAH sarvAH putrAn bhrAtRstathaiva ca . vAsudevArjunau yatra viddhyajeyAnalaM hi tAn .
etaccaiva mataM satyaM suhRdoH kRSNabhISmayoH . yadi nAdAsyase tAta pazcAt tapsyasi bhArata .
yathoktaM jAmadagnyena bhUyAneSa tato ' rjunaH . kRSNo hi devakIputro devairapi suduHsahaH . kiM te sukhapriyeNeha proktena bharatarSabha .
etat te sarvamAkhyAtaM yathecchasi tathA kuru . na hi tvAmutsahe vaktuM bhUyo bharatasattama .
vaizampAyana uvAca tasminaM vAkyAntare vAkyaM kSattApi viduro ' bravIt . duryodhanamabhiprekSya dhArtarASTramamarSaNam .
