pIDyamAnaH kSudhA tatra phalamUlAni karSayan . prAtiSThata tato rAjA damayantI tamanvagAt .
kSudhayA pIDyamAnastu nalo bahutithe ' hani . apazyacchakunAn kAMzciddhiraNyasadRzacchadAn .
sa cintayAmAsa tadA niSadhAdhipatirbalI . asti bhakSyo mamAdyAyaM vasu cedaM bhaviSyati .
tatastAn paridhAnena vAsasA sa samAvRNot . tasya tad vastrAmAdAya sarve jagmurvihAyasA .
utpadantaH khagA vAkyametadAhustato nalam . dRSTvA digvAsasaM bhUmau sthitaM dInamadhomukham .
vayamakSAH sudurbuddhe tava vAso jihIrSavaH . AgatA na hi naH prItiH savAsasi gate tvayi .
tAn samIpagatAnakSAnAtmAnaM ca vivAsasam . puNyazlokastadA rAjan damayantImathAbravIt . yeSAM prakopAdaizvaryAt pracyuto ' hamanindite . prANayAtrAM na vindeyaM duHkhitaH kSudhayAnvitaH . yeSAM kRte na satkAramakurvan mayi naiSadhAH . ime te zakunA bhUtvA vAso bhIru haranti me .
vaiSamyaM paramaM prApto duHkhito gatacetanaH . bhartA te ' haM nibodhedaM vacanaM hitamAtmanaH .
ete gacchanti bahavaH panthAno dakSiNApatham . avantImRkSavantaM ca samatikramya parvatam .
eSa vindhyo mahAzailaH payoSNI ca samudragA . AzramAzca maharSINAM bahumUlaphalAnvitAH . eSa panthA vidarbhANAmasau gacchati kosalAn . ataH paraM ca dezo ' yaM dakSiNe dakSiNApathaH .
bRhadazva uvAca etad vAkyaM nalo rAjA damayantIM samAhitaH . uvAcAsakRdAt hi bhaimImuddizya bhArata . .
tataH sA bASpakalayA vAcA duHkhena karzitA . uvAca damayantI taM naiSadhaM karuNaM vacaH .
udvejate me hRdayaM sIdantyaGgAni sarvazaH . tava pArthiva saMkalpaM cintayantyAH punaH punaH . hRtarAjyaM hRtadravyaM vivastraM kSucchramAnvitam . kathamutsRjya gaccheyamahaM tvAM nirjane vane . .
zrAntasya te kSudhArtasya cintayAnasya tat sukham . vane ghore mahArAja nAzayiSyAmyahaM klamam .
na ca bhAryAsamaM kiMcid vidyate bhiSajAM matam . auSadhaM sarvaduHkheSu satyametad bravImi te .
nala uvAca evametad yathA ' ' tya tvaM damayanti sumadhyame . nAsti bhAryAsamaM mitraM narasyArtasya bheSajam .
na cAhaM tyakta kAmastvAM kimalaM bhIru zaGkase . tyajeyamahamAtmAnaM na caiva tvAmanindite .
damayantyuvAca yadi mAM tvaM mahArAja na vihAtumihecchasi . tat kimarthaM vidarbhANAM panthAH samupadizyate .
avaimi cAhaM nRpate na tu mAM tyaktumarhasi . cetasA tvapakRSTena mAM tyajethA mahIpate . .
panthAnaM hi mamAbhIkSNamAkhyAsi ca narottama . ato nimittaM zokaM me vardhayasyamaropama .
yadi cAyamabhiprAyastava jJAtIn vrajediti . sahitAveva gacchAvo vidarbhAn yadi manyase .
vidarbharAjastatra tvAM pUjayiSyati mAnada . tena tvaM pUjito rAjan sukhaM vatsyasi no gRhe .
vaizampAyana uvAca tatastu zilpinaH sarve amAtyapravarAzca ye . vidurazca mahAprAjJo dhArtarASTra nyavedayan .
sajja kratuvaraM rAjan prAptakAlaM ca bhArata . sauvarNaM ca kRtaM sarvaM lAgalaM ca mahAdhanam .
etacchrutvA nRpazreSTho dhArtarASTro vizAmpate . AjJApayAmAsa nRpaH kraturAjapravartanam . tataH pravavRte yajJaH prabhUtArthaH susaMskRtaH . dIkSitazcApi gAndhAriryathAzAstraM yathAkramam .
prahRSTo dhRtarASTrazca vidurazca mahAyazAH . bhISmo droNaH kRpaH karNo gAndhArI ca yazasvinI .
nimantraNArthaM dUtAMzca preSayAmAsa zIghragAn . pArthivAnAM ca rAjendra brAhmaNAnAM tathaiva ca .
te prayAtA yathoddiSTA dUtAstvaritavAhanAH . tatra kaMcit prayAtaM tu dUtaM duHzAsano ' bravIt .
gaccha dvaitavanaM zIghraM pANDavAn pApapUruSAn . nimantraya yathAnyAyaM viprAMstasmin vane tadA .
sa gatvA pANDavAn sarvAnuvAcAbhipraNamya ca . duryodhano mahArAja yajate nRpasattamaH . svavIyarjitamarthaughamavApya kurusattamaH . tatra gacchanti rAjAno brAhmaNAzca tatastataH .
ahaM tu preSito rAjan kauraveNa mahAtmanA . Amantrayati vo rAjA dhArtarASTro janezvaraH . mano ' bhilaSitaM rAjJastaM kratuM draSTumarhatha .
tato yudhiSThiro rAjA tacchrutvA dUtabhASitam . abravInRpazArdUlo diSTyA rAjA suyodhanaH . yajate kratumukhyena pUrveSAM kIrtivardhanaH .
vayamapyupayAsyAmo na tvidAnI kathaMcana . samayaH paripAlyo no yAvad varSaM trayodazam .
zrutvaitad dharmarAjasya bhImo vacanamabravIt . tadA tu nRpatirgantA dharmarAjo yudhiSThiraH . astrazastrapradIpte ' gnau yadA taM pAtayiSyati . varSAt trayodazAdUrdhvaM raNasatre narAdhipaH . yadA krodhahavirmoktA dhArtarASTreSu pANDavaH . AgantAhaM tadAsmIti vAcyaste sa suyodhanaH .
zeSAstu pANDavA rAjan naivocuH kiMcidapriyam . dUtazcApi yathAvRttaM dhArtarASTra nyavedayat .
athAjagmurnarazreSThA nAnAjanapadezvarAH . brAhmaNAzca mahAbhAga dhArtarASTrapuraM prati .
te tvarcitA yathAzAstraM yathAvidhi yathAkramam . mudA paramayA yuktAH prItAzcApi narezvarAH .
dhRtarASTro ' pi rAjendra saMvRtaH sarvakauravaiH . harSeNa mahatA yukto viduraM pratyabhASata .
yathA sukhI janaH sarva : kSattaH syAdannasaMyutaH . tuSyet tu yajJasadane tathA kSipraM vidhIyatAm .
vidurastu tadAjJAya sarvavarNAnariMdama . yathA pramANato vidvAn pUjayAmAsa dharmavit . bhakSyapeyAnnapAnena mAlyaizcApi sugandhibhiH . vAsobhirvividhaizcaiva yojayAmAsa hRSTavat .
kRtvA hyAvasathAn vIro yathAzAstraM yathAkramam . sAntvayitvA ca rAjendro dattvA ca vividhaM vasu . . visarjayAmAsa nRpAn brAhmaNAMzca sahasrazaH . visRjya ca nRpAn sarvAn bhrAtRbhiH parivAritaH . viveza hAstinapuraM sahitaH karNasaubalaiH .
saMjaya uvAca krauJcaM dRSTvA tato vyUhamabhedyaM tanayastava . rakSyamANaM mahAghoraM pArthenAmitatejasA . .zA AcAryamupasaMgamya kRpaM zalyaM ca pArthiva . saumadattiM vikarNaM ca so ' zvatthAmAnameva ca . duHzAsanAdIn bhrAtR/zca sarvAneva ca bhArata . anyAMzca subahUzUrAn yuddhAya samupAgatAn . prAhedaM vacanaM kAle harSayaMstanayastava . nAnAzastrapraharaNAH sarvai yuddhavizAradAH . ekaikazaH samarthA hi yUyaM sarve mahArathAH .
pANDuputrAn raNe hantuM sasainyAn kimu saMhatAH . aparyAptaM tadasmAkaM balaM bhISmAbhirakSitam . paryAptamidameteSAM balaM bhImAbhirakSitam .
saMsthAnAH zUrasenAzca vetrikAH kukurAstathA . ArocakAstrigartAzca madrakA yavanAstathA . zatrujayena sahitAstathA duHzAsanena ca . vikarNena ca vIreNa tathA nandopanandakaiH . citrasenena sahitAH sahitAH pAribhadrakaiH . bhISmamevAbhirakSantu sahasainyapuraskRtAH .
tato bhISmazca droNazca tava putrAzca mAriSa avyUhanta mahAvyUhaM pANDUnAM pratibAdhakam .
bhISmaH sainyena mahatA samantAt parivAritaH . yayau prakarSan mahatIM vAhinIM surarADiva .
tamanvayAnmaheSvAso bhAradvAjaH pratApavAn . kuntalaizca dazArGgazca mAgadhaizca vizAmpate . vidarbhamaikalaizcaiva karNaprAvaraNairapi . sahitAH sarvasainyena bhISmamAhavazobhinam . gAndhArAH sindhusauvIrAH zivayo ' thavasAtayaH . zakunizca svasainyena bhAradvAjamapAlayat .
tato duryodhano rAjA sahitaH sarvasodaraiH . azvAtakaivikarNaizca tathA cAmbaSThakosalaiH . daradaizca zakaizcaiva tathA kSudrakamAlavaiH . abhyarakSata saMhaSTaH saubaleyasya vAhinIm .
bhUrizravAH zalaH zalyo bhagadattazca mAriSaH . vindAnuvindAvAvantyau vAmaM pArzvamapAlayan .
saumadattiH suzarmA ca kAmbojazca sudakSiNaH . zrutAyuzcAcyutAyuzca dakSiNaM pakSamAsthitAH .
azvatthAmA kRpazcaiva kRtavarmA ca sAtvataH . mahatyA senayA sAdhu senApRSThe vyavasthitAH .
pRSThagopAstu tasyAsan nAnAdezyA janezvarAH . ketumAn vasudAnazca putraH kAzyasya cAbhibhUH .
tataste tAvakAH sarve hRSTA yuddhAya bhArata . dadhmuH zaGkhAn mudA yuktAH siMhanAdAMstathonnadan .
teSAM zrutvA tu hRSTAnAM vRddhaH kurupitAmahaH . siMhanAdaM vinadyoccaiH zaGkha dadhmau pratApavAn .
tataH zaGkhAzca bheryazca pezyazca vividhAH pare . AnakAzcAbhyahanyanta sa zabdastumulo ' bhavat .
tataH zvetairhayairyukte mahati syandane sthitau . pradadhmatuH zaGkhavarau hemaratnapariSkRtau .
pAJcajanyaM hRSIkezo devadattaM dhanaMjayaH . pauNDraM dadhmau mahAzaGkha bhImakarmA vRkodaraH .
anantavijayaM rAjA kuntIputro yudhiSThiraH . nakulaH sahadevazca sughoSamaNipuSpakau .
kAzirAjazca zaibyazca zikhaNDI ca mahArathaH . dhRSTadyumno virATazca sAtyakizca mahArathaH . pAJcAlyAzca maheSvAsA draupadyAH paJca cAtmajAH . sarve dadhmurmahAzaGkhAn siMhanAdAMzca nedire .
sa ghoSaH sumahAMstatra vIraistaiH samudIritaH . nabhazca pRthivIM caiva tumulo vyanunAdayat . evamete mahArAja prahRSTAH kurupANDavAH . punayuddhAya saMjagmustApayAnAH parasparam .
mArkaNDeya uvAca devAnAM kathA saMjAtA mahItalaM gatvA mahIpati zibimauzInaraM sAdhvenaM zibiM jijJAsyAma iti . evaM bho ityuktvA agnIndrAvupatiSThetAm .
agniH kapotarUpeNa tamabhyadhAvadAmiSArthamindraH zyenarUpeNaH .
atha kapoto rAjJo divyAsanAsInasyotsaGgaM nyapatat .
atha purohito rAjAnamabravIt . prANarakSArthaM zyenAd bhIto bhavantaM prANArthI prapadyate .
vasu dadAtu antavAn pArthivo ' sya niSkRtiM kuryAd ghoraM kapotasya nipAtamAhuH .
atha kapoto rAjAnamabravIt . prANarakSArthaM zyenAd bhIto bhavantaM prANArthI prapadye aGgairaGgAni prApyArthI munirbhUtvA prANAMstvAM prapadye .
svAdhyAyena karzitaM brahmacAriNaM mAM viddhi . tapasA damena yuktamAcAryasyApratikUlabhASiNam . evaM yuktamapApaM mAM viddhiA .
gadAmi vedAn vicinomi chandaH sarve vedA akSarazo me adhItAH . na sAdhu dAnaM zrotriyasya pradAna mA prAdAH zyenAya na kapoto ' smi .
atha zyeno rAjAnamabravIt .
paryAyeNa vasatirvA bhaveSu sarge jAtaH pUrvamasmAt kapotAt . tvamAdadAno ' tha kapotamenaM mA tvaM rAjan vighnakartA bhavethAH .
rAjovAca kenedRzI jAtu parA hi dRSTA vAgucyamAnA zakunena saMskRtA . yAM vai kapoto vadate yAM ca zyena ubhau viditvA kathamastu sAdhu .
nAsya varSaM varSati varSakAle nAsya bIjaM rohati kAla uptam . bhItaM prapannaM yo hi dadAti zatrave na trANaM labhet trANamicchan sa kAle .
jAtA hrasvA prajA pramIyate sadA na vAsaM pitaro ' sya kurvate . bhItaM prapannaM yo hi dadAti zatrave nAsya devAH pratigRhaNanti havyam .
moghamannaM vindati cApracetAH svargAllokAd bhrazyati zIghrameva . bhItaM prapanaM yo hi dadAti zatrave sendrA devAH praharantyasya vajram .
ukSANaM paktvA saha odanena asmAt kapotAt prati te nayantu . yasmin deze smase ' tIva zyena tatra mAMsaM zibayaste vahantu .
zyena uvAca nokSANaM rAjan pArthayeyaM na cAnyadasmAnmAMsamadhikaM vA kapotAt . devairdattaH sodhyaM mamaiSa bhakSastanme dadasva zakunAnAmabhAvAt .
rAjovAca ukSANaM vehatamanUnaM nayantu te pazyantu puruSA mamaiva . bhayAhitasya dAyaM mamAntikAt tvAM pratyAmnAyaM tu tvaM hyena mA hiMsIH .
tyaje prANAn naiva dadyAM kapotaM saumyo hyayaM kiM na jAnAsi zyena . yathA klezaM mA kuruSveha saumya nAhaM kapotamarpayiSye kathaMcit .
yathA mAM vai sAdhuvAdaiH prasannAH prazaMseyuH zibayaH karmaNA tu . yathA zyena priyameva kuryAM prazAdhi mAM yad vadestat karomi .
zyena uvAca UrodakSiNAdutkRtya svapizitaM tAvad rAjan yAvanmAMsaM kapotena samam . tathA tasmAt sAdhu trAtaH kapotaH prazaMseyuzca zibayaH kRtaM ca priyaM syAnmameti .
atha dakSiNAdUrorutkRtya svamAMsapezIM tulayA dhArayat . gurutara eva kapota AsIt .
punaranyamuccakarta gurutara eva kapotaH . evaM sarva samadhikRtya zarIraM tulAyAmAropayAmAsA tat tathApi gurutara eva kapota AsIt .
atha rAjA svayameva tulAmAruroha . na ca vyalIkamAsId rAjJa etad vRttAntaM dRSTvA trAta ityuktvA prAlIyata zyeno ' tha rAjA abravIt .
kapotaM vidyuH zibayastvAM kapota pRcchAmi te zakune ko nu zyenaH . nAnIzvara IdRzaM jAtu kuryAdetaM praznaM bhagavan me vicakSva .
kapota uvAca vaizvAnaro ' haM jvalanodhUmaketurathaiva zyeno vajrahastaH zacIpatiH . sAdhu jJAtuM tvAmRSabhaM sauratheya nau jijJAsayA tvatsakAzaM prapannau .
yAmetAM pezIM mama niSkrayAya prAdAd bhavAnasinotkRtya rAjan . etad vo lakSma zivaM karomi hiraNyavarNaM ruciraM puNyagandham .
etAsAM prajAnAM pAlayitA yazasvI surarSINAmatha sammato bhRzam . etasmAt pArthAt puruSo janiSyati kapotarometi ca tasya nAma .
kapotaromANaM zibinaudbhidaM putraM prApsyasi nRpa vRSasaMhananaM yazodIpyamAnaM draSTAsi zUramRSabhaM saurathAnAm .
brAhmaNaH uvAca vivasvato gacchati paryayeNa voDhuM bhavAMstaM rathamekacakram . AzcaryabhUtaM yadi tatra kiMcid dRSTaM tvayA zaMsitumarhasi tvam .
nAga uvAca AzcaryANAmanekAnAM pratiSThA bhagavAn raviH . yato bhUtAH pravartante sarve trailokyasammatAH .
yasya razmisahasreSu zAkhAsviva vihaMgamAH . vasantyAzritya munayaH saMsiddhA daivataiH saha .
yato vAyurviniHsRtya sUryarazmyAzrito mahAn . vijRmbhatyambare tatra kimAzcAryamataH param .
vibhajya taM tu viprarSe prajAnAM hitakAmyayA . toyaM sRjati varSAsu kimAzcaryamata : param .
yasya maNDalamadhyastho mahAtmA paramatviSA . dIptaH samIkSate lokAn kimAzcaryamataH param .
zukro nAmAsitaH pAdo yazca vAridharo ' mbare . toyaM sRjati varSAsu kimAzcaryamataH param .
yo ' STamAsAMstu zucinA kiraNenokSitaM payaH . pratyAdatte punaH kAle kimAzcaryamataH param .
yasya tejovizeSeSu svayamAtmA pratiSThitaH . yato bIjaM mahI ceyaM dhAryate sacarAcarA .
yatra devo mahAbAhuH zAzvataH puruSottamaH . anAdinidhano vipra kimAzcaryamataH param .
AzcaryANAmivAzcaryamidamekaM tu me zRNu . vimale yanmayA dRSTamambare sUryasaMzrayAt .
purA madhyAhnasamaye lokAMstapati bhAskare . pratadityapratIkAzaH sarvataH samadRzyat .
sa lokAMstejasA sarvAn svabhAsA nirvibhAsayan . AdityAbhimukho ' bhyeti gaganaM pATayanniva .
hutAhutiriva jyotirvyApya tejomarIcibhiH . anirdezyena rUpeNa dvitIya iva bhAskaraH .
tasyAbhigamanaprAptI hastau dattau vivasvatA . tenApi dakSiNo hasto dattaH pratyarcitArthinA .
tato bhittvaiva gaganaM praviSTo razmimaNDalam . ekIbhUtaM ca tat tejaH kSaNenAdityatAM gatam .
tatra naH saMzayo jAtastayostejaH samAgame . anayoH ko bhavet sUryo rathastho yo ' yamAgataH .
te vayaM jAtasaMdehAH paryapRcchAmahe ravim . ka eSa divamAkramya gataH sUrya ivAparaH .
yudhiSThira uvAca gArhasthyaM dharmamakhilaM prabrUhi bharatarSabha . RddhimApnoti kiM kRtvA manuSya iha pArthiva .
bhISma uvAca atra te vartayiSyAmi pRrAvRttaM janAdhipa . vAsudevasya saMvAdaM pRthivyAzcaiva bhArata .
saMstutya pRthivIM devIM vAsudevaH pratApavAn . papraccha bharatazreSTha mAM tvaM yat pRcchase ' dya vai .
vAsudeva uvAca gArhasthyaM dharmamAzritya mayA vA madvidhena vA . kimavazyaM dhare kAryaM kiM vA kRtvA kRtaM bhavet .
pRthvI uvAca RSayaH pitaro devA manuSyAzcaiva mAdhava . ijyAzcaivArcanIyAzca yathA caiva nibodha me .
sadA yajJena devAzca sadA ' ' tithyena mAnuSAH . chandatazca yathA nityamarhAn bhuJjIta nityazaH .
tena paSigaNAH prItA bhavanti madhusUdana . nityamagniM paricaredabhuktvA balikarma ca .
kuryAt tathaiva devA vai prIyante madhusUdana . kuryAdaharahaH zrAddhamannAdyenodakena ca . payomUlaphalairvApi pitRRNAM prItimAharan . siddhAnnAd vaizvadevaM vai kuryAdagnau yathAvidhi . agnISomaM vaizvadevaM dhAnvantaryamanantaram . prajAnAM pataye caiva pRthagyomo vidhIyate .
tathaiva cAnupUrveNa balikarma prayojayet . dakSiNAyAM yamAyeti pratIcyAM varuNAya ca . somAya cApyudIcyAM vai vAstumadhye prajApateH . dhanvantare : prAgudIcyAM prAcyAM zakrAya mAdhava .
manuSyebhya iti prAhurbaliM dvAri gRhasya vai . marudbhyo daivatebhyazca balimantargRhe haret .
tathaiva vizvedevebhyo balimAkAzato haret . nizAcarebhyo bhUtebhyo baliM naktaM tathA haret .
evaM kRtvA baliM samyag dadyAd bhikSAM dvijAya vai . alAbhe brAhmaNasyAgnAvagramuddhRtya nikSipet .
yadA zrAddhaM pitRbhyo ' pi dAtumiccheta mAnavaH . tadA pazcAt prakurvIta nivRtte zrAddhakarmaNi .
pitRRn saMtarpayitvA tu baliM kuryAd vidhAnataH . vaizvadevaM tataH kuryAt pazcAd brAhmaNavAcanam .
tato ' nnena vizeSeNa bhojayedatithInapi . arcApUrva mahArAja tataH prINAti mAnavAn .
anityaM hi sthito yasmAt tasmAdatithirucyate . AcAryasya pituzcaiva sakhyurAptasya cAtitheH . idamasti gRhe mahyamiti nityaM nivedayet .
te yad vadeyustat kuryAditi dharmo vidhIyate . gRhasthaH puruSaH kRSNa ziSTAzI ca sadA bhavet .
rAjatvijaM snAtakaM ca guruM zvazurameva ca . . arcayenmadhuparkeNa parisaMvatsaroSitAn .
zvabhyazca zvapacebhyazca vayobhyazcAvaped bhuvi . vaizvadevaM hi nAmaitat sAyaMprAtarvidhIyate .
etAMstu dharmAn gArhasthyAn yaH kuryAdanasUyakaH . sa iharSivarAn prANya pretya loke mahIyate .
bhISma uvAca iti bhUmervacaH zrutvA vAsudevaH pratApavAn . tathA cakAra satataM tvamapyevaM sadAcara .
etad gRhasthadharmaM tvaM ceSTamAno janAdhipa . ihaloke yazaH prApya pretya svargamavApsyasi .
bhImasena uvAca smaranti vairaM rakSAMsi mAyAmAzritya mohinIm . hiDimbe vraja panthAnaM tvamimaM bhrAtRsevitam .
yudhiSThira uvAca kruddho ' pi puruSavyAghra bhIma mA sma striyaM vadhIH . zarIraguptyabhyadhikaM dharmaM gopAya pANDava .
vadhAbhiprAyamAyAntamadhIstvaM mahAbalam . rakSasastasya bhaginI kiM na : kruddhA kariSyati .
vaizampAyana uvAca hiDimbA tu tataH kuntImabhivAdya kRtAJjaliH . yudhiSThiraM tu kaunteyamidaM vacanamabravIt . Arye jAnAsi yad duHkhamiha strINAmanaGgajam . tadidaM mAmanuprAptaM bhImasenakRtaM zubhe .
soDhaM tat paramaM duHkhaM mayA kAlapratIkSayA . so ' yamabhyAgataH kAlo bhavitA me sukhodayaH .
mA hyuyatsRjya suhRdaH svadharma svajanaM tathA . vRto ' yaM puruSavyAghrastava putraH patiH zubhe .
vIreNAhaM tathAnena tvayA cApi yazasvini . pratyAkhyAtA na jIvAmi satyametad bravImi te .
tadarhasi kRpAM kartuM mayi tvaM varavarNini . matvA mUDheti tanmA tvaM bhaktA vAnugateti vA .
bhAnena mahAbhAge saMyojaya sutena ha . tamupAdAya gaccheyaM yatheSTaM devarUpiNam . punazcaivAnayiSyAmi visrambhaM kuru me zubhe .
ahaM hi manasA dhyAtA sarvAn neSyAmi vaH sadA . vRjinAt tArayiSyAmi durgeSu viSameSu ca . pRSThena vo vahiSyAmi zIghraM gatimabhIpsataH . yUyaM prasAdaM kuruta bhImaseno bhajeta mAm .
ApadastaraNe prANAn dhArayed yena tena vA . sarvamAvRtya kartavyaM taM dharmamanuvartatA .
Apatsu yo dhArayati dharma dharmaviduttamaH . vyasanaM hyeva dharmasya dharmiNAmApaducyate .
puNyaM prANAn dhArayati puNyaM prANadamucyate . yena yenAcared dharmaM tasmin gardA na vidyate .
