vaizampAyana uvAca tatheti tat pratijJAya hiDimbA rAkSasI tadA . bhImasenamupAdAya sordhvamAcakrame tataH .
zailazRGgeSu ramyeSu devatAyataneSu ca . mRgapakSivighuSTeSu ramaNIyeSu sarvadA . kRtvA ca paramaM rUpaM sarvAbharaNabhUSitA . saMjalpantI sumadhuraM ramayAmAsa pANDavam . tathaiva vanadurgeSu puSpitadumavalliSu . sarassu ramaNIyeSu padmotpalayuteSu ca . nadIdvIpapradezeSu vaidUryasikatAsu ca . sutIrthavanatoyAsu tathA girinadISu ca . kAnaneSu vicitreSu puSpitadrumavalliSu . himavadgirikuJjeSu guhAsu vividhAsu ca . praphullazatapatreSu saraskhamalavAriSu . sAgarasya pradezeSu maNihemaciteSu ca . palvaleSu ca ramyeSu mahAzAlavaneSu ca . devAraNyeSu puNyeSu tathA parvatasAnuSu . guhyakAnAM nivAseSu tApasAyataneSu ca . sarvartuphalaramyeSu mAnaseSu sarassu ca . bibhratI paramaM rUpaM ramayAmAsa pANDavam . ramayantI tathA bhImaM tatra tatra manojavA .
prajajJe rAkSasI putraM bhImasaMnAnmahAbalam . virUpAkSaM mahAvaktraM zarUkarNaM vibhISaNam .
bhImanAdaM sutAmrASThaM tIkSNadaMSTraM mahAbalam . maheSvAsaM mahAvIryaM mahAsattvaM mahAbhujam . mahAjavaM mahAkAyaM mahAmAyamariMdamam . dIrghaghoNaM mahoraskaM vikaTobaddhapiNDikam . amAnuSaM mAnuSajaM bhImavegaM mahAbalam . yaH pizAcanatItyAnyAn babhUvAtIva rAkSasAn .
bAlo ' pi yauvanaM prApto mAnuSeSu vizAmpate . sarvAstreSu paraM vIraH prakarSamagamad balI .
sadyo hi garbhAn rAkSasyo labhante prasavanti ca . kAmarUpadharAzcaiva bhavanti bahurUpikAH .
praNamya vikacaH pAdAvagRhaNAt sa pitustadA . mAtuzca parameSvAsastau ca nAmAsya cakratuH .
ghaTo hAsyotkaca iti mAtA taM pratyabhASata . abravIt tena nAmAsya ghaTotkaca iti sma ha .
anuraktazca tAnAsIt pANDavAn sa ghaTotkaca . teSAM ca dayito nityamAtmanityo babhUva ha .
saMvAsasamayo jIrNa ityAbhASya tatastu tAn . hiDimbA samayaM kRtvA svAM gatiM pratyapadyata .
ghaTotkaco mahAkAyaH pANDavAn pRthayA saha . abhivAdya yathAnyAyamabravIcca prabhASya tAn . kiM karomyahamAryANAM niHzaGkaM vadatAnaghAH . taM bruvantaM bhaimaseni kuntI vacanamabravIt .
tvaM kurUNAM kule jAtaH sAkSAd bhImasamo hyasi . jyeSThaH putro ' si paJcAnAM sAhAyyaM kuru putraka .
vaizampAyana uvAca pRthayApyevamuktastu praNamyaiva vaco ' bravIt . yathA hi rAvaNo loke indrajicca mahAbalaH . varmavIryasamo loke viziSTazcAbhavaM nRSu .
kRtyakAla upasthAsye pitRniti ghaTotkacaH . Amantrya rakSasAM zreSThaH pratasthe cottarAM dizam .
sa hi sRSTo maghavatA zaktihetormahAtmanA . karNasyAprativIryasya pratiyoddhA mahArathaH .
saMjaya uvAca uttareSu ca kauravya dvIpeSu zrUyate kathA . evaM tatra mahArAja bruvatazca nibodha me .
ghRtatoya : samudro ' tra dadhimaNDodako ' paraH . surodaH sAgarazcaiva tathAnyo jalasAgaraH .
paraspareNa dviguNA : sarve dvIpA narAdhipa . parvatAzca mahArAja samudraiH parivAritAH .
gaurastu madhyame dvIpe girirmAna : zilo mahAn . parvataH pazcime kRSNo nArAyaNasakho nRpa .
tatra ratnAni divyAni svayaM rakSati kezavaH . prasannazcAbhavat tatra prajAnAM vyadadhat sukham .
kuzastambaH kuzadvIpe madhye janapadaiH saha . sampUjyate zAlpalizca dvIpe zAlmalike nRpa .
krauJcadvIpe mahAkroJco girI ratnacayAkaraH . sampUjyate mahArAja cAturvaryena nityadA .
gomantaH parvato rAjan sumahAn sarvadhAtukaH . yatra nityaM nivasati zrImAn kamalalocanaH . mokSibhiH saMgato nityaM prabhurnArAyaNo hariH . kuzadvIpe tu rAjendra parvato vidrumaizcitaH .
svanAma nAmA durdharSo dvitIyo hemaparvataH . dyutimAn nAma kauravya tRtIyaH kumudo giriH .
caturthaH puSpavAn nAma paJcamastu kuzezayaH . SaSTho harigiri ma SaDete parvatottamAH .
teSAmantaraviSkambho dviguNaH sarvabhAgazaH . audbhidaM prathama varSaM dvitIyaM veNumaNDalam .
tRtIyaM surathAkAraM caturthaM kambalaM smRtam . dhRtimat paJcamaM varSa SaSThaM varSa prabhAkaram .
saptamaM kApilaM varSa saptaite varSalambhakAH . eteSu devagandharvAH prajAzca jagatIzvaraH . viharante ramante ca na teSu mriyate janaH . na teSu dasyavaH santi plecchajAtyo ' pi vA nRpa . .15 .
