krauJcAt paro vAmanako vAmanAdandhakArakaH . andhakArAt paro rAjan mainAkaH parvatottamaH .
mainAkAt parato rAjan govindo giriruttamaH . govindAt parato rAjan nibiDo nAma parvataH . parastu dviguNasteSAM viSkambho vaMzavardhana . dezAMstatra pravakSyAmi tanme nigadataH zRNu . .
krauJcasya kuzalo dezo vAmanasya manonugaH . manonugAt parazcoSNo dezaH kurukulodvaha .
uSNAt paraH prAvarakaH prAvArAdandhakArakaH . andhakArakadezAt tu munidezaH paraH smRtaH .
munidezAt parazcaiva procyate dundubhisvanaH . siddhacAraNasaMkIrNo gauraprAyo janAdhipa .
ete dezA mahArAja devagandharvasevitAH . puSkare puSkaro nAma parvato maNiratnavAn .
tatra nityaM prabhavati svayaM devaH prajApatiH . taM paryupAsate nityaM devAH sarve maharSayaH .
vAgbhirmano ' nukUlAbhiH pUjayanto janAdhipa . jambUdvIpAt pravartante ratnAni vividhAnyuta .
dvIpeSu teSu sarveSu prajAnAM kurusattama . brahmacaryeNa satyena prajAnAM hi damena ca . ArogyAyuHpramANAbhyAM dviguNaM dviguNaM tataH . eko janapado rAjan dvIpeSveteSu bhArata .
uktA janapadA yeSu dharmazcaikaH pradRzyate . Izvaro daNDapudyamya svayameva prajApatiH . dvIpAnetAn mahArAja rakSastiSThati nityadA . sa rAjA sa zivo rAjan sa pitA prapitAmahaH .
gopAyati narazreSTha prajAH sajaDapaNDitAH . bhojanaM cAtra kauravya prajAH svayamupasthitam . siddhameva mahAbAho taddhi bhuJjanti nityadA . tataH paraM samA nAma dRzyate lokasaMsthitiH .
caturasra mahArAja trayastriMzat tu maNDalam . tatra tiSThanti kauravya catvAro lokasammatAH . diggajA bharatazreSTha vAmanarAvatAdayaH . supratIkastathA rAjan prabhinnakaraTAmukhaH ! 
tasyAhaM parimANaM tu na saMkhyAtumihotsahe . asaMkhyAtaH sa nityaM hi tiryagUrdhvamadhastathA .
tatra vai vAyavo vAnti digbhyaH sarvAbhya eva hi . asambaddhA mahArAja tAn nigRhNanti te gajAH . puSkaraiH padmasaMkAzaivikasadbhirmahAprabhaiH . zatadhA punarevAzu te tAn muJcanti nityazaH .
zvasadbhirmucyamAnAstu diggajairiha mArutAH . Agacchanti mahArAja tatastiSThanti vai prajAH .
dhRtarASTra uvAca paro vai vistaro ' tyarthaM tvayA saMjaya kArtitaH . darzitaM dvIpasaMsthAnamuttaraM brUhi saMjaya .
saMjaya uvAca uktA dvIpA mahArAja grahaM vai zRNu tattvataH . svarbhAnoH kauravazreSTha yAvadeva pramANataH .
parimaNDalo mahArAja svarbhAnuH zrUyate grahaH . yojanAnAM sahasrANi viSkambho dvAdazAsya vai .
pariNAhena SaTtriMzad vipulatvena cAnagha . paSTimAhuH zatAnyasya budhAH paurANikAstathA .
candramAstu sahasrANi rAjannekAdaza smRtaH . viSkambheNa kuruzreSTha trayastriMzat tu maNDalam . ekonaSaSTiviSkambhaM zItarazmermahAtmanaH . sUryastvaSTau sahasrANi dve cAnye kurunandana . viSkambheNa tato rAjan maNDalaM triMzatA samam . aSTapaJcAzataM rAjan vipulatvena cAnagha . zrUyate paramodAraH patago ' sau vibhAvasuH . etat pramANamarkasya nirdiSTamiha bhArata .
sa rAhuzchAdayatyetau yathAkAlaM mahattayA . candrAdityau mahArAja saMkSepo ' yamudAhRtaH .
ityetat te mahArAja pRcchataH zAstracakSuSA . sarvamuktaM yathAtattvaM tasmAcchamamavApnuhi .
yathoddiSTaM mayA proktaM sanirmANamidaM jagat . tasmAdAzvasa kauravya putraM duryodhanaM prati .
zrutvedaM bharatazreSTha bhUmiparva manonugam . zrImAn bhavati rAjanyaH siddhArthaH sAdhusammataH .
AyurbalaM ca kIrtizca tasya tejazca vardhate . yaH zRNoti mahIpAla parvaNIdaM yatavrataH . prIyante pitarastasya tathaiva ca pitAmahAH . idaM tu bhArataM varSaM yatra vartAmahe vayam . pUrvaiH pravartitaM puNyaM tat sarvaM zrutavAnasi .
bhISma uvAca atraivodAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . zatakratozca saMvAdaM namucezca yudhiSThira .
zriyA vihInamAsInamakSobhyamiva sAgaram . bhavAbhavajJaM bhUtAnAmityuvAca puraMdaraH .
namuci ruvAca baddhaH pAzaizcayutaH sthAnAd dviSatAM vazamAgataH . zriyA vihIno namuce zocasyAho na zocasi .
anivAryeNa zokena zarIraM copatapyate . amitrAzca prahaSyanti zoke nAsti sahAyatA .
tasmAcchaka na zocAmi sarvaM hyevedamantavat . saMtApAd bhrazyate rUpaM saMtApAd bhrazyate zriyaH .
saMtApAda bhrazyate cAyurdharmazcaiva surezvara . vinIya khalu tad duHkhamAgataM vaimanasyajam . dhyAtavyaM manasA hRdyaM kalyANaM saMvijAnatA .
yadA yadA hi puruSaH kalyANe kurute manaH . tadA tasya prasidhyanti sarvArthA nAtra saMzayaH .
ekaH zAstA na dvitIyo ' sti zAstA garbhe zayAnaM puruSaM zAsti zAstA . tenAyuyuktaH pravaNAdivodakaM yathA niyukto ' smi tathA vahAmi .
bhavAbhavau tvabhijAnan garIyo jJAnAcchreyo na tu karomi . AzAsu dhAsu parAsu kurvan yathA niyukto ' smi tathA vahAmi .
yathA yathAsya prAptavyaM prApnotyeva tathA tathA . bhavitavyaM yathA yacca bhavatyeva tathA tathA .
yatra yatraiva saMyukto dhAtrA garbhe punaH punaH . tatra tatraiva vasati na yatra svayamicchati .
bhAvo yo ' yamanuprApto bhavitavyamidaM mama . iti yasya sadA bhAvo na sa muhyet kadAcana .
paryAyairhanyamAnAnAmabhiyokto na vidyate . duHkhametat tu yad dveSTA kartAhamiti manyate .
RSIMzca devAMzca mahAsurAMzca traividyavRddhAMzca vane munIMzca . kAnApado nopanamanti loke parAvarajJAstu na sambhramanti .
na paNDitaH kruddhyati nAbhipadyate na cApi saMsIdati na prahaSyati . na cArthakRcchravyasaneSu zocate sthitaH prakRtyA himavAnivAcalaH .
yamarthasiddhiH paramA na mohayet tathaiva kAle vyasanaM na mohayet . sukhaM ca duHkhaM ca tathaiva madhyama niSevate yaH sa dhuraMdharo naraH .
yAM yAmavasthAM puruSo ' dhigacchet tasyAM rametAparitapyamAnaH . evaM pravRddhaM praNudanmanoja saMtApanIyaM sakalaM zarIrAt .
na tatsadaH satparivat sabhA ca sA prApya yAM na kurute sadA bhayam . dharmatattvamavagAhya buddhimAn yo ' bhyupaiti sa dhuraMdharaH pumAn .
prAjJasya karmANi duranvayAni na vai prAjJo muhyati mohakAle . stAvat kRcchrAmApadaM prApya vRddhaH .
na mantrabalavIryeNa prajJayA pauruSeNa ca . na zIlena na vRttena tathA naivArthasampadA . alabhyaM labhate martyastatra kA paridevanA .
yadevamanujAtasya dhAtAra vidadhuH purA . tadevAnucariSyAmi kiM te mRtyuH kariSyati .
labdhavyAnyeva labhate gantavyAnyeva gacchati . prAptavyAnyeva cApnoti duHkhAni ca sukhAni ca .
etad viditvA kAtryena yo na muhyati mAnavaH . kuzalI sarvaduHkheSu sa vai sarvadhano naraH .
vaizampAyana uvAca saivaM vilaya karuNaM sonmAdeva tapasvinI . uttarA nyapatad bhUmau kRpaNA putragRddhinI .
tAM tu dRSTvA nipatitAM hataputraparicchadAm . cukroza kuntI duHkhArtA sarvAzca bharatastriyaH .
muhUrtamiva rAjendra pANDavAnAM nivezanam . aprekSaNIyamabhavadArtasvanavinAditam .
sA muhUrte ca rAjendra putrazokAbhipIDitA . kazmalAbhihatA vIra vairATI tvabhavat tadA .
pratilabhya tu sA saMjJAmuttarA bharatarSabha . aGkamAroSya taM putramidaM vacanamabravIt .
dharmajJasya sutaH sa tvamadharme nAvabudhyase . yastvaM vRdhNipravIrasya kuruSe nAbhivAdanam .
putra gatvA mama vaco brUyAstvaM pitaraM tvidam . durmaraM prANinAM vIra kAle ' prApte kathaMcana . yAhaM tvayA vinAyeha patyA putreNa caiva ha . martavye sati jIvAmi hatasvastirakiMcanA .
athavA dharmarAjJAhamanujJAtA mahAbhuja . bhakSayiSye viSaM ghoraM pravekSye vA hutAzanam .
athavA durmaraM tAta yadidaM me sahasradhA . patiputravihInAyA hRdayaM na vidIryate .
uttiSTha putra pazyemAM duHkhitA prapitAmahIm . ArtAmupaplutAM dInAM nimagnAM zokasAgare .
AryAMca pazya pAJcAlIM sAtvatI ca tapasvinIm . mAM ca pazya suduHkhArto vyAdhaviddhAM mRgImiva .
uttiSTha pazya vadanaM lokanAthasya dhImataH . puNDarIkapalAzAkSaM pureva capalekSaNam .
evaM vipralapantIM tu dRSTvA nipatitAM punaH . uttarAM tAM striyaH sarvAH punarutthApayaMstataH .
utthAya ca punadhairyAt tadA matsyapateH sutA . prAJjaliH puNDarIkAkSaM bhUmAvevAbhyavAdayat .
zrutvA sa tasyA vipulaM vilApaM puruSarSabhaH . upaspRzya tataH kRSNo brahmAstraM pratyasaMharat .
pratijajJe ca dAzArhastatya jIvitamacyutaH . abravIcca vizuddhAtmA sarve vizrAvayaJjagat . na bravImyuttare mithyA satyametad bhaviSyati . eSa saMjIvayAmyenaM pazyatAM sarvadehinAm .
noktapUrvaM mayA mithyA svaireSvapi kadAcana . na ca yuddhAt parAvRttastathA saMjIvatAmayam .
yathA me dayito dharmo brAhmaNazca vizeSataH . abhimanyoH suto jAto mRto jIvatvayaM tathA .
yathAhaM nAbhijAnAmi vijaye tu kadAcana . virAdhaM tena satyena mRto jIvatvayaM zizuH .
yathA satyaM ca dharmazca mayi nityaM pratiSThitau . tathA mRtaH zizurayaM jIvatAdabhimanyujaH .
yathA kaMsazca kezI ca dharmeNa nihatau mayA . tena satyena bAlo ' yaM punaH saMjIvatAmayam .
ityukto vAsudevena sa bAlo bharatarSabha . zanaiH zanairmahArAja prAspandata sacetanaH .
bhISma uvAca sa mokSamanucintyaiva zukaH pitaramabhyagAt . prAhAbhivAdya ca guruM zreyo ' rthI vinayAnvitaH . mokSadharmeSu kuzalo bhagavAn prabravItu me . yathA me manasaH zAntiH paramA sambhavet prabho .
zrutvA putrasya tu vacaH paramarSiruvAca tam . adhISva putra mokSaM vai dharmAMca vividhAnapi .
piturniyogAjjagrAha zuko dharmabhRtAM varaH . yogazAstraM ca nikhilaM kApilaM caiva bhArata .
sa taM brAhmayA zriyA yuktaM brahmatulyaparAkramam . mene putraM yadA vyAso mokSadharmavizAradam . uvAca gaccheti tadA janakaM mithilezvaram . sa te vakSyati mokSArthaM nikhilaM mithilezvaram .
piturniyogamAdAya jagAma mithilAM nRpa . praSTuM dharmasya niSThAM vai mokSasya ca parAyaNam .
uktazca mAnuSeNa tvaM pathA gacchetyavismitaH . na prabhAveNa gantavyamantarikSacareNa vai .
ArjaveNaiva gantavyaM na sukhAnveSiNA tathA . nAnveSTavyA vizeSAstu vizeSA hi prasaGginaH .
ahaMkAro na kartavyo yAjye tasmin narAdhipe . sthAtavyaM ca vaze tasya sa te chetsyati saMzayam .
sa dharmakuzalo rAjA mokSazAstravizAradaH . yAjyo mama sa yad brUyAt tat kAryamavizaGkayA .
evamuktaH sa dharmAtmA jagAma mithilAM muniH . padbhyAM zakto ' ntarikSaNa krAntuM pRthvI sasAgarAm .
sa girIzcApyatikramya nadItIrthasarAMsi ca . bahuvyAlamRgAkIrNA hyaTavIzca vanAni ca . meroharezca dve varSe varSa haimavataM tataH . krameNaivaM vyatikramya bhArataM varSamAsadat .
sa dezAn vividhAn pazyaMzcInahUNaniSevitAn . AryAvartamimaM dezamAjagAma mahAmuniH .
piturvacanamAjJAya tamevArthaM vicintayan . adhvAnaM so ' ticakrAma khecaraH khe carannivA16 .
pattanAni ca ramyANi sphItAni nagarANi ca . ratnAni ca vicitrANi pazyannapi na pazyati .
udyAnAni ca ramyANi tathaivAyatanAni ca . puNyAni caiva ratnAni so ' tyakAmadathAdhvagaH .
so ' cireNaiva kAlena videhAnAsasAda ha . rakSitAn dharmarAjena janakena mahAtmanA .
tatra grAmAn bahUna pazyan babanarasabhojanAn . pallIghoSAn samRddhAMzca bahugokulasaMkulAn .
