hastyazvarathasaMkIrNaM naranArIsamAkulam . pazyannapazyanniva tat samatikAmadacyutaH .
manasA taM vahan bhAraM tamevArthaM vicintayan . AtmArAmaH prasannAtmA mithilAmAsasAda ha .
