teSAM tu dvArapAlAnAmekaH zokasamanvitaH . madhyaM gatamivAdityaM dRSTvA zukamavasthitam .
pUjayitvA yathAnyAyamabhivAdya kRtAJjaliH . prAvezayat tataH kakSyAM dvitIyAM rAjavezmanaH .
tatrAsInaH zukastAta mokSamevAnvacintayat . chAyAyAmAtape caiva samadarzI mahAdyutiH .
