tAM kAlarAtrImiva pAzahastAM yamasya dhAtrImiva cograrUpAm . sa brahmadaNDapratimAmamoghAM sasarja yatto yudhi dharmarAjaH .
rabhyarcitA pANDusutaiH prayatnAt . sAMvartakagnipratimAM jvalantI kRtyAmatharvAGgirasImivogrAm .
IzAnahetoH pratinirmitAM tAM tvaSTrA ripUNAmasudehabhakSyAm . bhUmyantarikSAdijalAzayAni prasahya bhUtAni nihantumIzAm .
ghaNTApatAkAmaNivajranAlA vaidUryacitrAM tapanIyadaNDAm . tvaSTrA prayatnAnniyamena klRptAM brahmadviSAmantakarImamoghAm .
balaprayatnAdadhirUDhavegAM mantraizca ghorairabhimantrya yatnAt . sasarja mArgeNa ca tAM pareNa vadhAya madrAdhipatestadAnIm .
hato ' si pApetyabhigarjamAno rudro ' ndhakAyAntakaraM yatheSum . prasArya bAhuM sudRDhaM supANiM krodhena nRtyanniva dharmarAjaH .
tAM sarvazaktyA prahitAM suzaktiM yudhiSThireNAprativAryavIryam . pratigrahAyAbhinanarda zalyaH samyagdhutAmagnirivAjyadhArAm .
muro vizAlaM ca tathaiva bhittvA . viveza gAM toyamivAprasaktA yazo vizAlaM nRpaterdahantI .
nAsAkSikarNAsyaviniHsRtena prakyandatA ca vraNasambhavena . saMsiktagAtro rudhireNa so ' bhUt krauJco yathA skandahato mahAdriH .
prasArya vAhU ca rathAd gato gAM saMchinnavarmA kurunandanena . mahendravAhapratimo mahAtmA vajrAhataM zRGgamivAcalasya .
bAhU prasAryabhimukho dharmarAjasya madrarAT . tato nipatito bhUmAvindradhvaja ivocchritaH . sa tathA bhinnasarvAGgo rudhireNa samukSitaH .
pratyudgata iva premNA bhUmyA sa narapuGgavaH . priyayA kAntayA kAntaH patamAna ivorasi .
ciraM bhuktvA vasumatI priyAM kAntAmiva prabhuH . sarvairaGgaiH samAnizlaSya prasupta iva cAbhavat .
dharmya dharmAtmanA yuddhe nihato dharmasUnunA . samyagghuta iva sviSTaH prazAnto ' gnirivAdhvare .
zaktyA vibhinnahradayaM vipraviddhAyudhadhvajam . saMzAntamapi madrezaM lakSmI va vimuJcati .
tato yudhiSThirazcApamAdAyendradhanuSprabham . vyadhamad dviSataH saMkhye khagarADiva pannagAn . dehAn sunizitairbhallai ripUNAM nAzayan kSaNAt .
tataH pArthasya bANaugherAvRtAH sainikAstava . nimIlitAkSAH kSiNvanto bhRzamanyonyamarditAH . kSaranto rudhiraM dehairvipannAyudhajIvitAH .
tataH zalye nipatite madrarAjAnujo yuvA . bhrAtustulyo gaNaiH sarvai rathI pANDavamabhyayAt .
vivyAdha ca narazreSTho nArAcairbahubhistvaran . hatasyApacitiM bhrAtuzcikIrSuryuddhadurmadaH .
taM vivyAdhazugaiH SaDbhirdharmarAjastvaraniva . kArmukaM cAsya ciccheda kSurAbhyAM dhvajameva ca .
tato ' sya dIpyamAnena sudRDhena zitena ca . pramukhe vartamAnasya bhallenApAharacchiraH .
sakuNDalaM tad dadRze patamAnaM ziro rathAt . puNyakSayamanuprApya patan svargAdiva cyutaH .
tasyApakRttazIrSaM tu zarIraM patitaM rathAt . rudhireNAvasiktAGgaM dRSTvA sainyamabhajyata .
vicitrakavace tasmin hate madranRpAnuje . hAhAkAraM prakurvANAH kuravo ' bhipradudruvaH .
zalyAnujaM hataM dRSTvA tAvakAstyaktajIvitAH . vitresuH pANDavabhayAd rajodhvastAstadA bhRzam .
tAMstathA bhajyamAnAMstu kauravAn bharatarSabha . zinernaptA kiran bANairabhyavartata sAtyakiH .
tamAyAntaM maheSvAsaM duSprasahya durAsadam . hArdikyastavarito rAjan pratyagRhNAdabhItavat .
tau sametau mahAtmAnau vArSNeyau varavAjinau . hArdikyaH sAtyakizcaiva siMhAviva balotkaTau .
iSubhirvimalAbhAsaizchAdayantau parasparam . arcibhiriva sUryasva divAkarasamaprabhau .
cApamArgabaloddhatAn mArgaNAn vRSNisiMhayoH . AkAzagAnapazyAma pataGgAniva zIghragAn .
sAtyaki dazabhividdhvA hayAMzcAsya tribhiH zaraiH .74 cApamekena ciccheda hArdikyo nataparvaNA .
tannikRttaM dhanuH zreSThamapAsya zinipuGgavaH . anyadAdatta vegena vegavattaramAyudham .
tadAdAya dhanuH zreSThaM variSThaH sarvadhanvinAm . hArdikyaM dazabhirbANaiH pratyavidhyat stanAntare .
tato rathaM yugeSAM ca cchittvA bhallaiH susaMyataiH . azvAMstasyAvadhIt tUrNamUbhau ca pArSNisArathI .
tatastaM virathaM dRSTvA kRpaH zAradvataH prabho . apovAha tataH kSipraM rathamAropya vIryavAn .
madrarAje hate rAjan virathe kRtavarmaNi . duryodhanabalaM sarvaM punarAsIt parAGmukham .
tat pare nAnvabudhyanta sainyena rajasA vRte . balaM tu hatabhUyiSThaM tat tadA ' ' sIt parAGmukham .
tato muhUrtAt te ' pazyan rajo bhImaM samutthitam . vividhaiH zoNitasrAvaiH prazAntaM puruSarSabha .
tato duryodhano dRSTvA bhagnaM svabalamantikAt . javenApatataH pArthAnekaH sarvAnavArayat .
pANDavAn sarathAn dRSTvA dhRSTadyumnaM ca pArSatam . AnartaM ca durAdharSaM zitairbANairavArayat . taM pare nAbhyavartanta mA mRtyumivAgatam .
athAnyaM rathamAsthAya hArdikyo ' pi nyavartata . tato yudhiSThiro rAjA tvaramANo mahArathaH .
caturbhinijaghAnAzvAn patribhiH kRtavarmaNaH . vivyAdha gautamaM cApi SaDbhirbhallaiH sutejanaiH .
azvatthAmA tato rAjJA hatAzvaM virathIkRtam . tamapovAha hArdikyaM svarathena yudhiSThirAt .
tataH zAradvataH SaDbhiH pratyaviddhyad yudhiSThiram . vivyAdha cAzvAnnizitaistasyASTAbhiH zilImukhaiH .
evametanmahArAja yuddhazeSamavartata . tava durmatrite rAjan saha putrasya bhArata .
tasmin maheSvAsadhare vizaste saMgrAmamadhye kurupuGgavena . pArthAH sametAH paramaprahRSTAH zaGkhAn pradadhumurhatamIkSya zalyam .
yudhiSThiraM ca prazazaMsurAjau purA kRte vRtravadhe yathendram . cakruzca nAnAvidhavAdyazabdAn ninAdayanto vasudhA sametAH .
saMjaya uvAca tato vyUDheSvanIkeSu samutkRSTeSu mAriSa . tADyamAnAsu bherISu mRdaGgeSu nadatsu ca .
anIkAnAM ca saMhrAde vAditrANAM ca niHsvane . pradhyApiteSu zoSu saMnAde lomaharSaNe .
abhihArayatsu zanakairbharateSu yuyutsuSu . raudre muhUrte samprApte savyasAcI vyadRzyata .
balAnAM vAyasAnAM ca purastAt savyasAcinaH . bahulAni sahasraNi prAkrIDaMstatra bhArata .
mRgAzca ghorasaMnAdaH zivAzcAzivadarzanAH . dakSiNena prayAtAnAmasmAkaM prANadaMstathA .
sanirghAtA jvalantyazca peturulkAH sahasrazaH . cacAla ca mahI kRtsnA bhaye ghore samutthite .
viSvagvAtAH sanirghAtA rUkSAH zarkarakarSiNaH . vavurAyAti kaunteye saMgrAme samupasthite .
nAkulizca zatAnIko dhRSTadyumnazca pANDavAnAmanIkAni prAjJau tau vyUhatustadA .
tato rathasahasreNa dviradAnAM zatena ca . tribhirazvasahastraizca padAtInAM zataiH zataiH . pArSataH . adhyardhamAtre dhanuSAM sahasre tanayastava . agrataH sarvasainyAnAM sthitvA durmarSaNo ' bravIt .
adya gANDIvadhanvAnaM tapantaM yuddhadurmadam . ahamAvArayiSyAmi veleva makarAlayam .
adya pazyantu saMgrAme dhanaMjayamamarSaNam . viSaktaM mayi durdharSamazmakUTamivAzmani .
tiSThadhvaM sthano yUyaM saMgrAmamabhikAkSiNaH . yudhyAmi saMhatAnetAn yazo mAnaM ca vardhayan .
evaM bruvanmahArAja mahAtmA sa mahAmatiH . maheSvAsairvato rAjan maheSvAso vyavasthitaH .
tato ' ntaka iva kruddhaH savajra iva vAsavaH . daNDapANigi mahyo mRtyuH kAlena coditaH .
zUlapANirivAkSobhyo varuNaH pAzavAniva . yugAnkAMgnarivArciSmAn pradhakSyan vai punaH prajAH .
krodhAmarSabalodbhUto nivAtakavacAntakaH . jayo jetA sthitaH satye pArayiSyan mahAvratam .
AmuktakavacaH khaDgI jAmbUnadakirITabhRt . zubhramAlyAmbaradharaH svagadazcArukuNDalaH .
rathapravaramAsthAya naro nArAyaNAnugaH . vidhunvan gANDivaM saMkhye babhau sUrya ivoditaH .
so ' grAnIkasya mahata iSupAte dhanaMjayaH . vyavasthApya rathaM rAjazaGkha dadhmau pratApavAn .
athakRSNo ' pyasambhrAntaH pArthena saha mAriSa . prAdhyApayat pAJcajanyaM zaGkha pravaramojasA .
tayoH zaGkhapaNAdena tava sainye vizAmpate . Asan saMhRSTaromANaH kampitA gatacetasaH .
yathA trasyanti bhUtAni sarvANyazaniniH svanAt . tathA zaGkhapraNAdena vitresustava sainikAH .
prasusravuH zakRnmUtraM vAhanAni ca sarvazaH . evaM savAhanaM sarvamAvignamabhavad balam .
sIdanti sma narA rAjazaGkhazabdena mAriSa . visaMjJAzcAbhavan kecit kecid rAjan vitatrasu .
tataH kapimahAnAdaM saha bhUtairdhvajAlayaiH . akaroddha vyAditAsyazca bhISayaMstava sainikAn .
tataH zaGkhAzca bheryazca mRdaGgAzcAnakaiH saha . punarevAbhyahanyanta tava sainyapraharSaNAH .
nAnAvAditrasaMhAdaiH zvaiDitAsphoTitAkulaiH . siMhanAdaiH samutkuSTaiH samAdhUtairmahArathaiH .
tasmiMstu tumule zabde bhIrUNAM bhayavardhane . atIva hRSTo dAzArhamabravIt pAkazAsaniH .
janamejaya uvAca prAcetasasya dakSasya kathaM vaivasvate ' ntare . vinAzamagamad brahman hayamedhaH prajApateH .
devyA manyukRtaM matvA kruddhaH sarvAtmakaH prabhuH . prasAdAt tasya dakSeNa sa yajJaH saMdhita : katham . etad veditumiccheyaM tanme brUhi yathAtatham .
vaizampAyana uvAca purA himavataH pRSThe dakSo vai yajJamAharat . gaGgAdvAre zubhe deze RSisiddhaniSevite .
gandharvApsarasAkIrNe nAnAdumalatAvRte . RSisaGghaH parivRtaM dakSaM dharmabhRtAM varam . pRthivyAmantarikSe ca ye ca svarlokavAsinaH . sarve prAJjalayo bhUtvA upatasthuH prajApatim .
devadAnavagandharvAH pizAcoragarAkSasAH . hAhAhUhUca gandharvo tumburu radastathA . vizvAvasurvizvaseno gandharvApsarasastathA . AdityA vasavo rudrAH sAdhyAH saha marudgaNaiH . indreNa sahitAH sarve AgatA yajJabhAginaH . uSmapAH somapAzcaiva dhUmapA AjyapAstathA . RSayaH pitarazcaiva AgatA brahmaNA saha . ete cAnye ca bahavo bhUtagrAmAzcaturvidhAH . jarAyujANDajAzcaiva sahasA svedajodbhijaiH . AhUtA mantritAH sarve devAzca saha patnibhiH . virAjante vimAnasthA dIpyamAnA ivAgnayaH .
tAn dRSTvA manyunA ' ' viSTo dadhIcirvAkyamabravIt . nAyaM yajJo na vA dharmo yatra rudro na ijyate .
vadhabandhaM prapannA vai kiM nu kAlasya paryayaH . kiMnu mohAnna pazyanti vinAzaM paryupasthitam . upasthitaM mahAghoraM na budhyanti mahAdhvare .
ityuktavA sa mahAyogI pazyati dhyAnacakSuSA . sa pazyati mahAdevaM devIM ca varadAM zubhAm . nAradaM ca mahAtmAnaM tasyA devyAH samIpataH . saMtoSaM paramaM lebhe iti nizcitya yogavit .
ekamantrAstu te sarve yenezo na nimantritaH . tasmAd dezAdapakramya dadhIcirvAkyamabravIt . apUjyapUjanAccaiva pUjyAnAM cApyapUjanAt . nRghAtakasamaM pApaM zazvat prApnoti mAnavaH .
anRtaM noktapUrvaM me na ca vakSye kadAcana . devatAnAmRSINAM ca madhye satyaM bravImyaham .
AgataM pazubhartAraM sraSTAraM jagataH patim . adhvare hyagrabhoktAraM sarveSAM pazyata prabhum .
dakSa uvAca santi no bahavo rudrAH zUlahastAH kapardinaH . ekAdazasthAnagatA nAhaM vedmi mahezvaram .
dadhIciruvAca sarveSAmeva mantro ' yaM yenAsau na nimantritaH . yathAhaM zaMkarAdUrdhvaM nAnyaM pazyAmi daivatam . tathA dakSasya vipulo yajJo ' yaM na bhaviSyati .
dakSa uvAca etanmakhezAya suvarNapAtre haviH samastaM vidhimantrapUtam . viSNornayAmyapratimasya bhAgaM prabhurvibhuzcAhavanIya eSaH .
devyuvAca kiM nAma dAnaM niyamaM tapo vA kuryAmahaM yena patirmamAdyA labheta bhAgaM bhagavAnacintyo hyadhu tathA bhAgamatho tRtIyam .
evaM bruvANAM bhagavAnsa patnI prahRSTarUpaH kSubhitAmuvAca . na vetsi mAM devi kRzodarAGgi kiM nAma yuktaM vacanaM makheze .
ahaM vijAnAmi vizAlanetre dhyAnena hInA na vidantyasantaH . tavAdya mohena ca sendradevA lokAstrayaH sarvata eva mUDhAH .
mAmadhvare zaMsitAraH stuvanti rathantaraM sAmagAzcopagAnti . mAM brAhmaNA brahmavido yajante mamAdhvaryavaH kalpayante ca bhAgam .
devyuvAca suprAkRto ' pi puruSaH sarvaH strIjanasaMsadi . stauti gavAryate cApi svamAtmAnaM na saMzayaH .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca nAtmAnaM staumi devezi pazya me tanumadhyame . yaM vakSyAmi varArohe yAgArthe varavarNini .
ityuktvA bhagavAn patnImumAM prANairapi priyAm . so ' sRjad bhagavAn vaktrAd bhUtaM ghoraM praharSaNam .
tamuvAcAkSipa makhaM dakSasyeti mahezvaraH . tato vaktrAd vimuktena siMhenaikena lIlayA . . devyA manyuvyapohArthaM hato dakSasya vai kratuH .
manyunA ca mahAbhImA mahAkAlI mahezvarI . AtmanaH karmasAkSitve tena sArdhaM sahAnugA . devasthAnumataM matvA praNamya zirasA tataH .
AtmanaH sadRzaH zauryAd balarUpasamanvitaH . sa eva bhagavAn krodhaH pratirUpasamanvitaH .
anantabalavIryazca anantabalapauruSaH . vIrabhadra iti khyAto devyA manyupramArjakaH . so ' sRjad romakUpebhyo raumyAn nAma gaNezvarAn .
rudratulyA gaNA raudrA rudravIryaparAkramAH . te nipetustatastUrNaM dakSayajJavihiMsayA . bhImarUpA mahAkAyAH zatazo ' tha sahasrazaH .
tataH kalakilAzabdairAkAzaM pUrayanniva . tena zabdena mahatA trastAstatra divaukasaH .
parvatAzca vyazIryanta cakampe ca vasuMdharA . mArutAzcaiva ghUrNante cukSubhe varuNAlayaH .
agnayo naiva dIpyante naiva dIpyati bhAskaraH . grahA naiva prakAzante nakSatrANi na candramAH .
RSayo na prakAzante na devA na.ca mAnuSAH . evaM tu timirIbhUtaM nirdahantyapamAnitAH .
praharantyapare ghorA yUpAnutpATayanti ca . pramardanti tathA cAnye vimardanti tathA pare .
AdhAvanti pradhAvanti vAyuvegA manojavAH . cUrNyante yajJapAtrANi divyAnyAbharaNAni ca . vizIryamANA dRzyante tArA iva nabhastale .
divyAnnapAnabhakSyANAM rAzayaH parvatopamAH . kSIranadyo ' tha dRzyante ghRtapAyasakardamAH . dadhimaNDodakA divyAH khaNDazarkaravAlukAH . SaD rasAn nivahantyetA guDakulyA manoramAH .
uccAvacAni mAMsAni bhakSyANi vividhAni ca . pAnakAni ca divyAni leDacoSyANi yAni ca . bhuJjate vividhairvaktraivilumpantyAkSipanti ca . rudrakopAnmahAkAyA : kAlAgnisadRzopamAH .
kSobhayan surasainyAni bhISayantaH samantataH . krIDanti vividhAkArAzcikSipuH surayoSitaH .
rudrakodhAt prayatnena sarvadevaiH surakSitam . taM yajJamadahacchIghraM rudrakarmA sabhantataH .
cakAra bhairavaM nAdaM sarvabhUtabhavaMkaram . chittvA ziro vai yajJasya nanAda ca mumoda ca .
tato brahmAdayo devA dakSazcaiva prajApatiH . UcuH prAjjalayaH sarve kathyatAM ko bhavAniti .
vIrabhadra uvAca nAhaM rudro na vA devI naiva bhoktumihAgataH . devyA manyukRtaM matvA kruddhaH sarvAtmakaH prabhuH .
draSTuM vA naiva viprendrAn naiva kautUhalena vA . tava yajJavighAtArthaM samprAptaM viddhi mAmiha .
vIrabhadra iti khyAto rudrakopAd viniHsRtaH . bhadrakAlIti vikhyAtA devyAH kopAd viniHsRtA . preSitau devadevena yajJAntikamihAgatau .
zaraNaM gaccha viprendra devadevamumApatim . varaM krodho ' pi devasya varadAnaM na cAnyataH .
vIrabhadravacaH zrutvA dakSo dharmabhRtAM varaH . toSayAmAsa stotreNa praNipatya mahezvaram .
prapadye devamIzAnaM zAzvataM dhruvamavyayam . mahAdevaM mahAtmAnaM vizvasya jagataH patim .
prANApAnau saMnirudhya vaktrasthAnena yatnataH . vicArya sarvato dRSTiM bahudRSTiramitrajit . sahasA devadevezo hyagnikuNDAt samutthitaH .
bibhratsUryasahasrasya tejaH saMvartakopamaH . smitaM kRtvAbravId vAkyaM brUhi kiM karavANi te .
zrAvite ca makhAdhyAye devAnAM guruNA tataH . tumavAcAJjaliM kRtvA dakSo devaM prajApatiH bhItazaGkitavitrastaH sabASpavadanekSaNaH .
yadi prasanno bhagavAn yadi cAhaM bhavatpriyaH . yadi vAhamanugrAhyo yadi vA varado mama . yad dagdhaM bhakSitaM pItazitaM yacca nAzitam . cUrNIkRtApaviddhaM ca yajJasambhAramIdRzam . dIrghakAlena mahatA prayatnena susaMcitam . tanna mithyA bhavenmahyaM varametamahaM vRNe . tathAstvityAha bhagavAn bhaganetraharo haraH . dharmAdhyakSo virUpAkSastryakSo devaH prajApatiH .
jAnubhyAmavanIM gatvA dakSo labdhvA bhavAd varam . nAmnAmaSTasahasreNa stutavAn vRSabhadhvajam .
yudhiSThira uvAca yairnAmadheyaiH stutavAn dakSo devaM prajApatiH . vaktumarhasi me tAta zrotuM zraddhA mamAnagha .
bhISma uvAca zrUyatAM devadevasya nAmAnyadbhutakarmaNaH . gUDhavratasya guhyAni prakAzAni ca bhArata .
namaste devadeveza devAribalasUdana . devendrabalaviSTambha devadAnavapUjita .
sahasrAkSa virUpAkSa tryakSa yakSAdhipapriya . sarvata : pANipAdAnta sarvato ' kSiziromukhA .
sarvataHzrutimaॅlloke sarvamAvRtya tiSThasi . zaGkhakarNa mahAkarNa kumbhakarNArNavAlaya .
gajendrakarNa gokarNa pANikarNa namo ' stu te . zatodara zatAvarta zatajihva namo ' stu te .
gAyanti tvA gAyatriNo ' rcantyarkamarkiNaH . brahmANaM tvAM zatakratumUrdhvaM khamiva menire .
mUrtI hi te mahAmUrte samudrAmbarasaMnibhA sarvA vai devatA hyasmin gAvo goSTha ivAsate .
bhavaccharIre pazyAmi somamagni jalezvaram . Adityamatha vai viSNuM brahmANaM ca bRhaspatim .
bhagavAn kAraNaM kArya kriyA karaNameva ca . asatazca satazcaiva tathaiva prabhavApyayau .
namo bhavAya zarvAya rudrAya varadAya ca . pazUnAM pataye nityaM namo ' stvandhakaghAtine .
trijaTAya trizIrSAya trizUlavarapANine . tryambakAya trinetrAya tripuranAya vai namaH .
namazcaNDAya kuNDAya aNDAyANDadharAya ca . daNDine samakarNAya daNDimuNDAya vai namaH .
namordhvadaMSTrakezAya zuklAyAvatatAya ca . vilohitAya dhUmrAya nIlagrIvAya vai namaH .
namo ' stvapratirUpAya virUpAya zivAya ca . sUryAya sUryamAlAya sUryadhvajapatAkine .
namaH pramathanAthAya vRSaskandhAya dhanvine . zabUMdamAya daNDAya parNacIrapaTAya ca .
namo hiraNyagarbhAya hiraNyakavacAya ca . hiraNyakRtacUDAya hiraNyapataye namaH .
namaH stutAya stutyAya stUyamAnAya vai namaH . sarvAya sarvabhakSAya sarvabhUtAntarAtmane .
namo ho . ' tha mantrAya zukladhvajapatAkine . namo nAbhAya nAbhyAya namaH kaTakaTAya ca .
namo ' stu kRzanAsAya kRzAGgAya kRzAya ca . saMhRSTAya vihRSTAya namaH kilakilAya ca .
namo ' stu zayamAnAya zayitAyotthitAya ca . sthitAya dhAvamAnAya muNDAya jaTilAya ca .
namo nartanazIlAya mukhavAditravAdine . nAdyopahAralubdhAya gItavAditrazAline .
namo jyeSThAya zreSThAya balapramathanAya ca . kAlanAthAya kalyAya kSayAyopakSayAya ca .
bhImadundubhihAsAya bhImavratadharAya ca . ugrAya ca namo nityaM namo ' stu dazabAhave .
namaH kapAlahastAya citibhasmapriyAya ca . vibhISaNAya bhISmAya bhImavratadharAya ca .
namo vikRtavaktrAya khagajihvAya daMSTriNe . pakvAmamAMsalubdhAya tumbIvINApriyAya ca .
namo vRSAya vRSyAya govRSAya vRSAya ca . kaTaMkaTAya daNDAya namaH pacapacAya ca .
namaH sarvavariSThAya varAya varadAya ca . varamAlyagandhavastrAya varAtivarade namaH .
