AcArAd vardhate hyAyurAcAro hantyalakSaNam . AgamAnAM hi sarveSAmAcAraH zreSTha ucyate .
AcAraprabhavo dharmo dharmAdAyurvivardhate . etad yazasyamAyuSyaM svayaM svastyayanaM mahat . anukampya sarvavarNAn brahmaNA samudAhRtam .
yudhiSThira uvAca pitAmaha mahAprAjJa saMzayo me mahAnayam . saMchettavyastvayA rAjan bhavAn kulakaro hi naH .
puruSANAmayaM tAta durvRttAnAM durAtmanAm . kathito vAkyasaMcArastato vijJApayAmi te .
yaddhitaM rAjyatantrasya kulasya ca sukhodayam . AyatyAM ca tadAtve ca kSemavRddhikaraM ca yat . putrapautrAbhirAmaM ca rASTravRddhikaraM ca yat . annapAne zarIre ca hitaM yattad bravIhi me .
abhiSikto hi yo rAjA rASTrastho mitrasaMvRtaH . sasuhRtsamupeto vA sa kathaM rajayet prajAH .
yo hyasatpragraharatiH sneharAgabalAtkRtaH . indriyANAmanIzatvAdasajjanabubhUSakaH . tasya bhRtyA viguNatAM yAnti sarve kulodgatAH . na ca bhRtyaphalairathaiH sa rAjA samprayujyate .
etanme saMzayasyAsya rAjadharmAn sudurvidAn . bRhaspatisamo buddhyA bhavAn zaMsitumarhati .
zaMsitA puruSavyAghra tvannaH kulahite rataH . kSattA caiko mahAprAjJo yo naH zaMsati sarvadA .
tvattaH kulahitaM vAkyaM zrutvA rAjyahitodayam . amRtasyAvyayasyeva tRptaH svapsyAmyahaM sukham .
kIdRzAH saMnikarSasthA bhRtyAH sarvaguNAnvitAH . kIdRzaiH kiM kulInairvA saha yAtrA vidhIyate .
na hyeko bhRtyarahito rAjA bhavati rakSitA . rAjyaM cedaM janaH sarvastatkulIno ' bhikAGkSati .
bhISma uvAca na ca prazAstuM rAjyaM hi zakyamekena bhArata . asahAyavatA tAta naivArthAH kecidapyuta . labdhuM labdhA hyapi sadA rakSituM bharatarSabha .
yasya bhRtyajana : sarvo jJAnavijJAnakovidaH . hitaiSI kulajaH snigdhaH sa rAjyaphalamaznute .
mantriNo yasya kulajA asaMhAryAH sahoSitAH . nRpatermatidAH santaH sambandhajJAnakovidAH . anAgatavidhAtAra : kAlajJAnavizAradAH . atikrAntamazocantaH sa rAjyaphalama znute .
samaduHkhasukhA yasya sahAyAH priyakAriNaH . arthacintAparAH satyAH sa rAjyaphalamaznute .
janapadaH saMnikarSagataH sadA . akSudraH satpathAlambI sa rAjA rAjyabhAgbhavet . yasya nArto
kozAkhyapaTalaM yasya kozavRddhikarairnaraiH . AptaistuSTaizca satataM cIyate sa nRpottamaH .
koSThAgAramasaMhAvairAptaiH saMcayatatparaiH . pAtrabhUtairalubdhaizca pAlyamAnaM guNI bhavet .
vyavahArazca nagare yasya karmaphalodayaH . dRzyate zaMkhalikhitaH sa dharmaphalabhAG nRpaH .
saMgRhItamanuSyazca yo rAjA rAjadharmavit . SaDvargaM pratigRhNAti sa dharmaphalamaznute .
yudhiSThira uvAca dharmAdharmavimuktaM yad vimuktaM sarvasaMzayAt . janmamRtyuvimuktaM ca vimuktaM puNyapApayoH . yacchivaM nityamabhayaM nityamakSaramavyayam . zuci nityamanAyAsaM tad bhavAn vaktumarhati .
bhISma uvAca atra te vartayiSyAmi itihAsaM purAtanam . yAjJavalkyasya saMvAdaM janakasya ca bhArata . yAjJavalkyamRSizreSThaM daivarAtirmahAyazAH . papraccha janako rAjA prazna praznavidAM varam .
janaka uvAca katIndriyANi viprarSe kati prakRtayaH smRtAH . kimavyaktaM paraM brahma tasmAcca paratastu kim . prabhavaM cApyayaM caiva kAlasaMkhyAM tathaiva ca . vaktumarhasi viprendra tvadanugrahakAGkSiNaH .
ajJAnAt paripRcchAmi tvaM hi jJAnamayonidhiH . tadahaM zrotumicchAmi sarvametadasaMzayam .
yAjJavalkya uvAca zrUyatAmavanIpAla yadetadanupRcchasi . yogAnAM paramaM jJAnaM sAMkhyAnAM ca vizeSataH .
na tavAviditaM kiMcinmAM tu jijJAsate bhavAn . pRSTena cApi vaktavyameSa dharmaH sanAtanaH .
aSTau prakRtayaH proktA vikArAzcApi SoDaza . tatra tu prakRtIraSTau prAhuradhyAtmacintakAH .
avyaktaM ca mahAntaM ca tathAhaGkAra eva ca . pRthivI vAyurAkAzamApo jyotizca paJcamam . etAH prakRtayastvaSTau vikArAnapi me zRNu . zrotraM tvakcaiva cakSuzca jihvA ghrANaM ca paJcamam . zabdaH sparzaca rUpaM ca raso gandhastathaiva ca . vAk ca hastau ca pAdau ca pAyurmedraM tathaiva ca .
ete vizeSA rAjendra mahAbhUteSu paJcasu . buddhIndriyANyathaitAni savizeSANi maithila .
manaH SoDazakaM prAhuradhyAtmagaticintakAH . tvaM caivAnye ca vidvAMsastattvabuddhivizAradAH .
avyaktAcca mahAnAtmA samutpadyati pArthiva . prathamaM sargamityetadAhuH prAdhAnikaM budhAH .
mahatazcApyahaGkAra utpanno hi narAdhipa . dvitIyaM sargamityAhuretad buddhyAtmakaM smRtam .
ahaGkArAcca sambhUtaM mano bhUtaguNAtmakam . tRtIyaH sarga ityeSa AhaGkArika ucyate .
manasastu samudbhUtA mahAbhUtA narAdhipa . caturthaM sargamityetanmAnasaM viddhi me matam .
zabdaH sparzazca rUpaM ca raso gandhastathaiva ca . paJcamaM sargamityAhubhautikaM bhUtacintakAH .
cakSuzca jihvA ghrANaM ca paJcamam . sargaM tu SaSThamityAhurbahucintAtmakaM smRtam .
adhaH zrotrendriyagrAma utpadyati narAdhipa . saptamaM sargamityAhuretadaindriyakaM smRtam .
zrotraM tva tvak caiva UrdhvaM srotastathA tiryagutpadyati narAdhipa . aSTamaM sargamityAhuretadArjavakaM smRtam .
tiryasrotastvadhaHsrota utpadyati narAdhipa . navamaM sargamityAhuretadArjavakaM budhAH .
etAni nava sargANi tattvAni ca narAdhipa . caturviMzatiruktAni yathAzrutinidarzanAt .
ata UrdhvaM mahArAja guNasyaitasya tattvataH . mahAtmabhiranuproktAM kAlasaMkhyAM nibodha me .
arjuna uvAca tato nivAtakavacAH sarve vegena bhArata . abhyadravan mAM sahitAH pragRhItAyudhA raNe . .
AcchAdya sthapanthAnamutkrozanto mahArathAH . AvRtya sarvataste mAM zaravarSairavAkiran . .
tato ' pare mahAvIryAH zUlapaTTizapANayaH . zUlAni ca bhuzuNDIzca mumucurdAnavA mayi .
tacchUlavarSa sumahad gadAzaktisamAkulam . anizaM sRjyamAnaM tairapatanmadrathopari .
anye mAmabhyadhAvanta nivAtakavacA yudhi . zitazastrAyudhA raudrAH kAlarUpAH prahAriNaH .
tAnahaM vividhairbANairvegavadbhirajihmagaiH . gANDIvamuktairabhyanamekaikaM dazabhirmadhe .
te kRtA vimukhAH sarve matprayuktaiH zilAzitaiH . tato mAtalinA tUrNaM hayAste sampracoditAH .
mArgAn bahuvidhAMstatra vicerurvAtaraMhasaH . susaMyatA mAtalinA prAmananta diteH sutAn .
zataM zatAste harayastasmin yuktA mahArathe . zAntA mAtalinA yattA vyacarannalpakA iva .
teSAM caraNapAtena sthanemisvanena ca . mama bANanipAtaizca hatAste zatazo ' surAH .
gatAsavastathaivAnye pragRhItazarAsanAH . hatasArathayastatra vyakRSyanta turaMgamaiH .
te dizo vidizaH sarve pratirudhya prahAriNaH . abhyaghnan vividhaiH zastraistato me vyathitaM manaH .
tato ' haM mAtaleauryamapazyaM paramAdbhutam . azvAMstathA vegavato yadayatnAdadhArayat .
tato ' haM laghubhizcitrairastraistAnasurAn raNe . ciccheda sAyudhAn rAjan zatazo ' tha sahasrazaH .
evaM me caratastatra sarvayatnena zatruhan . prItimAnabhavad vIro mAtaliH zakrasArathiH .
vadhyamAnAstatastaistu hayaistena rathena ca . agaman prakSayaM kecitryavartanta tathA pare . spardhamAnA ivAsmAbhirnivAtakavacA raNe . zaravarSeH zarArtaM mAM mahadbhiH pratyavArayan .
tato ' haM laghubhizcitrairbrahmAstraparimantritaiH . vyadharma sAyakairAzu zatazo ' tha sahasrazaH .
tataH sampIDayamAnAste krodhAviSTA mahArathAH . apIDayan mAM sahitAH zarazUlAsivRSTibhiH .
tato ' hamastramAtiSThaM paramaM tigmataijasam . dayitaM devarAjasya mAdhavaM nAma bhArata .
tataH khaGgAstrizUlAMzca tomarAMzca sahasrazaH . astravIryeNa zatadhA tairmuktAnahamacchidam .
chittvA praharaNAnyeSAM tatastAnapi sarvazaH . pratyavidhyamahaM roSAd dazabhirdazabhiH zaraiH .
gANDIvAddhi tadA saMkhye yathA bhramarapaktayaH . niSpatanti mahAbANAstanmAtalirapUjayat .
teSAmapi tu bANAste tanmAtalirapUjayat . avAkiran mAM balavat tAnahaM vyadhamaM zaraiH .
vadhyamAnAstataste tu nivAtakavacAH punaH . zaravarSairmahadbhirmAM samantAt paryavArayan .
zaravegAnihatyAhamastrairastraivighAtibhiH . jvaladbhiH paramaiH zI .stAnavidhyaM sahasrazaH .
teSAM chinnAni gAtrANi visRjanti sma zoNitam . prAvRSIvAbhivRSTAni zRGgANyathadharAbhRtAm .
indrAzanisamasparzarvegavadbhirajihmagaiH . madbANairvadhyamAnAste samudvignAH sma dAnavAH .
zatadhA bhinnadehAste kSINapraharaNaujasaH . tato nivAtakavacA mAmayudhyanta mAyayA .
vaizampAyana uvAca vasatsu vai dvaitavane pANDaveSu mahAtmasu . anukIrNaM mahAraNyaM brAhmaNaiH samapadyata .
IryamANena satataM brahmaghoSeNa sarvazaH . brahmalokasamaM puNyamAsId dvaitavanaM saraH .
yajuSAmRcAM sAmnAM ca gadyAnAM caiva sarvazaH . AsIduccAryamANAnAM ni : svano hRdayaGgamaH .
jyAghoSazcaiva pArthAnAM brahmaghoSazcadhImatAm . saMsRSTaM brahmaNA kSatraM bhUya eva vyarocat .
athAbravId bako dAlabhyodharmarAja yudhiSThiram . sadhyAM kaunteyamAsInamRSibhiH parivAritam .
pazya dvaitavane pArtha brAhmaNAnAM tapasvinAm . homavelAM kuruzreSTha samprajvalitapAvakAm .
carantidharmaM puNye ' smiMstvayA guptAdhRtavratAH . bhRgavo ' Ggirasazcaiva vAsiSThAH kAzyapaiH saha . AgastyAzca mahAbhAgA AtreyAzcottamavratAH . sarvasya jagataH zreSThA brAhmaNAH saMgatAstvayA . .
idaM tu vacanaM pArtha zRNuSva gadato mama . bhrAtRbhiH saha kaunteya yat tvA vakSyAmi kaurava .
brahma kSatreNa saMsRSTaM kSatraM ca brahmaNA saha . udIrNe dahataH zatrUn vanAnIvAgnimArutau .
dicchannimaM lokamamuM ca jetum . vinItadharmArthamapetamohaM labdhvA dvijaM nudati nRpaH sapatnAn .
caran naiHzreyasaMdharma prajApAlanakAritam . nAdhyagacchad balilaki tIrthamanyatra vai dvijAt .
vairocaneH zrIrapi cAkSayA ' ' sIt . labvA mahIM brAhmaNasamprayogAt teSvAcaran duSTamatho vyanazyat .
varNaM dvitIyaM bhajate cirAya . samudraneminamate tu tasmai yaM brAhmaNaH zAsti nayairvinItam .
kuJjarasyeva saMgrAme parigRhyAGkuzagraham . brAhmaNairviprahINasya kSatrasya kSIyate balam .
brAhmaNyanupamA dRSTiH kSAtramapratimaM balam . tau yadA carataH sArdhaM tadA lokaH prasIdati .
yathA hi sumahAnagniH kakSaM dahati sAnilaH . tathA dahati rAjanyo brAhmaNena samaM ripum .
brAhmaNeSveva medhAvI buddhiparyeSaNaM caret . alabdhasya ca lAbhAya labdhasya parivRddhaye .
alabdhalAbhAya ca labdhavRddhaye yathArhatIrthapratipAdanAya yazasvinaM vedavidaM vipazcitaM bahuzrutaM brAhmaNameva vAsaya .
brAhmaNeSUttamA vRttistava nityaM yudhiSThira . tena te sarvalokeSu dIpyate prathitaM yazaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tataste brAhmaNAH sarve bakaM dAlbhyamapUjayan . yudhiSThire stUyamAne bhUyaH sumanaso ' bhavan .
dvaipAyano nAradazca jAmadagnyaH pRthuzravAH . indradyumno bhAlukizca kRtacetAH sahasrapAt . karNazravAzca muJjazca lavaNAzvazca kAzyapaH . hArItaH sthUNakarNazca agnivezyo ' tha zaunakaH . kRtavAk ca suvAk caiva bRhadazvo vibhAvasuH . Urdhvareto vRSAmitraH suhotro hotravAhanaH . ete cAnye ca bahavo brAhmaNAH saMzitavrataH . ajAtazatrumAnacuH puraMdaramivarSayaH .
kuntyuvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . vidulAyAzca saMvAdaM putrasya ca paraMtapa .
atra zreyazca bhUyazca yathAvad vaktumarhasi . yazasvinI manyumatI kule jAtA vibhAvarI .
kSatradharmaratA dAntA vidulA dIrghadarzinI . vizrutA rAjasaMsatsu zrutavAkyA bahuzrutA . .
vidulA nAma rAjanyA jagaheM putramaurasam . nirjitaM sindhurAjena zayAnaM dInacetasam .
vidulovAca anandana mayA jAta dviSatAM harSavardhana . na mayA tvaM na pitrA ca jAtaH kvAbhyAgato hyasi .
nirmanyuzcApyasaMkhyeyaH puruSaH klIbasAdhanaH . yAvajjIvaM nirAzo ' si kalyANAya dhuraM vaha .
mA ' ' tmAnamavamanyasva mainamalpena bIbharaH . manaH kRtvA sukalyANaM mA bhaistvaM pratisaMhara .
uttiSTha he kApuruSa mA zeSvaivaM parAjitaH . amitrAn nandayan sarvAn nirmAno bandhuzokadaH .
supUrA vai kunadikA supUro mUSikAJjaliH . susaMtoSaH kApuruSaH svalpakenaiva tuSyati .
apyaherArujan daMSTrAmAzveva nidhanaM vrajA api vA saMzayaM prApya jIvite ' pi parAkramaH .
apyareH zyenavacchidraM pazyestvaM viparikraman . vivadan vAthavA tUSNIM vyomni vAparizaGkitaH .
tvamevaM pretavaccheghe kasmAd vajrahato yathA . uttiSTha he kApuruSa mA svApsIH zatrunirjitaH .
mAstaM gamastvaM kRpaNo vizrUyasva svakarmaNA . mA madhye mA jaghanye tvaM mA ' dho bhUstiSTha garjitaH .
alAtaM tindukasyeva muhUrtamapi vijvala . mA tuSAgnirivAna—imAyasva jijIviSuH .
muhUrtaM jvalitaM zreyo na ca dhUmAyitaM ciram . mA ha sma kasyacid gehe jani rAjJaH kharo mRduH .
kRtvA mAnuSyakaM karma sRtvAjiM yAvaduttamam . dharmasyAnRNyamApnoti na cAtmAnaM vigarhate .
alabvA yadi vA labdhvA nAnuzocati paNDitaH . AnantaryaM cArabhate na prANAnAM dhanAyate .
udbhAvayasva vIryaM vA tAM vA gaccha dhruvAM gatim . dharma putrAgrataH kRtvA kiMnimittaM hi jIvasi .
iSTApUrtaM hi te klIba kIrtizca sakalA hatA . vicchinnaM bhogamUlaM te kiMnimittaM hi jIvasi .
zatrurnimajjatA grAhyo javAyAM prapatiSyatA . viparicchinnamUlo ' pi na viSIdet kathaMcana .
udyamya dhuramutkarSedAjAneyakRtaM smaran . kuru sattvaM ca mAnaM ca viddhi pauruSamAtmanaH .
udbhAvaya kulaM magnaM tvatkRte svayameva hi . yasya vRttaM na jalpanti mAnavA mahadadbhutam .
rAzivardhanamAtraM sa naiva strI na punaH pumAn . dAne tapasi satye ca yasya noccaritaM yazaH .
vidyAyAmarthalAbhe vA mAturuccAra eva saH . zrutena tapasA vApi zriyA vA vikrameNa vA .
janAn yo ' bhibhavatyanyAn karmaNA hi sa vai pumAn . na tveva jAlpI kApAlI vRttimeSitumarhasi .
nRzaMsyAmayazasyAM ca duHkhAM kApuruSocitAm . yamenamabhinandeyuramitrAH puruSaM kRzam .
lokasya samavajJAtaM nihInAsanavAsasam . aho lAbhakara hInamalpajIvanamalpakam .
nedRzaM bandhumAsAdya bAndhavaH sukhamedhate . avRttyaiva vipatsyAmo vayaM rASTrAt pravAsitAH .
sarvakAmarasaiIMnAH sthAnabhraSTA akiMcanAH . avalgukAriNaM satsu kulavaMzasya nAzanam .
kaliM putrapravAdena saMjaya tvAmajIjanam . niramarSaM nirutsAhaM nirvIryamarinandanam .
mA sma sImantinI kAcijjanayet putramIdRzam . mA dhUmAya jvalAtyantamAkramya jahi zAtravAn .
jvala mUrdhanyamitrANAM muhUrtamapi vA kSaNam . etAvAneva puruSo yadamarSI yadakSamI .
kSamAvAn niramarSazca naiva strI na punaH pumAn . saMtoSo vai zriyaM hanti tathAnukroza eva ca .
anutthAnabhaye cobhe nirIho nAznute mahat . ebhyo nikRtipApebhyaH pramuJcAtmAnamAtmanA .
AyasaM hRdayaM kRtvA mRgayasva punaH svakam . paraM viSahate yasmAt tasmAt puruSa ucyate .
tamAhurvyarthanAmAnaM strIvad ya iha jIvati . zUrasyorjitasattvasya siMhavikrAntacAriNaH .
diSTabhAvaM gatasyApi viSaye modate prajA . ya AtmanaH priyasukhe hitvA mRgayate zriyam . amAtyAnAmatho harSamAdadhAtyacireNa saH .
putra uvAca kiM nu te mAmapazyantyAH pRthivyA api sarvayA . kimAbharaNakRtyaM te kiM bhogairjIvitena vA .
mAtovAca kimadyakAnAM ye lokA dviSantastAnavApnuyuH . ye tvAdRtAtmanAM lokAH suhRdastAn brajantu naH .
bhRtyaivihIyamAnAnAM parapiNDopajIvinAm . kRpaNAnAmasattvAnAM mA vRttimanuvartithAH .
anu tvAM tAta jIvantu brAhmaNAH suhRdastathA . parjanyamiva bhUtAni devA iva zatakratum .
yamAjIvanti puruSaM sarvabhUtAni saMjaya . pakvaM dumamivAsAdya tasya jIvitamarthavat .
yasya zUrasya vikrAntairedhante bAndhavAH sukham . tridazA iva zakrasya sAdhu tasyeha jIvitam .
svabAhubalamAzritya yo ' bhyujjIvati mAnavaH . sa loke labhate kIrti paratra ca zubhAM gatim .
saMjaya uvAca tato duryodhano rAjA zakunizcApi saubalaH . duHzAsanazca putraste sUtaputrazca durjayaH .
samAgamya mahArAja mantraM cakrurvivakSitam . kathaM pANDusutAH saMkhye jetavyAH sagaNA iti .
tato duryodhano rAjA sarvAMstAnAha mantriNaH . sUtaputraM samAbhASya saubalaM ca mahAbalam .
droNo bhISmaH kRpaH zalyaH saumadattizca saMyuge . na pArthAn pratibAdhante na jAne tacca kAraNam .
avadhyamAnAste cApi kSapayanti balaM mama . so ' smi kSINabalaH karNa kSINazastrazca saMyuge . nikRtaH pANDavaiH zUrairavadhyairdaivatairapi .
so ' haM saMzayamApannaH prahariSye kathaM raNe . tamabravInmahArAjaM sUtaputro narAdhipam .
karNa uvAca mA zoca bharatazreSTha kariSye ' haM priyaM tava . . bhISmaH zAntavastUrNamapayAtu mahAraNAt .
nivRtte yudhi gAGgeye nyastazastre ca bhArata . ahaM pArthAn haniSyAmi sahitAn sarvasomakaiH .
pazyato yudhi bhISmasya zape satyena te nRpa . pANDaveSu dayAM nityaM sa hi bhISmaH karoti vai .
azaktazca raNe bhISmo jetumetAn mahArathAn . . abhimAnI raNe bhISmo nityaM cApi raNapriyaH .
sa kathaM pANDavAn yuddhe jeSyate tAtaM saMgatAn . sa tvaM zIghramito gatvA bhISmasya zibiraM prati .
anumAnya guruM vRddhaM zastraM nyAsaya bhArata . nyastazastre tato bhISme nihatAn pazya pANDavAn .
mayaikena raNe rAjan sasuhRdgaNabAndhavAn . evamuktastu karNena putro duryodhanastava . abravId bhrAtaraM tatra duHzAsanamidaM vacaH .
anuyAtraM yathA sarvaM sajjIbhavati sarvazaH . duHzAsana tathA kSipraM sarvamevopapAdaya . evamuktvA tato rAjan karNamAha janezvaraH . anumAnya raNe bhISmameSo ' haM dvipadAM varam .
AgamiSye tataH kSipraM tvatsakAzamariMdam . apakrAnte tato bhISme prahariSyasi saMyuge .
niSpapAta tatastUrNaM putrastava vizAmpate . sahito bhrAtRbhistaistu devairiva zatakratuH .
tatastaM nRpazArdUlaM zArdUlasamavikramam . ArohayaddhayaM tUrNaM bhrAtA duHzAsanastadA . aGgadI baddhamukuTo hastAbharaNavAn nRpa . dhArtarASTro mahArAja vibabhau sa pathi vrajan .
bhaNDIpuSpanikAzena tapanIyanibhena ca . anuliptaH parAddhyana candanena sugandhinA . arajo ' mbarasaMvItaH siMhakhelagatirnRpa . zuzubhe vimalArciSmAn nabhasIva divAkaraH . taM prayAntaM naravyAghraM bhISmasya zibiraM prati . anujagmurmaheSvAsAH sarvalokasya dhanvinaH .
bhrAtarazca maheSvAsAstridazA iva vAsavam . hayAnanye samAruhya gajAnanye ca bhArata .
rathAnanye narazreSThaM parivaH samantataH . AttazastrAzca suhRdo rakSaNArthaM mahIpateH .
prAdurbabhUvuH sahitAH zakrasyevAmarA divi . sa pUjyamAnaH kurubhiH kauravANAM mahAbalaH .
prayayau sadanaM rAjA gAGgeyasya yazasvinaH . anvIyamAnaH satataM sodaraiH parivAritaH .
