na mAmarhasi dharmajJa vaktumevaM kathaMcanA dharmapatnImabhiratAM tvayi rAjIvalocane .
tvameva tu mahAbAho mayyapatyAni bhArata . vIra vIryopapannAni dharmato janayiSyasi .
svargaM manujazArdUla gaccheyaM sahitA tvayA . apatyAya ca mAM gaccha tvameva kurunandana . .
na hyahaM manasApyanyaM gaccheyaM tvadRte naram . tvattaH prativiziSTazca ko ' nyo ' sti bhuvi mAnavaH .
imAM ca tAvad dharmAtman paurANIM zRNu me kathAm . parizrutAM vizAlAkSa kIrtayiSyAmi yAmaham .
vyuSitAzva iti khyAto babhUva kila pArthivaH . purA paramadharmiSThaH pUrorvaMzavivardhanaH .
tasmiMzca yajamAne vai dharmAtmani mahAbhuje . upAgamastato devAH sendrA devarSibhiH saha .
amAdyadindraH somena dakSiNAbhirdvijAtayaH . vyuSitAzvasya rAjarSestato yajJe mahAtmanaH . devA brahmarSayazcaiva cakruH karma svayaM tadA . vyuSitAzvastato rAjannati mAn vyarocata .
sarvabhUtAn prati yathA tapana : zizirAtyaye . sa vijitya gRhItvA ca nRpatIn rAjasattamaH . prAcyAnudIcyA pAzcAnyAn dAkSiNAtyAnakAlayat . azvamedhe mahAyajJe vyuSitAzvaH pratApavAn .
babhUva sa hi rAjendro dazanAgabalAnvitaH . apyatra gAthAM gAyanti ye purANavido janAH . vyuSitAzve yazovRddha manuSyendre kurUttama . vyuSitAzvaH samudrAntAM vijityemAM vasuMdharAm . apAlayat sarvavarNAn pitA putrAnivaurasAn . yajamAno mahAyajJairbrAhmaNebhyo dhanaM dadau .
anantaratnAnyAdAya sa jahAra mahAkratUn . suSAva ca bahUn somAn somasaMsthAstatAna ca .
AsIt kAkSIvatI cAsya bhAryA paramasammatA . bhadrA nAma manuSyendra rUpeNAsadRzI bhuvi .
kAmayAmAsatustau ca parasparamiti zrutam . sa tasyAM kAmasampanno yakSmaNA samapadyata . tenAcireNa kAlena jagAmAstamivAMzumAn . tasmin prete manuSyendre bhAryAsya bhRzaduHkhitA .
aputrA puruSavyAghra vilalApeti naH zrutam . bhadrA paramaduHkhArtA tannibodha janAdhipa .
bhadrovAca nArI paramadharmajJa sarvA bhartRvinAkRtA . patiM vinA jIvati yA na sA jIvati duHkhitA .
patiM vinA mRtaM zreyo nAryAH kSatriyapuGgava . tvadgatiM gantumicchAmi prasIdasva nayasva mAm . tvayA hInA kSaNamapi nAhaM jIvitumutsahe . prasAdaM kuru me rAjanitastUrNaM nayasva mAm .
pRSThato ' nugamiSyAmi sameSu viSameSu ca . tvAmahaM narazArdUla gacchantamanivartitum .
chAyevAnugatA rAjan satataM vazavartinI . bhaviSyAmi naravyAghra nityaM priyahite ratA .
adyaprabhRti mAM rAjan kaSTA hRdayazoSaNaH . Adhayo ' bhibhaviSyanti tvAmRte puSkarekSaNa .
abhAgyayA mayA nUnaM viyuktAH sahacAriNaH . tena me viprayogo ' yamupapannastvayA saha .
viprayuktA tu yA patyA muhUrtamapi jIvati . duHkhaM jIvati sA pApA narakasyeva pArthiva .
saMyuktA viprayuktAzca pUrvadehe kRtA mayA . tadidaM karmabhiH pApaiH pUrvadeheSu saMcitam . duHkhaM mAmanusamprAptaM rAjaMstvadviprayogajam . adyaprabhRtyahaM rAjan kuzasaMstarazAyinI . bhaviSyAmyasukhAviSTA tvadarzanaparAyaNA .
darzayasva naravyAghra zAdhi mAmasukhAnvitAm . kRpaNAM cAtha karuNaM vilapantI narezvara .
kunyuvAca evaM bahuvidhaM tasyAM vilapantyAM punaH punaH . taM zavaM sampariSvajya vAk kilAntarhitAbravIt .
uttiSTha bhadre gaccha tvaM dadAnIha varaM tava . janayiSyAmyapatyAni tvayyahaM cAruhAsini .
AtmakIye varArohe zayanIye caturdazIm . aSTamI vA RtusnAtA saMvizethA mayA saha .
evamuktA tu sA devI tathA cakre pativratA . yathoktameva tadvAkyaM bhadrA putrArthinI tadA .
sA tena suSave devI zavena bharatarSabha . trIn zAlvAMzcaturo madrAn sutAn bharatasattama .
tathA tvamapi mayyevaM manasA bharatarSabha . zakto janayituM putrAMstapoyogabalAnvitaH .
vaizampAyana uvAca tasmin dazArhAdhitau prayAte yudhiSThiro bhImasenArjunau ca . yamau ca kRSNA ca purohitazca rathAn mahArhAn paramAzvayuktAn . AsthAya vIrAH sahitA vanAya pratasthire bhUtapatiprakAzAH . hiraNyaniSkAn vasanAni gAzca pradAya zikSAkSaramantravidyaH .
preSyAH puro viMzatirAttazastrA dhanUMSi zastrANi zarAMzca dIptAn . maurvIzca yantrANi ca sAyaMkAzca sarve samAdAya jaghanyamIyuH .
tatastu vAsAMsi ca rAjaputryA dhAtryazca dAsyazca vibhUSaNaM ca . tadindrasenastvaritaH pragRhya jaghanyamevopayayau rathena .
tataH kuruzreSThamupetya paurAH pradakSiNaM cakruradInasattvAH . taM brAhmaNAzcAbhyavadan prasannA mukhyAzca sarve kurujADulAnAm .
sa cApi tAnabhyavadat prasanna : sahaiva tairdhAtRbhirdharmarAjaH . tasthau ca tatrAdhipatirmahAtmA dRSTvA janaughaM kurujAGgalAnAm .
piteva putreSu sa teSu bhAvaM cakre kurUNAmRSabho mahAtmA . te cApi tasmin bharatapravardai tadA babhUvuH pitarIva putrAH .
tatastamAsAdya mahAjanaughAH kurupravIraM parivArya tasthuH . hA nAtha hAdharma iti bruvANA bhItAzca sarve ' zrumukhAzca rAjan .
varaH kurUNAmadhipaH prajAnAM piteva putrAnapahAya cAsmAn . paurAnimAJjAnapadAMzca sarvAn hitvA prayAtaH kva nudharmarAjaH .
dhigdhArtarASTra sunRzaMsabuddhiM dhik saubalaM pApamatiM ca karNam . anarthamicchanti narendra pApA yedharmanityasya satastavaivam .
svayaM nivezyApratimaM mahAtmA puraM mahAdevapuraprakAzam . zatakratuprasthamameyakarmA hitvA prayAtaH kva nudharmarAjaH .
cakAra yAmapratimAM mahAtmA sabhA mayo devasabhAprakAzAm . tAM devaguptAmiva devamAyAM hitvA prayAtaH kva nudharmarAjaH .
tAndharmakAmArthaviduttamaujA bIbhatsuruccaiH sahitAnuvAca . AdAsyate vAsamimaM niruSya vaneSu rAjA dviSatAM yazAMsi .
dvijAtimukhyAH sahitAH pRthak ca bhavadbhirAsAdya tapasvinazca . prasAdyadharmArthavidazca vAcyA yathArthasiddhiH paramA bhavetraH .
ityevamukte vacane ' rjunena brAhmaNAH sarvavarNAzca rAjan . mudAbhyanandana sahitAzca cakruH pradakSiNadharmabhRtAM variSTham . te
Amantrya pArthaM ca vRkodaraM ca dhanaMjayaM yAjJasenI yamau ca . pratasthire rASTramapetaharSA yudhiSThireNAnumatA yathAsvam .
zrIbhagavAnuvAca bhAvaM jijJAsamAno ' haM praNayAdidamabruvam . na caukSepAnna pANDityAna krodhAnna vivakSayA .
vedAhaM tava mAhAtmyamuta te veda yad balam . uta te veda karmANi na tvAM paribhavAmyaham .
yathA cAtmani kalyANaM sambhAvayasi pANDava . sahasraguNamapyetat tvayi sambhAvayAmyaham .
yAdRze ca kule janma sarvarAjAbhipUjite . bandhumizca suhRddhizca bhIma tvamasi tAdRzaH .
jijJAsanto hi dharmasya saMdigdhasya vRkodara . paryAyaM nAdhyavasyanti devamAnuSayorjanAH .
sa eva heturbhutvA hi puruSasyArthasiddhiSu . vinAze ' pi sa evAsya saMdigdhaM karma pauruSam .
anyathA paridRSTAni kavibhirdoSadarzibhiH . anyathA parivartante vegA iva nabhasvataH .
sumantritaM sunItaM ca nyAyatazcopapAditam . kRtaM mAnuSyakaM karbha daivenApi visthyate .
daivamapyakRtaM karma pauruSeNa vihanyate . zItamuSNaM tathA varSaM kSutpipAse ca bhArata .
yadanyad diSTabhAvasya puruSasya svayaM kRtam . tasmAdanuparodhazca vidyate tatra lakSaNam .
lokasya nAnyato vRttiH pANDavAnyatra karmaNaH . evaMbuddhiH pravarteta phalaM syAdubhayAnvaye .
ya evaM kRtabuddhiH sa karmasveva pravartate . nAsiddho vyathate tasya na siddhau harSamaznute .
tatreyamanumAtrA me bhImasena vivakSitA . naikAntasiddhirvaktavyA zatrubhiH saha saMyuge .
nAtiprahINarazmiH syAt tathA bhAvaviparyaye . viSAdamached glAni vApyetamarthaM bravImi te .
zvobhUte dhRtarASTrasya samIpaM prApya pANDava . yatiSye prazamaM kartuM yuSmadarthamahApayan .
zamaM cet te kariSyanti tato ' nantaM yazomama . bhavatAM ca kRtaH kAmasteSAM ca zreya uttamam .
te cedabhinivekSyante nAbhyupaiSyanti me vacaH . kuravo yuddhamevAtra ghoraM karma bhaviSyati .
asmin yuddhe bhImasena tvayi bhAraH samAhitaH . dhUrarjunena dhAryA syAd voDhavya itaro janaH .
ahaM hi yantA bIbhatsorbhavitA saMyuge sati . dhanaMjayasyaiSa kAmo na hi yuddhaM na kAmaye .
tasmAdAzaGkamAno ' haM vRkodara matiM tavA gadataH klIbayA vAcA tejaste samadIdipam .
zaunaka uvAca purANamakhilaM tAta pitA te ' dhItavAnpurA . kaccittvamapi tatsarvamadhISe laumaharSaNe .
purANe hi kathA divyA AdivaMzAzca dhImatAm . kathyante ye purA ' smAbhiH zrutapUrvAH pitustava . .
caiva tato mayA . tatra vaMzamahaM pUrvaM zrotumicchAmi bhArgavam . kathayasva kathAmetAM kalyAH sma zravaNe tava .
sautiruvAca yadadhItaM purA samyak dvijazreSThairmahAtmabhiH . vaizaMpAyanaviprAyaistaizcApi kathitaM yathA .
yadadhItaM ca pitrA me samyak tAvacchRNuSva yo devaiH sendraiHsarSimarudgaNaiH . pUjitaH pravaro vaMzo bhArgavo bhRgunandana . imaM vaMzamahaM pUrvaM bhArgavaM te mahAmune .
nigadAmi yathAyuktaM purANAzrayasaMyutam . bhRgurmaharSirbhagavAn brahmaNA vai svayaMbhuvA . varuNasya kratau jAtaH pAvakAditi naH zrutam . bhRgoH sudayitaH putrazcyavano nAma bhArgavaH .
cyavanasya ca dAyAdaH pramatirnAma dhArmikaH . pramaterapyabhUtputro ghRtAcyAM rururityuta .
rurorapi suto jajJe zunako vedapAragaH . pramadvarAyAM dharmAtmA tava pUrvapitAmahaH .
tapasvI ca yazasvI ca zrutavAn brahmavittamaH . dhArmikaH satyavAdI ca niyato niyatAzanaH .
zaunaka uvAca sUtaputra yathA tasya bhArgavasya mahAtmanaH . cyavanatvaM parikhyAtaM tanmamAcakSva pRcchataH .
sautiruvAca bhRgoH sudayitA bhAryA pulometyabhivizrutA . tasyAM samabhavadgarbho bhRguvIryasamudbhavaH .
tasmin garbhe ' tha saMbhUte pulomAyAM bhRgUdvaha . samaye samazIlinyAM dharmapatnyAM yazasvinaH . abhiSekAya niSkrAnte bhRgau dharmabhRtAM vare . AzramaM tasya rakSo ' tha pulomAbhyAjagAma ha .
taM pravizyAzramaM dRSTvA bhRgorbhAryAmaninditAm . hRcchayena samAviSTo vicetAH samapadyata .
abhyAgataM tu tadrakSaH pulomA cArudarzanA . nyamantrayata vanyena phalamUlAdinA tadA .
tAM tu rakSastadA brahman hRcchayenAbhipIDitam . dRSTvA hRSTamabhUdrAjan jihIrSustAmaninditAm .
jAtamityabravItkAryaM jihIrSurmuditaH zubhAm . sA hi pUrvaM vRtA tena pulomnA tu zucismitA .
tAM tu prAdAtpitA pazcAd bhRgave zAstravattadA . tasya tatkilbiSaM nityaM hRdi vartati bhArgava .
idamantaramityevaM hartuM cakre manastadA . athAgnizaraNe ' pazyajjvalantaM jAtavedasam .
tamapRcchattato rakSaH pAvakaM jvalitaM tadA . zaMsa me kasya bhAryeyamagne pRcche Rtena vai .
mukhaM tvamasi devAnAM vada pAvaka pRcchate . mayA hIyaM vRtA pUrvaM bhAryArthe varavarNinI .
pazcAdimAM pitA prAdAddhagave ' nRtakArakaH . seyaM yadi varArohA bhRgorbhAryA rahogatA .
tathA satyaM samAkhyAhi jihIrSAmyAzramAdimAm . samanyustatra hRdayaM pradahanniva tiSThati . matpUrvAbhAryAM yadimAM bhRgurApa sumadhyamAm .
sautiruvAca evaM rakSastamAmantrya jvalitaM jAtavedasam . zaGkamAnaM bhRgorbhAryAM puna : punarapRcchata .
tvamagne ! sarvabhUtAnAmantazcarasi nityadA . sAkSivatpuNyapApeSu satyaM brUhi kave vacaH .
matpUrvA ' pahatA bhAryA bhRguNA ' nRtakAriNA . seyaM yadi tathA me tvaM satyamAkhyAtumarhasi .
zrutvA tvatto bhRgorbhAryAM hariSyAmyAzramAdimAm . jAtavedaH pazyataste vada satyAM giraM mama .
sautiruvAca tasyaitadvacanaM zrutvA saptAcirduHkhito ' bhavat . bhIto ' nRtAcca zApAcca bhRgorityabravIcchanaiH .
agniruvAca tvayA vRtA pulomeyaM pUrvaM dAnavanandana . kiM tviyaM vidhinA pUrvaM mantravana vRtA tvayA .
pitrA tu bhRgave dattA pulomeyaM yazasvinI . dadAti na pitA tubhyaM varalobhAnmahAyazAH .
athemAM vedadRSTena karmaNA vidhipUrvakam . bhAryAmRSi guH prApa mAM puraskRtya dAnava .
seyamityavagacchAmi nAnRtaM vaktumutsahe . nAnRtaM hi sadA loke pUjyate dAnavottama .
nArada uvAca hiraNyapuramityetat khyAt puravaraM mahat . daityAnAM dAnavAnAM ca mAyAzatavicAriNAm .
analpena prayatnena nirmitaM vizvakarmaNA . mayena manasA sRSTaM pAtAlatalamAzritam .
atra mAyAsahasrANi vikurvANA mahaujasaH . dAnavA nivasanti sma zUrA dattavarAH purA .
naite zakreNa nAnyena yamena varuNena vA . zakyante vazamAnetuM tathaiva dhanadena ca . .4 ! 
asurAH kAlakhaJjAzca tathA viSNupadodbhavAH . nairRtA yAtudhAnAzca brahmapAdodbhavAzca ye . daMSTriNo bhImavegAzca vAtavegaparAkramAH . mAyAvIryopasampannA nivasantyatra mAtale .
nivAtakavacA nAma dAnavA yuddhadurmadAH . jAnAsi ca yathA zakro naitAzaknoti bAdhitum .
bahuzo mAtale tvaM ca tava putrazca gomukhaH . nirbhagno devarAjazca sahaputraH zacIpatiH .
pazya vezmAni raukmANi mAtale rAjatAni ca . karmaNA vidhiyuktena yuktAnyupagatAni ca .
vaidUryamaNicitrANi pravAlarucirANi ca . arkasphaTikazubhrANi vajrasArojjvalAni ca . .
pArthivAnIva cAbhAnti padmarAgamayAni ca . zailAnIva ca dRzyante dAravANIva cApyuta .
sUryarUpANi cAbhAnti dIptAgnisadRzAni ca . maNijAlavicitrANi prAMzUni nibiDAni ca .
naitAni zakyaM nirdeSTuM rUpato dravyatastathA . guNatazcaiva siMddhAni pramANaguNavanti ca .
AkrIDAn pazya daityAnAM tathaiva zayanAnyuta . ratlavanti mahArhANi bhAjanAnyAsanAni ca .
jaladAbhAMstathA zailAMstoyaprasravaNAni ca . kAmapuSpaphalAMzcApi pAdapAn kAmacAriNaH .
mAtale kazcidatrApi ruciraste varo bhavet . athavAnyAM dizaM bhUmergacchAva yadi manyase .
mAtalistvabravIdenaM bhASamANaM tathAvidham . devarSe naiva me kArya vipriyaM tridivaukasAm .
nityAnuSaktavairA hi bhrAtaro devadAnavAH . parapakSaNa sambandhaM rocayiSyAmyahaM katham .
anyatra sAdhu gacchAva draSTuM nArhAmi dAnavAn . jAnAmi tava cAtmAnaM hiMsAtmakamanaM tathA .
mArkaNDeya uvAca upaviSTaM tu taM skandaM hiraNyakavacasrajam . hiraNyacUDamukuTaM hiraNyAkSaM mahAprabham .
lohitAmbarasaMvItaM tIkSNadaMSTra manoramam . sarvalakSaNasampannaM trailokyasyApi supriyam .
tatastaM varadaM zUraM yuvAnaM mRSTakuNDalam . abhajat padmarUpA zrIH svayameva zarIriNI .
zriyA juSTaH pRSuyazAH sa kumAravarastadA . niSaNNo dRzyate bhUtaiH paurNamAsyAM yathA zazI .
apUjayan mahAtmAno brAhmaNAstaM mahAbalam . idamAhustadA caiva skandaM tatra maharSayaH .
RSaya UcuH hiraNyagarbha bhadraM te lokAnAM zaGkaro bhava . tvayA SaDrAjajAtena sarve lokA vazIkRtAH .
abhayaM ca punardattaM tvayaivaiSAM surottamA tasmAdindro bhavAnastu trailokyasyAbhayaMkaraH .
skanda uvAca kimindraH sarvalokAnAM karotIha tapodhanAH . kathaM devagaNAMzcaiva pAti nityaM surezvaraH .
RSaya UcuH indro dadhAti bhUtAnAM balaM tejaH prajAH sukham . tuSTaH prayacchati tathA sarvAn kAmAn surezvaraH .
durvRttAnAM saMharati vratasthAnAM prayacchati . anuzAsti ca bhUtAni kAryeSu balasUdanaH . asUrye ca bhavet sUryastathAcandre ca candramAH . bhavatyagnizca vAyuzca pRthivyApazca kAraNaiH . etadindreNa kartavyamindre hi vipulaM balam . tvaM ca vIra balI zreSThastasmAdindro bhavasva naH .
zakra uvAca bhavasvendro mahAbAho sarveSAM naH sukhAvahaH . abhiSicyasva caivAdya prAptarUpo ' si sattama .
skanda uvAca zAdhi tvameva trailokyamavyaco vijaye rataH . ahaM te kiGkaraH zakra na mamendratvamIpsitam .
zakra uvAca balaM tavAdbhutaM vIra tvaM devAnAmarIn jahi . avajJAsyanti mAM lokA vIryeNa tava vismitAH .
indratve tu sthitaM vIra balahInaM parAjitam . Avayozca mitho bhede prayatiSyantyatandritAH . bhedite ca tvayi vibho loko dvaidhamupeSyati . dvidhAbhUteSu lokeSu nizciteSvAvayostathA .
vicahaH sampravarteta bhUtabhedAnmahAbala . tatra tvaM mAM raNe tAta yathAzraddhaM vijeSyasi . tasmAdindro bhavAneva bhavitA mA vicAraya .
skanda uvAca tvameva rAjA bhadraM te trailokyasya mamaiva ca . . karomi kiM ca te zakra zAsanaM tad bravIhi me .
indra uvAca ahamindro bhaviSyAmi tava vAkyAnmahAbala . . yadi satyamidaM vAkyaM nizcayAd bhASitaM tvayA . yadi vA zAsanaM skanda kartumicchasi me zRNu . abhiSicyasva devAnAM sainApatye mahAbalA
skanda uvAca dAnavAnAM vinAzAya devAnAmarthasiddhaye . gobrAhmaNahitArthAya sainApatye ' bhiSiJca mAm .
mArkaNDeya uvAca so ' bhiSikto maghavatA sarvairdevagaNaiH saha . atIva zuzubhe tatra pUjyamAno maharSibhiH . tatra tat kAJcanaM chatraM dhriyamANaM vyarocata . yathaiva susamiddhasya pAvakasyAtmamaNDalam .
vizvakarmakRtA cAsya divyA mAlA hiraNmayI . AbaddhA tripuraghnena svayameva yazasvinA . Agamya manujavyAghra saha devyA paraMtapa .
arcayAmAsa suprIto bhagavAn govRSadhvajaH . rudramagniM dvijAH prAhU rudrasUnustatastu saH .
rudreNa zukramutsRSTaM tacchveta : parvato ' bhavat . pAvakasyendriyaM zvete kRttikAbhiH kRtaM nage .
pUjyamAnaM tu rudreNa dRSTvA sarve divaukasaH . rudrasUnuM tataH prAhurguhaM guNavatAM varam .
anupravizya rudreNa vahni jAto hyayaM zizuH . tatra jAtastataH skando rudrasUnustato ' bhavat .
rudrasya vahnaH svAhAyAH SaNNAM strINAM ca bhArata . jAtaH skandaH surazreSTho rudrasUnustato ' bhavat .
araje vAsasI rakta vasAnaH pAvakAtmajaH . bhAti dIptavapuH zrImAn raktAbhrAbhyAmivAMzumAn . .
kukkuTazcAgninA dattastasya keturalaMkRtaH . rathe samucchrito bhAti kAlAgniriva lohitaH .
yA ceSTA sarvabhUtAnAM prabhA zAntirbalaM tathA . acatastasya sA zaktirdevAnAM jayavardhinI .
viveza kavacaM cAsya zarIre sahajaM tathA . yudhyamAnasya devasya prAdurbhavati tat sadA . zaktidharmo balaM tejaH kAntatvaM satyamunnatiH . brahmaNyatvamasammoho bhaktAnAM parirakSaNam . nikRntanaM ca zatrUNAM lokAnAM cAbhirakSaNam . skandena saha jAtAni sarvANyeva janAdhipa .
evaM devagaNaiH sarvaiH so ' bhiSiktaH svalaMkRtaH . babhau pratIta : sumanAH paripUrNendumaNDala DalaH .
iSTaiH svAdhyAyaghoSaizca devatUryavarairapi . devagandharvagItaizca sarvairapsarasAM gaNaiH .
etaizcAnyaizca bahubhistuSTairhaSTaiH svalaMkRtaiH . susaMvRtaH pizAcAnAM gaNairdevagaNaistathA . krIDan bhAti tadA devairabhiSiktazca pAvakiH . abhiSiktaM mahAsenamapazyanta divaukasaH . vinihatya tamaH sUryaM yathehAbhyuditaM tathA . athainamabhyayuH sarvA devasenAH sahasrazaH .
asmAkaM tvaM patiriti bruvANA : sarvato dizaH . tAH samAsAdya bhagavAn sarvabhUtagaNairvRtaH . arcitastu stutazcaiva sAntvayAmAsa tA api . zatakratuzcAbhiSicya skandaM senApati tadA .
sasmAra tAM devasenAM yA sA tena vimokSitA . ayaM tasyAH patirnUnaM vihito brahmaNA svayam . vicintyetyAnayAmAsa devasenAM hyalaMkRtAm . skandaM provAca balabhidiyaM kanyA surottama . ajAte tvayi nirdiSTA tva patnI svayambhuvA . tasmAt tvamasyA vidhivat pANi mantrapuraskRtam . gRhANa dakSiNaM devyAH pANinA padmavarcasA . evamuktaH sa jacAha tasyAH pANiM yathAvidhi .
bRhaspatirmantraviddhi jajApa ca juhAva ca . evaM skandasya mahiSIM devasenAM vidurjanAH .
SaSThI yAM brAhmaNAH prAhurlakSmImAzAM sukhapradAm . sinIvAlI kuhUM caiva savRttimaparAjitAm .
