nArAyaNaM namaskRtya naraM caiva narottamam . devI sarasvatI vyAsaM tato jayamudIrayet . .
janamejaya uvAca evaM vRSNyandhakakule zrutvA mausalamAhavam . pANDavAH kimakurvanta tathA kRSNe divaM gate .
vaizampAyana uvAca zrutvaivaM kauravo rAjA vRSNInAM kadanaM mahat . prasthAne matimAdhAya vAkyamarjunamabravIt . kAla : pacati bhUtAni sarvANyeva mahAmate . kAlapAzamahaM manye tvamapi draSTumarhasi .
ityuktaH sa tu kaunteyaH kAlaH kAla iti bruvan . anvapadyata tad vAkyaM bhrAturyeSThasya dhImataH .
arjunasya mataM jJAtvA bhImaseno yamau tathA . anvapadyanta tad vAkyaM yaduktaM savyasAcinA .
tato yuyutsumAnAyya pravrajan dharmakAmyayA . rAjyaM paridadau sarvaM vaizyAputre yudhiSThiraH .
abhiSicya svarAjye ca rAjAnaM ca parikSitam . duHkhArtazcAbravId rAjA subhadrA pANDavAgrajaH . eSa putrasya putraste kururAjo bhaviSyati . yadUnAM parizeSazca vajro rAjA kRtazca ha .
parikSiddhAstinapure zakraprasthe ca yAdavaH . vajro rAjA tvayA rakSyo mA cAdharme manaH kRthAH .
ityuktvA dharmarAjaH sa vAsudevasya dhImataH . mAtulasya ca vRddhasya rAmAdInAM tathaiva ca . bhrAtRbhiH saha dharmAtmA kRtvodakamatandritaH zrAddhAnyuddizya sarveSAM cakAra vidhivat tadA .
dvaipAyanaM nAradaM ca mArkaNDeyaM tapodhanam . bhAradvAjaM yAjJavalkyaM harimuddizya yatnavAn .
abhojayat svAdu bhojyaM kIrtayitvA ca zAGgiNam . dadau ratnAni vAsAMsi grAmAnazvAn rathAMstathA . striyazca dvijamukhyebhyastadA zatasahasrazaH . kRpamabhyarcya ca gurumatha paurapuraskRtam . ziSyaM parikSitaM tasmai dadau bharatasattamaH . tatastu prakRtIH sarvAH samAnAyya yudhiSThiraH .
sarvamAcaSTa rAjarSizcikIrSitamathAtmanaH . te zrutvaiva vacastasya paurajAnapadA janAH . bhRzamudvignamanamo nAbhyanandanta tadvacaH . naivaM kartavyamiti te tadocustaM janAdhipam .
na ca rAjA tathAkArSIt kAlaparyAyadharmavit . tato ' numAnya dharmAtmA paurajAnapadaM janam .
