susambaddhau tu tau damyau damanAyAbhiniHsRtau . AsInamuSTraM madhyena sahasaivAbhyadhAvatAm . tayoH samprAptayoruSTraH skandhadezamamarSaNaH . utthAyokSipya tau damyau prasasAra mahAjavaH .
hriyamANau tu tau damyau tenoSTreNa pramAthinA . niyamANau ca samprekSya maGkistatrAbravIdidam . na caivAvihitaM zakyaM dakSaNApIhituM dhanam . yuktena zraddhayA samyagIhAM samanutiSThatA .
