maNI voSTrasya lambete priyau vatsatarau mama . zuddhaM hi daivmevedaM haThenaivAsti pauruSam .
yadi vApyupapadyeta pauruSaM nAma karhicit anviSyamANaM tadapi daivamevAvatiSThate .
tasmAnirveda eveha gantavyaH sukhamicchatA . sukhaM svapiti nirviNNo nirAzazcArthasAdhane .
aho samyak zukenoktaM sarvataH parimucyatA . pratiSThatA mahAraNyaM janakasya nivezanAt .
yaH kAmAnApnuyAt sarvAn yazcaitAn kevalAMstyajet . prApaNAt sarvakAmAnAM parityAgo viziSyate .
nAntaM sarvavidhitsAnAM gatapUrvo ' sti kazcana . zarIre jIvite caiva tRSNA mandasya vardhate .
nivartasva vidhitsAbhyaH zAmya nirvidya kAmuka asakRccAsi nikRto na ca nirvidyase tataH .
yadi nAhaM vinAzyaste yadyevaM ramase mayA . mA mAM yojaya lobhena vRthA tvaM vittakAmuka .
saMcitaM saMcitaM dravyaM naSTaM tava punaH punaH . kadAcinmokSyase mUDha dhanehAM dhanakAmuka .
aho na mama bAlizyaM yo ' haM krIDanakastava . kiM naivaM jAtu puruSaH pareSAM preSyatAmiyAt .
na pUrve nApare jAtu kAmAnAmantamApnuvan . tyaktvA sarvasamArambhAn pratibuddho ' smi jAgRmi .
nUnaM te hRdayaM kAma vajrasAramayaM dRDham . yadanarthazatAviSTaM zatadhA na vidIryate .
jAnAmi kAma tvAM caiva yacca kiMcit priyaM tava . tavAhaM priyamanvicchannAtmanyupalabhe sukham .
kAma jAnAmi te mUlaM saMkalpAt kila jAyase . na tvAM saMkalpayiSyAmi samUlo na bhaviSyasi .
IhA dhanasya na sukhaM labdhvA cintA ca bhUyasI . labdhanAze yathA mRtyurlabdhaM bhavati vA na vA .
parityAge na labhate tato duHkhataraM nu kim . na ca tuSyati labdhena bhUya eva ca mArgati .
anutarSula evArthaH svAdu gAGgamivodakam . madvilApanametattu pratibuddho ' smi saMtyaja .
ya imaM mAmakaM dehaM bhUtagrAmaH samAzritaH . sa yAtvito yathAkAmaM vasatAM vA yathAsukham .
na yuSmAsviha me prItiH kAmalobhAnusAriSu . tasmAdutsRjya kAmAn vai sattvamevAzrayAmyaham .
sarvabhUtAnyahaM dehe pazyan manasi cAtmanaH . yoge buddhiM zrute sattvaM mano brahmaNi dhArayan . vihariSyAmyanAsaktaH sukhI lokAn nirAmayaH . yayA mAM tvaM puna : vaM duHkheSu praNidhAsyasi .
tvayA hi me praNunnasya gatiranyA na vidyate . tRSNAzokazramANAM hi tvaM kAma prabhavaH sadA .
dhananAze ' dhikaM duHkhaM manye sarvamahattaram . jJAtayo hyavamanyante mitrANi ca dhanAccyutam .
avajJAnasahaustu doSAH kaSTatarA ' dhane . dhane sukhakalA yA tu sApi duHkhairvidhIyate .
dhanamasyeti puruSaM puro nimanti dasyavaH . klizyanti vividhairdaNDainityamudvejayanti ca .
arthalolupatA duHkhamiti buddhaM cirAnmayA . yad yadAlambase kAma tattadevAnurudhyase . . atattvajJo ' si bAlazca dustoSo ' pUraNo ' nalaH .
naiva tvaM vettha sulabhaM naiva tvaM vettha durlabham . pAtAla iva duSpUro mAM duHkhairyoktumicchasi . nAhamadya samAveSTuM zakyaH kAma punastvayA .
nirvedamahamAsAdya dravyanAzAd yadRcchayA . nirvRttiM paramAM prApya nAdya kAmAn vicintaye .
atiklezAn sahAmIha nAhaM buddhyAmbuddhimAn . nikRto dhananAzena zaya sarvAGgavijvaraH .
parityajAmi kAma tvA hitvA sarvamanogatI : . na tvaM mayA punaH kAma vatsyase na ca raMsyase .
kSamiSye kSipamANAnAM na hisiSye vihiMsitaH . dveSyayuktaH priyaM vakSyAsamyanAdRtya tadapriyam .
tRptaH svasthendriyo nityaM yathAlabdhena vartayan . na sakAmaM kariSyAmi tvAmahaM zatrumAtmanaH . nirvedaM nirvRtiM tRptiM zAnti satyaM damaM kSamAm . sarvabhUtadayAM caiva viddhi mAM samupAgatam .
tasmAt kAmazca lobhazca tRSNA kArpaNyameva ca . tyajantu mAM pratiSThantaM sattvastho hyasmi sAmpratam .
prahAya kAmaM lobhaM ca sukhaM prApto ' smi sAmpratam . nAdya lobhavazaM prApto duHkhaM prApsyAmyanAtmavAn .
