dhRtarASTra puraskRtya gAndhArI ca yazasvinIm . mAtaraM ca pRthAM dhImAn bhrAtR/zca puruSarSabhAn . janArdanenAnugato vidureNa ca dhImatA . yuyutsunA ca kauravyo yuyudhAnena vA vibho . mahatA rAjabhogena pAribaheNa saMvRtaH . stUyamAno mahAtejA bhISmasyAgnAnanuvrajan .
nizcakAma purAt tasmAd yathA devapatistathA . AsasAda kurukSetra tataH zAntanavaM nRpaH .
upAsyamAnaM vyAsena pArAzaryeNa dhImatA . nAradena ca rAjarSe devalenAsitena ya . hataziSTairnRpaizcAnyairnAnAdezasamAgataH . rakSibhizca mahAtmAnaM rakSyamANaM samantataH . zayAnaM vIrazayane dadarza nRpatistataH . tato rathAdavAtIrya bhrAtRbhiH saha dharmarAT . abhavAdyAtha kaunteyaH pitAmahamariMdama . dvaipAyanAdIn viprAMzca taizca pratyabhinanditaH .
Rtvigbhirbrahmakalpaizca bhrAtRbhiH saha dharmajaH . AsAdya zaratalpasthamRSibhiH parivAritam .
abravId bharatazreSThaM dharmarAjo yudhiSThiraH . bhrAtRbhiH saha kauravyaH zayAnaM nimnagAsutam . yudhiSThiro ' haM nRpate namaste jAhnavIsuta . zRNoSi cenmahAbAho brUhi kiM karavANi te .
prApto ' smi samaye rAjannagnInAdAya te vibho . AcAryAn brAhmaNAMzcaiva Rtvijo bhrAtarazca me . putrazva te mahAtejA dhRtarASTro janezvaraH . upasthitaH sahAmAtyo vAsudevazva vIryavAn .
hataziSTAzva rAjAnaH sarvaM ca kurujAMgalAH . tAn pazya narazArdUla samunmIlaya locane .
yacceha kiMcit kartavye tatsarvaM prApitaM mayA . yathoktaM bhavatA kAle sarvameva ca tat kRtam .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktastu gAGgeyaH kuntIputreNa dhImatA . dadarza bhAratAn sarvAn sthitAn samparivArya ha .
tatazva taM balI bhISmaH pragRhma vipulaM bhujam . udyanmeghasvaro vAgmI kAle vacanamabravIt .
diSTyA prApto ' si kaunteya sahAmAtyo yudhiSThira . parivRtto hi bhagavAn sahasrAMzurdivAkaraH .
aSTapaJcAzataM rAjyaH zayAnasyAdya me gatAH . zareSu nizitAgreSu yathA varSazata tathA .
mAgho ' yaM samanuprApto mAsaH saumyo yudhiSThira . tribhAgazeSaH pakSo ' yaM zuklo bhavitumarhati .
evamuktvA tu gAGgeyo dharmaputraM yudhiSThiram . dhRtarASTramathAmanJya kAle vacanamabravIt .
bhISma uvAca rAjan viditadharmo ' si sunirNItArthasaMzayaH . bahuzrutA hi te viprA bahavaH paryupAsitAH .
vedazAsrANi sarvANi dharmozca manujezvara . vedAMzca caturaH sarvAn nikhilenAnubuddhyase .
na zocitavyaM kauravya bhavitavyaM hi tat tathA . zrutaM devarahasyaM te kRSNadvaipAyanAdapi .
yathA pANDoH sutA rAjaMstathaiva tava dharmataH . tAn pAlaya sthito dharme guruzuzrUSaNe ratAn .
dharmarAjo hi zuddhAtmA nideze sthAsyate tava . AnRzaMsyaparaM hyenaM jAnAmi guruvatsalam .
taba putrA durAtmAnaH krodhalobhaparAyaNAH . IrSyAbhibhUtA durvRttAstAn na zocitumarhasi .
vaizampAyana uvAca etAvaduktvA vacanaM dhRtarASTra manISiNam . vAsudevaM mahAbAhumabhyabhASata kauravaH .
bhISma uvAca bhagavan devadeveza surAsuranamaskRta . trivikrama namastubhyaM zaGkhacakragadAdhara .
vAsudevo hiraNyAtmA puruSaH savitA virAT . jIvabhUto ' nurUpastvaM paramAtmA sanAtana .
trAyasva puNDarIkAkSa puruSottama nityazaH . anujAnIhi mAM kRSNa vaikuNTha puruSottama . rakSyAzca te pANDaveyA bhavAn yeSAM parAyaNam .
uktavAnasmi durbuddhiM mandaM duryodhanaM tadA . yataH kRSNastato dharmo yato dharmastato jayaH .
vAsudevena tIrthena putra saMzAmya pANDavaiH . saMdhAnasya paraH kAlastaveti ca punaH punaH .
na ca me tad vaco mUDhaH kRtavAn sa sumandadhIH . ghAtayitveha pRthivIM tataH sa nidhanaM gataH .
tvAM tu jAnAmyahaM devaM purANamRSisattamam . nareNa sahitaM deva vadaryAM suciroSitam .
tathA me nAradaH prAha vyAsazca sumahAtapAH . naranArAyaNAvetau sambhUtau manujeSviti .
sa mAM tvamanujAnIhi kRSNa mokSye kalevaram . tvayAha samanujJAto gaccheyaM paramAM gatim .
vAsudeva uvAca anujJAnAmi bhISma tvAM vasUn prApnuhi pArthiva . na te ' sti vRjinaM kiMcidihaloke mahAdyute .
pitRbhakto ' si rAjarSe mArkaNDeya ivAparaH . tena mRtyustava vaze sthito bhRtya ivAnataH .
vaizampAyana uvAca evamuktastu gAGgeyaH pANDavAnidamabravIt . dhRtarASTramukhAMzcapi sarvozca suhRdastathA .
prANAnutsraSTumicchAmi tatrAnujJAtumarhatha . satyeSu yatitavyaM vaH satyaM hi paramaM balam .
AnRzaMsyaparairbhAvyaM sadaiva niyatAtmabhiH . brahmaNyairdharmazIlaizca taponityaizca bhAratAH .
ityuktvA suhRdaH sarvAn sampariSvajya caiva hA punarevAbravId dhImAn yudhiSThiramidaM vacaH . brAhmaNAzcaiva te nityaM prAjJAzcaiva vizeSataH . AcAryA Rtvijazcaiva pUjanIyA janAdhipa .
yudhiSThira uvAca kimAhurdaivataM viprA rAjAnaM bharatarSabha . manuSyANAmadhipatiM tanme brUhi pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . bRhaspatiM vasumanA yathA papraccha bhArata . .
rAjA vasumanA nAma kausalyo dhImatAM varaH . maharSi kila papraccha kRtaprajJaM bRhaspatim .
sarvaM vainayikaM kRtvA vinayajJo bRhaspatim . dakSiNAnantaro bhUtvA praNamya vidhipUrvakam . vidhiM papraccha rAjyasya sarvalokahite rataH . prajAnAM sukhamanvicchan dharmazIlaM bRhaspatim .
vasumanA uvAca kena bhUtAni vardhante kSayaM gacchanti kena vA . kamarcanto mahAprAjJa sukhamavyayamApnuyuH . evaM pRSTo mahAprAjJaH kausalyenAmitaujasA . rAjasatkAramavyagraM zazaMsAsmai bRhaspatiH .
bRhaspatiruvAca rAjamUlo mahAprAjJa dharmo lokasya lakSyate . prajA rAjabhayAdeva na khAdanti parasparam .
rAjA hyevAkhilaM lokaM samudIrNaM samutsukam . prasAdayati dharmeNa prasAdya ca virAjate .
yathA hyanudaye rAjan bhUtAni zazisUryayoH . andhe tamasi majjeyurapazyantaH parasparam . yathA hyanudake matsyA nirAkrande vihaGgamAH . vihareyuryathAkAmaM vihiMsantaH punaH punaH . vimathyAtikrameraMzca viSahyApi parasparam . abhAvamacireNaiva gaccheyurnAtra saMzayaH . evameva vinA rAjJA vinazyeyurimAH prajAH . andhe tamasi majjeyuragopAH pazavo yathA .
hareyurbalavanto ' pi durbalAnAM parigrahAn hanyukyacchamAnAMzca yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
mamedamiti loke ' smin na bhavet samparigrahaH . na dArA na ca putraH syAnna dhenaM na parigrahaH .
viSvaglopaH pravarteta yadi rAjA na pAlayet . mamedamiti loke ' smin na bhavet samparigrahaH . yAnaM vastramalaGkArAn ratnAni vividhAni ca .
hareyuH sahasA pApA yadi rAjA na pAlayet . pated bahuvidhaM zastraM bahudhA dharmacAriSu .
adharmaH pragRhItaH syAd yadi rAjA na pAlayet . mAtaraM pitaraM vRddhamAcAryamatithiM gurum .
kli znIyurapi hiMsyurvA yadi rAjA na pAlayet . vadhabandhapiraklezo nityamarthavatAM bhavet .
mamatvaM ca na vindeyuryadi rAjA na pAlayet . antAzcAkAla eva syurloko ' yaM dasyusAd bhavet .
pateyurnarakaM ghoraM yadi rAjA na pAlayet . na yonidoSo varteta na kRSirna vaNikpathaH . majjed dharmastrayI na syAd yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
na yajJAH sampravarteyurvidhivat svAptadakSiNAH . na vivAhAH samAjo vA yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
na vRSA : sampravarteran na madhyeraMzca gargarAH . ghoSAH praNAzaM gaccheyuryadi rAjA na pAlayet .
trastamudvignahRdayaM hAhAbhUtamacetanam . kSaNena vinazet sarvaM yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
na saMvatsarasatrANi tiSTheyurakutobhayAH . vidhivad dakSiNAvanti yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
brAhmaNAzcaturo vedAn nAdhIyoraMstapasvinaH . vidyAsnAtA vratasnAtA yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
na labhed dharmasaMzleSaM hataviprahato janaH . hartA svasthendriyo gacched yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
hastAddhastaM parimuSed bhidyeran sarvasetavaH . bhayArta vidravet sarvaM yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
anayAH sampravarteran bhaved vai varNasaMkaraH . durbhikSamAvized rASTraM yadi rAjA na pAlayet .
vivRtya hi yathAkAmaM gRhadvArANi zerate . manuSyA rakSitA rAjJA samantAdakutobhayAH . .
nAkruSTaM sahate kazcit kuto vA hastalAghavam . yadi rAjA na samyag gAM rakSayatyapi dhArmikaH .
striyazcapuruSA mArga sarvAlaGkArabhUSitAH . nirbhayAH pratipadyante yadi rakSati bhUmipaH .
dharmameva prapadyante na hiMsanti parasparam . anugRhNanti cAnyonyaM yadA rakSati bhUmipaH .
yajante ca mahAyajJaistrayo varNAH pRthagvidhaiH . yuktAzcAdhIyate vidyAM yadA rakSati bhUmipaH .
vArtAmUlo hyayaM lokastrayyA vai dhArya te sadA . tat sarvaM vartate samyag yadA rakSati bhUmipaH .
yadA rAjA dhuraM zreSThAmAdAya vahati prajAH . mahatA balayogena tadA lokaH prasIdati .
yasyAbhAvena bhUtAnAmabhAvaH syAt samantataH . bhAve ca bhAvo nityaM syAt kastaM na pratipUjayet .
tasya yo vahate bhAraM sarvalokabhayAvaham . tiSThan priyahite rAjJa ubhau lokAvimau jayet .
yastasya puruSaH pApaM manasApyanucintayet . asaMzayamiha kliSTaH pretyApi narakaM vrajet .
na hi jAtvavamantavyo manuSya iti bhUmipaH . mahatI devatA hyeSA nararUpeNa tiSThati .
kurute paJcarUpANi kAlayuktAni yaH sadA . bhavatyagnistathA ' ' dityo mRtyurvaizravaNo yamaH .
yadA hyAsIdata : pApAn dahatyugreNa tejasA . mithyopacarito rAjA tadA bhavati pAvakaH .
yadA pazyati cAreNa sarvabhUtAni bhUmipaH . kSemaM ca kRtvA vrajati tadA bhavati bhAskaraH .
azucIzca yadA kruddhaH kSiNoti zatazo narAn . saputrapautrAn sAmAtyAMstadA bhavati so ' ntakaH .
yadA tvadhArmikAn sarvAMstIkSNairdaNDainiyacchati . dhArmikAMzcAnugRhNAti bhavatyatha yamastadA .
yadA tu dhanadhArAbhistarpayatyupakAriNaH . Acchinatti na ratnAni vividhAnyapakAriNAm . zriyaM dadAti kasmaicit kasmAccidapakarSati . tadA vaizravaNo rAjA loke bhavati bhUmipaH .
nAsyApavAde sthAtavyaM dakSeNAklizkarmaNA . dharmyamAkAGkSatA lokamIzvarasyAnasUyatA . na hi rAjJaH pratIpAni kurvan sukhamavApnuyAt . putro bhrAtA vayasyo vA yadyapyAtmasamo bhavet .
kuryAt kRSNagatiH : zeSaM jvalito ' nilasArathiH . na tu rAjAbhipannasya zeSaM kvacana vidyate .
tasya sarvANi rakSyANi dUrataH parivarjayet . mRtyoriva jugupseta rAjasvaharaNAnnaraH .
nazyedabhimRzan sadyo mRgaH kUTamiva spRzan . Atmasvamiva rakSeta rAjasvamiha buddhimAn .
mahAntaM narakaM ghoramapratiSThamacetanam . patanti cirarAtrAya rAjavittApahAriNaH .
rAjA bhojo virAT samrATa kSatriyo bhUpatirnRpaH . ya ebhiH stUyate zabdaiH kastaM nArcitumarhati .
tasmAd bubhUSurniyato jitAtmA niyatendriyaH . medhAvI smRtimAn dakSaH saMzrayeta mahIpatim .
kRtajJaM prAjJamakSudraM dRDhabhaktiM jitendriyam . dharmanityaM sthitaM nItyaM mantriNaM pUjayennRpaH .
dRDhabhaktiM kRtaprajJaM dharmajJaM saMyatendriyam . zUramakSudrakarmANaM niSiddhajanamAzrayet .
rAjA pragalbhaM kurute manuSyaM rAjA kRzaM vai kurute manuSyam . rAjAbhipannasya kutaH sukhAni rAjAbhyupetaM sukhinaM karoti .
rAjA prajAnAM hRdayaM garIye gatiH pratiSThA sukhamuttamaM ca . samAzritA lokamimaM paraM ca jayanti samyak puruSA narendra .
narAdhipazcApyanuziSya medinI damena satyena ca sauhRdena . mahadbhiriSTvA kratubhirmahAyarzA striviSTape sthAnamupaiti zAzvatam .
sa evamukto ' GgirasA kausalyo rAjasattamaH . prayatnAt kRtavAn vIraH prajAnAM paripAlanam .
yudhiSThira uvAca dhaninazcAdhanA ye ca vartayante svatantraNaH . sukhaduHkhAgamasteSAM kaH kathaM vA pitAmaha .
bhISma uvAca atrApyudAharantImamitihAsaM purAtanam . zampAkeneha muktena gItaM zAntigatena ca .
abravInmAM purA kazcid brAhmaNastyAgamAzritaH . klizyamAnaH kudAreNa kucailena bubhukSayA . .
utpannamiha loke vai janmaprabhRti mAnavam . vividhAmanyupavartante duHkhAni ca sukhAni ca . .
tayorekatare mArge yadenamabhisannayet . na sukhaM prApya saMhaSyennAsukhaM prApya saMjvaret .
na vai carasi yacchreya Atmano vA yadIziSe . akAmAtmApi hi sadA dhuramudyamya caiva ha .
akiMcanaH paripatan sukhamAsvAdayiSyasi . akiMcanaH sukhaM zete samuttiSThati caiva ha .
AkiMcanyaM sukhaM loke pathyaM zivamanAmayam . anamitrapatho hyeSa durlabhaH sulabho mataH .
akiMcanasya zuddhasya upapannasya sarvataH . avekSamANastrIllokAn na tulyamiha lakSaye .
AkiMcanyaM ca rAjyaM ca tulayA samatolayam . atyaricyata dAriyaM rAjyAdapi guNAdhikam .
AkiMcanye ca rAjye ca vizeSaH sumahAnayam . nityodvigno hi dhanavAn mRtyorAsyagato yathA .
naivasyAgnirna cAriSTo na mRtyunaM ca dasyavaH . prabhavanti dhanatyAgAd vimuktasya nirAziSaH .
taM vai sadA kAmacaramanupastIrNazAyinam . bAhUpadhAnaM zAmyantaM prazaMsanti divaukasaH .
dhanavAn krodhalobhAbhyAmAviSTo naSTacetanaH . tiryagIkSaH zuSkamukhaH pApako bhRkuTImukhaH .
nirdazanadharoSThaM ca kruddho dAruNabhASitA . kastamicchet paridraSTuM dAtumicchati cenmahIm .
zriyA hyabhIkSNaM saMvAso mohayatyavicakSaNam . sA tasya cittaM harati zAradAbhramivAnilaH . athainaM rUpamAnazca dhanamAnazca vindati .
abhijAto ' smi siddho ' smi nAsmi kevalamAnuSaH . ityebhiH kAraNaistasya tribhizcittaM pramAdyati .
samprasaktamanA bhogAn visRjya pitRsaMcitAn . parikSINaH parasvAnAmAdAnaM sAdhu manyate .
tamatikrAntamaryAdamAdadAnaM tatastataH . pratiSedhanti rAjAno lubdhA mRgAmiveSubhiH .
evametAni duHkhAni tAni tAnIha mAnavam . vividhAnyupapadyante gAtrasaMsparzajAnyapi .
teSAM paramaduH : khAnAM buddhyA bhaiSajyamAcaret . lokadharmamavajJAya dhruNAvAmadhruvaiH saha .
nAtyaktvA sukhamApnoti nAtyaktvA vindate param . nAtyaktvA cAbhayaH zete tyaktvA sarvaM sukhI bhava .
ityeddhAstinapure brAhmaNenopavarNitam . zampAkena purA mahyaM tasmAt tyAgaH paro mataH .
saMjaya uvAca tataH sa sAtyakirthImAn mahAtmAvRSNipuGgavaH . sudarzanaM nihatyAjau yantAraM punarabravIt .
rathAzvanAgakalilaM zarazaktyUmimAlinam . khaGgamatsyaM gadAgrAhaM zUrAyudhamahAsvanam . prANApahAriNaM raudraM vAdivotkruSTanAditam . yodhAnAmasukhasparze durdharSamajayaiSiNAm . tIrNAH sma dustaraM tAta droNAnIkamahArNavam . jalasaMdhabalenAjau puruSAdairivAvRtam . ato ' nyat pRtanAzeSaM manye kunadikAmiva . tartavyAmalpasalilAM codayAzvAnasambhramam .
hastaprAptamahaM manye sAmprataM savyasAcinam . nirjitya durgharaM droNaM sapadAnugamAhave .
hArdikyaM yodhavarye ca manye prAptaM dhanaMjayam . na hi me jAyate trAso dRSTvA sainyAnyanekazaH .
vaDheriva pradIptasya vane zuSkatRNolape . pazya pANDavamukhyena yAtAM bhUmi kirITinA .
pattyazvarathanAgaughaiH patitairviSamIkRtAm . dravate tad yathA sainyaM tena bhagnaM mahAtmanA .
rathaiviparidhAvadbhirgajairazcaizca sArathe . kauzeyAruNasaMkAzametadudbhUyate rajaH .
abhyAzasthamahaM manye zvetAzvaM kRSNAsArathim . sa eSa zrUyate zabdo gANDIvasyAmitaujasaH .
yAdRzAni nimittAni mama prAdurbhavanti vai . anastaMgata Aditye hantA saindhavamarjunaH .
zanairvizrambhayannazvAn yAhi yatrArivAhinI . yaute satalatrANAH suyodhanapurogamAH .
daMzitAH krUrakarmANaH kAmbojA yuddhadurmadAH . zarabANAsanadharA yavanAzca prahAriNaH .
zakAH kirAtA daradA barbarAstAmraliptakAH . anye ca bahavo mlecchA vividhAyudhapAmayaH .
yaute satalatrANAH suyodhanapurogamAH . mAmevAbhimukhAH sarve tiSThanti samarArthinaH .
etAn sarathanAgAzvAn nihatyAjau sapattinaH . idaM durge mahAghoraM tIrNamevopadhAraya .
sUta uvAca na sambhramo me vArSNeya vidyate satyavikrama . yadyapi syAt tava kruddho jAmadagnyo ' grataH sthitaH .
droNo vA rathinAM zreSThaH kRpo madrezvaro ' pi vA . tathApi sambhramo na syAt tvAmAzritya mahAbhuja .
tvayA subahavo yuddhe nirjitAH zatrusUdana . daMzitAH krUrakarmANaH kAmbojA yuddhadurmadAH .
zarabANAsanadharA yavanAzca prahAriNaH . zakAH kirAtA daradA barbarAstAmraliptakAH .
anye ca bahavo mlecchA vividhAyudhapANayaH . na ca me sambhramaH kazcid bhUtapUrvaH kathaMcana .
kimutaitat samAsAdya dhIrasaMyugagoSpadam . AyuSman katareNa tvAM prApayAmi dhanaMjayam .
keSAM kruddho ' si vArSNeya keSAM mRtyurupasthitaH . keSAM saMyamanImadya gantumutsahate manaH .
ke tvAM yudhi parAkrAntaM kAlAntakayamopamam . dRSTvA vikramasampannaM vidraviSyanti saMyuge . keSAM vaivasvato rAjA smarate ' dya mahAbhuja .
sAtyakiruvAca muNDAnetAn haniSyAmi dAnavAniva vAsavaH . pratijJA pArayiSyAni kAmbojAneva mAM vaha .
adyaiSAM kadanaM kRtvA priyaM yAsyAmi pANDavam . adya drakSyanti me vIrye kauravAH sasuyodhanAH .
muNDAnIke hate sUta sarvasainyeSu cAsakRt . adya kauravasainyasya dIryamANasya saMyuge . zrutvA virAvaM bahudhA saMtapsyati suyodhanaH . adya pANDavamukhyasya zvetAzvasya mahAtmanaH . AcAryasya kRtaM mArge darzayiSyAmi saMyuge . adya mANanihatAn yodhamukhyAn sahasrazaH . dRSTvA duryodhano rAjA pazcAttApaM gamiSyati . adya me kSiprahastasya kSipataH sAyakottamAn . alAtacakrapratimaM dhanurdrakSyanti kauravAH . matsAyakacitAGgAnAM rudhiraM sravatA muhuH . sainikAnAM vadhaM dRSTvA saMtapsyati suyodhanaH .
adya me kruddharUpasya nighnatazca varAn varAn . dvirarjunamimaM lokaM maMsyate ' dya suyodhanaH . adya rAjasahasrANi nihatAni mayA raNe . dRSTvA duryodhano rAjA saMtapsyati mahAmRdhe . adha snehaM ca bhaktiM ca pANDaveSu mahAtmasu . hattvA rAjasahasrANi darzayiSyAmi rAjasu . valaM vIrye ka - tajJatvaM mama jJAsyanti kauravAH
saMjaya uvAca evamuktastadA sUta : zikSitAn sAdhuvAhinaH . zazAGkasaMnikAzAn vai vAjino vyanudad bhRzam .
te pivanta ivAkAzaM yuyudhAnaM hayottamAH . prApayan yavanAzIghraM mana : pavanaraMhasaH .
tyAMka te samAsAdya pRtanAsvanivartinam . vahavo laghuhastAzca zaravadhairavAkiran .
teSAmiSUnathAstrANi vegavAn nataparvabhiH . acchinat sAtyakI rAjan nainaM te prApnuva - zarAH .
rukmaputraiH sunizitairgApatrairajihmagaiH . ucakarta zirAMsyugro yavanAnAM bhujAnapi .
saikyAyasAni varmANi kAMsyAni ca samantataH . bhittvA dehAMstathA teSAM zarA jagmurmahItalam .
tehanyamAnA vIreNamlecchAH sAtyakinA raNe . zatazo ' bhyapataMstatra vyasavo basudhAtale .
